reference: Macedonian President Gjorge Ivanov, an opponent of the plebiscite on the name change, has said he will disregard the vote.
translation: Umengameli wezwe laseMacedonia u-Gjorge Ivanov omelene nokushintshwa kwegama uthe lelivoti uzolishaya indiva.

source: Kodwa, abahambisana nokushintshwa kwegama sibala uNdunankulu u-Zoran Zaev lokhu bakubona njengento okumele yenziwe ukuze babe ngamalungu e-EU ne-NATO.
reference: However, supporters of the referendum, including Prime Minister Zoran Zaev, argue that the name change is simply the price to pay to join the EU and NATO.
translation: Kodwa, abahambisana nokushintshwa kwegama sibala uNdunankulu u-Zoran Zaev lokhu bakubona njengento okumele yenziwe ukuze babe ngamalungu e-EU ne-NATO.

source: Iyihlabe inhlali iBells of st martins ngobunzima obubhekene namabandla ase Harlem.
reference: The Bells of St. Martin's Fall Silent as Churches in Harlem Struggle
translation: Iyihlabe inhlali iBells of st martins ngobunzima obubhekene namabandla ase Harlem.

source: ‚ÄúNgokomlando, abantu abadala engifakane nabo umlomo bathi kwakunesonto nendawo yokucima ukoma kuzo zonke izitaladi,‚Äù ebeka uMnu. u-Adams.
reference: Historically, the old people I've talked to say there was a bar and a church on every corner, Mr. Adams said.
translation: Ngokomlando, abantu abadala engifakane nabo umlomo bathi kwakunesonto nendawo yokucima ukoma kuzo zonke izitaladi, ebeka uMnu. u-Adams.

source: ‚ÄúNamuhla, akukho ngisho esokubika‚Äù.
reference: Today, there's neither.
translation: Namuhla, akukho ngisho esokubika.

source: Uthi ukunyamalala kwezindawo zokucima ukoma kuyezwakala.
reference: He said the disappearance of bars was understandable.
translation: Uthi ukunyamalala kwezindawo zokucima ukoma kuyezwakala.

source: ‚ÄúAbantu sebehlanganyela ngezindlela ezihlukene namuhla,‚Äù esho kanje.
reference: People socialize in a different way nowadays, he said.
translation: Abantu sebehlanganyela ngezindlela ezihlukene namuhla, esho kanje.

source: ‚ÄúAmajoyinti akusesizo izindawo lapho kwakuhlanganwa khona imihla ngemihla.‚Äù
reference: Bars are no longer neighborhood living rooms where people go on a regular basis.
translation: Amajoyinti akusesizo izindawo lapho kwakuhlanganwa khona imihla ngemihla.

source: Okwamabandla kuyamkhathaza kakhulu ngoba imali etholwa abaholi ngokudayisa impahla yamabandla ayizukuhlala isikhathi eside bese abantu kufane nokuthi abenzanga lutho.
reference: As for churches, he worries that the money from selling assets will not last as long as leaders expect it to, "and sooner or later they'll be right back where they started."
translation: Okwamabandla kuyamkhathaza kakhulu ngoba imali etholwa abaholi ngokudayisa impahla yamabandla ayizukuhlala isikhathi eside bese abantu kufane nokuthi abenzanga lutho.

source: Uqhube wathi amasonto angaphendulwa izinto zokuhlala ezinabantu abangeke basize ngalutho incosana yamabandla asele.
reference: Churches, he added, could be replaced by apartment buildings with condominiums filled with the kind of people who will not help the neighborhood's remaining sanctuaries.
translation: Uqhube wathi amasonto angaphendulwa izinto zokuhlala ezinabantu abangeke basize ngalutho incosana yamabandla asele.

source: Iningi labantu abathenga amagumbi okuhlala kulamabhilidi abantu abamhlophe‚Äù, uqhube wathi, ‚Äúbazokwenza kusheshe kufike ukuvalwa kwalamabandla ngokusemthethweni ngoba mancane amathuba ukuthi babe ngamalunga alasonto‚Äù.
reference: The overwhelming majority of people who buy condominiums in these buildings will be white, he said, "and therefore will hasten the day that these churches close altogether because it is unlikely that most of these people who move into these condominiums will become members of these churches."
translation: Iningi labantu abathenga amagumbi okuhlala kulamabhilidi abantu abamhlophe", uqhube wathi, "bazokwenza kusheshe kufike ukuvalwa kwalamabandla ngokusemthethweni ngoba mancane amathuba ukuthi babe ngamalunga alasonto".

source: Womabili amasonto akhiwa ngamalunga ebala elimhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe idolobha labantu abamnyama yaba yi Metropolitan Community ngo 1870 yaba yi St Martins emva kweminyaka elishumi.
reference: Both churches were built by white congregations before Harlem became a black metropolis - Metropolitan Community in 1870, St. Martin's a decade later.
translation: Womabili amasonto akhiwa ngamalunga ebala elimhlophe ngaphambi kokuba iHarlem ibe idolobha labantu abamnyama yaba yi Metropolitan Community ngo 1870 yaba yi St Martins emva kweminyaka elishumi.

source: Ibandla lokqala elalinamalunga amhlophe laphuma ngeminyaka yawo-1930.
reference: The original white Methodist congregation moved out in the 1930s.
translation: Ibandla lokqala elalinamalunga amhlophe laphuma ngeminyaka yawo-1930.

source: Ibandla elinamalunga amnyama elalikhonzela esakhiweni esiseduze yathatha isakhiwo.
reference: A black congregation that had been worshiping nearby took title to the building.
translation: Ibandla elinamalunga amnyama elalikhonzela esakhiweni esiseduze yathatha isakhiwo.

source: I-St Martins yathathwa ibandla lamalunga amnyama elaiholwa uMfu John Howard Johnson, owahola umbhikisho wokulwisana nabahwebi baku-125th street ababemelene nokuqasha bethuthukise abantu abamnyama.
reference: St. Martin's was taken over by a black congregation under the Rev. John Howard Johnson, who led a boycott of retailers on 125th Street, a main street for shopping in Harlem, who resisted hiring or promoting blacks.
translation: I-St Martins yathathwa ibandla lamalunga amnyama elaiholwa uMfu John Howard Johnson, owahola umbhikisho wokulwisana nabahwebi baku-125th street ababemelene nokuqasha bethuthukise abantu abamnyama.

source: Iqubula lomlilo wango 1939 lashiya indlu yesonto ilimele, kodwa ngenkathi amalunga ebandla lika Mfu Johnson enza amalungiselo okwakha kabusha baqalisa nangokwkha icarillon.
reference: A fire in 1939 left the building badly damaged, but as Father Johnson's parishioners made plans to rebuild, they commissioned the carillon.
translation: Iqubula lomlilo wango 1939 lashiya indlu yesonto ilimele, kodwa ngenkathi amalunga ebandla lika Mfu Johnson enza amalungiselo okwakha kabusha baqalisa nangokwkha icarillon.

source: UMfu. U-David Johnson oyindodana aphinde kube nguye olandela uMfu. uJohnsosn wayibiza ngensimbi yabantu abampofu.
reference: The Rev. David Johnson, Father Johnson's son and successor at St. Martin's, proudly called the carillon "the poor people's bells."
translation: UMfu. U-David Johnson oyindodana aphinde kube nguye olandela uMfu. uJohnsosn wayibiza ngensimbi yabantu abampofu.

source: Ungoti owayedlala lezinsimbi ngoJulayi wathi: ‚ÄúIgugu lesintu‚Äù kanti ‚Äúiwuphawu lomlando ongesuswe‚Äù.
reference: The expert who played the carillon in July called it something else: "A cultural treasure" and "an irreplaceable historical instrument."
translation: Ungoti owayedlala lezinsimbi ngoJulayi wathi: "Igugu lesintu" kanti "iwuphawu lomlando ongesuswe".

source: Ungoti wase-University yase-Michigan u-Tiffany Ng wathi kungokokuqala ngqa emhlabeni jikeelele ukuba lensimbi ishaywe ngumculi omnyama u-Dionisio A. Lind, owaqhubekela ukuyodlala eRiverside Church eminyakeni eli18 edlule.
reference: The expert, Tiffany Ng of the University of Michigan, also noted that it was the first carillon in the world to be played by a black musician, Dionisio A. Lind, who moved to the larger carillon at the Riverside Church 18 years ago.
translation: Ungoti wase-University yase-Michigan u-Tiffany Ng wathi kungokokuqala ngqa emhlabeni jikeelele ukuba lensimbi ishaywe ngumculi omnyama u-Dionisio A. Lind, owaqhubekela ukuyodlala eRiverside Church eminyakeni eli18 edlule.

source: Ibandla i-St Martins alisivalanga isikhala sakho kusho uMnu. uMerriweather.
reference: Mr. Merriweather said that St. Martin's did not replace him.
translation: Ibandla i-St Martins alisivalanga isikhala sakho kusho uMnu. uMerriweather.

source: Okwenzeke ezinyangeni ezimbalwa ezedlule e St Martins inzukayikeyi yo makhi nosonkontileka, abanye abalethwe abaholi bebandla abanye belethwe amadikhoni.
reference: What has played out at St. Martin's over the last few months has been a complicated tale of architects and contractors, some brought in by the lay leaders of the church, others by the Episcopal diocese.
translation: Okwenzeke ezinyangeni ezimbalwa ezedlule e St Martins inzukayikeyi yo makhi nosonkontileka, abanye abalethwe abaholi bebandla abanye belethwe amadikhoni.

source: I-vestry okungabaholi bebandla abazimele ibhalele ithimba lamadikhoni ngezikhalo zokuthi bengafuni ukubathwesa izindleko zomakhi nosonkontileka ekubeni bona njenge-vestry bengangeni ekuqashweni kwalabo sonkontileka nomakhi.
reference: The vestry - the parish's governing body, made up of lay leaders - wrote the diocese in July with concerns that the diocese "would seek to pass along the costs" to the vestry, even though the vestry had not been involved in hiring the architects and contractors the diocese sent in.
translation: I-vestry okungabaholi bebandla abazimele ibhalele ithimba lamadikhoni ngezikhalo zokuthi bengafuni ukubathwesa izindleko zomakhi nosonkontileka ekubeni bona njenge-vestry bengangeni ekuqashweni kwalabo sonkontileka nomakhi.

source: Amanye amalunga ebandla akhale ngokungaphumeli obala kwamadikhoni.
reference: Some parishioners complained of a lack of transparency on the diocese's part.
translation: Amanye amalunga ebandla akhale ngokungaphumeli obala kwamadikhoni.

source: Ushaka ulimaze oneminyaka engu-13 ubudala lobster dive e-Carlifornia.
reference: Shark injures 13-year-old on lobster dive in California
translation: Ushaka ulimaze oneminyaka engu-13 ubudala lobster dive e-Carlifornia.

source: Kuthiwa loshaka ulimaze lomfana oneminyaka eli13 ngomgqibelo eyozingela amalobster ecalifornia ngosuku lokuvulela ukuzingelwa kwama lobster.
reference: A shark attacked and injured a 13-year-old boy Saturday while he was diving for lobster in California on the opening day of lobster season, officials said.
translation: Kuthiwa loshaka ulimaze lomfana oneminyaka eli13 ngomgqibelo eyozingela amalobster ecalifornia ngosuku lokuvulela ukuzingelwa kwama lobster.

source: Lesi sehlo senzeke lingakashayi elesi7 ekuseni bude buduze ne Beacon‚Äôs Beach e Encitas.
reference: The attack occurred just before 7 a.m. near Beacon's Beach in Encinitas.
translation: Lesi sehlo senzeke lingakashayi elesi7 ekuseni bude buduze ne Beacon's Beach e Encitas.

source: U-Chad Hammel utshele abakwa KSWB-TV e SanDiego ukuthi kade betshuza nabangani ngomgqibelo ekuseni ngesikhathi ezwa lomfana ememeza efuna usizo, babe sebegwedla baze bafika kuye bamsiza ukumtakula emanzini.
reference: Chad Hammel told KSWB-TV in San Diego he had been diving with friends for about half an hour Saturday morning when he heard the boy screaming for help and then paddled over with a group to help pull him out of the water.
translation: U-Chad Hammel utshele abakwa KSWB-TV e SanDiego ukuthi kade betshuza nabangani ngomgqibelo ekuseni ngesikhathi ezwa lomfana ememeza efuna usizo, baze sebegwedla beze bafika kuye bamsiza ukumtakula emanzini.

source: U-Hammel uqhube wahi ubezitshela ukuthi umfana ujabulele ukubamba lobster kantu uyamemeza ebazisa uselunywe ushaka!
reference: Hammel said at first he thought it was just excitement of catching a lobster, but then he "realized that he was yelling, 'I got bit!
translation: U-Hammel uqhube wahi ubezitshela ukuthi umfana ujabulele ukubamba lobster kantu uyamemeza ebazisa uselunywe ushaka!

source: Ungilumile!
reference: I got bit!'
translation: Ungilumile!

source: Ube lunywe kuvela ithambo‚Äù, kusho Hammel okubone esesondele kumfana.
reference: His whole clavicle was ripped open," Hammel said he noticed once he got to the boy.
translation: Ube lunywe kuvela ithambo", kusho Hammel okubone esesondele kumfana.

source: ‚ÄúNgimemeze wonke umuntu ukuthi aphume emanzini: ‚ÄòKunoshaka phakathi!‚Äù enezezela.
reference: I yelled at everyone to get out of the water: 'There's a shark in the water!' Hammel added.
translation: Ngiyayikhomba yonke imbala ukuthi iphumele emanzini: 'Kunoshaka lapho! ebhekise.

source: Umfanyana uphuthunyiswe ngenophephela emhlane e-Rady Children‚Äôs Hospital e San Diego lapho esesimeni esibucayi khona.
reference: The boy was airlifted to Rady Children's Hospital in San Diego where he is listed in critical condition.
translation: Umdala uphuthunyiswe ngesijima semva e-Rady Children's Hospital eSan Diego lapho esimo esiyingozi.

source: Uhlobo lukashaka ohlasele umfana alwaziwa.
reference: The species of shark responsible for the attack was unknown.
translation: Uhlobo lweshaka elilwa nomfana lungaziwa.

source: Obhekele ezokuphepha u-Capt Larry Giles ekhuluma esithangamini sabezindaba uth ushaka uke wabonakala endaweni emavikini adlule kodwa babona ukuthi akulona uhlobo olunobungozi.
reference: Lifeguard Capt. Larry Giles said at a media briefing that a shark had been spotted in the area a few weeks earlier, but it was determined not to be a dangerous species of shark.
translation: Oyingcondvo yezokuphepha uCapt Larry Giles ekhuluma esithangamini sabezindaba ukuthi ishaka seyibonwa emavikini adlule kodwa bona ukuthi akulona uhlobo olunobungozi.

source: Giles uthe isisulu silimale ngendlela ethusa kakhulu esifubeni.
reference: Giles added the victim sustained traumatic injuries to his upper torso area.
translation: Giles uthe isisulu sichithwe ngendlela enokunakha kakhulu.

source: Abezomthetho bakuvalile ukungena elwandle kusuka ePonto beach e-Casablad kuye kufile Swami e-Ecinitas isikhathi esingamahora angu-48 ukuze baphenye balungisele nezokuphepha.
reference: Officials shut down beach access from Ponto Beach in Casablad to Swami's in Ecinitas for 48 hours for investigation and safety purposes.
translation: Abezomthetho bavale ukungena elwandle kusuka ePonto beach eCasablad kuze kufile Swami eEcinitas isikhathi esingamahora angu-48 ukuze baphenywe balunge nezokuphepha.

source: Giles ukubalulile ukuthi kunezinhlobo ezingaphezu kuka-135 zoshaka kulendawo kodwa iningi alihlonzwa njengabanobungozi.
reference: Giles noted that there are more than 135 shark species in the area, but most are not considered dangerous.
translation: Giles ubalulile ukuthi kunezinhlobo ezingaphezu kuka-135 zeshaka kulendawo kodwa iningi alihlonzwe njengabanobungozi.

source: Izinhlelo ze-Sainsbuty‚Äôs zibafaka kwimakethe yezobuhle yase-UK
reference: Sainsbury's plans push into UK beauty market
translation: Izinhlelo ze-Sainsbury's zifaka kwimakethe yobuhle yaseMelika.

source: I-Sainsbury izobangisana ne-Bots, Superdrug ne Debenhams ngezitolo zayo ezihlukeniseke ngemikhakha yobuhle nabasizi abaqeqeshekile.
reference: Sainsbury's is taking on Boots, Superdrug and Debenhams with department store-style beauty aisles staffed with specialist assistants.
translation: I-Sainsbury izocinisana ne-Bots, Superdrug ne Debenhams ngezitolo zayo ezahlukene ngobuhle nabasizi abaqeqeshekile.

source: Njengengxenye yemizamo yabo yokuzama ukungena kwimakethe yezobuhle elingansiselwa ku-2.8bn, engenye yezimakethe ezikhula kakhulu ekubeni kubukeka eyemfashini nezinto zasendlini ibukeka ihlehlela emuva. Amaphasiji amakhulu ezitolo azoqala ngqa ezitolo ezingu-11 ezweni lonke bese edluliselwa ezweni lonke uma kube yimpumelelo.
reference: As part of a substantial push into the UK's ¬£2.8bn beauty market, which is continuing to grow while fashion and homeware sales fall back, the larger beauty aisles will be tested out in 11 stores around the country and taken to more stores next year if it proves a success.
translation: Njengenxenye yokuzama ukungena kwimakethe yobuhle elihamba ku-2.8bn, enye yezimakethe ezikhula kakhulu ekubeni kubukeka yimfashini nezinto zasendlini ibukeka ihluleka. Amaphaseji amakhulu ezitolo azoqala ezitolo ezingu-11 ezweni lonke bese edluliselwa ezweni lonke uma kube yimpumelelo.

source: Ukuxhaswa kwezimali kwezobuhle kuza emva kokuba amasuphamakethe efuna izindlela zokusebenzisa izikhala ezivulwe ukwehla kokudayiswa kwezinto zasendlini.
reference: The investment in beauty comes as supermarkets hunt for ways to use up shelf space once sued for TVs, microwaves and homeware.
translation: Ukuxhaswa kwezimali zokubhala kuza emva kokuba amasuphamakethe efuna izindlela zokusebenzisa izikhala ezivulwe ukwehla kokudayiswa kwezinto zasendlini.

source: I-Sainsbury ithi izophindaphinda imikhiqizo yabo ukufika ku-3000 ifake imikhiqizom yako-Revlon Essie Tweezerman noDkt. U-PawPaw okokuqala ngqa.
reference: Sainsbury's said it would be doubling the size of its beauty offering to up to 3,000 products, including brands such as Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman and Dr. PawPaw for the first time.
translation: I-Sainsbury ithi izobalwa imikhiqizo yabo ukuya ku-3000 ifake imikhiqizo ka-Revlon Essie Tweezerman noDkt. U-PawPaw okokuqala.

source: Imikhiqizo ebivele ikhona yako Lorela Maybelline no Burt‚Äôs bees izothola isikhala esithe xaxa nezindawo ezinezikhangiso zabo ngokukhethekile.
reference: Existing ranges from L'Oreal, Maybelline and Burt's Bees will also get more space with branded areas similar to those found in shops like Boots.
translation: Imikhiqizo ebivele ikhona ka-Lorela Maybelline no Burt's bees izothola isikhala esithe xaxa nezindawo ezinezikhangiso zabo ngokukhethekile.

source: Le supamakethe izophinde ikhiphe kabusha ezokuziphaqula ubuso ukuze iningi nlemikhiqizo yabo ibe nokuyizitshalo nezithelo kuphela njengoba iningi labathengi abancane befuna loko.
reference: The supermarket is also relaunching its Boutique makeup range so that the majority of products are vegan-friendly - something increasingly demanded by younger shoppers.
translation: Le supamakethe izophinde ikhiphe kabusha izinto zokuziphaqula ubuso ukuze iningi lemikhiqizo yabo ibe nokuyizitshalo nezithelo kuphela njengoba iningi labathengi abancane befuna loko.

source: Ngaphezulu, umdayisi weziqholo Fragrance shop uzozwa amanzi ngobhoko ezitolo ezili2 zakwa sainsbury‚Äôs kwesokuqala esivule eCroydon ningizimu ne london evikini eledlule kanti esesibili sovula eSolly Oak e Birmingham ngasemaphetheleni inyaka.
reference: In addition, perfume retailer the Fragrance Shop will be testing out concessions in two Sainsbury's stores, the first of which opened in Croydon, south London, last week while a second opens in Selly Oak, Birmingham, later this year.
translation: Ngaphezulu, umdayisi weziqholo Fragrance shop uzozwa amanzi ngobhoko ezitolo ezili-2 zakwa-Sainsbury's kwesokuqala esivule eCroydon naseNingizimu ne-London evikini eledlule kanti esibili sovula eSolly Oak eBirmingham ngasemaphetheleni inyaka.

source: Ukuthenga ngobuchwepheshe kanye nokuthenga kancane ezitolo eziseduze yikona osekubangele amasupamakethe enze okukhulu ukuheha abathengi.
reference: Online shopping and a shift towards buying small amounts of food daily at local convenience stores means supermarkets are having to do more to persuade people to visit.
translation: Ukuthenga ngobuchwepheshe kanye nokuthenga kancane ezitolo eziseduze yikona osekubangele amasupamakethe enze okukhulu ukuheha abathengi.

source: U-Mike Coupe usihlalo we Sainsbury uthe ngokuyinhloko bazobheka ngokuqhubekayo umnyango wezitolo ezingamasupamakethe ukuze bazame ukulwisana nabehlisi bamanani u-Aldi no-Lidl namasevisi engeziwe nezinto ezingekhona ukudla.
reference: Mike Coupe, the chief executive of Sainsbury's, has said the outlets will look increasingly like department stores as the supermarket chain tries to fight back against the discounters Aldi and Lidl with more services and non-food.
translation: U-Mike Coupe usihlalo we-Sainsbury uthe ngokuyinhloko bazobheka ngokuqhubekayo umnyango wezitolo ezingamasupamakethe ukuze bazame ukulwisana nabehlisi bamanani u-Aldi no-Lidl namasevisi engeziwe nezinto ezingekhona ukudla.

source: I-Sainsbury isifake i-Argos kumakhulu ezitolo yafaka ne Habitats eyayithenga eminyakeni emibili eyedlule lokhu osekusize ukukhuphula ukuthengwa kokudla kwabo benza nenzuzo.
reference: Sainsbury's has been putting Argos outlets in hundreds of stores and has also introduced a number of Habitats since it bought both chains two years ago, which it says has bolstered grocery sales and made the acquisitions more profitable.
translation: I-Sainsbury isifake i-Argos kumakhulu ezitolo yafaka ne-Habitats eyayithenga eminyakeni emibili eyedlule lokhu osekusize ukukhuphula ukuthengwa kokudla kwabo benza nenzuzo.

source: Imizamo eyedlule yamasupamakethe yokuvuselela ezobuhle nezekhemisi ayibanga yimpumelelo.
reference: The supermarket's previous attempt to revamp its beauty and pharmacy departments ended in failure.
translation: Imizamo eyedlule yamasupamakethe yokuvuselela ubuhle nezekhemisi ayibanga yimpumelelo.

source: Sainsbury ibuye yazama inhlanganyela neBoots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yama 2000s nayo yafeyila emva kokungaboni ngasolinye ukuthi inzuzo yezekhemisi ozokwabiwa kanjani kumasupamakethe ayo.
reference: Sainsbury's tested a joint venture with Boots in the early 2000s, but the tie-up ended after a row over how to split the revenues from the chemist's stores in its supermarkets.
translation: I-Sainsbury ibuye yazama inhlanganyela ne-Boots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yama-2000s nayo yafeyila emva kokungaboni ngasolinye ukuthi inzuzo yezekhemisi ozokwabiwa kanjani kumasupamakethe ayo.

source: Lendlela yokwenza entsha iza emva kokuba bedayise izitolo zabo ezingu-281 ku-Celesio ongumnikazi we Lloyds pharmacy ngo 125m eminyakeni emithathu edlule.
reference: The new strategy comes after Sainsbury's sold its 281-store pharmacy business to Celesio, the owner of the Lloyds Pharmacy chain, for ¬£125m, three years ago.
translation: Lendlela yokwenza entsha iza emva kokuba bedayise izitolo zabo ezingu-281 ku-Celesio ongumnikazi we-Lloyds pharmacy ngo-125m eminyakeni emithathu edlule.

source: U-Lloyds naye uzosiza ngokufaka ezokuziphaqula zabadla elikapondo ezinjengo-La Roche Posay no-Vichy.
reference: It said Lloyds would play a role in the plan, by adding an extended range of luxury skincare brands including La Roche-Posay and Vichy in four stores.
translation: U-Lloyds naye uzosiza ngokufaka ezokuziphaqula zabadla elikapondo ezinjengabo La Roche Posay no-Vichy.

source: Umqondisi wezokuhweba u-Paul Mills uthe: ‚ÄúSishintshe indlela amaphaseji ethu abukeka ngayo ukujabulisa amakhasimende wethu.
reference: Paul Mills-Hicks, Sainsbury's commercial director, said: "We've transformed the look and feel of our beauty aisles to enhance the environment for our customers.
translation: Umqondisi wezokuhweba u-Paul Mills uthe: "Sishintshe indlela amaphaseji ethu abukeka ngayo ukujabulisa amakhasimende wethu.

source: Saphinde safaka abasizi abaqeqeshekile ngokusezingeni babe seduzane ukucebisa abathengi.
reference: We've also invested in specially trained colleagues who will be on hand to offer advice.
translation: Saphinde safaka abasizi abaqeqeshekile ngokusezingeni babe seduzane ukucebisa abathengi.

source: Imikhiqizo enhlobonhlobo yenzelwe ukumelana nazo zonke izidingo kanti nezindawo zezitolo zethu zisibeka eqhulwini sisho ukuthi manje singena kuwo wonke amakhona okubekela inselele indlela yakudala yokuthenga.‚Äô

source: ‚ÄùSisebenzelana kahle ne-North Korea ‚Äú washo.

translation: Afterwards he passed the ball back to the player, Hazard in the box.

source: U-Hazard uvele wahlula amadefenda wabe eselishaya ngesekwesokunxele ladlula u-Alisson Becker.
reference: Hazard outran the defense and finished into the far post netting with a left footed shot past Liverpool's Alisson Becker.
translation: Hazard beat the defenders and shot with his left foot past Alisson Becker.

source: I-Liverpool ithwale nzima ngenkathi idlalla ne Napoli kwi-Champions League ngolwesithathu e Stadio San e Naples.
reference: Liverpool battles Napoli in the group stage of the Champions League at 3 p.m. on Wednesday at Stadio San Paolo in Naples, Italy.
translation: Liverpool struggled while playing against Napoli in the Champions League on Wednesday at San Paolo Stadium in Naples.

source: I-Chelsea yona ibibhekene ne Videoton kwi UEFA Europa League ngolwesinane e-London.
reference: Chelsea faces Videoton in the UEFA Europa Leaguge at 3 p.m. on Thursday in London.
translation: Chelsea faced Videoton in the UEFA Europa League on Thursday in London.

source: Inani labashonile ngokuzamazama komhlaba linyukuele ku-832 e-Indonesia
reference: Death toll from Indonesia tsunami rises to 832
translation: The number of earthquake deaths rose to 832 in Indonesia.

source: Inani labashonile kulokhu kuzamazama liyanda ngokusho kwabezindaba ekseni ngesonto.
reference: The death toll in Indonesia's earthquake and tsunami has climbed to 832, the country's disaster agency said early Sunday.
translation: The number of earthquake deaths continues to increase according to news reports this weekend.

source: Iningi libambeke ezindlini zawo eziwe ngemaginithudi ka 7.5 ngenkathi kuzamazama ngo-Lwesihlanu okwenze kwaba namagagasi acishe abe u-20 fidi ngobude, kusho usomlomo we-ejensi u-Sutopo Purwo Nugroho kwabezindaba.
reference: Many people were reported trapped in the rubble of buildings brought down in the 7.5 magnitude earthquake which struck Friday and triggered waves as high as 20 feet, agency spokesman Sutopo Purwo Nugroho told a news conference.
translation: Many were trapped in buildings with a magnitude of 7.5 during Friday's earthquake which created landslides about 20 feet wide, said agency spokesperson Sutopo Purwo Nugroho to the media.

source: Idolobha lase Palu,elinabantu abawu-380,000 babe senkingeni ngesikhathi kuwa isakhiwo.
reference: The city of Palu, which has more than 380,000 people, was strewn with debris from collapsed buildings.
translation: The city of Palu, with 380,000 people, was in crisis when buildings collapsed.

source: Amaphoyisa abophe abangu-32 ngokusolwa kokubulala ngemva kokugwazwa okugcine kuholele ekushoneni kowesifazane
reference: Police arrest man, 32, on suspicion of murder after woman is stabbed to death
translation: 32 police officers were arrested on suspicion of murder after an incident that ultimately led to a woman's death.

source: Ukuhlolwa kombulali kuqaliwe ngemva kokutholalakala komzimba wesifazane e-Merseyside ekseni.
reference: A murder investigation has been launched after woman's body was found in Birkenhead, Merseyside this morning.
translation: Investigation of the murderer began after a woman's body was discovered in Merseyside.

source: Lona wesifazane oneminyaka engu-44 ngo 7:55 ekseni enemamanxeba e-Grayson ,kanye nomsolwa oneminyaka engu 32.
reference: The 44-year-old was found at 7.55am with stab wounds on Grayson Mews on John Street, with a 32-year-old man being arrested on suspicion of murder.
translation: Umusetjhana womfazi oneminyaka engu-44 ngo 7:55 ekseni enemamanxeba e-Grayson, kanye nomsolwa oneminyaka engu-32.

source: Amaphpyisa afuna abazwile noma babona ngesikhathi sesenzakalo.
reference: Police have urged people in the area who saw or heard anything to come forward.
translation: Iphoyisa lifuna abantu abazwe noma babona ngesikhathi sesenzakalo.

source: Umseshi u-Brian O‚ÄôHagan uthi: ‚ÄúUphenyo lisesezinyathelweni zokuqala sizosizwa ababonile futhi bezwa esithradini sa-John e-Birkenhead
reference: Detective Inspector Brian O'Hagan said: 'The investigation is in the early stages but I would appeal to anyone who was in the vicinity of John Street in Birkenhead who saw or heard anything suspicious to contact us.
translation: Umseshi u-Brian O'Hagan uthi: "Uphenyo lusesezinyathweni zokuqala sizosiza abantu abazwe futhi bezwa esithradini sa-John e-Birkenhead".

source: Lokhu kungaba noma ubani ,kodwa silibele abashayeli bamatekisi ,okungenzeka babonile base bethwebula izithombe yibona abangaba usuzo kulolu phenyo.
reference: I would also appeal to anyone, particularly taxi drivers, who may have captured anything on dashcam footage to contact us as they may have information which is vital to our investigation.'
translation: Lokhu kungaba noma ubani, kodwa silibele amashayeli etekisi, okungenzeka babonile base bethwebula izithombe yibona abangaba usuzo kulolu phenyo.

source: Okhulumela amaphoyisa uvumile ukuthi bawutholile umzimba endlini yakhe e-Birkenhead.
reference: A police spokesman has confirmed the woman whose body was found is local to Birkenhead and she was found inside a property.
translation: Okhulumela amaphoyisa uvumile ukuthi bawutholile umzimba endlini yakhe e-Birkenhead.

source: Ababazi futhi besondelelne nalona wesifaane baqhamukile namuhla bezobuza imbuzo mayelana nalomshophi.
reference: This afternoon friends who believe they know the woman have arrived at the scene to ask questions about where she was found this morning.
translation: Ababazi futhi besondelelne nalona wesifaane baqhamukile namuhla bezobuza imbuzo mayelana nalomshophi.

source: Uphenyo lusaqhibeka njengiiba amaphoyisa ethe azodlulisela ulwazi ezihlobeni.
reference: Investigations are ongoing as police have said they are in the process of informing the victim's next of kin.
translation: Uphenyo lusaqhubeka njengoba amaphoyisa ethe azodlulisela ulwazi ezihlobeni.

source: Umshayeli wetekisi ohlala e-Grayso Mews ebezama ukubuyela lapho ahlala khina ngesikhathi amaphoyis emazisa ukuthi akuvunyelwe muntu esakhiweni.
reference: A taxi driver who lives in Grayson Mews has just tried to get back into his flat but is being told by police no one is allowed in or out of the building.
translation: Umshayeli wetekisi ohlala e-Grayso Mews ebezama ukubuyela lapho ahlala khona ngesikhathi amaphoyisa emazisa ukuthi akuvunyelwe muntu esakhiweni.

source: Umane waphelellwa amazwi uma ewa ukuthi kwenzekekn
reference: He was speechless when he discovered what happened.
translation: Umane waphelellwa amazwi uma ewa ukuthi kwenzekekile.

source: Abahlali baziswe ukthi kuselwe amahora ambalwa bese bevunyelwa ukungena.
reference: Residents are now being told it will be hours until they are allowed back in.
translation: Abahlali baziswe ukuthi kuselwe amahora ambalwa bese bevunyelwa ukungena.

source: Elinye lamaphoyisa lizwakale litshela enye indoda ukuthi sonke isakhiwo siyaseshwa.
reference: A police officer was heard telling one man that the entire area is now being treated as a crime scene.
translation: Elinye lamaphoyisa lizwakale litshela enye indoda ukuthi sonke isakhiwo siyaseshwa.

source: Owesifazane uqhamuke esigcawini.
reference: A woman appeared at the scene in tears.
translation: Owesifazane uqhamuke esigcawini.

source: Ubelokhu ephindaphinda ethi‚Äùkwaze kwakubi‚Äù.
reference: She keeps repeating 'it's so awful'.
translation: Ubelokhu ephindaphinda ethi "kwaze kwakubi".

source: Ngesikhathi sika 2:00 emini amaphoyisa abesemotweni indawo beyivalele ngenye engaphandle.
reference: At 2pm two police vans were inside the cordon with another van just outside.
translation: Ngesikhathi sika 2:00 emini amaphoyisa abesemotweni indawo beyivalele ngenye engaphandle.

source: Abaseshi bebemile beqondisa kulendawo evalelwe bebheke uxhaxha lwamaflethi.
reference: A number of officers were stood inside the cordon monitoring the block of flats.
translation: Abaseshi bebemile beqondisa kulendawo evalelwe bebheke uxhaxha lwamaflethi.

source: Noma ubani onolwazi ucelwa ukuba ashiye umyalezo @MerPolCC,afonele ku-101 noma athintane no-Crimestoppers ku-0800 555¬†111 ngo-30 September.
reference: Anyone with information is asked to DM @MerPolCC, call 101 or contact Crimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555 111 quoting log 247 of 30th September.
translation: Noma ubani onolwazi ucelwa ukuba ashiye umyalezo @MerPolCC, afonele ku-101 noma athintane no-Crimestoppers ku-0800 555 111 ngo-30 September.

source: Isithombe esisephalamende sa-Cromwell sibe isikhumbuzo samumva.
reference: Parliament's statue of Cromwell becomes latest memorial hit by 'rewriting history' row
translation: Isithombe esisephalamende sa-Cromwell sibe isikhumbuzo samumva.

source: Lokhu kuye kwabangela iningi labahlali baseNgilandi ukuba lithikamezeke ngenxa yamasiko kanye nezinkolelo.
reference: Its banishment would be poetic justice for his Taliban-like destruction of so many of England's cultural and religious artefacts carried out by his fanatical Puritan followers.
translation: Lokhu kuye kwabangela iningi labahlali baseNgilandi ukuba lithikamezeke ngenxa yamasiko kanye nezinkolelo.

source: Nokho u-Cromwell uchaze umbono ka Mr Crick njengowubuwula futhi efuna ukbhala kabusha umlando.
reference: But the Cromwell Society described Mr Crick's suggestion as "folly" and "attempting to rewrite history."
translation: Nokho u-Cromwell uchaze umbono ka Mr Crick njengowubuwula futhi efuna ukubhala kabusha umlando.

source: U-John Godsmith omele i-Cromwell Society uthe: ‚ÄúKumangazile kakhulu ukuzwa mayelana nokususwa kwesithombe ebesingaphandle kwephalamende
reference: John Goldsmith, chairman of the Cromwell Society, said: "It was inevitable in the present debate about the removal of statues that the figure of Oliver Cromwell outside the Palace of Westminster would become a target.
translation: U-John Godsmith omele i-Cromwell Society uthe: "Kumangazile kakhulu ukuzwa mayelana nokususwa kwesithombe ebesingaphandle kwephalamende".

source: Abezempi abatholanga myalezo ovela ku-Cromwell.
reference: The iconoclasm of the English civil wars was neither ordered nor carried out by Cromwell.
translation: Abezempi abatholanga myalezo ovela ku-Cromwell.

source: Mhlawumbe u-Cromwell ubengaba idlozi elikahle ku-Thomas owayephila ngesikhati sangaphambili.
reference: Perhaps the wrong Cromwell would be sacrificed for the actions of his ancestor Thomas in the previous century.
translation: Mhlawumbe u-Cromwell ubengaba idlozi elikahle ku-Thomas owayephila ngesikhati sangaphambili.

source: Umnumuzane William Hmao obemelele u-Cromwelll ngezango-19th century ebambe naye iqembu ukholelwa ukuthi ukumukhumbula kungaba into inhle.
reference: Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft's magnificent representation of Cromwell is evidence of 19th century opinion and part of the historiography of a figure who many believe is still worth celebrating.
translation: Umnumuzane William Hmao obemelele u-Cromwelll ngezango-19th century ebambe naye iqembu ukholelwa ukuthi ukumukhumbula kungaba into enhle.

source: Umnumzane u-Goldsmith watshela ithelegrafu ngesonto ‚Äúu-Cromwell unconywa iningi, mhlawumbe kunaba into ekahe ukukhnjulwa kwakhe.
reference: Mr Goldsmith told The Sunday Telegraph: "Cromwell is regarded by many, perhaps more in the late 19th century than today, as a defender of parliament against external pressure, in his case of course the monarchy.
translation: Umnumzane u-Goldsmith watshela ithelegrafu ngesonto "u-Cromwell unconywa iningi, mhlawumbe kunaba into ekahe ukukhunjulwa kwakhe.

source: Kungakhathaliseki ukthi umlando uvusa kuphi ukungezwani.
reference: Whether that is a wholly accurate representation is the subject of continuing historical debate.
translation: Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi umlando uvusa kuphi ukungezwani.

source: Emakhulwini e-17 aye ashintha isizwe futhi u-Cromwell uvele phambili njengomummeleli ongahlukanisa aphinde akhe intuthuko yezwe lakithi.
reference: What is certain is that the conflict of the mid 17th century has shaped the subsequent development of our nation, and Cromwell is an individual recognisable figure who represents one side of that divide.
translation: Ekuqaleni kweminyaka ye-17, isizwe sashintsha futhi uCromwell wabukeka njengomnumzane owalungisa futhi wakhuba intuthuko yendabuko.

source: Imiphumela ayithola njengenkosi yobuvikeli kufanele ikhunjulwe nayo.
reference: His achievements as Lord Protector are also worth celebrating and commemorating."
translation: Iziphumo zokuvikela kumele zikhombiswe ngendlela efanele.

source: Ingulube ilume yaze yabulala umlimi wase China.
reference: Killer Pig Mauls Chinese Farmer to Death
translation: Ingulube yabheka yayibulala umlimi waseMandla.

source: Lomlimi wahlaselwa futhi wabulawa yingulube emakethe yase-Southwest China, ngokulandisa kwabezindaba.
reference: A farmer was attacked and killed by a pig in a market in southwest China, according to local media reports.
translation: Lomlimi wahlaselwa futhi wabulawe yingulube emakethe yasenyakatho-ntshonalanga yeChina, ngokuthi kwethulwe yizindaba.

source: Le ndoda,eyesibongo sakwa Yuan itholakale ifile ,igcwelel igazi emzimbeni emakethe yase-Liupanshui esifundaweni sase-Guizhou eningizimu yase-China ngesonto.
reference: The man, identified only by his surname "Yuan," was found dead with a severed artery, covered in blood near a sty at the market in Liupanshui in Guizhou province, the South China Morning Post reported Sunday.
translation: Lo muntu wesibongo sakwaYuan utholakala efile, ugcwele igazi emakethe yaseLiupanshui esifundeni saseGuizhou ophone yeChina ngesonto.

source: Umlimi onezingulube ulungele ukuzijova ngohlaka 30 enyangeni kaMay 2005 e-Xining yase Qinghai ,e-China.
reference: A pig farmer prepares to inject vaccines into pigs at a hoggery on May 30, 2005 in Xining of Qinghai Province, China.
translation: Umlimi onezingulube ulungele ukuzijova ngohlaka wesithathu enyangeni kaNhlolanja 2005 eXining aseQinghai, eChina.

source: Uye wavakashela umzala wakhe yena ohlala eYunnan esifundazweni sifanayo ngolwesithathu ukuze amdayisele izingulube ezingu 15 emakethe.
reference: He had reportedly travelled with his cousin from the neighboring Yunnan province Wednesday to sell 15 pigs at the market.
translation: Wayevakashela umzala wakhe ohlala eYunnan esifundeni esifanayo ngolwesithathu ukuze amdayisele izingulube ezingu-15 emakethe.

source: Osukwini olulalendelayo ekseni ,umzala wakhe atholakala efile,eduze komnyango kukhona ingulube.
reference: The following morning, his cousin found him dead, and discovered a door to a neighbouring pig sty open.
translation: Ngosuku olulandelayo, umzala wakhe utholakala efile, eduze komnyango kukhona ingulube.

source: Uthi lengulube yayi eyesilisa ikhuluphele  Inkulu inegazi emlonyeni.
reference: He said that in the sty was a large male pig with blood on its mouth.
translation: Uthi lengulube isisesimnyama, iphume kakhulu inegazi emlonyeni.

source: Ngemva kokuhlolwa okuningiliziwe uqinisekise ngokuthi lengulube yesisindo sama pound angu-550 iyona eyadla lomlimi.
reference: A forensic examination confirmed that the 550 pound hog had mauled the farmer to death, according to the report.
translation: Ngemva kokubiza okuqinisekisiwe, kuvezwe ukuthi lengulube engu-550 pound iyona eyabulala lomlimi.

source: ‚ÄùUmlenze womzala wami wawugcwele igazi,‚Äù kwasho umzala, wathi isibongo sakhe ‚Äúngu-WU,‚Äù kwasho izindaba zakusihlwa zase-Guiyang.
reference: My cousin's legs were bloody and mangled, the cousin, referred to by his surname "Wu," said, as quoted by the Guiyang Evening News.
translation: Umlenze womzala wami ugcwele igazi, kwasho umzala, wathi isibongo sakhe "nguWU," kwasho izindaba zakusihlwa zaseGuiyang.

source: Amakhamera abinisa u-Yuan engena emakethe ngo 4:40 ngolwesine ezokondla izingulube.
reference: Security camera footage showed Yuan entering the market at 4.40 am Thursday to feed his pigs.
translation: Amakhamera abheka uYuan efika emakethe ngo-4:40 ntambama ezokondla izingulube.

source: Umzimba wakhe watholwa ngemva kwehora.
reference: His body was found about an hour later.
translation: Umzimba wakhe utholakala ngemuva kwehora.

source: Isilwane esabulala lendoda sasingesona esika Yuan noma umzala wakhe.
reference: The animal who killed the man did not belong to Yuan or his cousin.
translation: Isilwane esabulala lo muntu sasingowesibongo sakwaYuan noma umzala wakhe.

source: Umphathi walemakethe utshele abaezindaba ukuthi lengulube yayivalelwe ukuvimbela ukthi ingalimazi muntu ,kuyilapho amaphoyisa eqeoqa ubufakazi.
reference: A market manager told the Evening News that the pig had been locked away to prevent it attacking anyone else, while police gathered evidence at the scene.
translation: Umphathi walemakethe utshele abezindaba ukuthi lengulube yayivalelwe ukuvikela ukuthi ingalimazi muntu, lapho amaphoyisa eqoqa ubufakazi.

source: Umndeni ka-Yuan neziphahimandla zasemakethe ziyaxoxisana mayelana nokulungiselela umufi umngcwabo.
reference: Yuan's family and market authorities are reportedly negotiating compensation for his death.
translation: Umndeni kaYuan neziphahimandla zasemakethe ziyaxoxisana mayelana nokuhlanga komngcwabo.

source: Nakuba kungavamile, amacala ezingulube ezihlasela abantu aye abikwa ngaphambilini.
reference: Though rare, cases of pigs attacking humans have been recorded before.
translation: Nakuba kungavamile, amacala ezingulube ezihlasela abantu aye abikwe ngaphambilini.

source: Ngo-2016, ingulube yahlaseka owesifazane nomyeni wakhe epulazini labo e-Massachusetts, yashiya indoda ilimele kabi.
reference: In 2016, a pig attacked a woman and her husband at their farm in Massachusetts, leaving the man with critical injuries.
translation: Ngo-2016, ingulube yahlasela umfazi nomyeni wakhe epulazini labo eMassachusetts, yashiya indoda ilimele kakhulu.

source: Eminyakeni eyishumi edlule, ingulube enesisindo esingamaphawundi angu-650 yahlasela ugandaganda ohamba u-Welsh umlimi kwaze kwaba umkakhe osabisa lesi silwane.
reference: Ten years previously, a 650 pound pig pinned a Welsh farmer to his tractor until his wife scared the animal away.
translation: Eminyakeni eyishumi edlule, ingulube engu-650 pound yahlasela umgandi ohambe umlimi uWelsh kuze kuba umkakhe osabisa lesi silwane.

source: Ngemva kokuba umlimi wase-Oregon edliwe yizingulube zakhe ngo-2012, omunye wabalimi base-Manitoba watshela Abezindaba e-CBC ukuthi izingulube akuvamile ukuthi zibe nolaka kodwa iphunga legazi "kungazibangela."
reference: After an Oregon farmer was eaten by his pigs in 2012, one Manitoba farmer told CBC News that pigs are not normally aggressive but the taste of blood can act as a "trigger."
translation: Ngemva kokuba umlimi waseOregon abulawe yizingulube zakhe ngo-2012, omunye wabalimi baseManitoha watshela abezindaba kaCBC ukuthi izingulube azivamile ukuba namanga kodwa iphunga legazi "kungazibangela".

source: Izinsalela Zesishingishane uRosa zizoletha izimvula ezingamandla eningizimu-ntshonalanga ye-US
reference: Hurricane Rosa's remnants to bring widespread heavy rain to southwest US
translation: Izinsalela zeshishingane uRosa zizoletha izimvula ezingamandla enengizimu-ntshonalanga yeUS.

source: Ngokwesibikezelo sezulu, Isishingishane uRosa sizoya ngokuphelelwa amandla uma sesiya ngasemanzini apholile asogwini lwasenyakathi ye-Mexico.
reference: As forecast, Hurricane Rosa is weakening as it moves over the cooler waters of the northern coast of Mexico.
translation: Ngokwesibonelo sezulu, ishishingane uRosa sizoyiswa ngokuphelelwa amandla uma siya ngasemanzini apholile asogwini lwasenyakathi yeMexico.

source: Nokho, uRosa uzoletha .
reference: However, Rosa will bring flooding rains across northern Mexico and the southwest U.S. over the coming days.
translation: Nokho, uRosa uzoletha.

source: uRosa unesivinini somoya esingu 85 mph, isiphepho ngasinye, kusukela ngo 5 a.m. Eastern time Sunday, and was located 385 miles southwest of Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
reference: Rosa had winds of 85 mph, a Category 1 Hurricane, as of 5 a.m. Eastern time Sunday, and was located 385 miles southwest of Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
translation: uRosa unesivinini somoya esingu 85 mph, isiphepho ngasinye, kusukela ngo 5 a.m. Eastern time Sunday, futhi wayeseminyango ye-385 miles ngaseNtshonalanga ne-Punta Eugenia, Mexico.

source: uRosa ulindelwe ukuba abheke eNyakatho ngeSonto.
reference: Rosa is expected to move north on Sunday.
translation: uRosa ulindelwe ukuba abheke eNyakatho ngeSonto.

source: Okwamanje,umkhombe uyaqala ushintsha isimo kwi-Pacific Ocean futhi uhamba ngempumalanga ubheke entshonalanga  yase U.S Njengoba uRosa esondela esiqhingini sase Baja California ngoMsombuluko isiphepho sizoqala ukuqinisa ngomswakama ezindaweni zaseNyakatho phakathi neNtshonalanga e-U.S.
reference: Meanwhile, a trough is beginning to take shape over the Pacific Ocean and move east toward the West Coast of the U.S. As Rosa approaches the Baja California peninsula on Monday as a tropical storm it will begin to push deep tropical moisture northward into the southwest U.S.
translation: Okwamanje, umkhombe uyaqala ushintsha isimo kwi-Pacific Ocean futhi uhamba ngempumalanga ubheke entshonalanga yase U.S Njengoba uRosa esondela esiqhingini sase Baja California ngoMsombuluko isiphepho sizoqala ukuqinisa ngomswakama ezindaweni zaseNyakatho phakathi neNtshonalanga e-U.S.

source: uRosa uzoletha imvula enobude obubalelwa kuma-inches ayishumi ezindaweni ezithile eMexico ngoMsombuluko.
reference: Rosa will bring up to 10 inches of rain in parts of Mexico on Monday.
translation: uRosa uzoletha imvula enobude obubalelwa kuma-inches ayishumi ezindaweni ezithile eMexico ngoMsombuluko.

source: Ngakho-ke, ezinsukwini ezilandelayo umswakama uzohlangana nomkhombe bese kwakhekha imvula enamandla futhi eyandile ezindaweni zaseNtshonalanga.
reference: Then, tropical moisture interacting with the approaching trough will create widespread heavy rainfall in the Southwest over the coming days.
translation: Ngakho-ke, ezinsukwini ezilandelayo umswakama uzohlangana nomkhombe bese kwakhekha imvula enamandla futhi eyandile ezindaweni zaseNtshonalanga.

source: LocalEzindaweni ezisondele, imvula ebalelwa kwi-inch kuya kwamane izodala izikhukhula ezigubezelayo eziyingozi, ukukhukhuleka kwadoti ngisho nokudilika kwenhlabathi ezingwadule.
reference: Locally, 1 to 4 inches of rain will cause dangerous flash flooding, debris flows and possibility landslides in the desert.
translation: Ezindaweni ezisondele, imvula ebalelwa kwi-inch kuya kwamane izodala izikhukhula ezigubezelayo eziyingozi, ukukhukhuleka kwadoti ngisho nokudilika kwenhlabathi ezingwadule.

source: tropiUmswakama uzokwenza izinga lemvula libe nga-inches amabili kuya kwamathathu ngehora ngokunembile, ikakhulukazi ezindaweni zaseNingizimu yase-Nevada nase Arizona.
reference: Deep tropical moisture will cause rainfall rates to approach 2 to 3 inches per hour in spots, especially in parts of southern Nevada and Arizona.
translation: Umswakama uzokwenza izinga lemvula libe nga-inches amabili kuya kwamathathu ngehora ngokunembile, ikakhulukazi ezindaweni zaseNingizimu yase-Nevada nase Arizona.

source: Amazinga emvula angaba ngama-inch amabili kuya kwamane ilindelekile e Ningizimu yasentshonalanga,ikakhulukazi eningi yayo e Arizona.
reference: As much as 2 to 4 inches of rain is expected in parts of the Southwest, especially over much of Arizona.
translation: Amazinga emvula angaba ngama-inch amabili kuya kwamane ilindelekile e Ningizimu yasentshonalanga, ikakhulukazi eningi yayo e Arizona.

source: Izikhukhula ezigubezelayo zikindelekile zihambisana nesimo esiwohloza ngokushesha ngenxa yokuhlakazeka kwemvelo ye mvula enomswakama.
reference: Flash flooding is possible with rapidly deteriorating conditions due to the scattered nature of tropical rain.
translation: Izikhukhula ezigubezelayo zikindelekile zihambisana nesimo esiwohloza ngokushesha ngenxa yokuhlakazeka kwemvelo ye mvula enomswakama.

source: Kungaba ubuwula ukuvula ibhizinisi okwagule empeleni ngoba sekuza izimvula ezinoswakama.
reference: It would be extremely ill advised to venture out into the desert on foot with the threat of tropical rainfall.
translation: Kungaba ubuwula ukuvula ibhizinisi okwagule empeleni ngoba sekuza izimvula ezinoswakama.

source: Izimvula ezinamandla zingabangela imihosha ukuba ibe imifula ebukeka ngathi iseniminyaka yaba khona ukuduma kona kobangela isivuthela somoya ezindaweni eziseduze ozobe uhamba nothuli.
reference: Heavy rain could cause canyons to become raging rivers and thunderstorms will bring locally gusty winds and blowing dust.
translation: Izimvula ezinamandla zingabangela imihosha ukuba ibe imifula ebukeka ngathi iseniminyaka yaba khona ukuduma kona kobangela isivuthela somoya ezindaweni eziseduze ozobe uhamba nothuli.

source: Izikhombe ezizayo zizoletha imvula enamandla ezindaweni ezisondelene neNingizimu California nasogwini.
reference: The approaching trough will bring some locally heavy rain to parts of the Southern California coastline.
translation: Izikhombe ezizayo zizoletha imvula enamandla ezindaweni ezisondelene neNingizimu California nasogwini.

source: Izimvula ezibalelwa kumahhafu we-inch, zingadala umonakalo omncane wodoti nemigwaqo eshelelayo
reference: Rainfall totals of over half an inch are possible, which could cause minor debris flows and slick roadways.
translation: Izimvula ezibalelwa kumahhafu we-inch, zingadala umonakalo omncane wodoti nemigwaqo eshelelayo.

source: lena koba imvula yokuqala esifundeni njengoba nje kuyisikhathi sazo izimvula.
reference: This would be the region's first rainfall of their wet season.
translation: Lena koba imvula yokuqala esifundeni njengoba nje kuyisikhathi sazo izimvula.

source: Ezinye izimvula ezihlakazekile zizoqala ukusondela i-Arizona ntambama ngesonto nasekuseni ngoMsombuluko, ngaphambi kokuba imvula yande ntambama ngoMsombuluko nangolwesibili.
reference: Some scattered tropical rain showers will begin to approach Arizona late Sunday and early Monday, before the rain becomes more widespread late Monday and Tuesday.
translation: Ezinye izimvula ezihlakazekile zizoqala ukusondela i-Arizona ntambama ngesonto nasekuseni ngoMsombuluko, ngaphambi kokuba imvula yande ntambama ngoMsombuluko nangolwesibili.

source: Imvula izosabalala emagumbini amane ngolwesibili kuze kube ngulwesithathuthu.
reference: Heavy rain will spread into the Four Corners on Tuesday and last through Wednesday.
translation: Imvula izosabalala emagumbini amane ngolwesibili kuze kube ngulwesithathuthu.

source: Enyangeni ka-October sizobona ukushitsha kwamazinga okushisa e-U.S njengoba i-Arctic izobe iya ngokuphola, kodwa izindawo ezingama-Tropics zizofudumala.
reference: October can see some intense temperature swings across the U.S. as the Arctic gets cooler, but the tropics remain quite warm.
translation: Enyangeni ka-October sizobona ukushitsha kwamazinga okushisa e-U.S njengoba i-Arctic izobe iya ngokuphola, kodwa izindawo ezingama-Tropics zizofudumala.

source: Ngokuvamile lokhu kubangela ukushintsha emazingeni okushisa ngesikhathi esincane.
reference: Sometimes this leads to dramatic changes in temperature over short distances.
translation: Ngokuvamile lokhu kubangela ukushintsha emazingeni okushisa ngesikhathi esincane.

source: Kunesibonelo esihle samadkingozi ekushintsheni kwamazinga okushisa ezindaweni eziphakathi e U.S ngesonto.
reference: There is a great example of dramatic temperature differences through the central U.S. on Sunday.
translation: Kunesibonelo esihle samadkingozi ekushintsheni kwamazinga okushisa ezindaweni eziphakathi e U.S ngesonto.

source: Kunomahluko ka 20-degrees emazingeni okushisa phajathi kwe- Kansas City, Missouri, and Omaha, Nebraska, naphakathi kwe-St. Louis ne Des Moines, Iowa.
reference: There is nearly a 20-degree temperature difference between Kansas City, Missouri, and Omaha, Nebraska, and between St. Louis and Des Moines, Iowa.
translation: Kunomahluko ka 20-degrees emazingeni okushisa phajathi kwe- Kansas City, Missouri, and Omaha, Nebraska, naphakathi kwe-St. Louis ne Des Moines, Iowa.

source: Ezinsukwini ezilandelayo ihlobo elibala ukufudumala lizozama ukwakheka lande futhi.
reference: Over the next few days, lingering summer warmth will try to build and expand again.
translation: Ezinsukwini ezilandelayo ihlobo elibala ukufudumala lizozama ukwakheka lande futhi.

source: Phakathi ne U.S nase Mpumalanga kulindeleke ukubonakala koqala kwa-October nokufudumala kuka- 80s kusukela ezinkangala zaseNingizimu kuya enyakatho.
reference: Much of the central and eastern U.S. is expected to see a warm start to October with widespread 80s from the Southern Plains to parts of the Northeast.
translation: Phakathi ne U.S nase Mpumalanga kulindeleke ukubonakala koqala kwa-October nokufudumala kuka- 80s kusukela ezinkangala zaseNingizimu kuya enyakatho.

source: e-New York City kulindeleke ukuba ifinyelele emazingeni ka- 80 degrees ngolwesibili okobe kusho ukuthi ibe ngaphezulu ngo 10 degrees kwavamile .
reference: New York City could reach 80 degrees on Tuesday, which would be approximately 10 degrees above average.
translation: e-New York City kulindeleke ukuba ifinyelele emazingeni ka- 80 degrees ngolwesibili okobe kusho ukuthi ibe ngaphezulu ngo 10 degrees kwavamile.

source: abahloli bethu bezemvelo bathe lokhu kubinise ukuthi amazinga azokhuphuka ezindaweni zasempumalanga .
reference: Our long term climate forecast is indicating high chances for above-average temperatures for the eastern U.S. through the first half of October.
translation: Abahloli bethu bezemvelo bathe lokhu kubinise ukuthi amazinga azokhuphuka ezindaweni zasempumalanga.

source: baangaphezu kuka  20 million abantu ababukela icala la   Brett Kavanaugh
reference: More than 20 million people watched Brett Kavanaugh hearing
translation: baangaphezu kuka 20 million abantu ababukela icala la Brett Kavanaugh

source: bangaphezu kuka 20 million abantu ababuke ubufakazi bokhethwe inkantool u- Brett Kavanaugh nowesifazane owamubeka icala lokumhlukumeza ngokucansi ngeminyaka yo-1980, Christine Blasey Ford, on six television networks.
reference: More than 20 million people watched Thursday's gripping testimony by Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh and the woman who accused him of a sexual assault that allegedly occurred in the 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, on six television networks.
translation: bangaphezu kuka 20 million abantu ababuke ubufakazi bokhethwe inkantool u-Brett Kavanaugh nowesifazane owamubeka icala lokumhlukumeza ngokucansi ngeminyaka yo-1980, Christine Blasey Ford, on six television networks.

source: okwamanje,ipolitiki iqhubekile,nokusakaza nakuba bekunakuphazamiseka ezinhlelweni zabo ezijwayelekile ngenxa ykushintsha kwezinto ngokungalindelekile ngolwesihlanu ngomzuzu wokugcina:isivumelwano esenziwe u Arizona Sen.u Jeff Flake we FBI uzoqala uphenyo lamacala .
reference: Meanwhile, the political standoff continued, with broadcasters interrupting regular programming for Friday's last-minute twist: an agreement engineered by Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake for the FBI to conduct a one-week investigation of the charges.
translation: okwamanje, ipolitiki iqhubekile, nokusakaza nakuba bekunakuphazamiseka ezinhlelweni zabo ezijwayelekile ngenxa ykushintsha kwezinto ngokungalindelekile ngolwesihlanu ngomzuzu wokugcina: isivumelwano esenziwe u Arizona Sen. u Jeff Flake we FBI uzoqala uphenyo lamacala.

source: uFord utshele ijaji ukuthi uqiniseka kakhulu ukuthi u- Kavanaugh wazama ukumphuphutha nokumkhumula izimphahla zakhe eMazingeni aphezulu ngesikhathi kunombuthano eskoleni sabo.
reference: Ford told the Senate Judiciary Committee that she's 100 percent certain that Kavanaugh groped her drunkenly and tried to take off her clothes at a high school party.
translation: uFord utshele ijaji ukuthi uqiniseka kakhulu ukuthi u-Kavanaugh wazama ukumphuphutha nokumkhumula izimphahla zakhe eMazingeni aphezulu ngesikhathi kunombuthano eskoleni sabo.

source: uKavanaugh,enikeza ubufakazi  enkantolo,uthe naye uqiniseka ngokuphelele ukuthi akwenzekanga lutho.
reference: Kavanaugh, in impassioned testimony, said he's 100 percent certain that it didn't happen.
translation: uKavanaugh, enikeza ubufakazi enkantolo, uthe naye uqiniseka ngokuphelele ukuthi akwenzekanga lutho.

source: Ngokombiko wakwa-Nielsen bangaphezu kwa 20.4 million abantu abababukela .
reference: It's likely that more than the 20.4 million people reported by Nielsen on Friday watched it.
translation: Ngokombiko wakwa-Nielsen bangaphezu kwa 20.4 million abantu abababukela.

source: lombiko uvele enkampanini ebibalala ababukeli ku- CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel naku MSNBC.
reference: The company was counting average viewership on CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel and MSNBC.
translation: lombiko uvele enkampanini ebibalala ababukeli ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel naku MSNBC.

source: Figuresa amanye amanani awasheshanga ukutholakala kuziteshi ebizisakaza kubawa i-  PBS, C-SPAN ne  the Fox Business Network.
reference: Figures weren't immediately available for other networks that showed it, including PBS, C-SPAN and the Fox Business Network.
translation: Figuresa amanye amanani awasheshanga ukutholakala kuziteshi ebizisakaza kubawa i-PBS, C-SPAN ne the Fox Business Network.

source: futhu u-Nielsen ngokuvamile uyaye ubhekanane nenselele ekubaleni inani  lababukele besemahhovisi abo.
reference: And Nielsen usually has some trouble measuring people who watch in offices.
translation: futhu u-Nielsen ngokuvamile uyaye ubhekanane nenselele ekubaleni inani lababukele besemahhovisi abo.

source: ukuze basivezele indlela ababona ngayo, ukuthi inani labantu lithi alilingane nelabazo bukela umdlalo webhola noma abaze kumiklonyeliswo .
reference: To put that in perspective, that's an audience size similar to that for a playoff football game or the Academy Awards.
translation: ukuze basivezele indlela ababona ngayo, ukuthi inani labantu lithi alilingane nelabazo bukela umdlalo webhola noma abaze kumiklonyeliswo.

source: i-Fox News Channel,enomqondisi onombono ovuna u- Kavanaugh,okuye kwaholela ekutheni zonke iziteshi zibe nababukeli besilinganiso sika 5.69 million  lonke usuku lwecala ,ngokusho kuka - Nielsen.
reference: Fox News Channel, whose opinion hosts have strongly backed Kavanaugh's appointment, led all networks with an average of 5.69 million viewers during the all-day hearing, Nielsen said.
translation: i-Fox News Channel, enomqondisi onombono ovuna u-Kavanaugh, okuye kwaholela ekutheni zonke iziteshi zibe nababukeli besilinganiso sika 5.69 million lonke usuku lwecala, ngokusho kuka-Nielsen.

source: i-ABC ibe sendaweni yesibili ngababukeli abangu- 3.26 million .
reference: ABC was second with 3.26 million viewers.
translation: i-ABC ibe sendaweni yesibili ngababukeli abangu-3.26 million.

source: i-CBS yona ibe nenani la  3.1 million,i- NBC yona ibeno- 2.94 million,i- MSNBC yona ibe no 2.89 million kwathi i-CNN yabano 2.52 million, ngokusho kwe-Nielsen.
reference: CBS had 3.1 million, NBC had 2.94 million, MSNBC had 2.89 million and CNN had 2.52 million, Nielsen said.
translation: i-CBS yona ibe nenani la 3.1 million, i-NBC yona ibeno-2.94 million, i-MSNBC yona ibe no 2.89 million kwathi i-CNN yabano 2.52 million, ngokusho kwe-Nielsen.

source: Ukulangazelelwa kokufuna ukwazi kusaqhubeka kuphezulu ngemva kwecala.
reference: Interest remained high after the hearing.
translation: Ukulangazelelwa kokufuna ukwazi kusaqhubeka kuphezulu ngemva kwecala.

source: u-Flake uyena obebhekwe ngabomvu kwidrama ebengolwesihlanu .
reference: Flake was the central figure in Friday's drama.
translation: u-Flake uyena obebhekwe ngabomvu kwidrama ebengolwesihlanu.

source: Ngemva kokukhishwa isitatimende esimayelana nokuvotelwa uhlangothi lwa-Kavanaugh,uye wabanjwa amakhamera ase-  CNN nawase  CBS ngolwesihlanu ekseni ngenkathi ememezwa isixuku ngesikhathi ezama ukugibela ikheshi elizomyisa phambi kwejaji .
reference: After the moderate Republican's office issued a statement that he would be voting in favor of Kavanaugh, he was caught be CNN and CBS cameras Friday morning being shouted at by protesters as he tried to ride an elevator to a Judiciary Committee hearing.
translation: Ngemva kokukhishwa isitatimende esimayelana nokuvotelwa uhlangothi lwa-Kavanaugh, uye wabanjwa amakhamera ase-CNN nawase CBS ngolwesihlanu ekseni ngenkathi ememezwa isixuku ngesikhathi ezama ukugibela ikheshi elizomyisa phambi kwejaji.

source: Esakazwa bukhoma yisiteshi sa-CNN,uye wama wabhekisa amehlo phansi okwesikhashana eshaywa amahloni.
reference: He stood with eyes downcast for several minutes as he was berated, televised live on CNN.
translation: Esakazwa bukhoma yisiteshi sa-CNN, uye wama wabhekisa amehlo phansi okwesikhashana eshaywa amahloni.

source: Nimi lapha phambi kwakho, kwaso omunye wesifazane .
reference: I'm standing right here in front of you, one woman said.
translation: Nimi lapha phambi kwakho, kwaso omunye wesifazane.

source: Ucabanga ukuthi ukhuluma iqiniso phambi kwezwe?	Do you think he's telling the truth to the country?

ds_ntrex_zu	244	zu	Watshelwa, Unamandla uma iningi labesifazane lingenamandla.""
translation: He was told, "you have power when so many women are powerless.""

source: uFlake wathi ihhovisi lakhe lakhipha isistatimende wabe esethi ,ngaphambi kokuba ikheshi livaleke ,wathi unokuningi kokukusho phambi kwenkantolo .
reference: Flake said that his office had issued a statement and said, before the elevator closed, that he would have more to say at the committee hearing.
translation: uFlake wathi ihhovisi lakhe lakhipha isistatimende wabe esethi, ngaphambi kokuba ikheshi livaleke, wathi unokuningi kokukusho phambi kwenkantolo.

source: Zisebenzisa izintambo iziteshi ziye zasakaza icala ,lapho kuye kwafika isikhathi sokuba ijaji livotele ukukululwa kuka Kavanaugh.
reference: The cable and broadcast networks were all covering live hours later, when the Judiciary Committee was to vote to advance Kavanaugh's nomination to the full Senate for a vote.
translation: Zisebenzisa izintambo iziteshi ziye zasakaza icala, lapho kuye kwafika isikhathi sokuba ijaji livotele ukukululwa kuka Kavanaugh.

source: Kodwa ke u Flake utheuzokwenza lokho kuphela uma eseqonda ukuthi I- FBI ibheke zonke izinhlangothi zaloludaba ngeviki elizayo,lokho okukade kufunwa intando yeniningi.
reference: But Flake said he would only do so with the understanding that the FBI would look into the allegations against the nominee for the next week, which minority Democrats have been urging.
translation: Kodwa ke u Flake utheuzokwenza lokho kuphela uma eseqonda ukuthi I-FBI ibheke zonke izinhlangothi zaloludaba ngeviki elizayo, lokho okukade kufunwa intando yeniningi.

source: u-Flake uye washintsha umqondo umngani wakhe ngenkathi bexoxa nomngane wakhe , Democratic Sen. Chris Coons.
reference: Flake was convinced in part by conversations with his friend, Democratic Sen. Chris Coons.
translation: u-Flake uye washintsha umqondo umngani wakhe ngenkathi bexoxa nomngane wakhe, Democratic Sen. Chris Coons.

source: Ngemva kokuxoxa no- Coonskanye nephalamende u-Flake uye wathatha isinqumo.
reference: After a conversation with Coons and several senators afterwards, Flake made his decision.
translation: Ngemva kokuxoxa no-Coonskanye nephalamende u-Flake uye wathatha isinqumo.

source: Flake's choice had poweIsinqumo saFlake besinamandla,ngoba ngokwezakhamuzi azizange zivotele u-Kavanaugh ngaphandle kokuqedwa kophenyo..
reference: Flake's choice had power, because it was evident Republicans would not have the votes to approve Kavanaugh without the investigation.
translation: IsiQhubekho sika-Flake sasivikela ngokusebenzisa amandla, ngoba ngokwezakhamzi bekungekho noma bekuphuthunyiswe ngokuphelele uphenyo ngo-Kavanaugh.

source: uMongameli u- Trumpuye wavula uphenyo nge-FBI ukuze athole okumelene no- Kavanaugh.
reference: President Trump has opened an FBI investigation into the allegations against Kavanaugh.
translation: UMongameli u-Trump wavula uphenyo we-FBI ukuze athole okufanele ngo-Kavanaugh.

source: i-British PM  May uye yagxeka maylanana   'nokudlalwa kwepolitiki' e Brexit
reference: British PM May accuses critics of 'playing politics' over Brexit
translation: IPrimi Minister yase-Britain uMnu May wathi kubekhona 'ukudlalwa kwepolitiki' ku-Brexit.

source: usekela  Minister Theresa May uye waqinisa ezinsolweni zakhe zokushiya i European Union ngoba‚Äù idlala ngepolitiki ‚Äú ikusasa laseBrithani kanye nokubukelwa phansi kwesiziwe washo loku kuyi-interview ephepheni I Sunday Times  .
reference: Prime Minister Theresa May accused critics of her plans to leave the European Union of "playing politics" with Britain's future and undermining the national interest in an interview with the Sunday Times newspaper.
translation: USekela Minister uTheresa May wavikela izinhloso zakhe zokushiya iEuropean Union ngoba "idlala ngepolitiki" isiqu sase-Britain, njengoba esho ku-interview nephephandaba le-Sunday Times.

source: i-Britain's Prime Minister Theresa May ufikile embuthanweni e  Birmingham, Britain, September 29, 2018.
reference: Britain's Prime Minister Theresa May arrives for the Conservative Party Conference in Birmingham, Britain, September 29, 2018.
translation: IPrimi Minister yase-Britain uTheresa May ufike emhlanganweni eBirmingham, Britain, ngo-29 September 2018.

source: kwenye i- interview ilandelwa ilena ayena nephepha eyavela ekhasini lokuqala ,okade engu minister Boris Johnson uye waqhubeka nokuhlasela oakubize nge-  Chequers plan for Brexit,  ethi ucela i Britain ne  EU kufanele iqoqe  "konke."
reference: In another interview next to the one with her on the newspaper's front page, her former foreign minister Boris Johnson pressed his attack of her so-called Chequers plan for Brexit, saying a proposal that Britain and the EU should collect each other's tariffs was "entirely preposterous."
translation: Ku-interview enye eyalandelwa nephephandaba, uNgqongqoshe Boris Johnson uqhubeke ekhononda i-Chequers plan ye-Brexit, ethi i-Britain ne-EU kumele "ziqoqe konke."

source: Wayde Sims ukudutshulwa : Amaphoysa abophe umsolwa u- Dyteon Simpson e- LSU player's death
reference: Wayde Sims shooting: Police arrest suspect Dyteon Simpson in LSU player's death
translation: Ukubulawa kuka Wayde Sims: Amaphoyisa abheke umsolwa uDyteon Simpson ngokufa kwe-LSU player.

source: Amaphoyisa abophe umsolwa ekudutshulweni nasekufeni kuka Wayde Sims,obeneminyaka engu-20 edlala I basketball e LSU.
reference: Police have arrested a suspect in the fatal shooting death of Wayde Sims, a 20-year-old basketball player at LSU.
translation: Amaphoyisa abheke umsolwa ekubulaweni nasekufeni kuka Wayde Sims, oneminyaka engu-20 edlala i-basketball e-LSU.

source: uDyteon Simpson,ona- 20,uye waboshwa njengoba sekungokwesibili eboshelwa ukubulala ,nokusho kwe kwe Baton Rouge we Police Department .
reference: Dyteon Simpson, 20, has been arrested and booked into prison on a second-degree murder charge, the Baton Rouge Police Department said.
translation: UDyteon Simpson, oneminyaka engu-20, uboshwe njengoba sekungokwesibili eboshwe ngokubulala, ngokusho kwamaphoyisa eBaton Rouge.

source: OfficialsAbasemthwthweni baye bakhulula I video phakathi kuka Sims no Simpson futhi iphoyisa lithi uSim ulahlekelwe izibuko ngenkathi belwa.
reference: Officials released video of the confrontation between Sims and Simpson, and police said Sims lost his glasses during the fight.
translation: Abasemthethweni bakhiphe ividio ephakathi kuka Sims no Simpson, iphoyisa lithi uSims ulahlekelwe izibuko ngenkathi belwa.

source: IPhoyisa liye lazithola esigcawini lapho ebekuliwa khona kuzona kwabe sekutholakala I-DNA yakhe, nokusho kwe  CBS affiliate WAFB.
reference: Police recovered the glasses from the scene and said they found Simpson's DNA on them, CBS affiliate WAFB reports.
translation: Iphoyisa lathola izimpawu esigcawini lapho bebesilwa khona, lapho kutholakala i-DNA yakhe, ngokusho kwe-CBS affiliate WAFB.

source: Ngemva kokubza uSimpson, iphoyisa lithi uvumile ukuthi wadubula u  Wayde.
reference: After questioning Simpson, police said he admitted to fatally shooting Wayde.
translation: Ngemva kokubiza uSimpson, iphoyisa lithi uvumile ukuthi wadubula uWayde.

source: Isibopho sakhe siye sabekwa ku-$350,000, ngokusho kuka Advocate .
reference: His bond has been set at $350,000, the Advocate reports.
translation: Isibopho sakhe sabekwa ku-$350,000, ngokusho kuka Advocate.

source: Empumalanga i Baton Rouge Parish Coroner's Office ikhiphe I prilimi ngolwesihlanu , bethi okwenze afe kube isilonda  sokudutshulwa ekhanda kuya entanyeni.
reference: The East Baton Rouge Parish Coroner's Office released a preliminary report Friday, saying the cause of death is a gunshot wound to the head into the neck.
translation: Iphoyisa laseMpumalanga eBaton Rouge Parish Coroner's Office likhiphe incazelo yokuqala ngolwesihlanu, ithi usiko lokudutshulwa kwenzeke evele ekhanda kuya entanyeni.

source: i department iye yakina udumo umbaaleki ngomsebenzi Louisiana State , ENiningizimu  University amaphoyisa  nezakhamizi baye banceda ekusizeni kokucwaninga okuholele ekuboshweni .
reference: The department is crediting the Louisiana State Police fugitive task force, the state police crime lab, Southern University police and area citizens in assisting in the investigation leading to the arrest.
translation: Isikhungo siye sakhaba ukuphoxeka ngomsebenzi we-Louisiana State University, amaphoyisa nezakhamizi zisiza ekucubunguleni okwenzele ekuboshweni.

source: LSU umqondisi uJoe Alleva weLSU uye wabonga izakhamizi ‚Äúngokuzinikela kokufuna ubulungiswa."
reference: LSU athletic director Joe Alleva thanked area law enforcement for its "diligence and pursuit of justice."
translation: UMqondisi we-LSU uJoe Alleva sibonga izakhamizi "ngokuzinikela kokufuna ubulungiswa."

source: Sims wayeneminyaka engu 20.
reference: Sims was 20 years old.
translation: USims wayengu-20 yeminyaka.

source: ubede bakhekhe bebuyizinyawo eziyisithupha kweziyisithupha wakhulela e Baton Rouge, lapho ubaba wakhe , Wayne, adlalela khona  ibasketball edlalela i LSU.
reference: The 6-foot-6 forward grew up in Baton Rouge, where his father, Wayne, also played basketball for LSU.
translation: Washayela ezinyawo eziyisithupha kuya eziyisithupha wakhulela eBaton Rouge, lapho ubaba wakhe, uWayne, edlala i-basketball ye-LSU.

source: Washaya amaphuzu angu 5.6 futhi nama  and 2.6 ribhowundi angu 2.6 emdlalweni kwisizini edlule.
reference: He averaged 5.6 points and 2.6 rebounds a game last season.
translation: Washaya amaphuzu angu-5.6 namabhowundi angu-2.6 esizini edlule.

source: Ekuseni ngolwesihlanu ,umqeqeshi we-LSU basketball uWill Wade wathi iqembu "lishaqekile" futhi babuhlungu " ngenxa yokufa kuka-Wayde .
reference: On Friday morning, LSU basketball coach Will Wade said the team is "devastated" and "in shock" by Wayde's death.
translation: Ekuseni ngolwesihlanu, umqeqeshi we-LSU basketball uWill Wade wathi iqembu "lishaqekile" futhi libuhlungu "ngenxa yokudala kuka-Wayde.

source: yolokhu esihlla sikhathazeke ngakho,kwasho u-Wade.
reference: This is what you worry about at all times, Wade said.
translation: Sihlala sikhathazeke, kusho uWade.

source: intaba yomlilo ikhafule umlotha e Mexico City
