reference: The dueling protests reflect the divisiveness of a visitor hailed as a hero by some German Turks and reviled as an autocrat by others.
translation: Le mbikhisho ikhombisa ukwehlukana phakathi kwemibono ye-sivakashi esibonakal siyiqhawe kuma-German Turks futhi njengondlovukayiphikiswa kwabanye.

source: Ingozi kumgwaqo Deptford: Mgibeli webayisekile ushonile eshayisana nemoto
reference: Deptford road crash: Cyclist dies in collision with car
translation: Ingozi kumgwaqo Deptford: Umgibeli webayisekile ushonile eshayisana nemoto.

source: Umdlali we bhayisekile ushonile ingozini ebadakanya imoto  eLondon.
reference: A cyclist has died in a collision involving a car in London.
translation: Umdlali webhayisekile ushonile engozini ebadakanya imoto eLondon.

source: Ingozi uyenzeke eduze kwenhlanganandlela kwemimgwaqo ubestwood kanye no Evelyn, umgwaqo o busy Deptford, e ningizimu ne mpumalanga ye dolobha, ngabo 10:15 BST.
reference: The crash happened near the junction of Bestwood Street and Evelyn Street, a busy road in Deptford, in the south-east of the city, at about 10:15 BST.
translation: Ingozi yenzeke eduze kwenhlanganandlela kwemimgwaqo uBestwood kanye no-Evelyn, umgwaqo o-busy Deptford, e-ningizimu ne-mpumalanga ye-dolobha, ngabo 10:15 BST.

source: u mshayeli wemoto umile futhi abezimo eziphuthumayo bafikile, kodwa umlisa ushonile endaweni yesgameko.
reference: The driver of the car stopped and paramedics attended, but the man died at the scene.
translation: Umshayeli wemoto umile futhi abezimo eziphuthumayo bafikile, kodwa umlisa ushonile endaweni yesgameko.

source: Lengozi ifike emva kwenyanga ukuthi kushone umgibeli we bhayisekili eshayisiwe wbaleka umshayeli ku mgwaqo uChilders, kude buduze kwendaweni embalwa ne ngozi yango mgqibelo.
reference: The crash comes months after another cyclist died in a hit-and-run on Childers Street, about a mile away from Saturday's crash.
translation: Lengozi ifike emva kwenyanga ukuthi kushone umgibeli webhayisekili eshayisiwe wabeleka umshayeli ku-mgwaqo uChilders, kude buduze kwendaweni embalwa ne-ngozi yango-mgqibelo.

source: Amphoyisa amaspala athe abaphenyi bamatasa bafuna ukuzwazi imininigwane yomlisa kuzi bazise abomndeni.
reference: The Metropolitan Police said officers were working to identify the man and inform his next-of-kin.
translation: Amphoyisa amaspala athe abaphenyi bamatasa bafuna ukuzwazi imininigwane yomlisa kuzi bazise abomndeni.

source: Ukuvalwa kwemigwaqo kanye nokushintshwa kwemizila yamabhasi sekubekiwe futhi abashayeli wabazwayiswa ukuthi bagweme lemizila.
reference: Road closures and bus diversions are in place and motorists have been advised to avoid the area.
translation: Ukuvalwa kwemigwaqo kanye nokushintshwa kwemizila yamabhasi sekubekiwe futhi abashayeli wabazwayiswa ukuthi bagweme lemizila.

source: Ijele lase Long Lartin:  Amaphosiya ayisithupha emva kwesiphithiphithi
reference: Long Lartin prison: Six officers hurt in disorder
translation: Ijele lase-Long Lartin: Amaphosiya ayisithupha emva kwesiphithiphithi.

source: Ojele abayisithupha balimele ekuthikamaziseni kwijele labesilisa eliqahswe kakhulu, kusho ihhovisi lase Jele.
reference: Six prison officers have been injured in a disturbance at a high security men's jail, the Prison Office has said.
translation: Ojele abayisithupha balimele ekuthikamaziseni kwijele labesilisa eliqashwe kakhulu, kusho ihhovisi lase-Jele.

source: Isiphithiphithi sisuke e HMP Long Lartin e Worcestershire ngo 09;30 BST ngeSonto futhi kusaqhubeka.
reference: Disorder broke out at HMP Long Lartin in Worcestershire at about 09:30 BST on Sunday and is ongoing.
translation: Isiphithiphithi sisuke e-HMP Long Lartin e-Worcestershire ngo-09:30 BST ngeSonto futhi kusaqhubeka.

source: Ucwepheshe  ‚ÄúTornado‚Äù ojele wabalethwe ukuba bazobhekana nokuphazamiseka, okubandakanya iboshwa eziyi isishangalombili futhi liqhukethwe ophikweni olulodwa.
reference: Specialist "Tornado" officers have been brought in to deal with the disturbance, which involves eight inmates and is contained to one wing.
translation: Ucwepheshe "Tornado" ojele wabalethwe ukuba bazobhekana nokuphazamiseka, okubandakanya iboshwa eziyi-isishangalombili futhi liqhukethwe ophikweni olulodwa.

source: Ojele hlengiwele ukwelimala kancane endaweni yesigameko.
reference: The officers were treated for minor facial injuries at the scene.
translation: Ojele hlengiwele ukwelimala kancane endaweni yesigameko.

source: Okhulumela ijele uthe: ‚ÄúAbaqeqeshwe ngokhethekile sebedutshiwe ukuba basize kwisigameko esiqhubekayo e HMP Long Lartin
reference: A Prison Service spokesperson said: "Specially trained prison staff have been deployed to deal with an ongoing incident at HMP Long Lartin.
translation: Okhulumela ijele uthe: "Abasebenzi abaqeqeshwe ngokohlwathi sebehoxiswe ukuba basizo kwisimo esiqhubekayo e HMP Long Lartin

source: Abasenzi abayisithupha abalimele sibelashiwe.
reference: Six members of staff have been treated for injuries.
translation: Abasebenzi abayisithupha abalimele sikwelashwe.

source: Asilubekezeli udlame emajele ethu, and sifuna ukucacisa ukuthi labo aba bandakanye bazo dluliswelwa emaphoyiseni futhi bacithe isikhathi esinde jele‚Äù.
reference: We do not tolerate violence in our prisons, and are clear that those responsible will be referred to the police and could spend longer behind bars."
translation: Asilubekezeli udlame emajele ethu, futhi sifuna ukucacisa ukuthi labo abahlanganwe badalwe emaphoyiseni bese bevalwa isikhathi eside ejele".

source: HMP Long Lartin imumethe iziboshwa izngaphezu kwa 500, Kubalwa phakhathi izigilamkhuba zakulellizwe eziyingozi.
reference: HMP Long Lartin holds more than 500 prisoners, including some of the country's most dangerous offenders.
translation: HMP Long Lartin inamaqoqo enkulungwane yangaphezu kwe-500, kubalwa phakathi izigwebebe zendabuko ezingcolisayo.

source: Ngo Nhlangulana kwabikwa ukuthi umpathi jele was thola ukwelashwa emva kokuba ahlaselwe isiboshwa.
reference: In June it was reported that the prison's governor received hospital treatment after being attacked by a prisoner.
translation: Ngo Nhlangulana kwencazwe ukuthi umphathi wejele wathola ukunakekelwa emva kokuba ahlaselwe isiboshwa.

source: Futhi ngo Mfumfu ngonyaka odlule ojele abasiza uma kubhikhishwa babizwa kuze bazosiza ukulesimo esihazimisayo lapho abasebenzi bahlaselwa beshawa ngabhola snukha.
reference: And in October last year riot officers were called to the prison to deal with a serious disturbance in which staff were attacked with pool balls.
translation: Futhi ngo Mfumfu ngonyaka odlule ejele labathatha ababesiza uma kubhikhishwa babhekwa ukuze basizo esimweni esibucayi lapho abasebenzi bebhemizelwa beshaya ngamagwebu.

source: Isiphepho Rosa ihlasela iPhoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City hambisana nezikhukhula(Izindawo ezinesomiso ziyohlomula)
reference: Hurricane Rosa Threatening Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City With Flash Flooding (Drought Areas May Benefit)
translation: Isiphepho Rosa sihlasela iPhoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City neminye yendawo ezinesifo (Izindawo ezinesimo ziyohlupeka).

source: Akujwayelekile ukuthi isishingishane sihlasele e Arizona, kodwa ilokho ekuzokwenzeka ekuqaleni kwesonto nge sonto elizayo njengoba amandla ka Hurricane Rosa Eqhubeka esondela ogwadule eNingizimu-ntshonalanga, Uletha izingozi zezikhukhula.
reference: It's rare for a tropical depression to hit Arizona, but that's exactly what's likely to happen early happen early next week as Hurricane Rosa's remaining energy tracks across the Desert Southwest, delivering flash flooding risks.
translation: Akwenzeki kanjalo ukuthi isiphepho sihlasele e Arizona, kodwa lokhu kuzokwenzeka ekuqaleni kwesonto elizayo njengoba amandla kaRosa Rosa aqhubeka esondela ngase Ningizimu-ntshonalanga, zenza izimo ezimbi.

source: Izangoma zezulu sezoikhiphe isexwayiso ukuthi niqaphe izikhukhula ngo Msombuluko nango Lwesibili e Ntshonalanga Arizona ukuya eningizimu kanye empumalanga Nevada, eningizimu-mpumalanga Carlifornia and Utah, kubalwa amadolobha ase Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, and Salt Lake City.
reference: The National Weather Service has already issued flash flood watches for Monday and Tuesday for western Arizona into southern and eastern Nevada, southeastern California and Utah, including the cities of Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, and Salt Lake City.
translation: Izingqqi zokwabelana ngezulu zenze isexwayiso sokuthi niqaphele izimo emva kokudlula ngo Msombuluko neLwesibili eNtshonalanga Arizona kuya eNingizimu kanye nempumalanga Nevada, eNingizimu-mpumalanga kaCalifornia ne Utah, kubalwa namadolobha asePhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, ne Salt Lake City.

source: Rosa ulindekele ukuthi athathe indlela phezu kwe Phoenix ngo Lwesibili, eza ngo Msobuluko ne mvula.
reference: Rosa is expected to take a direct path over Phoenix on Tuesday, approaching late Monday with rain.
translation: Rosa kulindeleke ukuthi athinte indlela phezu kwePhoenix ngoLwesibili, eza ngoMsombuluko nendlula.

source: Izangoma zezulu ePhoenix bathe ku ngomyalezo ka Twitter ukuthi ‚ÄúIzishingishane iziyishumi kuphela ezagcina ziyisi shingishane ngaphakathi kwamakhilomitha awu 200 e Phoenix kusukela ngo 1950!
reference: The National Weather Service in Phoenix noted in a tweet that only "ten tropical cyclones have maintained tropical storm or depression status within 200 miles of Phoenix since 1950!
translation: Izingqqi zokwabelana ngezulu ePhoenix zithi kwi Twitter "Izimo zingama-shumi kuphela ezasala ziyisimo ngaphakathi kwamakhilomitha angu-200 ePhoenix kusukela ngo-1950!

source: UKatrina(1967) waye siphepho ngaphakhathi kwamakhilomitha awu 40 nakumzila wase AZ‚Äù.
reference: Katrina (1967) was a hurricane within 40 miles of the AZ border."
translation: UKatrina (1967) wayesimo ngaphakathi kwamakhilomitha angu-40 namzila wase-AZ".

source: I National Hurricane Center ibikezela 2 kuya 4 amasentimitha emvul, ehambisana namanani awu 6 amasentimitha kwi Mogollan Rim e Arizona.
reference: The latest National Hurricane Center models predict 2 to 4 inches of rainfall, with isolated amounts up to 6 inches in the Mogollon Rim of Arizona.
translation: I-National Hurricane Center ibike 2 kuya ku-4 wamasentimitha emvula, ehambisana namanani angu-6 amasentimitha eMogollan Rim e-Arizona.

source: Kwezinye indawo zogwadule eNingizimu-ntshonalanga kubalwa maphakathine Rockies kanye ne Great Basin zilindekele ukuthi zithole amasentimitha awu 1 to 2, maseziphelele kunga baliselwa ku masentimitha angu 4 umakwenzeka.
reference: Other areas of the Desert Southwest including the central Rockies and the Great Basin are likely to get 1 to 2 inches, with isolated totals up to 4 inches possible.
translation: Kweminye yendawo yaseNingizimu-ntshonalanga kubalwa phakathi kweRockies nase-Great Basin kulindeleke ukuthi ithole amasentimitha angu-1 kuya ku-2, ngokuphelele ingaba amasentimitha angu-4.

source: Ngalezo zingozi zezi khukhula, u Rosa angahle abe isibusiso njengoba ingxenye ihlaselwe isomiso.
reference: For those out of flash flood risk, Rosa's rain may be a blessing since the region is drought-stricken.
translation: Ngalezi zimo, uRosa angaba isibusiso ngoba enye yendawo yahlutshwe yisifo.

source: Noma izikhukhula ziyingozi kakhulu, enye yemvula uzoba isimvuzo ngoba eNingizimu-ntshonalanga ihlaselwe isomiso.
reference: Although flooding is a very serious concern, some of this rainfall will likely be beneficial since the Southwest is currently experiencing drought conditions.
translation: Noma izimo zingangcolisayo, enye yemvula izoba yisibusiso ngoba eNingizimu-ntshonalanga yahlutshwa yisifo.

source: Ngokwe U.S Drougth Monitor( babheka izomiso), amaphesenti angu 40 we Arizona ahlaselwe isomiso, ekwiyona eyisibili enkulu ohlwini, weather.com ibikile.
reference: According to the U.S. Drought Monitor, just over 40 percent of Arizona is experiencing at least extreme drought, the second highest category," weather.com reported.
translation: Ngokwe-U.S Drought Monitor (ababheka izimo), amaphesenti angu-40 weArizona ayisifo, eyona yesibili enkulu, weather.com yabika.

source: Okukuqala, isiphepho uRosa ezodlula phambi kwe Baja California peninsula of Mexico.
reference: First, Hurricane Rosa's path leads to landfall across the Baja California peninsula of Mexico.
translation: Okokuqala, isiphepho uRosa sizodlula phambi kwe-Baja California peninsula yase-Mexico.

source: Rosa, Usanawo amandla esiphepho ngeSonto ekuseni njengoba hamba ngesivinini sama khilomitha angu 85 nge hora, 385 wamakhilomitha eningizimu ne Punta Eugenia, eMexico futhi nyukela enyakatho ngesivinini esingu 12 wakhilomitha nge hora.
reference: Rosa, still at hurricane strength Sunday morning with maximum winds of 85 miles per hour, is 385 miles south of Punta Eugenia, Mexico and moving north at 12 miles per hour.
translation: Rosa, seneminzi yamandla ngeSonto ekuseni njengoba ihamba ngesivinini samakhilomitha angu-85 ngehora, 385 wamakhilomitha eNingizimu ne-Punta Eugenia, eMexico futhi yehla enyakatho ngesivinini esingu-12 wamakhilomitha ngehora.

source: Isiphepho sisondela ngase manzini apholile kwi Pacific futhi ngalokho lindekele ukuthi yehla amandla.
reference: The storm is encountering cooler waters in the Pacific and therefore powering down.
translation: Isiphepho sisondela ngase manzini apholile kwi-Pacific futhi kulindeleke ukuthi yahluleka.

source: Ngakho ke, silindelekile ukuthi siwele eMexico sesiyisiphepho esishisayo esinamandla ntambama noma ngo Msombuluko.
reference: Thus, it's expected to make landfall in Mexico at tropical storm strength in the afternoon or evening on Monday.
translation: Ngakho ke, kulindeleke ukuthi siyehle eMexico sibe yisiphepho esibucayi ntambama noma ngoMsombuluko.

source: Imvula kwidlanzana lezindawo e Mexico ingaba nkulu, ingadala umonakalo ngezikhukhula.
reference: Rainfall across portions of Mexico could be heavy, posing a significant flooding risk.
translation: Imvula kwindawo yase-Mexico ingaba khulu, ingadala umonakalo wezimo.

source: Imvula ihlanga kusukaku 3 kuya 6 wamasentimitha Baja California iyakwi nyakatho-ntshonalanga Sonara, nama sentimitha awu 10 angezeka,‚Äùweather.com reported.
reference: Rainfall totals of 3 to 6 inches are expected from Baja California into northwestern Sonora, with up to 10 inches possible, weather.com reported.
translation: Imvula ihamba kusukela ku-3 kuya ku-6 wamasentimitha eBaja California iyakwi nyakatho-ntshonalanga esonara, amasentimitha angu-10 angezeka, "weather.com yabika".

source: Rosa uzobe esanyukela enyakatho phesheya njenge sphepho ngaphambi kokuba afike emzileni wase Arizona ngezikhathi zasekuseni ngilwesibili eshingishane, izonyuka idlule e Arizona futhi ingene nase ningizimu Utah ngezikhathi zasebusuku ngolwesibili.
reference: Rosa will then track north across Mexico as a tropical storm before reaching the Arizona border in the early morning hours Tuesday as a tropical depression, which will then track up through Arizona and into southern Utah by late Tuesday night.
translation: Rosa izobe sinyukela enyakatho phesheya njengomoya phambi kokuba ifike emzileni wase-Arizona ngezikhathi zasekuseni ngolwesibili esimo, izonyuka idlule e-Arizona futhi ingene nase-ningizimu Utah ngezikhathi zasebusuku ngolwesibili.

source: Ubungozi obukhulu obulindelekile obungadalwa uRosa noma akushiyayo imvula enamandla e Baja California, inyakatho-ntshonalanga Sonara, nase U.S. Ugwadule Southwest, ‚Äú kusho abakwa National Hurricane Cente.r
reference: The main hazard expected from Rosa or its remnants is very heavy rainfall in Baja California, northwestern Sonora, and the U.S. Desert Southwest, the National Hurricane Center said.
translation: Ubungozi obukhulu obulindelekile obungadalwa uRosa noma akushiyayo imvula enamandla eBaja California, enyakatho-ntshonalanga esonara, nase-U.S. ugwadule Southwest," kusho abakwa-National Hurricane Center.

source: Lezi zimvula kulindeleke ukuthi ziveze izikhukhula ezihamba nomphefumulo kanye nezinhlayiya ezigeleza ezikhungweni, nasezindaweni eziphakeme zezintaba.
reference: These rains are expected to produce life-threatening flash flooding and debris flows in the deserts, and landslides in mountainous terrain.
translation: Lezi zimvula kulindeleke ukuthi ziveze izikhukhula ezihamba nomphefumulo kanye nezinhlayiya ezigeleza ezikhungweni, nasezindaweni eziphakeme zezintaba.

source: Ukuhlasela kuka Midsomer: Abane abazame ukubulala baboshiwe
reference: Midsomer Norton attack: Four attempted murder arrests
translation: Ukuhlasela kuka Midsomer: Abane abazame ukubulala baboshiwe

reference: Three teenage boys and a 20-year-old man have been arrested on suspicion of attempted murder after a 16-year-old was found with stab wounds in Somerset.
translation: Abafana abancane no nendoda enimnyaka engu 20 baboshiwe emva kwezinsolo zokuzama ukubalala emva kukuba umfana oneminyaka engu 16 etholakele gweziwe e Somerset.

source: Umfana osemncane utholakele elimele endaweni yase Excelsior Terrac yase Midsomer Norton, ngekhathi zabo 04:00 BST ngomgqibelo.

translation: Umfana osemncane utholakele elimele endaweni yase Excelsior Terrac yase Midsomer Norton, ngekhathi zabo 04:00 BST ngomgqibelo.

source: Uphuthunyise esibhedlela lapho esesimweni esifanele.
reference: He was taken to hospital where he remains in a "stable" condition.
translation: Uphuthunyise esibhedlela lapho esesimweni esifanele.

source: amadoda ayodwa eniminyaka engu 17, amabili anaminyaka engu 18 kanye neyodwa eneminyaka engu 20 aboshiwe phakathi nobusuku eRadstock, Avon nase Somerset kusho amaphoyisa.
reference: A 17-year-old, two 18-year-olds and a 20-year-old man were arrested overnight in the Radstock area, Avon and Somerset Police said.
translation: Amadoda ayodwa eniminyaka engu 17, amabili anaminyaka engu 18 kanye neyodwa eneminyaka engu 20 aboshiwe phakathi nobusuku eRadstock, Avon nase Somerset kusho amaphoyisa.

translation: Amaphoyisa ayacela ukuthi uma kukhona noma ubani ongase abe filimu kumakhalekhukhwini ukuthi kwenzakalani akeze ngaphambili.

source: Trump uthi Kavanaugh ‚Äòhluphekile, ngonya, inzondo‚Äô ye Democractic Party
reference: Trump says Kavanaugh 'suffered, the meanness, the anger' of the Democratic Party
translation: Trump uthi Kavanaugh 'hluphekile, ngonya, inzondo' ye Democractic Party

source: Ivoti likaJaji uKavanaugh livota ukulahla amaqhinga angenabuhlungu nesicasulayo eDemocratic Party, kusho uTrump emhlanganweni wase Wheeling, eNtshonalanga Virginia.
reference: A vote for Judge Kavanaugh is a vote to reject the ruthless and outrageous tactics of the Democratic Party, Trump said at a rally in Wheeling, West Virginia.
translation: Ivoti likaJaji uKavanaugh livota ukulahla amaqhinga angenabuhlungu nesicasulayo eDemocratic Party, kusho uTrump emhlanganweni wase Wheeling, eNtshonalanga Virginia.

source: U-Trump uthe uKavanaugh uye "wahlupheka, intukuthelo" yeDemocratic Party kuyo yonke inqubo yakhe yokuphakanyiswa.
reference: Trump said that Kavanaugh has "suffered the meanness, the anger" of the Democratic Party throughout his nomination process.
translation: U-Trump uthe uKavanaugh uye "wahlupheka, intukuthelo" yeDemocratic Party kuyo yonke inqubo yakhe yokuphakanyiswa.

source: U-Kavanaugh ufakazile ngaphambi kweCongress ngoLwesine, ngokuphikisana nokuphikisana nenkohlakalo evela kuChristine Blasey Ford ukuthi wahlaselwa ngokocansi eminyakeni engamashumi eminyaka edlule lapho esebancane.
reference: Kavanaugh testified before Congress on Thursday, forcefully and emotionally denying an allegation from Christine Blasey Ford that he sexually assaulted her decades ago when they were teenagers.
translation: U-Kavanaugh ufakazile ngaphambi kweCongress ngoLwesine, ngokuphikisana nokuphikisana nenkohlakalo evela kuChristine Blasey Ford ukuthi wahlaselwa ngokocansi eminyakeni engamashumi eminyaka edlule lapho esebancane.

source: Ford also ufakazile ecaleni mayelana nezinsolo zakhe.
reference: Ford also testified at the hearing about her allegation.
translation: Ford futhi ufakazile ecaleni mayelana nezinsolo zakhe.

source: The Mengameli uthe ngo mgqibelo ‚Äú abantu baseMelika khwalithi nesibindi‚Äù sika Kavanaugh ngalolo suku.
reference: The President said on Saturday that the "American people saw the brilliant and quality and courage" of Kavanaugh that day.
translation: Mengameli uthe ngo mgqibelo "abantu baseMelika khwalithi nesibindi" sika Kavanaugh ngalolo suku.

source: ‚ÄúIvoti ukuqinisekisa ukuthi iJaji uKavanaugh livota ukuqinisekisa enye yezingqondo zomthetho ezifezeke kakhulu esikhathini sethu, ummeli onomlando omningi wenkonzo yomphakathi, "etshela isixuku sabantu abaseWest Virginia.
reference: A vote to confirm Judge Kavanaugh is a vote to confirm one of the most accomplished legal minds of our time, a jurist with a sterling record of public service, he told the crowd of West Virginia supporters.
translation: Ivoti ukuqinisekisa ukuthi iJaji uKavanaugh livota ukuqinisekisa enye yezingqondo zomthetho ezifezeke kakhulu esikhathini sethu, ummeli onomlando omningi wenkonzo yomphakathi, etshela isixuku sabantu abaseWest Virginia.

source: Umengameli uthe fahla ngokuphakanyiswa kuka Kavanaugh ngenkathi ekhuluma ngokubaluleka kokufika kwa Republican kukhetho olumaphakathi.
reference: The President obliquely referred to Kavanaugh's nomination while talking about the importance of Republican turnout in the midterm elections.
translation: Umengameli uthe fahla ngokuphakanyiswa kuka Kavanaugh ngenkathi ekhuluma ngokubaluleka kokufika kwa Republican kukhetho olumaphakathi.

source: Amasonto amahlanu ukusuka kwelinye lamakhetho obaluleke kunazo zonke esikhathini sethu sokuphila.

source: ‚ÄùIngakho ngiyonke indawo ngilwela indawo yabaholi abaqotho‚Äù.
reference: That's why I'm all over the place fighting for great candidates.
translation: Ingakho ngiyonke indawo ngilwela indawo yabaholi abaqotho.

reference: Trump argued that Democrats are on a mission to "resist and obstruct."

source: Kushone okungenani abantu abangu -384, abaningi bagugulwe ngamagagasi amakhulu ngenkathi ehlasele amabhisi, ngenkathi kuzamazama umhlaba ne tsunami ishaya kwi sqingi sase Indonesian sase Sulawesi, kusho izikhulu ngomgqibelo.
reference: At least 384 people were killed, many swept away as giant waves crashed onto beaches, when a major earthquake and tsunami hit the Indonesian island of Sulawesi, authorities said on Saturday.

source: Amakhulu abantu ayebuthene emcimbini ogwini edolobheni lasePalu ngoLwesihlanu lapho amagagasi aphakeme ngamamitha angu-18 ehlaselwa osebeni ngehora lesishiyagalolunye, ebulala abaningi ekufeni kwabo futhi ebhubhisa noma yini endleleni.
reference: Hundreds of people had gathered for a festival on the beach in the city of Palu on Friday when waves as high as six meters (18 feet) smashed onshore at dusk, sweeping many to their deaths and destroying anything in their path.
translation: Amakhulu abantu ayebuthene emcimbini ogwini edolobheni lasePalu ngoLwesihlanu lapho amagagasi aphakeme ngamamitha angu-18 ehlaselwa osebeni ngehora lesishiyagalolunye, ebulala abaningi ekufeni kwabo futhi ebhubhisa noma yini endleleni.

source: I-tsunami yalandela ukuzamazama komhlaba okungamamitha angu-7.5.
reference: The tsunami followed a 7.5 magnitude earthquake.
translation: I-tsunami yalandela ukuzamazama komhlaba okungamamitha angu-7.5.

source: Ngesikhathi usongo lwama-tsunami luvela ngoLwesine, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo ogwini futhi abazange baphuthume ngokushesha futhi baba yizisulu, kusho uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, okhulumela i-Indonesia, ekuhlaseleni izinhlekelele eBNPB.
reference: When the tsunami threat arose yesterday, people were still doing their activities on the beach and did not immediately run and they became victims, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, the spokesman for Indonesia's disaster mitigation agency BNPB said in a briefing in Jakarta.
translation: Ngesikhathi usongo lwama-tsunami luvela ngoLwesine, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo ogwini futhi abazange baphuthume ngokushesha futhi baba yizisulu, kusho uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, okhulumela i-Indonesia, ekuhlaseleni izinhlekelele eBNPB.

source: I-tsunami ayizange ifike yodwa, yahudula izimoto, izingodo, izindlu, zishaya yonke into emhlabathini, kusho Nugroho, wanezela ukuthi i-tsunami yayidabula ulwandle oluvulekile ngesivinini esingu-800 kph (497 mph) ngaphambi kokushaya ezihlabathini.
reference: The tsunami didn't come by itself, it dragged cars, logs, houses, it hit everything on land, Nugroho said, adding that the tsunami had traveled across the open sea at speeds of 800 kph (497 mph) before striking the shoreline.
translation: I-tsunami ayizange ifike yodwa, yahudula izimoto, izingodo, izindlu, zishaya yonke into emhlabathini, kusho Nugroho, wanezela ukuthi i-tsunami yayidabula ulwandle oluvulekile ngesivinini esingu-800 kph (497 mph) ngaphambi kokushaya ezihlabathini.

source: Abanye bantu bagibele ezihlahleni bebalekela I-Tsunami, esho.

translation: Abanye bantu bagibele ezihlahleni bebalekela I-Tsunami, esho.

reference: Announcing the change on Twitter on Saturday, he wrote: "The being formally known as Kanye West."
translation: Ukumemezela ushintsho ku-Twitter ngoMgqibelo, wabhala: " Uyaziwa ngokuthi Kanye Kanye."

source: U-West, oneminyaka-41, ibizwe ngegama lisidlaliso Ngesikhathi esithile futhi wasebenzisa i-moniker njengesihloko se-albhamu yakhe yesishiyagalombili, eyakhishwa ngo-Juni.
reference: West, 41, has been nicknamed Ye for some time and used the moniker as the title for his eighth album, which was released in June.
translation: U-West, usanda kwaba nonyaka-41, ibizwe ngegama elisidlaliso Ngesikhathi esithile futhi wasebenzisa i-moniker njengesihloko se-albhamu yakhe yesishiyagalombili, eyakhishwa ngo-Juni.

source: Ushintsho luze ngaphambi kokubonakala kwakhe ngoMgqibelo ebusuku , lapho kulindeleke ukuthi uqale i-albhamu yakhe entsha Yandhi.
reference: The change comes ahead of his appearance on Saturday Night Live, where he is expected to launch his new album Yandhi.
translation: Ushintsho luze ngaphambi kokubonakala kwakhe ngoMgqibelo ebusuku, lapho kulindeleke ukuthi uqale i-albhamu yakhe entsha Yandhi.

source: Ubeke umculi u-Ariana Grande embukisweni oye wakhansela "ngezizathu eziphathelene nomoya wakhe ," kusho umsunguli wohlelo .
reference: He replaces singer Ariana Grande on the show who cancelled for "emotional reasons," the show's creator said.
translation: Ubeke umculi u-Ariana Grande embukisweni oye wakhansela "ngezizathu eziphathelene nomoya wakhe," kusho umsunguli wohlelo.

source: Kanye nokuba yisifinyezo segama lakhe lobuchwepheshe lamanje, u-West usho ngaphambili ukuthi leli gama linencazelo engokwenkolo kuye.
reference: As well as being an abbreviation of his current professional name, West has previously said the word has religious significance for him.
translation: Kanye nokuba yisifinyezo segama lakhe lobuchwepheshe lamanje, u-West usho ngaphambili ukuthi leli gama linencazelo engokwenkolo kuye.

source: Ngiyakholwa ukuthi 'ye' igama elivame ukusetshenziswa kakhulu eBhayibhelini, futhi eBhayibhelini kusho 'wena,' kusho uWest ngasekuqaleni konyaka, ekhuluma ngesihloko sakhe se-albhamu nomsakazo u-Big Boy.
reference: I believe 'ye' is the most commonly used word in the Bible, and in the Bible it means 'you,' West said earlier this year, discussing his album title with radio host Big Boy.
translation: Ngiyakholwa ukuthi 'ye' igama elivame ukusetshenziswa kakhulu eBhayibhelini, futhi eBhayibhelini kusho 'wena,' kusho uWest ngasekuqaleni konyaka, ekhuluma ngesihloko sakhe se-albhamu nomsakazo u-Big Boy.

source: Ungomunye wabalobi abadumile ukushintsha igama labo.
reference: He is one of a number of famous rappers to change their name.
translation: Ungomunye wabalobi abadumile ukushintsha igama labo.

source: USean Combs uye waziwa ngokuyinhloko njengoPuff Daddy, uP. Diddy noma uDididy, kodwa kulo nyaka wamemezela ukuthi uthanda ukuthandwa ngamagama ethi Love and Brother Love     .
reference: Sean Combs has been variously known as Puff Daddy, P. Diddy or Diddy, but this year announced his preference for the names Love and Brother Love.
translation: USean Combs uye waziwa ngokuyinhloko njengoPuff Daddy, uP. Diddy noma uDididy, kodwa kulo nyaka wamemezela ukuthi uthanda ukuthandwa ngamagama ethi Love and Brother Love.

source: Lowo owayengumhlanganyeli waseNtshonalanga, uJAY-Z, uyenzile noma ngaphandle kwezingqungquthela nezihloko.
reference: A former West collaborator, JAY-Z, has also made do with or without a hyphen and capitals.
translation: Lowo owayengumhlanganyeli waseNtshonalanga, uJAY-Z, uyenzile noma ngaphandle kwezingqungquthela nezihloko.

source: Ama-AMLO aseMexico ayifuni ukusebenzisa impi ngokumelene nezakhamuzi
reference: Mexico's AMLO vows not to use military against civilians
translation: Ama-AMLO aseMexico ayifuni ukusebenzisa impi ngokumelene nezakhamuzi.

source: UMongameli waseMexico okhethwe u-Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador uye wathembisa ukuthi angeke asebenzise ibutho lempi ngokumelene nezakhamuzi njengoba leli zwe lisondela eminyakeni engu-50 yokuhlaselwa igazi ngokumelene nabafundi.
reference: Mexican President-elect Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador has vowed to never use military force against civilians as the country approaches the 50th anniversary of a bloody reprisal against students.
translation: UMongameli waseMexico okhethwe u-Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador uye wathembisa ukuthi angeke asebenzise ibutho lempi ngokumelene nezakhamuzi njengoba leli zwe lisondela eminyakeni engu-50 yokuhlaselwa igazi ngokumelene nabafundi.

source: I-Lopez Obrador yethembisa ngoMgqibelo eTlatelolco Plaza ukuba "ungalokothi usebenzise amasosha ukucindezela abantu baseMexico."
reference: Lopez Obrador promised Saturday at Tlatelolco Plaza to "never ever use the military to repress the Mexican people."
translation: I-Lopez Obrador yethembisa ngoMgqibelo eTlatelolco Plaza ukuba "ungalokothi usebenzise amasosha ukucindezela abantu baseMexico."

source: Amaphoyisa asjuntshwe ekuboniseni okunokuthula e-plaza ngo-Okthoba 2, 1968, ebulala abantu abangaba ngu-300 ngaleso sikhathi lapho ukunyakaza kwabafundi be-leftist bekugxila kulo lonke elaseLatin America.
reference: Troops fired on a peaceful demonstration at the plaza on Oct. 2, 1968, killing as many as 300 people at a time when leftist student movements were taking root throughout Latin America.
translation: Amaphoyisa asjuntshwe ekuboniseni okunokuthula e-plaza ngo-Okthoba 2, 1968, ebulala abantu abangaba ngu-300 ngaleso sikhathi lapho ukunyakaza kwabafundi be-leftist bekugxila kulo lonke elaseLatin America.

source: I-Lopez Obrador ithembise ukusekela abaseMexico abasha ngokunikeza izinsizakalo zanyangazonke kulabo abafunda nokuvula amanyuvesi amaningi omphakathi mahhala.
reference: Lopez Obrador has pledged to support young Mexicans by giving monthly subsidies to those who study and opening more free public universities.
translation: I-Lopez Obrador ithembise ukusekela abaseMexico abasha ngokunikeza izinsizakalo zanyangazonke kulabo abafunda nokuvula amanyuvesi amaningi omphakathi mahhala.

source: Uthi ukungasebenzi kanye nokungabi namathuba okufunda kudonsela intsha emacimbini yobugebengu.
reference: He has said that unemployment and a lack of educational opportunities draws youth to criminal gangs.
translation: Uthi ukungasebenzi kanye nokungabi namathuba okufunda kudonsela intsha emacimbini yobugebengu.

source: U.S kumele inyuse uxhaso lwe A.I.
reference: U.S. should double A.I. funding
translation: U.S kumele inyuse uxhaso lwe A.I.

source: Njengoba i-China isebenza ngokwengeziwe kwi I.A, i-U.S. kufanele iphinde kabili inani elisebenzisayo ucwaningo emkhakheni, kusho umtshali-zimali no-AI, uKai-Fu Lee, osebenzele i-Google, i-Microsoft ne-Apple.
reference: As China becomes more active in artificial intelligence, the U.S. should double the amount it spends on research in the field, says investor and AI practitioner Kai-Fu Lee, who has worked for Google, Microsoft and Apple.
translation: Njengoba i-China isebenza ngokwengeziwe kwi I.A, i-U.S. kufanele iphinde kabili inani elisebenzisayo ucwaningo emkhakheni, kusho umtshali-zimali no-AI, uKai-Fu Lee, osebenzele i-Google, i-Microsoft ne-Apple.

source: Amazwana avela emva kwezinhlangothi ezehlukene zombuso wase-U.S. wenze smemezelo e-AI, njengoba nje jikelele we-U.S. ingekho isu elihlelekile le-AI.
reference: The comments come after various parts of the U.S. government have made AI announcements, even as the U.S. overall lacks a formal AI strategy.
translation: Amazwana avela emva kwezinhlangothi ezehlukene zombuso wase-U.S. wenze smemezelo e-AI, njengoba nje jikelele we-U.S. ingekho isu elihlelekile le-AI.

source: Phakathi naleso sikhathi, i-China yaqalisa uhlelo layo ngonyaka odlule: ihlose ukuba u numba .1 ku-AI  ngo-2030.
reference: Meanwhile, China introduced its plan last year: it's aiming to be No.1 in AI innovation by 2030.
translation: Phakathi naleso sikhathi, i-China yaqalisa uhlelo layo ngonyaka odlule: ihlose ukuba u numba .1 ku-AI  ngo-2030.

source: Isabelomali sokucwaninga nge-AI sizoba yisiqalo esihle, ngoba nje wonke amanye amazwe asekude kakhulu ngemuva kwe-U.S., futhi sifuna ukuphumelela okulandelayo ku-AI, kusho uLee.
reference: Double the AI research budget would be a good start, given that all other countries are so much farther behind U.S., and we're looking for the next breakthrough in AI, said Lee.
translation: Isabelomali sokucwaninga nge-AI sizoba yisiqalo esihle, ngoba nje wonke amanye amazwe asekude kakhulu ngemuva kwe-U.S., futhi sifuna ukuphumelela okulandelayo ku-AI, kusho uLee.

source: Ukuphikisana nokuxhaswa kwemali kungaphindaphinda amathuba okuba kwenziwe ukufezeka okukhulu kwe-AI e-U.S., u-Lee utshele i-CNBC ekuxoxweni kuleli sonto.
reference: Doubling funding could double the chances that the next big AI achievement will be made in the U.S., Lee told CNBC in an interview this week.
translation: Ukuphikisana nokuxhaswa kwemali kungaphindaphinda amathuba okuba kwenziwe ukufezeka okukhulu kwe-AI e-U.S., u-Lee utshele i-CNBC ekuxoxweni kuleli sonto.

source: Lee, incwadi yakhe ethi "AI Superpowers:   I-China, i-Silicon Valley ne-New World Order "yashicilelwa kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, Umphathi we-Sinovation Ventures, eyitshale kwenye yezinkampani ezivelele kakhulu ze-AI eChina, Face ++.
reference: Lee, whose book "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" was published this month by Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, is CEO of Sinovation Ventures, which has invested in one of the most prominent AI companies in China, Face++.
translation: Lee, incwadi yakhe ethi "AI Superpowers: I-China, i-Silicon Valley ne-New World Order" yashicilelwa kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, Umphathi we-Sinovation Ventures, eyitshale kwenye yezinkampani ezivelele kakhulu ze-AI eChina, Face ++.

source: Eminyakeni yama-1980s eCarnegie Mellon University wasebenza ohlelweni lwe-AI olusha umdlali wase-Othello waseMelika obala kakhulu, futhi kamuva waba ngumphathi we-Microsoft Research noMongameli wegatsha lase-Google laseChina
reference: In the 1980s at Carnegie Mellon University he worked on an AI system that beat the highest-ranked American Othello player, and later he was an executive at Microsoft Research and president of Google's China branch.
translation: Eminyakeni yama-1980s eCarnegie Mellon University wasebenza ohlelweni lwe-AI olusha umdlali wase-Othello waseMelika obala kakhulu, futhi kamuva waba ngumphathi we-Microsoft Research noMongameli wegatsha lase-Google laseChina.

source: U-Lee wavuma ukuncintisana kobuchwepheshe be-U.S. wangaphambilini njengoMnyango wezokuPhepha oPhezulu wezokuPhepha weRobotics Challenge futhi wabuza ukuthi ngabe olandelayo uzoba nini, ukuze asize ukubona izimboni ezilandelayo.
reference: Lee acknowledged previous U.S. government technology competitions like the Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge and asked when the next one would be, in order to help identify the next visionaries.
translation: U-Lee wavuma ukuncintisana kobuchwepheshe be-U.S. wangaphambilini njengoMnyango wezokuPhepha oPhezulu wezokuPhepha weRobotics Challenge futhi wabuza ukuthi ngabe olandelayo uzoba nini, ukuze asize ukubona izimboni ezilandelayo.

source: Abacwaningi base-U.S. ngokuvamile kufanele basebenze kanzima ukuze banqobe izibonelelo zikahulumeni, kusho uLee..
reference: Researchers in the U.S. often have to work hard in order to win government grants, Lee said.
translation: Abacwaningi base-U.S. ngokuvamile kufanele basebenze kanzima ukuze banqobe izibonelelo zikahulumeni, kusho uLee..

source: Akusikho iChina esusa abaholi bezemfundo; yizinkampani, kusho u-Lee.
reference: It's not China that is taking away the academic leaders; it's the corporates, Lee said.
translation: Akusikho iChina esusa abaholi bezemfundo; yizinkampani, kusho u-Lee.

source: I-Facebook, i-Google nezinye izinkampani zobuchwepheshe zisebenzise izikhanyiso ezivela emanyuvesi ukuze zisebenze ku-AI eminyakeni kamuva.
reference: Facebook, Google and other technology companies have hired luminaries from universities to work on AI in recent years.
translation: I-Facebook, i-Google nezinye izinkampani zobuchwepheshe zisebenzise izikhanyiso ezivela emanyuvesi ukuze zisebenze ku-AI eminyakeni kamuva.

source: U-Lee wathi izinguquko zomgomo wokufuduka zingasiza nase-U.S. ukuqinisa imizamo yawo ye-AI.
reference: Lee said immigration policy changes could also help the U.S. bolster its AI efforts.
translation: U-Lee wathi izinguquko zomgomo wokufuduka zingasiza nase-U.S. ukuqinisa imizamo yawo ye-AI.

source: Ngicabanga ukuthi amakhadi aluhlaza kufanele ahlinzekwe ngokuzenzakalelayo kuma-PhD ku-AI, usho kanje.
reference: I think green cards should automatically be offered to PhD's in AI, he said.
translation: Ngicabanga ukuthi amakhadi aluhlaza kufanele ahlinzekwe ngokuzenzakalelayo kuma-PhD ku-AI, usho kanje.

source: UMkhandlu Wase-China WaseChina ukhiphe Sokuthuthukisa Intuthuko Yenhlakanipho Yomhlahlandlela olandelayo we-Generation Intelligence Intelligence Plan ngoJulayi 2017.
reference: China's State Council issued its Next Generation Artificial Intelligence Development Plan in July 2017.
translation: UMkhandlu Wase-China WaseChina ukhiphe Sokuthuthukisa Intuthuko Yenhlakanipho Yomhlahlandlela olandelayo we-Generation Intelligence Intelligence Plan ngoJulayi 2017.

source: China National Natural Science Foundation ikhiphe imali kubantu ezikhungweni zokufunda ezifana nalendlela i-Nationla Science Foundation nezinye ezikhipha ngayo imali kubacwaningi, kodwa ikhwalithi yomsebenzi wezifundiswa lincane e-China, kusho Lee.
reference: China's National Natural Science Foundation provides funding to people at academic institutions similar to the way that the National Science Foundation and other government organizations dole out money to U.S. researchers, but the quality of academic work is lower in China, Lee said.
translation: China National Natural Science Foundation ikhiphe imali kubantu ezikhungweni zokufunda ezifana nalendlela i-Nationla Science Foundation nezinye ezikhipha ngayo imali kubacwaningi, kodwa ikhwalithi yomsebenzi wezifundiswa lincane e-China, kusho Lee.

source: Ekuqaleniu konyaka. Defense Department eisingule i Joint Artificial Intelligence Center, ekumele ihlanganise ophathini bakulo mkhakha kanye nezifundiswa, futhi ne White House imemezele ukwakhiwa kwekomidi elikhethekile le Artificial Intelligence.
reference: Earlier this year the U.S. Defense Department established a Joint Artificial Intelligence Center, which is meant to involve partners from industry and academia, and the White House announced the formation of Select Committee on Artificial Intelligence.
translation: Ekuqaleniu konyaka. Defense Department eisingule i Joint Artificial Intelligence Center, ekumele ihlanganise ophathini bakulo mkhakha kanye nezifundiswa, futhi ne White House imemezele ukwakhiwa kwekomidi elikhethekile le Artificial Intelligence.

source: Kulenyanga  i-DARPA imemezele $2 billion kuhlelo olubizwa AI Next.
reference: And this month DARPA announced a $2 billion investment in an initiative called AI Next.
translation: Kulenyanga  i-DARPA imemezele $2 billion kuhlelo olubizwa AI Next.

source: I NSF, itshale ngaphuze kuka $100 million ngonyaka kucwaningo lwe AI .
reference: As for the NSF, it currently invests more than $100 million per year in AI research.
translation: I NSF, itshale ngaphuze kuka $100 million ngonyaka kucwaningo lwe AI .

source: Kuse njalo, Umthetho wase Melika wokwakha iNational Security Commision nge Artificial Intelligence iyakakabi nomnyakazo.
reference: Meanwhile, U.S. legislation that sought to create a National Security Commission on Artificial Intelligence has not seen action in months.
translation: Kuse njalo, Umthetho wase Melika wokwakha iNational Security Commision nge Artificial Intelligence iyakakabi nomnyakazo.

source: Abantu base Macedonia bayavota ukuthi balishintshe yini igama lezwe noma cha.
reference: Macedonians vote in referendum on whether to change country's name
translation: Abantu base Macedonia bayavota ukuthi balishintshe yini igama lezwe noma cha.

source: Abantu base Macedonia bavotile nge- Sonto ukuthi bagiuqule igama lezwe libe ‚ÄúRepublic of North Macedonia,‚Äù isiqhumo esizoxazulula ingxabano nezwe lase Greece eseli vimbe ubulunga be European Union ne NATO.
reference: The people of Macedonia voted in a referendum on Sunday on whether to change its name to "Republic of North Macedonia," a move that would resolve a decades-old dispute with Greece which had blocked its membership bids for the European Union and NATO.
translation: Abantu base Macedonia bavotile nge- Sonto ukuthi bagiuqule igama lezwe libe "Republic of North Macedonia," isiqhumo esizoxazulula ingxabano nezwe lase Greece eseli vimbe ubulunga be European Union ne NATO.

source: I-Greece, elibiza Macedonia negsifundazwe sayo, liyaqhubeka lithi omakhelwane babo abasenyakatho komzila wabo bafuna indawo yabo futhi bafuna ukungena kwio NATO and EU.
reference: Greece, which has a province called Macedonia, maintains that its northern neighbor's name represents a claim on its territory and has vetoed its entrance into NATO and the EU.
translation: I-Greece, elibiza Macedonia negsifundazwe sayo, liyaqhubeka lithi omakhelwane babo abasenyakatho komzila wabo bafuna indawo yabo futhi bafuna ukungena kwio NATO and EU.

source: Ohulumeni bobabili benza ngesivumelwane nge-gama elibhekiwe, kodwa abanye bathi ukushintsha leli gama kusho ukubukela phansi amasiko iningi labantu base Macedonia aba Slavic
reference: The two governments struck a deal in June based on the proposed new name, but nationalist opponents argue the change would undermine the ethnic identity of Macedonia's Slavic majority population.
translation: Ohulumeni bobabili benza ngesivumelwane nge-gama elibhekiwe, kodwa abanye bathi ukushintsha leli gama kusho ukubukela phansi amasiko iningi labantu base Macedonia aba Slavic

source: Umengameli Gjorge Ivanov uthe ngeke avote futhi ukubhikisha ukuvota kwenza kube manqikanqika ukuthi 50 percent wabantu bazofika kuze loluketho lube semthethweni.
reference: President Gjorge Ivanov has said he will not be voting in the referendum and a boycott campaign has cast doubts on whether turnout will meet the minimum 50 percent required for the referendum to be valid.
translation: Umengameli Gjorge Ivanov uthe ngeke avote futhi ukubhikisha ukuvota kwenza kube manqikanqika ukuthi 50 percent wabantu bazofika kuze loluketho lube semthethweni.

source: Umbuzo kwi phepha lokuvota lifundeka kanje: " Uvumelana nobulungu be NATO ne EU ngesivumelwano se Greece."
reference: The question on the referendum ballot read: "Are you for NATO and EU membership with acceptance of the agreement with Greece."
translation: Umbuzo kwi phepha lokuvota lifundeka kanje: " Uvumelana nobulungu be NATO ne EU ngesivumelwano se Greece."

source: Abavumelana nokushintshwa gama, kubalwa Ndunankulu Zoran Zaev, uthi iyona into oyikhokha ngoku vuma izinhlaka izifana ne EU ne Nato kwi Macedonia, amanye amazwe avele ngohlakazeka kwe Yugoslavia
reference: Supporters of the name change, including Prime Minister Zoran Zaev, argue that it is a price worth paying to pursue admission into bodies such as the EU and NATO for Macedonia, one of the countries to emerge from the collapse of Yugoslavia.
translation: Abavumelana nokushintshwa gama, kubalwa Ndunankulu Zoran Zaev, uthi iyona into oyikhokha ngoku vuma izinhlaka izifana ne EU ne Nato kwi Macedonia, amanye amazwe avele ngohlakazeka kwe Yugoslavia

source: Ngifikile izolo ukuzovotela kusas lezwe lethu, ukuze intsha yaseMacedonia izophila kahle ngaphansi kwe-umbrella ye-European Union ngoba kuchaza izimpilo zethu zonke ezipheile, kusho u-Olivera Georgijevska, 79, eSkopje.
reference: I came today to vote for the future of the country, for young people in Macedonia so they can be live freely under the umbrella of the European Union because it means safer lives for all of us, said Olivera Georgijevska, 79, in Skopje.
translation: Ngifikile izolo ukuzovotela kusas lezwe lethu, ukuze intsha yaseMacedonia izophila kahle ngaphansi kwe-umbrella ye-European Union ngoba kuchaza izimpilo zethu zonke ezipheile, kusho u-Olivera Georgijevska, 79, eSkopje.

source: Noma kungabophi ngokomthetho, amalunga anele ephalamende bathe isinqumo sevoti bazosamukela.
reference: Although not legally binding, enough members of parliament have said they will abide by the vote's outcome to make it decisive.
translation: Noma kungabophi ngokomthetho, amalunga anele ephalamende bathe isinqumo sevoti bazosamukela.

source: Ushintsho uzodinga izinxenye ezimbili kwezintantathu ukudla umhlanganio ephalamende.
reference: The name change would requires a two-thirds majority in parliament.
translation: Ushintsho uzodinga izinxenye ezimbili kwezintantathu ukudla umhlanganio ephalamende.

source: Ikhomishane yokuvota yezwe ithi ibingekho imibiko ebikiwe yokungahambisani ngo 1 p.m.
reference: The state election commission said there had been no reports of irregularities by 1 p.m.
translation: Ikhomishane yokuvota yezwe ithi ibingekho imibiko ebikiwe yokungahambisani ngo 1 p.m.

source: Kodwa, ibisolokhu iku 16 percent, kuno 34 percent wokuvota okwedlule kwasephalamende ngo 2016 ngenkathi  66 percent wabavotiababhalisile befaka amavoti abo.
reference: However, turnout stood at only 16 percent, compared to 34 percent in last parliamentary election in 2016 when 66 percent of the registered voters cast their ballot.
translation: Kodwa, ibisolokhu iku 16 percent, kuno 34 percent wokuvota okwedlule kwasephalamende ngo 2016 ngenkathi  66 percent wabavotiababhalisile befaka amavoti abo.

source: Ngiphumile ukuzovota ngenxa yezingane zami, indawo yethu e-Europe, kusho uGjose Tanevski, 62, umvoti kwidolobha, Skopje.
reference: I came out to vote because of my children, our place is in Europe, said Gjose Tanevski, 62, a voter in the capital, Skopje.
translation: Ngiphumile ukuzovota ngenxa yezingane zami, indawo yethu e-Europe, kusho uGjose Tanevski, 62, umvoti kwidolobha, Skopje.

source: I-PM yaseMacedonia uZoran Zaev, umkakhe uZorica nendodana yakhe uDushko bavotele ireferendum eMacedonia ngokushintsha igama lezwe elizovula indlela ukujoyina iNATO  neEuropean Union eStrumica, eMacedonia Septhemba 30, 2018.
reference: Macedonia's PM Zoran Zaev, his wife Zorica and his son Dushko cast their ballot for the referendum in Macedonia on changing the country's name that would open the way for it to join NATO and the European Union in Strumica, Macedonia September 30, 2018.
translation: I-PM yaseMacedonia uZoran Zaev, umkakhe uZorica nendodana yakhe uDushko bavotele ireferendum eMacedonia ngokushintsha igama lezwe elizovula indlela ukujoyina iNATO  neEuropean Union eStrumica, eMacedonia Septhemba 30, 2018.

source: Phambikwephalamende eSkopje, uVladimir Kavardarkov, 54, belungisa isigcawu futhi edonsanezihlalo phambi kwamatendeabekwe yilabo abazomelana nereferendum.

reference: Sadly today, it is not the tone of many meetings and the promise of "kinder, gentler" politics has long been forgotten if, indeed, it ever began.

source: Sekuya ngokuya kucaca ukuthi imibono eyahlukene ayisavumelekile eqenjini Labasebenzi nanokuthi imibono yahlulelwa ngokuthi yamukelekile yini kubaholi beqembu.
reference: It has become increasingly apparent that differing views are not tolerated in the Labour party and every opinion is judged on whether it is acceptable to the party leadership.
translation: Kusafika ukukhanya ukuthi imibono eyahlukene ayikwazi ukuhlala eqenjini Lezisebenzi futhi ukuthi imibono ihluliwe ukuthi iyavunyelwa yini kubaholi beqembu.

source: Loku kuqale ngemva nje kokuthi u-Jeremy abe umholi, nakozakwethu ebengithi sinemibono efanayo yezepolitiki nabo sebebheke ukuthi ngijike ngithathe izinhlangothi ebengingeke ngivumelane nazo - kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ezokuphepha kwesizwe noma esemakethe engayodwana ye-EU.
reference: This started shortly after Jeremy became leader, as colleagues with whom I had previously thought I shared a similar political outlook began expecting me to do a U-turn and take positions I would never have otherwise agreed with - whether on national security or the EU single market.
translation: Lokhu kwaqala emva kokuba u-Jeremy abe umholi, namaqawe ethu abengithi sinengqondo efanayo ngepolitiki sebe sengichithwe ukuba ngithathe izindlela engingazange ngivumelane nazo - ngaphandle kokuthi zibe ngezokuphepha kwesizwe noma zibe zama-EU.

source: Noma yinini lapho ngikhuluma emphakathini - akusabalulekile nokuthi ngithini - kuzoza igagasi lokuhlukunyezwa ezingosini zokuxhumana lithi angikhishwe, lichitha ipolitiki engachemile, lithi akumelwe ngibe seqenjini Labasebenzi.
reference: Whenever I speak publicly - and it doesn't really matter what I say - there follows a tirade of abuse on social media calling for deselection, denouncing the politics of the centre, telling me I should not be in the Labour party.
translation: Noma ngingasiniki ithuba emphakathini - akusabalulekile nokuthi ngichaza - kuza kuba umkhankaso wokuntshontsha wathi ngingasiniki ithuba, wachitha ipolitiki engingavikeli, wathi angidingeki eqenjini Lezisebenzi.

source: Futhi akusimina kuphela osebhekene nalokhu.
reference: And that is not just my experience.
translation: Futhi akufani nami kuphela okwenzayo lokhu.

source: Nakanjani, ngiyazi ukuthi ngibe nenhlanhla kunozakwethu ngoba izinkulumo ezibhekiselwe k‚Äômina zisathanda ukuba ngepolitiki.
reference: Indeed, I know I am more fortunate than some of my colleagues as the comments directed at me tend to be political.
translation: Noma kunjalo, ngiyazi ukuthi ngibe nelungelo kunye namaqawe ngoba izincazelo zami zisetshenziswa epolitiking.

source: Ngisamangele ekutheni labozakwethu basayibambile em‚Äôsebenzini nasekuzimiseleni kwabo bangazinyezi yize bebhekene nokucwasa okungokobulili noma okobuhlanga.
reference: I am in awe of the professionalism and determination of those colleagues who face a torrent of sexist or racist abuse every day but never shy away.
translation: Ngikhathazekile ukuthi lama qhawe ahlala embonini nasekwenziweni bese bengasiniki ithuba noma bechaza ngobuhlanga noma ngendlela.

source: Enye yezinto ezidikibalisa kakhulu kulenkathi yezepolitiki indlela amazinga okuhlukumeza asevele abangajwayelekile.
reference: One of the most disappointing aspects of this era of politics is how levels of abuse have become normalised.
translation: Enye yezinto ezingqamukayo kakhulu kwezipolotiki yindlela amacala okuchitha asivikela.

source: Jeremy Corbyn wathi ngeviki eliphelile i-Labour party kumelwe ibeke isiko lwemingcele.
reference: Jeremy Corbyn claimed last week that the Labour party should foster a culture of tolerance.
translation: Jeremy Corbyn wathi ngeviki eliphelile i-Labour kumele ibeke umlando womgomo.

source: Iqiniso liwukuthi asisasliona leli sonto elikhulu futhi engazethembi noma ukushintsha kwemithetho yokutomula iqembu liya lincipha.
reference: The reality is we are no longer that broad church and with every "no-confidence" motion or change of selection rules the party becomes narrower.
translation: Iqiniso liwukuthi asisasliona leli sonto elikhulu futhi engazethembi noma ukushintsha kwemithetho yokutomula iqembu liya lincipha.

source: Benginezeluleko eziningi eminyakeni emibili edlule nginxuswa ukuba ngizehlise, ngingakhulumi kakhulu futhi kuzoba ‚Äúsengilungile.‚Äù
reference: I have had lots of advice over the past two years urging me to keep my head down, not to be so vocal and then I would "be all right."
translation: Benginezeluleko eziningi eminyakeni emibili edlule nginxuswa ukuba ngizehlise, ngingakhulumi kakhulu futhi kuzoba "sengilungile."

source: Kodwa akusikhona lokho engikuzele kwezepolitiki.
reference: But that is not what I came into politics to do.
translation: Kodwa akusikhona lokho engikuzele kwezepolitiki.

source: Selokhu ngazihlangazisa ne-Labour eminyakeni engu-32 edlule njengomfundi, ngacasulwa  uhulumeni Thatcher ngokunganki ngokuthi ashiye amagubi esokole ecekeleke phansi, bengifuna ukuletha izinkonzo zomphakathi ezingcono kakhulu kulabo abazidinga kakhulu ‚Äì mhlawumbe njengohulumeni wendawo noma njenongqongqoshe kahulumeni.
reference: Ever since I joined Labour 32 years ago as a school pupil, provoked by the Thatcher government's neglect that had left my comprehensive school classroom literally falling down, I've sought to champion better public services for those who need them most - whether as a local councillor or government minister.
translation: Selokhu ngazihlangazisa ne-Labour eminyakeni engu-32 edlule njengomfundi, ngacasulwa uhulumeni Thatcher ngokunganki ngokuthi ashiye amagubi esokole ecekeleke phansi, bengifuna ukuletha izinkonzo zomphakathi ezingcono kakhulu kulabo abazidinga kakhulu ‚Äì mhlawumbe njengohulumeni wendawo noma njenongqongqoshe kahulumeni.

source: Angikaze ngizifihle kwezepolitiki, kuhlanganise nasokhethelweni lokugcina.
reference: I have never hidden my politics, including at the last election.
translation: Angikaze ngizifihle kwezepolitiki, kuhlanganise nasokhethelweni lokugcina.

source: Akukho muntu e-Nottingham East nganoma iyiphi indlela ongadideka mayelana ngomthetho yokuma kwamia kanye nezindawo zokuphikisana ngobuholi bamanje.
reference: No one in Nottingham East could have been in any way confused about my policy positions and areas of disagreement with the current leadership.
translation: Akukho muntu e-Nottingham East nganoma iyiphi indlela ongadideka mayelana ngomthetho yokuma kwamia kanye nezindawo zokuphikisana ngobuholi bamanje.

source: Kulabo abakhutheze uhambo ngoLwesihlanu, konke engingakusho ukuthi lapho izwe liqhubekela phambili kwi- Brexit lokho kuyolimza abaninikhaya, amabhizinisi kanye nenkonzo yethu yomphakathi, angifisi ukuchitha isikhathi kanye namandla ngokuqotho bami kumholi we- Labour party.
reference: To those who promoted the motion on Friday, all I would say is that when the country is ploughing towards a Brexit that will hurt households, businesses and our public services, I do not understand the desire to waste time and energy on my loyalty to the Labour party leader.
translation: Kulabo abakhutheze uhambo ngoLwesihlanu, konke engingakusho ukuthi lapho izwe liqhubekela phambili kwi- Brexit lokho kuyolimza abaninikhaya, amabhizinisi kanye nenkonzo yethu yomphakathi, angifisi ukuchitha isikhathi kanye namandla ngokuqotho bami kumholi we- Labour party.

source: Ngempela kodwa munye umyalezo enginawo awuqndile kw-Nottingham Momentum, kwabangikimi, kungaba amalungu e- Labour noma cha: Ngiyaziqenya ngokunikhonza kanti futhi ngiyathembisa ukuthi angeke kube bikho ukusongelwa noma ngokwezepolitiki okuzongivimela ukwenza engikukholelwa ukuthi kuzoba okungcono kini nonke.
reference: But really the one message I have is not to Nottingham Momentum, it is to my constituents, whether Labour members or not: I am proud to serve you and I promise that no amount of deselection threats or political expediency will deter me from acting in what I believe are the best interests of you all.
translation: Ngempela kodwa munye umyalezo enginawo awuqndile kw-Nottingham Momentum, kwabangikimi, kungaba amalungu e- Labour noma cha: Ngiyaziqenya ngokunikhonza kanti futhi ngiyathembisa ukuthi angeke kube bikho ukusongelwa noma ngokwezepolitiki okuzongivimela ukwenza engikukholelwa ukuthi kuzoba okungcono kini nonke.

source: Leslie uyi-MP  wase-Nottingham East
reference: Chris Leslie is MP for Nottingham East
translation: Leslie uyi-MP  wase-Nottingham East

source: Ayr ina-38- 17 Melrose: Ayr engakaze ihlulwe ihlezi phezulu
reference: Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: Unbeaten Ayr go top
translation: Ayr ina-38- 17 Melrose: Ayr engakaze ihlulwe ihlezi phezulu

source: Ama-tries amibili akamuva ayicezukisile imiphumela yokugcina, kodwa akungatshazwa Ayr iyakufanelekela ukunconywa kulo mdlalo wanamuhla  obe muhle kakhulu  we-Tennent's Premiership.

reference: We've been tested over our games this far, and we're still unbeaten, so I have to be happy, he said.

translation: Robyn Christie wase Melrose uthe: " udumo ku Ayr, basebenzise wonke amathuba ukwedlula thina."

source: I-try yemizuzu engu-14 ka Grant Anderson ifakwe ngu- Frazier Climo, ebeka phambili Ayr, kodwa, cap Rory Hughes wesi-soctland uthole ikhadi eliphuzi, yakhululwa emdlalweni Warriors, okubangele Melrose  wazenzela ngamaqaku futhi  Jason Baggot ubambisise wonke ama-try.
reference: Grant Anderson's 14th minute try, converted by Frazier Climo, put Ayr in front, but, a yellow card for Scotland cap Rory Hughes, released for the game by Warriors, allowed Melrose to make numbers tell and Jason Baggot grabbed an unconverted try.
translation: I-try yemizuzu engu-14 ka Grant Anderson ifakwe ngu- Frazier Climo, ebeka phambili Ayr, kodwa, cap Rory Hughes wesi-soctland uthole ikhadi eliphuzi, yakhululwa emdlalweni Warriors, okubangele Melrose  wazenzela ngamaqaku futhi  Jason Baggot ubambisise wonke ama-try.

source: Climo ubanagele Ayr yahamba phambili ngepenadi, ngaphambi nje, kwesiwombe sokuqala, ufake i-solo try ukwenza u-17-5 ku Ayr ngekhefu.

translation: Climo ubanagele Ayr yahamba phambili ngepenadi, ngaphambi nje, kwesiwombe sokuqala, ufake i-solo try ukwenza u-17-5 ku Ayr ngekhefu.

reference: There was then a lengthy hold-up for a serious injury to Ruaridh Knott, who was stretchered off, and from the restart, Ayr surged further ahead through a Stafford McDowall try, converted by Climo.
translation: Kube sekukhona ukubanjwa kwesikhathi ngenxa yokulimala kanzima Ruaridh Knott, wakhishelwa ngaphandle ngohlaka, uma zisuka futhi Ayr ngamandla yaqhubekela phambili nge-try ka Stafford McDowall, efakwe ngu-Climo.

source: Ukaputeni obambele we- Ayr ubese enikwa ikhadi eliphuzi, kanti futhi, Melrose ikweletise kakhulu nge-try ka-Bruce Colvine, ekugcineni ngamandla.
reference: Ayr acting captain Blair Macpherson was then yellow-carded, and again, Melrose made the extra man pay with an unconverted Bruce Colvine try, at the end of a spell of fierce pressure.
translation: Ukaputeni obambele we- Ayr ubese enikwa ikhadi eliphuzi, kanti futhi, Melrose ikweletise kakhulu nge-try ka-Bruce Colvine, ekugcineni ngamandla.

source: Abasekhaya babuyile, noma kunjalo, kanti lapho Struan Hutchinson uthole ikhandi eliphuzi ngemva kokukeqa u- Climo engaphethe bhola, ngaphandle komgqa wepenadi, MacPherson uthinte phansi egasele  Ayr.
reference: The home side came back, however, and when Struan Hutchinson was yellow-carded for tackling Climo without the ball, from the penalty line-out, MacPherson touched down at the back of the advancing Ayr maul.
translation: Abasekhaya babuyile, noma kunjalo, kanti lapho Struan Hutchinson uthole ikhandi eliphuzi ngemva kokukeqa u- Climo engaphethe bhola, ngaphandle komgqa wepenadi, MacPherson uthinte phansi egasele  Ayr.

translation: Climo ufake, njengoba eke wenza ekuqaleni, ngemva Kyle Rowe ehlangana nebhola elikhahlelwe David Armstrong elithumela le David Armstrong ohlangothini lwabasekhaya kwi-try yesihlanu.

translation: 'Ulwandle luyingqayizivele yethu': Abaphathi base-Bolivia bethemba ukuthi inkantolo izovula indlela ehamba nelasePhakade.

reference: Naval bases from Lake Titicaca to the Amazon are daubed with the motto: "The sea is ours by right.

source: Kuzo zonke izindawo zase Bolivia, inkumbulo nge-coastline yalahlekela e-Chile ngekhulu lesi-19 umuthombo usacace bha ‚Äì njengoba kulangazelela ukuya e-Pacific Ocean futhi.
reference: Throughout landlocked Bolivia, the memory of a coastline lost to Chile in a bloody 19th-century resource conflict is still vivid - as is the yearning to sail the Pacific Ocean once more.
translation: Kuzo zonke izindawo zase-Bolivia, ukukhumbula i-coastline eyalahlekwe yi-Chile ngenkulu yesi-19 kuyacaca ‚Äì njengomdabuko wokufuna ukuya oluNdawonye lwamaPhakade.

reference: Those hopes are perhaps at their highest in decades, as Bolivia awaits a ruling by the international court of justice on 1 October after five years of deliberations.
translation: Lawa mathemba mhlawumbe aphezulu eminyakeni, i-Bolivia ilindele ukuhlonishwa yinkantolo yomhlaba wonke ngoMsombuluko, emva kweminyaka emihlanu.

source: ‚ÄúI-Bolivia inawo Amandla, umoya wobunye kanye nokuzithoba, kanti empeleni iwulindele ngabomvu umuphumela,‚Äù kusho Roberto Calzadilla, okhulumela ngokusemthethweni i-Bolivia.
reference: Bolivia has the momentum, a spirit of unity and serenity, and is of course expecting with a positive view the outcome, said Roberto Calzadilla, a Bolivian diplomat.
translation: I-Bolivia inawo amandla, umoya wobunye kanye nokuzithoba, futhi iyilindele ngokunakha, kusho uRoberto Calzadilla, umphathi wesiviki sase-Bolivia.

source: Abaningi e-Bolivia bazobukela ICJ ruling kuma-screens amakhulu kuyo yonke indawo, ngethemba elikhulu lokhuthi inkantolo i- Hague izovuna isikhalo se-Bolivia sokuthi ‚Äì ngemva kwezinkulumo ezidonse iminyaka ‚Äì  i-Chile iphoqwe ukuxoxisana ngokunika i-Bolivia ilawule ingxenye yolwandle.
reference: Many Bolivians will watch the ICJ ruling on big screens across the country, hopeful that the tribunal in The Hague will find in favour of Bolivia's claim that - after decades of fitful talks - Chile is obliged to negotiate granting Bolivia a sovereign outlet to the sea.
translation: Abaningi base-Bolivia bazobukela isigqibo se-ICJ kumakhono amakhulu kuyo yonke indawo, ngenhloso yokuthi inkantolo ye-Hague izovikela isibongo sase-Bolivia ‚Äì emva kwezinkulumo ezidonse iminyaka ‚Äì ukuthi i-Chile idingwe yokuxoxisana ngokunika i-Bolivia ilawule ingxenye yolwandle.

source: Evo Morales, umongameli ofanelekayo wase- Bolivia ‚Äì obhekene nomshuduliswano omude ngokhetho-futhi ngonyaka ozayo- unokuningi okusamhlalele ngoMsombuluko.
reference: Evo Morales, Bolivia's charismatic indigenous president - who faces a controversial battle for re-election next year - also has plenty riding on Monday's ruling.
translation: UEvo Morales, umongameli obizwa wase-Bolivia ‚Äì owobala umshuduliswano omude ngokhetho futhi ngonyaka ozayo- unokwenza okuningi ngoMsombuluko.

source: ‚Äú siseduze kakhulu ukubuyeila e-Pacific Ocean," efunga ngasekupheleni kuka-Agasti.

translation: Siseduzane kakhulu nokuya oluNdawonye lwamaPhakade, efunga ngaphelani kuka-Agasti.

source: Kodwa abanye abahlaziyibakholwa ukuthi inkantolo mancane amathuba okuvuna i-Bolivia - kanti lelo gama liyoshintsha uma ivuma.

translation: Kodwa abanye abacubunguli bancike ukuthi inkantolo inamathuba amancane okuvikela i-Bolivia - futhi lelo gama liyoshintsha uma ivikela.

source: I-Netherlands-isekela indikimba i-UN anawo amandla ukuklomelisa izindawo zase-Chile, igomele ngokuthi angake kunqunywe umphumela wokuphumelela kwezinkulumo.
reference: The Netherlands-based UN body has no power to award Chilean territory, and has stipulated that it will not determine the outcome of possible talks.
translation: I-Netherlands-isekela indikimba ye-UN inawo amandla ukuqinisekisa izindawo zase-Chile, igqugquzela ukuthi kungacinisekiswa umphumela wokuphumelela kwezinkulumo.

source: Ukuthi abe-ICJ ruling beza kuphela ezinyangeni eziyithupha ngemva kwezimpikiswano kwezwakala ukuthi udaba ‚Äùbelungenzima,‚Äù kusho inqapheli yomthetho womhlaba wonke yaseChile, Paz Z√°rate.
reference: That the ICJ's ruling comes only six months after the final arguments were heard indicates the case "wasn't complicated," said Paz Z√°rate, a Chilean expert in international law.
translation: Ukuthi i-ICJ ibika ukuthi izosiza ezinyangeni eziyithupha ngemva kwezimpikiswano ezivezwe njengoba "zinzima," kusho inqapheli yomthetho womhlaba wonke yase-Chile, uPaz Z√°rate.

source: Buqama nasekufezekiseni izinjongo ze-Bolivia, iminyaka emine eyedlule kungenzeka ibahlehlisele emuva.
reference: And far from furthering Bolivia's cause, the past four years may have set it back.
translation: Singacinisekisa izinjongo zase-Bolivia, iminyaka emine eyedlule ingakwazi ukuphatha.

source: ‚ÄúUdaba lokuvunyelwa ukusebenzisa ulwandle lungenelelwe ngokungemvume iziphathimandla zaseBolivia,‚Äù kusho u-Zarate.

translation: Udaba lokuvunyelwa kokusebenzisa ulwandle lungaqondakali ngokungavumelani kweziphathimandla zase-Bolivia, kusho uZarate.

source: Inkulumo ka-Morales egqugquzela udlame ikhubaza ukubambisana kwelase-Chile, wabeka kanjalo.

translation: Inkulumo ka-Morales egqugquzela udlame ikhubaza ukubambisana kwase-Chile, wabeka kanjalo.

reference: Bolivia and Chile will at some point continue to talk, but it will be extremely difficult to hold discussions after this.
translation: I-Bolivia ne-Chile esikhathini esithile zizoxoxisana, kepha kuyoba nzima kakhulu ukuqhubeka nokubonisana emva kwalokhu.

source: Amazwe amabili awakashintshisani ngamanxusa kusuka ngonyaka ka 1962.
reference: The two countries have not exchanged ambassadors since 1962.
translation: Amazwe amabili angakhoni ukukroba kusukela ngonyaka ka-1962.

source: Owayengumongameli u-Eduardo Rodriguez Veltze, omele elase-Bolivia e-Hague uzichithile izinsolo zokuthi inkantolo isheshe kakhulu ukuthatha isinqumo.
reference: Former president Eduardo Rodr√≠guez Veltz√©, Bolivia's representative at The Hague, rejected the idea that the court's decision-making was unusually speedy.
translation: Owayengumongameli uEduardo Rodriguez Veltze, omele i-Bolivia e-Hague, uchithile izinsolo zokuthi inkantolo ishesha ukuthatha isinqumo.

source: U-Msombuluko uzolethela I-Bolivia ‚Äúithuba eliyingqayizivele lokuqala isikhathi esisha sobudlelwane ne-Chile‚Äù kanye nethuba ‚Äú lokumisa iminyaka engama 139 yokungavumelani ngezinto ezizozuzisa lamazwe omabili‚Äù, ubeke kanjalo.
reference: Monday will bring Bolivia "an extraordinary opportunity to open a new era of relations with Chile" and a chance to "put an end to 139 years of disagreements with mutual benefits," he said.
translation: UMsombuluko uzolethela i-Bolivia "ithuba eliyingqayizivele lokuqala isikhathi esisha sobudlelwane ne-Chile" kanye nethuba "lokumisa iminyaka engama-139 yokungavumelani," wabeka kanjalo.

source: u-Calzidilla futhi uyakuphika ukuthi uMorales ‚Äì osengomunye womongameli abadumile e-Melika yama-Latin ‚Äì wasebenzisa udaba lwezasolwandle njengesisekelo kwezombusazwe.
reference: Calzadilla also denied that Morales - still one of Latin America's most popular presidents - was using the maritime issue as a political crutch.
translation: uCalzidilla futhi uyaphika ukuthi uMorales ‚Äì osengomunye womongameli abadumile e-Melika yama-Latin ‚Äì wasebenzisa udaba lwezasolwandle njengesisekelo kwezombusazwe.

source: ‚ÄúI-Bolivia ayisoze yalahla ilungulelo layo lokusebenzisa ulwandle i-Pacific Ocean.‚Äù Usho kanjalo
reference: Bolivia will never give up its right to have access to the Pacific Ocean, he added.
translation: I-Bolivia ayinakusetshenziswa ilungelo layo lokusebenzisa ulwandle i-Pacific Ocean. Usho kanjalo

source: ‚ÄúIsinqumo siyithuba lokuthi kubonakale ukuthi sidinga ukunqoba osekwadlula.‚Äù
reference: The ruling is an opportunity to see that we need to overcome the past.
translation: Isinqumo siyisisizo sokuthi kubonakale ukuthi sidinga ukunqoba osekwadlula.

source: i-North Korea ithi ukuyekiswa ukuhloma ngezikhali zenuzi ngeke kwenzeke ngaphandle uma izokwazi ukuthemba elase-Melika.
reference: North Korea says nuclear disarmament won't come unless it can trust US
translation: i-North Korea ithi ukuyekiswa ukuhloma ngezikhali zenuzi kungenzeka ngaphandle uma izokwazi ukuthemba elase-Melika.

source: Ungqongqoshe wezangaphandle e-North Korea u-Ri Yong Ho uthi izwe lakhe angeke liyeke ukuhloma ngezikhali zenuzi kuqala ngaphandle kokuthi bathembe i-Washington.
reference: North Korean Foreign Minister Ri Yong Ho says his nation will never disarm its nuclear weapons first if it can't trust Washington.
translation: Ungqongqoshe wezangaphandle e-North Korea u-Ri Yong Ho uthi izwe lakhe angeke liyeke ukuhloma ngezikhali zenuzi kuqala ngaphandle kokuthi bathembe i-Washington.

source: u-Ri ubekhuluma ngoMgqibelo kwingungquthela yamazwe abumbene.
reference: Ri was speaking Saturday at the United Nations General Assembly.
translation: u-Ri ebekhuluma ngoMgqibelo kwingungquthela yamazwe abumbene.

source: Unxuse i-Melika ukuthi ilandele izithembiso zayo eyazenza kwingqungquthela ese-Singapore eyayiphakathi kwabaholi abayizimbangi.
reference: He called on the United States to follow through on promises made during a summit in Singapore between the rivals' leaders.
translation: Unxuse i-Melika ukuthi ilandele izithembiso zayo eyazenza kwingqungquthela ese-Singapore eyayiphakathi kwabaholi abayizimbangi.

reference: His comments come as US. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo seems to be on the verge of restarting deadlocked nuclear diplomacy more than three months after the Singapore with North Korea's Kim Jong Un.
translation: Ukuphawula kwakhe kuze ngesikhathi i-Melika. Unobhala wezwe u-Mike Pompeo ubukeka esengcupheni yokuqala udaba olungaxazululeki lwenuzi emva kwezinyanga ezintathu iSingapore no-Kim Jon Un wase-North Korea.

source: u-Ri uthi kuyiphupho elingefezeke ukuthi unswinyo oluqhubekayo nokunqaba kwe-U.S. kwisivumelwano esiqeda impi kwelase-Korea ukuthi koke kwenze iNorth Korea iguqe.
reference: Ri says it's a "pipe dream" that continued sanctions and U.S. objection to a declaration ending the Korean War will ever bring the North to its knees.
translation: u-Ri uthi kuyiphupho elingefezeke ukuthi unswinyo oluqhubekayo nokunqaba kwe-U.S. kwisivumelwano esiqeda impi kwelase-Korea ukuthi koke kwenze iNorth Korea iguqe.

source: i-Washington iwayaqaphelisisa ukuthi ingavumi ukwenza izimemezelo i-Pyongyang ingakaqali ukushabalalisa izikhali zayo.

translation: i-Washington iwayaqaphelisisa ukuthi ingavumi ukwenza izimemezelo i-Pyongyang ingakaqali ukushabalalisa izikhali zayo.

source: Bobabili Kim ne U.S. /Melika  Umongameli uDonald Trump udinga ingqungquthela yesibili.

translation: Bobabili Kim ne U.S. /Melika  Umongameli uDonald Trump udinga ingqungquthela yesibili.

source: Kodwa ke kunokusabalala kongabazane lokuthi i-Pyongyang izimisele ngokuyeka izikhali izwe okungenzeka lizibuka njengayona ndlela kuphela yokuphepha.
reference: But there is widespread skepticism that Pyongyang is serious about renouncing an arsenal that the country likely sees as the only way to guarantee its safety.

translation: u-Pompeo uhlela ukuvakashela e-Pyongyang ngenyanga ezayo ukulungiselela ingqungquthela yesibili ka Kim no Trump.

source: Imfashini yase-Paris ikhombisa okuningi okugqokwa ekhanda okuza ezitolo zezingubo eziseduze nawe
reference: Paris fashion shows reveal latest line in massive headwear on it's way to a High Street near you
translation: Imfashini yase-Paris ikhombisa okuningi okugqokwa ekhanda okuza ezitolo zezingubo eziseduze nawe

source: Uma ufuna ukwandisa uhlu lwezigqoko zakho noma uvele uvimbe ilanga ngokuphelele ungabe usabheka kude.

reference: Designers Valentino and Thom Browne unveiled an array of wacky oversized head gear for their SS19 collection on the runway which dazzled the style set at Paris Fashion Week.
translation: Abathungi u-Valentino no-Thom Browne baveze uhlu lwezigqoko ezinkulu zasekhanda kumgodla wabo i-SS19 kumbukiso obukwi-Paris Fashion Week.

source: Izigqoko ezingakholeki zigcwale kwi-Instagram kulelihlobo, futhi labathungi balethe imibukiso edonsa amehlo.
reference: Highly impractical hats have swept Instagram this summer and these designers have sent their eye-popping creations down the catwalk.
translation: Izigqoko ezingakholeki zigcwale kwi-Instagram kulelihlobo, futhi labathungi balethe imibukiso edonsa amehlo.

reference: The stand out piece by Valentino was an over-the-top beige hat adorned with a feather-like wide brim that swamped the models heads.

source: Ezinye zezinto ezongosayizi abakhulu zibandakanya amakhabe anamatshe ayigugu, isigqoko sabathakathi.
reference: Other over-sized accessories included bejeweled watermelons, a wizard hat and even a pineapple - but they are not designed to keep your head warm.
translation: Ezinye zezinto ezongosayizi abakhulu zibandakanya amakhabe anamatshe ayigugu, isigqoko sabathakathi.

translation: u-Thom Browne uveze izifihli zobuso ezingavamile esikhathini se Halloween.

source: Izinto eziningi zokufihla ubuso zivalekile emlonyeni zibukeka njengo-Hannibal Lecter kunokubukeka njengento eyakhiwe abathungi bengqephu abaphambili.

translation: Enye into eyakhiwe ifana nezingubo zokutshuza ngaphansi kwamanzi inento yokuphefumula kanye nezibuko.

source: Uma uqhubeka nemfashini engadumile ungazibeka enhlanhleni.

source: Ababuki besitayela baqagula ukuthi izigqoko ezinkulu kungenzeka ukube zisendleleni eya emigaqeni emikhulu enezitolo zezimpahla.

translation: Ababuki besitayela baqagula ukuthi izigqoko ezinkulu kungenzeka ukube zisendleleni eya emigaqeni emikhulu enezitolo zezimpahla.

source: Isigqoko esikhulukazi silandele maduze I ‚ÄòLa Bomba‚Äô, isigqoko esiwumhelane esingalingana izinyawo ezimbili ukuvuleka kulokhu okusitha ilanga, esibonakale kwi ‚Äúeveryone‚Äù ka Rihanna kuya ku Emily Ratajkowski.

translation: Isigqoko esikhulukazi silandele maduze I 'La Bomba', isigqoko esiwumhelane esingalingana izinyawo ezimbili ukuvuleka kulokhu okusitha ilanga, esibonakale kwi "everyone" ka Rihanna kuya ku Emily Ratajkowski.

source: Uphawu lwenkolo oluyisisekelo sesigqoko esingakholakali esidume emakhasini ezokuxhumana sithumele ezinye izimpahla kumbukiso- isikhwama sasolwandle esicishe silingane nesudi yokubhukuda besikhonjiswa umbukisi omodelayo.
reference: The cult label behind the highly impractical hat that was splashed across social media sent another big creation down the catwalk - a straw beach bag almost as big as the swimsuit-clad model toting it.
translation: Uphawu lwenkolo oluyisisekelo sesigqoko esingakholakali esidume emakhasini ezokuxhumana sithumele ezinye izimpahla kumbukiso- isikhwama sasolwandle esicishe silingane nesudi yokubhukuda besikhonjiswa umbukisi omodelayo.

source: Isikhwama esisaorintshi elishile esakhiwe ngesihlahla rafiya, saphethwa ngerafiya, sagqokiswa isikhumba esimhlophe esibambweni, besizihambela sodwa kumbukiso we-Jacquemus‚Äô La Riviera SS19 kumbukiso wemfashini e-Paris.
reference: The burnt orange raffia bag, trimmed with raffia fringing and topped with a white leather handle, was the stand out piece in Jacquemus' La Riviera SS19 collection at Paris Fashion Week.
translation: Isikhwama esisaorintshi elishile esakhiwe ngesihlahla rafiya, saphethwa ngerafiya, sagqokiswa isikhumba esimhlophe esibambweni, besizihambela sodwa kumbukiso we-Jacquemus' La Riviera SS19 kumbukiso wemfashini e-Paris.

source: Umgqokisi wosaziwayo uLuke Armitage utshele i-FEMAIL  ‚ÄòNgilindele ukubona izigqoko ezinkulu nezikhwama zasolwandle zifika ezitolo ezisemigaqweni emikhulu kulelihlobo elizayo-njengoba abathungi bebe nomthelela omkhulu kuzobanzima ukuziba isidingo sokwenza izinto ezithe xaxa ngokwesikali.‚Äô
reference: Celebrity stylist Luke Armitage told FEMAIL: 'I'm expecting to see large hats and beach bags arrive on the high street for next summer - as the designer has made such a huge impact it would be hard to ignore the demand for the oversized accessories.'
translation: Umgqokisi wosaziwayo uLuke Armitage utshele i-FEMAIL  'Ngilindele ukubona izigqoko ezinkulu nezikhwama zasolwandle zifika ezitolo ezisemigaqweni emikhulu kulelihlobo elizayo-njengoba abathungi bebe nomthelela omkhulu kuzobanzima ukuziba isidingo sokwenza izinto ezithe xaxa ngokwesikali.'

source: u-John Edward: Ikhono kwezolimu libalulekile kwizakhamuzi ezwenikazi.
reference: John Edward: Languages skills essential for global citizens
translation: u-John Edward: Ikhono kwezolimu libalulekile kwizakhamuzi ezwenikazi.

source: Izikole ezizimele eScotland zigcina imininingwane yemiphumela emihle, futhi lokhu kuqhubekile ngonyaka ka-2018 ngeminye imiphumela yokuhlolwa emihle, eqinisekiswa kuphela ukuphumelela komuntu eyedwa kanye nozakwabo kwezemidlalo, ezobuciko, ezomculo, neminye imizamo yomphakathi.
reference: Scotland's independent schools maintain a track record of academic excellence, and this has continued in 2018 with another set of outstanding exam results, which is only strengthened by individual and collective success in sports, art, music and other community endeavours.
translation: Izikole ezizimele eScotland zigcina imininingwane yemiphumela emihle, futhi lokhu kuqhubekile ngonyaka ka-2018 ngeminye imiphumela yokuhlolwa emihle, eqinisekiswa kuphela ukuphumelela komuntu eyedwa kanye nozakwabo kwezemidlalo, ezobuciko, ezomculo, neminye imizamo yomphakathi.

source: Ngesibalo esinykayo sabafundi esingamashumi amathathu ezinkulungwane e-Scotland, lezizikolezimelwe iScottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), ziphokophelela ekuletheni usizo oluseqophelweni eliphezulu.
reference: With upwards of 30,000 pupils across Scotland, these schools, represented by The Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), strive to deliver the best level of service to their pupils and parents.
translation: Ngesibalo esinykayo sabafundi esingamashumi amathathu ezinkulungwane e-Scotland, lezizikolezimelwe iScottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), ziphokophelela ekuletheni usizo oluseqophelweni eliphezulu.

source: Izikole ezizimele zihlose ukulungiselela abafundi ekungeneni ezingeni eliphezulu lemfundo, nasemkhakheni abayikhethayo nasendaweni njengezakhamuzi ezweni.
reference: Independent schools aim to prepare their pupils for further and higher education, their chosen career and their place as global citizens.
translation: Izikole ezizimele zihlose ukulungiselela abafundi ekungeneni ezingeni eliphezulu lemfundo, nasemkhakheni abayikhethayo nasendaweni njengezakhamuzi ezweni.

source: Njengemnyango wezemfundo ongahlela futhi uqalise uhlelo lwemfundo olukhethekile, sibona izilimu zesimanje ziqhubeka ziba ulimu oludumile futhi oluthandwayo njengesifundo esikhethile ezikoleni.
reference: As an education sector that can design and implement a bespoke school curriculum, we are seeing modern languages continue as a popular and desired subject of choice within schools.
translation: Njengemnyango wezemfundo ongahlela futhi uqalise uhlelo lwemfundo olukhethekile, sibona izilimu zesimanje ziqhubeka ziba ulimu oludumile futhi oluthandwayo njengesifundo esikhethile ezikoleni.

source: uNelson Mandela wathi: ‚Äúuma ukhuluma nendoda ngolimu eluzwayo, lokho okushoyo kuya ngqo ekhanda lakhe‚Äù
reference: Nelson Mandela said: "If you talk to a man in a language he understands, that goes to his head.
translation: uNelson Mandela wathi: "uma ukhuluma nendoda ngolimu eluzwayo, lokho okushoyo kuya ngqo ekhanda lakhe"

source: Uma ukhuluma naye ngolimu lwakhe lokhu okushoyo kuya enhliziyweni.‚Äù
reference: If you talk to him in his own language that goes to his heart."
translation: Uma ukhuluma naye ngolimu lwakhe lokhu okushoyo kuya enhliziyweni."
