source: Lesi isikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuthi ngeke sathembela kwiSingisi njalo uma sifuna ukwakha ubudlelwano nokuthembana nabanttu bakwamanye amazwe.
reference: This is a powerful reminder that we can't just rely on English when wanting to build relationships and trust with people from other countries.
translation: Lesi isikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuthi ngeke sathembela kwiSingisi njalo uma sifuna ukwakha ubudlelwano nokuthembana nabanttu bakwamanye amazwe.

source: Kusuka kwimiphumela yokukuhlolwa yezivivinyo zalonyaka, singabona ukuthi ezolimu izona eziphambili eqhulwini kuphunyelelwa kuzona kakhulu ezikoleni ezizimele.
reference: From this year's recent exam results, we can see that languages are topping the league tables with the highest pass rates within independent schools.
translation: Kusuka kwimiphumela yokukuhlolwa yezivivinyo zalonyaka, singabona ukuthi ezolimu izona eziphambili eqhulwini kuphunyelelwa kuzona kakhulu ezikoleni ezizimele.

source: Bangamashumi ayisthupha nesishiyagalombili sebebebonke abafundi abafunde izilimu zangaphandle bathola Isigaba Esiphezulu kuka-A.
reference: A total of 68 per cent of pupils who studied foreign languages achieved a Higher grade A.
translation: Bangamashumi ayisthupha nesishiyagalombili sebebebonke abafundi abafunde izilimu zangaphandle bathola Isigaba Esiphezulu kuka-A.

source: Izinkomba, eziqoqwe ezikoleni ezingamashumi ayisikhombisa nane ezingamalungu ka-SCIS, zikhombisa ukuthi amaphesenti angamashumi ayisikhombisa nambili abafundi bathole Isigaba Esiphezulu A kwi-Mandarin, ekubeni abanye abangamaphesenti angamashumi ayisikhombisa nambili abafunda isiJalimane, abamaphesenti amashumi ayisithupha nesishiyagalolunye  bethole  balabo bafunda isiFrench aabanye abangamaphesenti angamashumi ayisithupha nantathu bafunda i-Spanish nabo bathole o-A.
reference: The data, collected from SCIS's 74 member schools, showed that 72 per cent of students achieved a Higher grade A in Mandarin, while 72 per cent of those studying German, 69 per cent of those studying French and 63 per cent studying Spanish also achieved an A.
translation: Izinkomba, eziqoqwe ezikoleni ezingamashumi ayisikhombisa nane ezingamalungu ka-SCIS, zikhombisa ukuthi amaphesenti angamashumi ayisikhombisa nambili abafundi bathole Isigaba Esiphezulu A kwi-Mandarin, ekubeni abanye abangamaphesenti angamashumi ayisikhombisa nambili abafunda isiJalimane, abamaphesenti amashumi ayisithupha nesishiyagalolunye  bethole  balabo bafunda isiFrech aabanye abangamaphesenti angamashumi ayisithupha nantathu bafunda i-Spanish nabo bathole o-A.

source: Lokhu kukhombisa ukuthi izikole ezizimele e-Scotland zigqugquzela izilimi zamazwe angaphandle njengamakhono abalulekile ezinganeni, abantu abasha ekungangabazeki bazozidinga esikhathini esizayo.
reference: This demonstrates that independent schools in Scotland are supporting foreign languages as vital skills that children and young people will undoubtedly require in the future.
translation: Lokhu kukhombisa ukuthi izikole ezizimele e-Scotland zigqugquzela izilimi zamazwe angaphandle njengamakhono abalulekile ezinganeni, abantu abasha ekungangabazeki bazozidinga esikhathini esizayo.

source: Ulimu manje njengesifundo ongakhetha kuso, luthathwa njengokufanayo nezifundo eziwungqaphambili (isayensi, ubuchwepheshe, ezonjiniyela, nezibalo) ezikoleni ezimele ohlelweni lwezifundo nakwenye indawo.
reference: Languages now, as a subject choice, are being held in the same regard as STEM subjects (science, technology, engineering and mathematics) in independent school curriculums and elsewhere.
translation: Ulimu manje njengesifundo ongakhetha kuso, luthathwa njengokufanayo nezifundo eziwungqaphambili (isayensi, ubuchwepheshe, ezonjiniyela, nezibalo) ezikoleni ezimele ohlelweni lwezifundo nakwenye indawo.

source: Ucwaningo olwenziwe i-UK Commission for Employmeny and Skills ngonyaka ka 2014 ithole ukuthi izizathu abaqashi  bengakwazi ukuvala izikhala eziyishumi nesikhombisa lamaphesenti (17 per cent) kwenziwe ukushoda kwamakhono okusebenzisa izilimi.
reference: A survey by the UK Commission for Employment and Skills in 2014 found that of reasons employers gave for struggling to fill vacancies, 17 per cent were attributed to a languages skills shortage.
translation: Ucwaningo olwenziwe i-UK Commission for Employmeny and Skills ngonyaka ka 2014 ithole ukuthi izizathu abaqashi  bengakwazi ukuvala izikhala eziyishumi nesikhombisa lamaphesenti (17 per cent) kwenziwe ukushoda kwamakhono okusebenzisa izilimi.

source: Ngakhoke ikakhulu, ikhono lwezilimi luya ngokubaluleka ekulungiseleni intsha kwezamathuba omsebenzi.
reference: Therefore more and more, language skills are becoming imperative in order to prepare young people for their future careers.
translation: Ngakhoke ikakhulu, ikhono lwezilimi luya ngokubaluleka ekulungiseleni intsha kwezamathuba omsebenzi.

source: Ngemisebenzi eminingi elindelekile endinga izilimi, lamakhono abalulekile ezweni elibumbene.
reference: With more prospective job opportunities requiring languages, these skills are essential in a globalised world.
translation: Ngemisebenzi eminingi elindelekile endinga izilimi, lamakhono abalulekile ezweni elibumbene.

source: Nomangabe umuntu uthatha muphi umkhakha, uma befunda ulimu lwesibili, bazibeka ethubeni elingcono ekusaseni labo ekubeni nekhono elinjenganaleli.
reference: Regardless of the career someone chooses, if they've learned a second language, they'll have a real advantage in the future having a life-long skill such as this.
translation: Nomangabe umuntu uthatha muphi umkhakha, uma befunda ulimu lwesibili, bazibeka ethubeni elingcono ekusaseni labo ekubeni nekhono elinjenganaleli.

source: Ukukwazi ukukhuluma ngqo nabantu abasuka emazweni angaphandle kubeka umuntu okwazi ukukhuluma izilimu eziningi phambili kulabo aqhudelana nabo.
reference: Being able to communicate directly with people from foreign countries will automatically put a multilingual person ahead of the competition.
translation: Ukukwazi ukukhuluma ngqo nabantu abasuka emazweni angaphandle kubeka umuntu okwazi ukukhuluma izilimu eziningi phambili kulabo aqhudelana nabo.

source: Ngokocwaningo lwase-YouGov lwabantu abadala abangaphezu kwezinkulungwane ezine (4000) base-UK ngonyaka ka 2013, abangama shumi ayisikhombisa nanhlanu (75) wamaphesenti babengakwazi ukukhuluma kahle ulimu lwakwamanye amazwe angaphandle nokuba nengxoxo kahle futhi isiFrench siwulona limu kuphela olukhulwa abantu anagamaphesenti enziwa izinombolo ezimbili, ishumi nanhlanu (15) lamaphesenti.
reference: According to a YouGov poll of more than 4,000 UK adults in 2013, 75 per cent were unable to speak a foreign language well enough to hold a conversation and with French being the only language spoken by a double-digit percentage, 15 per cent.
translation: Ngokocwaningo lwase-YouGov lwabantu abadala abangaphezu kwezinkulungwane ezine (4000) base-UK ngonyaka ka 2013, abangama shumi ayisikhombisa nanhlanu (75) wamaphesenti babengakwazi ukukhuluma kahle ulimu lwakwamanye amazwe angaphandle nokuba nengxoxo kahle futhi isiFrench siwulona limu kuphela olukhulwa abantu anagamaphesenti enziwa izinombolo ezimbili, ishumi nanhlanu (15) lamaphesenti.

source: Ingakho ukutshala kwezokufundiswa kwezilimu kubalulekile ezinganeni zanamuhla.
reference: This is why putting the investment into language teaching now is important for today's children.
translation: Ingakho ukutshala kwezokufundiswa kwezilimu kubalulekile ezinganeni zanamuhla.

source: Ukuba nezilimu eziningi ozaziyo, ikakhulu lezo zamazwe asathuthuka, kuyosiza ekucijiseni izingane ngamathuba angconono okuthola umsebenzi ongcono.
reference: Having multiple languages, particularly those of developing economies, will equip children with a better chance of finding meaningful employment.
translation: Ukuba nezilimu eziningi ozaziyo, ikakhulu lezo zamazwe asathuthuka, kuyosiza ekucijiseni izingane ngamathuba angconono okuthola umsebenzi ongcono.

source: E-Scotland, isikole nesikole siyahluka olimini olusifundisayo.
reference: Within Scotland, each school will differ in the languages they teach.
translation: E-Scotland, isikole nesikole siyahluka olimini olusifundisayo.

source: Iningi lezikole zigxila ekufundiseni ikakhulu izilimu ezindala nezamanje, kanti ezinye zifundisa izilimu ezithathwa njengezibaluleke kakhulu e-UK uma kubhekwa ngale konyaka ka 2020, njenge-Mandarin ne-Japanese.
reference: A number of schools will focus on the more classic modern languages, whereas others will teach languages that are deemed to be most important for the UK when looking ahead to 2020, such as Mandarin or Japanese.
translation: Iningi lezikole zigxila ekufundiseni ikakhulu izilimu ezindala nezamanje, kanti ezinye zifundisa izilimu ezithathwa njengezibaluleke kakhulu e-UK uma kubhekwa ngale konyaka ka 2020, njenge-Mandarin ne-Japanese.

source: Noma ngabe yini ingane yakho ekuthandayo, kunezinhlobo eziningi zezilimu ongakhetha kuzo ezikoleni ezizimele, nothisa abangongoti kulendawo.
reference: Whatever your child's interest, there will always be a number of languages to choose from within independent schools, with teaching staff who are specialists in this area.
translation: Uma ungane yakho ethandayo, kunezinhlobo eziningi zezilimo ongakhetha kuzo ezikole ezizimele, nothisa abangcwothi kulendawo.

source: Izikole ezizimele zase-Scotland zizibophezele ekunikeni isimo sezemfundo esizolungisela izingane futhi zicije izingane ngamakhono adingeka ukuthi ziphumelele, kulokhu ikusasa elikuphethe.
reference: Scottish independent schools are dedicated to providing a learning environment that will prepare children and arm them with the skills required to succeed, whatever the future holds.
translation: Izikole ezizimele zase-Scotland zibophezele ukuveza isimo sezemfundo esizolungisa izingane futhi zicijisele izingane ngamakhono adingeka ukuthi ziphumelele, kulokhu ikusasa elikuphethe.

source: Kungephikwe esikhathini samanje, kwezamabhizinisi emhlabeni wonke jikelele ukuthi izilimu zizoqhubeka nokubaluleka kwikusasa lezwe, ngakho lokhu mele kuvezwe kwezemfundo.
reference: It can't be denied at this time, in a global business environment, that languages continue to be vitally important to the country's future, so this must be mirrored in education.
translation: Akushiwo namhlanje, kwezamabhizinisi emhlabeni wonke jikelele ukuthi izilimo zizoqhubeka nokubaluleka kwikusasa lezwe, ngakho lokhu mele kuvezwe kwezemfundo.

source: Empeleni, izilimu zesimanje kumele zibandakanywe ‚Äúkumakhono ezokuxhumana kwemhlaba wonke jikelele.‚Äù
reference: Indeed, modern languages should really be considered "international communication skills."
translation: Empeleni, izilimo zamanje kumele zibandakanywe "kumakhono ezokuxhumana kwemhlaba wonke jikelele."

source: Izikole ezizimele zizoqhubeka nokunikezela ngalelithuba, ukuhluka, nobungoti kubantu baseScotland abasebancane.
reference: Independent schools will continue to offer this choice, diversity and excellence for Scotland's young people.
translation: Izikole ezizimele zizoqhubeka nokunikezela ngalelithuba, ukuhluka, nobungoti kubantu baseScotland abasebancane.

source: Kumele ukwenze kahle.
reference: Il faut bien le faire.
translation: Kumele ukwenze kahle.

source: u-John Edward ungumqondisi we-Scottish Council of Independent Schools.
reference: John Edward is Director of the Scottish Council of Independent Schools
translation: u-John Edward ungumqondisi we-Scottish Council of Independent Schools.

source: u-Lebron uzodlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala kwi-Lakers nge-Sonto e-San Diego
reference: LeBron to make Lakers debut Sunday in San Diego
translation: u-Lebron uzodlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala kwi-Lakers nge-Sonto e-San Diego

source: Sekuseduze kuphele ukulinda kubalandeli abalindele ukubona u-Lebron James edlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala we-Los Angeles Lakers.
reference: The wait is nearly over for fans looking to see LeBron James make his first start for the Los Angeles Lakers.
translation: Sekuseduze kuphele ukulinda kubalandeli abalindele ukubona u-Lebron James edlala umdlalo wakhe wokuqala we-Los Angeles Lakers.

source: U-Luke Walkon ongumqeqeshi umemezele ukuthi u-James uzodlala ngesonto emdlalweni wokuzilungeselela ukuqala kwemidlalo yesizini, bazodlala ne-Denver Nuggets e-San Diego.
reference: Lakers coach Luke Walton has announced that James will play in Sunday's preseason opener against the Denver Nuggets in San Diego.
translation: U-Luke Walkon ongumqeqeshi umemezele ukuthi u-James uzodlala ngesonto emdlalweni wokuzilungeselela ukuqala kwemidlalo yesizini, bazodlala ne-Denver Nuggets e-San Diego.

source: Kodwa ke, ekutheni mingaki imizuzu azoyidlala kusazonqunya.
reference: But just how many minutes he'll play has yet to be determined.
translation: Kodwa ke, ekutheni mingaki imizuzu azoyidlala kusazonqunya.

source: ‚ÄúKuzoba ngaphezulu kowodwa ibe ngaphansi kwengamashumi amabili nesishiyagalombili,‚Äù kusho u Walton ekhasini leLakers.
reference: It will be more than one and less than 48, said Walton on the Lakers" official website.
translation: Kuzoba ngaphezulu kowodwa ibe ngaphansi kwengamashumi amabili nesishiyagalombili, kusho u Walton ekhasini leLakers.

source: Intatheli ye-Lakers u-Mike Trudell ubike ku-Twitter ukuthi u-James maningi amathuba okuthi adlale imizuzu efinyeziwe.
reference: Lakers reporter Mike Trudell tweeted that James will likely play limited minutes.
translation: Intatheli ye-Lakers u-Mike Trudell ubike ku-Twitter ukuthi u-James maningi amathuba okuthi adlale imizuzu efinyeziwe.

source: Emva kokuzilolonga kulelisonto, u-James ube esebuzwa mayelana nohlelo lwakhe ne-Lakers ngemidlalo eyisithupha ayidlale ingakaqali isizini.
reference: Following practice earlier this week, James was asked about his plans for the Lakers" six-game preseason schedule.
translation: Emva kokuzilolonga kulelisonto, u-James ube esebuzwa mayelana nohlelo lwakhe ne-Lakers ngemidlalo eyisithupha ayidlale ingakaqali isizini.

source: ‚ÄúAngidingi imidlalo yokuzicijisela ukuqala kwesizini okwamanje ezingeni lamikulomkhakha wami ukuze ngilungele ukuqala ukudlala‚Äù ngokusho kwakhe.
reference: I don't need preseason games at this stage of my career to get ready, he said.
translation: Angidingi imidlalo yokuzicijisela ukuqala kwesizini okwamanje ezingeni lamikulomkhakha wami ukuze ngilungele ukuqala ukudlala ngokusho kwakhe.

source: Umdlalo yomjaho wezimoto i-Trump‚Äôs West Virginia Rally Time uvezwa kuhlelo lwe-YouTube
reference: Trump's West Virginia Rally Time, YouTube Channel
translation: Umdlalo yomjaho wezimoto i-Trump's West Virginia Rally Time uvezwa kuhlelo lwe-YouTube

source: Umongameli u-Donald Trump uqala isivunguvungu somkhankaso ngomjaho wezimoto e ubusuku ohlelweni iWheeling, e-West Virgina.
reference: President Donald Trump begins a flurry of campaign rallies tonight in Wheeling, West Virginia.
translation: Umongameli u-Donald Trump uqala isivunguvungu somkhankaso ngomjaho wezimoto e ubusuku ohlelweni iWheeling, e-West Virgina.

source: Umjaho ka-Trump wokuqala kweyisihlanu ayihlelile ngesonto elizayo, kubandakanya ukuma ezindaweni zobungani kubalwa ne Tennessee ne-Mississippi.
reference: It's Trump's first of five scheduled rallies in the next week, including stops in friendly places including Tennessee and Mississippi.
translation: Umjaho ka-Trump wokuqala kweyisihlanu ayihlelile ngesonto elizayo, kubandakanya ukuma ezindaweni zobungani kubalwa ne Tennessee ne-Mississippi.

source: Ngesiqinisekiso sevoti elizokhetha ozovala isikhala sasenkantolo enkulu, uTrump uhlose ukwakha abalandeli kulolukhetho lwamaphakathi njengoba ama Republicans esengozini yokulahlekelwa ukubusa isigungu ngoLwezi.
reference: With the confirmation vote on hold for his pick to fill the Supreme Court vacancy, Trump is aiming to build support for upcoming mid-term elections since Republicans are at risk of losing control of Congress when votes are cast on Nov.
translation: Ngesiqinisekiso sevoti elizokhetha ozovala isikhala sasenkantolo enkulu, uTrump uhlose ukwakha abalandeli kulolukhetho lwamaphakathi njengoba ama Republicans esengozini yokulahlekelwa ukubusa isigungu ngoLwezi.

source: Umjaho wokhetho ka-Trump‚Äôs e-West Virgina , uzoqala ngasikhathi sini?
reference: What time is Trump's West Virginia rally tonight and how do you watch online?
translation: Umjaho wokhetho ka-Trump's e-West Virgina , uzoqala ngasikhathi sini?

source: Umjaho wokhetho ka-Trump e-Wheeling, West Virginia izoqala ngehora lesikhombisa kusihlwa. ET ebusuku, ngomgqibelo, 29 Mandulo 2018.
reference: Trump's Wheeling, West Virginia rally is scheduled for 7 p.m. ET tonight, Saturday, September 29, 2018.
translation: Umjaho wokhetho ka-Trump e-Wheeling, West Virginia izoqala ngehora lesikhombisa kusihlwa. ET ebusuku, ngomgqibelo, 29 Mandulo 2018.

source: Ungabuka umjaho wokhetho luka-Trump e-West Virginia ngokungena ku-YouTube ubuke okwenzeka manje.
reference: You can watch Trump's West Virginia rally online below via live stream on YouTube.
translation: Ungabuka umjaho wokhetho luka-Trump e-West Virginia ngokungena ku-YouTube ubuke okwenzeka manje.

source: U-Trump kungenzeka ahole ukalalelwa kwalelisonto koqokwe inkantoloinkantolo enkulu, u-Brett Kavanaugh, eshubiswe izinsolo zamacala ezocansi nesikhulu esilindelwe sevoti le-Senate njengoba I-FBI isaphenya.
reference: Trump is likely to address this week's hearings for Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh, which became tense over sexual misconduct allegations with an anticipated Senate confirmation vote on hold for up to a week while the FBI investigates.
translation: U-Trump kungenzeka ahole ukalalelwa kwalelisonto koqokwe inkantoloinkantolo enkulu, u-Brett Kavanaugh, eshubiswe izinsolo zamacala ezocansi nesikhulu esilindelwe sevoti le-Senate njengoba I-FBI isaphenya.

source: Kodwa ke inhlosongqangi yalesivunguvungu somkhankaso ukusiza ama-Republicans athole umdlandla wokubhekana nokhetho lukaLwezi.
reference: But the primary aim of this flurry of rallies is helping Republicans facing touch November elections gain some momentum.
translation: Kodwa ke inhlosongqangi yalesivunguvungu somkhankaso ukusiza ama-Republicans athole umdlandla wokubhekana nokhetho lukaLwezi.

source: Ngakhoke, umongameli uTrump kumkhankaso wakhe uthe lemijaho yeimoto emihlanu ngesonto elizayo uhlose ‚Äúukunika umdlandla amavolontiya nabalandeli njengoba amaRepublicans ezama ukuvikela nokwandisa isibalo sabalandeli abanaso ephalamende,‚Äù ngokuka Reuters.
reference: Thus, President Trump's campaign said these five rallies in the next week are aimed at "energizing volunteers and supporters as Republicans try to protect and expand the majorities they hold in the Senate and House of Representatives," according to Reuters.
translation: Ngakhoke, umongameli uTrump kumkhankaso wakhe uthe lemijaho yeimoto emihlanu ngesonto elizayo uhlose "ukunika umdlandla amavolontiya nabalandeli njengoba amaRepublicans ezama ukuvikela nokwandisa isibalo sabalandeli abanaso ephalamende," ngokuka Reuters.

source: ‚Äúukulawula isigungu kubalulekile kuloluhlelo lwamongameli lokuhambela amazwe amaningi angakwazi ukuwahambela njengoba siphokophelele kwisikhathi esimatasa somkhakhankaso‚Äù kuphika usomlomo womkhankaso ka-Trump onqabele I-Reuters ukuthi idalule igama lakhe.
reference: Control of Congress is so critical for his agenda that the president will travel to as many states as possible as we head into the busy campaign season, a Trump campaign spokesman who declined to be named told Reuters.
translation: Ukulawula isigungu kubalulekile kuloluhlelo lwamongameli lokuhambela amazwe amaningi angakwazi ukuwahambela njengoba siphokophelele kwisikhathi esimatasa somkhakhankaso kuphika usomlomo womkhankaso ka-Trump onqabele I-Reuters ukuthi idalule igama lakhe.

source: Ihlelelwe i-Wesbanco Arena ese Wheeling, imijaho yanamuhla yezimoto ingaletha abalandeli abasuka e ‚ÄúOhio nasePennsylvania isakazwe kwezokuxhumana zasePittsburgh,‚Äù ngokusho kwe-West Virginia Metro News.
reference: Scheduled for Wesbanco Arena in Wheeling, tonight's rally could bring supporters from "Ohio and Pennsylvania and draw coverage from the Pittsburgh media," according to the West Virginia Metro News.
translation: Ihlelelwe i-Wesbanco Arena ese Wheeling, imijaho yanamuhla yezimoto ingaletha abalandeli abasuka e "Ohio nasePennsylvania isakazwe kwezokuxhumana zasePittsburgh," ngokusho kwe-West Virginia Metro News.

source: Ngomgqibelo kuzobe kungokwesibili ezinyangeni ezimbili uTrump evakashela e-West Virginia, izwe aliwina ngamaphesenti angaphezu kwamashumi amabili ngonyaka ka-2016.
reference: Saturday will be the second time in the past month that Trump has visited West Virginia, the state he won by more than 40 percentage points in 2016.
translation: Ngomgqibelo kuzobe kungokwesibili ezinyangeni ezimbili uTrump evakashela e-West Virginia, izwe aliwina ngamaphesenti angaphezu kwamashumi amabili ngonyaka ka-2016.

source: u-Trump uzama ukusiza omele ukungena i-West Virgina Republican Senate.
reference: Trump is trying to help West Virginia Republican Senate candidate Patrick Morrisey, who is trailing in the polls.
translation: u-Trump uzama ukusiza omele ukungena i-West Virgina Republican Senate.

source: ‚ÄúAkusilo uphawu oluhle ku-Morrisey ukuthi umongameli eze azame ukuzomulekelela awine ukhetho,‚Äù kusho u-Simon Haeder, ungoti kwezombusazwe eNyuvesi yaseWest Virgina , ngokubika kuka-Reuters.
reference: It's not a good sign for Morrisey that the president has to come to try to give him a boost in the polls, said Simon Haeder, a political scientist at West Virginia University, according to Reuters.
translation: Akusilo uphawu oluhle ku-Morrisey ukuthi umongameli eze azame ukuzomulekelela awine ukhetho, kusho u-Simon Haeder, ungoti kwezombusazwe eNyuvesi yaseWest Virgina , ngokubika kuka-Reuters.

source: Indebe ye-Ryder 2018 Iqembu lase-Melika liyazethemba ukulwa ligcine amathemba ekhona emidlalweni yosuku olulodwa ngeSonto.
reference: Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA show stomach for fight to keep hopes alive heading into Sunday singles
translation: Indebe ye-Ryder 2018 Iqembu lase-Melika liyazethemba ukulwa ligcine amathemba ekhona emidlalweni yosuku olulodwa ngeSonto.

source: Emva kwemhlangano emithathu yohlangothi olulodwa, ngoMgqibelo ntambama, kungenzeka lemidlalo ye-Ryder Cup bekumele iphindwe izikhawu ezine.
reference: After three one-sided sessions, Saturday afternoon's foursomes might just have been what this Ryder Cup needed.
translation: Emva kwemhlangano emithathu yohlangothi olulodwa, ngoMgqibelo ntambama, kungenzeka lemidlalo ye-Ryder Cup bekumele iphindwe izikhawu ezine.

source: Isikhali somdlandla ngokuphelele siwuhlelo lomdlalo oluqaliwe kodwa ke abadlali abakholelwa kuwo, ongefaniswe.
reference: The swinging pendulum of momentum is a completely invented sporting concept but one that players truly believe in, and never more so than at competitions like these.
translation: Isikhali somdlandla ngokuphelele siwuhlelo lomdlalo oluqaliwe kodwa ke abadlali abakholelwa kuwo, ongefaniswe.

source: Pho kukuphi lapho bezothi  manje ngamandla?
reference: So where would they say the momentum is now?
translation: Pho kukuphi lapho bezothi  manje ngamandla?

source: ‚ÄúBahola ngamaphuzu ayisithupha kanti manje asemane, ngakho siyaqhubeka njengokungathi ngamandla amancane Ngiyacabanga‚Äù kusho Jordan Spieth njengoba ezishayela kancane osukwini.
reference: They had a six-point lead and now it's four, so we are carrying that as a little bit of momentum I guess, said Jordan Spieth as he strolled off for the day.
translation: Bahola ngamaphuzu ayisithupha kanti manje asemane, ngakho siyaqhubeka njengokungathi ngamandla amancane Ngiyacabanga kusho Jordan Spieth njengoba ezishayela kancane osukwini.

source: Europe inamathuba , ngempela, amaphuzu amane ngaphambili kwangamashumi nambili.
reference: Europe have the advantage, of course, four points ahead with twelve more in play.
translation: Europe inamathuba , ngempela, amaphuzu amane ngaphambili kwangamashumi nambili.

source: Americans, njengoba eshilo Spieth, banokujabula okuncane kanti banokuningi abangakhuthazwa ngakho, hhayi ngendlela ka Spieth kanye no Justin Thomas abadlale ndawonye usuku lonke kanti ngamunye uthole amaphuzu amathathu kwamane.
reference: The Americans, as Spieth says, feel they have a little wind in their sails though and they have plenty to be encouraged by, not least the form of Spieth and Justin Thomas who played together all day and each boast three points from four.
translation: Americans, njengoba eshilo Spieth, banokujabula okuncane kanti banokuningi abangakhuthazwa ngakho, hhayi ngendlela ka Spieth kanye no Justin Thomas abadlale ndawonye usuku lonke kanti ngamunye uthole amaphuzu amathathu kwamane.

source: Spieth ubelokhu eyingozi futhi ubehola ngesibonelo.
reference: Spieth has been lethal from tee to green and is leading by example.
translation: Spieth ubelokhu eyingozi futhi ubehola ngesibonelo.

source: Labo ababukele bebejabula kakhulu uma sekunguye, ukushaya ngesineke igalofu kubaluleke ukuze umdlalo ulingane  lapho yena kanye Thomas beshiyana ngamabili.
reference: Those guttural screams of celebration got louder as his round went on, sinking a crucial putt to take match four all-square when he and Thomas had been two down after two.
translation: Labo ababukele bebejabula kakhulu uma sekunguye, ukushaya ngesineke igalofu kubaluleke ukuze umdlalo ulingane  lapho yena kanye Thomas beshiyana ngamabili.

source: Igalofu lakhe alifaka banqoba umdlalo ngo-15 injabulo efanayo, loluhlobo likuthsela ukuthi uyakholwa ukuthi iqembu American alikaphumi.
reference: His putt that won them the match on 15 was met with a similar scream, the sort that tells you he believes that the American team is not out of this.
translation: Igalofu lakhe alifaka banqoba umdlalo ngo-15 injabulo efanayo, loluhlobo likuthsela ukuthi uyakholwa ukuthi iqembu American alikaphumi.

source: ‚Äúngempela kuzomele umbe ujule futhi ukhathazeke ngowakho umdlalo,‚Äù kusho u-Spieth.
reference: You've really just got to dig deep and worry about your own match, Spieth said.
translation: ngempela kuzomele umbe ujule futhi ukhathazeke ngowakho umdlalo, kusho u-Spieth.

source: Sekungamunye walabadlali  abasele manje.
reference: It is all each of these players has left now.
translation: Sekungamunye walabadlali  abasele manje.

source: Imigodi engu-18 ukuzibeka uphawu.
reference: 18 holes to make a mark.
translation: Imigodi engu-18 ukuzibeka uphawu.

source: Okuwukuphela komdlali onamapuzu amaningi ukudlula Spieth kanye Thomas ezinsukwini ezimbili ezidlule yilaba Francesco Molinari kanye Tommy Fleetwood, akubuzwa kule Ryder Cup.
reference: The only players with more points than Spieth and Thomas over the past two days are Francesco Molinari and Tommy Fleetwood, the indisputable story of the Ryder Cup.
translation: Okuwukuphela komdlali onamapuzu amaningi ukudlula Spieth kanye Thomas ezinsukwini ezimbili ezidlule yilaba Francesco Molinari kanye Tommy Fleetwood, akubuzwa kule Ryder Cup.

source: Europe's odd kodwa umbhanqwano owenza kahe kakhulu futhi ozimisele.
reference: Europe's odd but adorable couple are four from four and can do no wrong.
translation: Europe's odd kodwa umbhanqwano owenza kahe kakhulu futhi ozimisele.

source: Moliwood bawukuphela komata abangeke baqale i-bogey ngoMgqibelo ntambama, kodwa bagwema i-bogeys  uMgqibelo ekuseni, uLwesihlanu ntambama kanye noLwesihlanu ekuseni.
reference: Moliwood were the only pair not to shoot a bogey on Saturday afternoon, but they also avoided bogeys on Saturday morning, Friday afternoon and the back nine on Friday morning.
translation: Moliwood bawukuphela komata abangeke baqale i-bogey ngoMgqibelo ntambama, kodwa bagwema i-bogeys  uMgqibelo ekuseni, uLwesihlanu ntambama kanye noLwesihlanu ekuseni.

source: Loku kugijima, ngangendlela  koubili abanomfutho ngayo kusuka kulolu quqaba olunomsindo abaphetha ngokuthi bangabadlali abazonqoba ngeSonto, kanti akuphinde kube khona abadlali abaziwayo abazoba nomdlandla ukunqoba European njengoba ilanga liyishonela Le Golf National kune-Fleetwood noma Molinari.
reference: That run, and the way their energy seems to flow both to and from this boisterous crowd cements that they are the players to beat on Sunday, and there would be no more popular player to seal a potential European victory as the sun sets over Le Golf National than Fleetwood or Molinari.
translation: Loku kugijima, ngangendlela  koubili abanomfutho ngayo kusuka kulolu quqaba olunomsindo abaphetha ngokuthi bangabadlali abazonqoba ngeSonto, kanti akuphinde kube khona abadlali abaziwayo abazoba nomdlandla ukunqoba European njengoba ilanga liyishonela Le Golf National kune-Fleetwood noma Molinari.

source: Yomibili kanye kanye imigodi ayifani
reference: Preferably both simultaneously on different holes.
translation: Yomibili kanye kanye imigodi ayifani

source: Inkulumo ngodumo European alukashintshi, yize kunjalo.
reference: Talk of European glory remains premature, though.
translation: Inkulumo ngodumo European alukashintshi, yize kunjalo.

source: Bubba Watson kanye Webb Simpson benza omncane umsebenzi Sergio Garcia, amaqhawe e-fourballs  asekuseni, lapho eboshelwa Alex Noren.
reference: Bubba Watson and Webb Simpson made short work of Sergio Garcia, the morning's fourballs hero, when he was paired with Alex Noren.
translation: Bubba Watson kanye Webb Simpson benza omncane umsebenzi Sergio Garcia, amaqhawe e-fourballs  asekuseni, lapho eboshelwa Alex Noren.

source: Bogey  kanye two doubles baphambili bashiye igebe elide Spaniard kanye Swede abangeke balifice.
reference: A bogey and two doubles on the front nine dug the Spaniard and the Swede into a hole they never got close to climbing out of.
translation: Ibhegi enkulu kabili behlulekela kudala u-Spaniard noSwede.

source: NgeSonto, akukho muntu ozokusiza uphume emgodi wakho.
reference: On Sunday, though, there is nobody to help you out of your hole.
translation: NgeSonto, akekho ozokusiza ukuphumula emgodini.

source: Fourballs kanye foursomes bajabulela ukubukela eduze ngenxa yokubambisana phakathi komata,  iseluleko abasinikayo, siseluleko abangasiki kanye nendlela iqhinga elingashintsha masinyane.
reference: The fourballs and foursomes are so fascinating to watch up close because of the interactions between pairings, the advice they give, the advice they don't and the way that a strategy can change in an instant.
translation: Amabili angu-4 nabahlanganisi bajabulela ukubheka eduze ngenxa yokubambisana komata, usizo abanikezayo, usizo abanganikeziyo kanye nendlela yokushintsha ngokushesha.

source: Europe idlale kahle kakhule njengeqembu futhi yahola kwaba sekugcineni kodwa i foursomes ibonisile ukuthi iQembu USA belisasenamandla okuqhubeka, ngokukhethile Stateside, belingabaza.
reference: Europe have played better as a team thus far and take a significant lead into the final day but this foursomes session also showed that Team USA has the stomach for the fight that some, especially Stateside, had been doubting.
translation: I-Europe idlale kahle kakhulu njengeqembu futhi yawina ekugcineni, kepha amabili angu-4 abonise ukuthi iQembu lase-USA lisadala, ngokushesha esimweni, belizungeze.

source: Europe ithathe 10-6 ihola ngosuku lokugcina Ryder Cup.
reference: Europe take 10-6 lead into Ryder Cup final day
translation: I-Europe ithathe 10-6 iwina ngosuku lokugcina lwe-Ryder Cup.

source: Europe izoba sebamathebeni amaingi amahle ngosuku lokugcina Ryder Cup ngemva kokuphuma fourballs kanye foursomes ngoMgqibelo ngo10-6  ihola United States.
reference: Europe will take a healthy advantage into the final day of the Ryder Cup after emerging from Saturday's fourballs and foursomes matches with a 10-6 lead over the United States.
translation: I-Europe izoba sezindaweni ezinhle ngosuku lokugcina lwe-Ryder Cup ngemva kokuphumela kwamabili angu-4 ngomgqibelo ngo-10-6 iwina i-United States.

source: duo Tommy Fleetwood kanye Francesco Molinari banqoba kabili ngaphezu kokudonsa kanzima Tiger Woods ngamaphuzu amane Le-Golf National.
reference: Inspired duo Tommy Fleetwood and Francesco Molinari led the charge with two victories over a struggling Tiger Woods to take their tally so far at Le Golf National to four points.
translation: Umabili Tommy Fleetwood noFrancesco Molinari banqoba kabili kakhulu ngokunakha u-Tiger Woods ngamaphuzu amane e-Golf National.

source: Osohlangothini  lwe-Europe Thomas Bjorn, ukuzimisele ukugicna indebe eyabalahlekela e-Hazeltine eminyakeni emibili edlule, ukwehluleka America kwi- fourballs yasekusseni, ibeke uchungechunge luka-3-1.
reference: Thomas Bjorn's European side, bidding to retain the trophy they lost at Hazeltine two years ago, dominated a misfiring American side in the morning fourballs, taking the series 3-1.
translation: Umlindeli we-Europe uThomas Bjorn, uqinisekine ukukhokha indebe eyabelekelwa e-Hazeltine eminyaka emibili edlule, ukulahleka kwe-America kwamabili angu-4 asekuseni, ubeke amaphuzu angu-3-1.

source: U.S. iyimise kanzima nakakahulu i-foursomes, ukunqoba imidlalo emibili, kodwa angeke imane izigwazele ibhece.
reference: The U.S. offered more resistance in the foursomes, winning two matches, but they could not eat into the deficit.
translation: I-U.S. ihlala kahle kakhulu kwamabili angu-4, inqoba imidlalo emibili, kepha ayikwazi ukugcina indebe.

source: Ngasohlangothini Jim Furyk udinga amaphuzu ayisishiyagalolunye emidlalweni engu-12 yangeSonto ukuze agcine indebe.
reference: Jim Furyk's side need eight points from Sunday's 12 singles matches to retain the trophy.
translation: Umlindeli Jim Furyk udinga amaphuzu angamashumi ayisithathu emidlalweni yokugcina ukuze agcine indebe.

source: Fleetwood ungowokuqala e-Europe ukuzizuzela amaphuzuamane  kulandelana ngenkathi yena kanye Molinari, yambiza "Molliwood" ngemva kwempelasonto enhle bangabesili abazuze amaphuzu amane  emidlalweni yabo emine yokuvula emlandweni we-Ryder Cup.
reference: Fleetwood is the first European rookie to win four points in a row while he and Molinari, dubbed "Molliwood" after a sensational weekend are only the second pair to win four points from their opening four matches in Ryder Cup history.
translation: Fleetwood wokuqala we-Europe ozonqoba amaphuzu amaningi ngokulandelelana naye noMolinari, abizwa "Molliwood" ngemva yesiphethu esinhle bazonqoba amaphuzu amane emidlalweni yabo emine yokuqala.

source: Ngokwehlula Woods no Patrick Reed kwi fourballs emva kwalokho bazigwazela ibhece Woods kanye Bryson Dechambeau waseAmerica ngo-5&4.
reference: Having crushed Woods and Patrick Reed in the fourballs they then gelled superbly to beat a deflated Woods and American rookie Bryson Dechambeau by an even more emphatic 5&4.
translation: Ngokuqeda uWoods noPatrick Reed kwamabili angu-4 emva kwalokho bawina uWoods noBryson Dechambeau base-America ngo-5&4.

source: U-Woods, ungenile emidlalweni emibili yangoMngqibelo, wabonisa ukuzimisela okukhulu kodwa yena manje ulahlekelwe imidlalo engu-19 kwengu-29 fourballs kanye foursomes kulandelana.
reference: Woods, who dragged himself through two matches on Saturday, showed occasional bursts of brilliance but he has now lost 19 of his 29 matches in fourballs and foursomes and seven in a row.
translation: UWoods, owadlala imidlalo emibili ngomgqibelo, wabonisa ukukhathazeka kakhulu kepha manje ulahlekele emidlalo engu-19 kwangu-29 yamabili angu-4.

source: U-Justin Rose, uzihlalele kwi-fourballs yasekuseni, waphindela kumata Henrik Stenson kwi-foursomes ngo-2&1 ukwehlula Dustin Johnson kanye Brooks Koepka ‚Äì isigaba sokuqala nesesithathu emhlabeni wonke.
reference: Justin Rose, rested for the morning fourballs, returned to partner Henrik Stenson in the foursomes to a 2&1 defeat of Dustin Johnson and Brooks Koepka - ranked one and three in the world.
translation: UJustin Rose, owayehleli kwamabili angu-4 asekuseni, waphindela kumata uHenrik Stenson kwamabili angu-4 ngo-2&1 ukuqeda uDustin Johnson noBrooks Koepka ‚Äì isigaba sokuqala nesithathu emhlabeni.

source: Futhi bazimisele ukubuyela emandleni nganoma iyiphi indlela abngayithola, buka nje unya, nokungcola.
reference: Europe did not have it al their own way though on a pleasant, breezy day south west of Paris.
translation: Baqinisekine ukubuya emandleni nganoma yini, buka ngokushesha futhi.

source: U-Jordan Spieth kanye Justini bahlomuhle izikhathi ezintathu behlula ama-America ngamaphuzu amathathu ngoMgqibelo.
reference: Three-times major winner Jordan Spieth and Justin Thomas set the benchmark for the Americans with two points on Saturday.
translation: UJordan Spieth noJustin bahlomule izikhathi ezintathu beqeda base-America ngamaphuzu amathathu ngomgqibelo.

source: Bazizuzele u-2&1 ngokwehlula Jon Rahm kanye Ian Poulter baseSpain kwi- fourballs kwathi kamuva bahlula Poulter kanye Rory McIlroy ngo- 4&3 kwi- foursomes ngenkathi begeja imigodi emibili evuleikle.
reference: They earned a gritty 2&1 win over Spain's Jon Rahm and Ian Poulter in the fourballs and returned later to beat Poulter and Rory McIlroy 4&3 in the foursomes having lost the opening two holes.
translation: Banqoba ngo-2&1 ngokuqeda uJon Rahm noIan Poulter base-Spain kwamabili angu-4 futhi kamuva bahlula uPoulter noRory McIlroy ngo-4&3 kwamabili angu-4 ngenkathi bezama imigodi emibili.

source: Emlandweni Ryder Cup kukabili kuphela ukuba neqembu lisuka emaphuzwini amane liya emidlalweni engayodwa, ngakolunye uhlangothini Furyk udinga ukulinganisa kuphela ukuze avikele indebe.
reference: Only twice in Ryder Cup history has a team come back from a four-point deficit going into the singles, although as holders Furyk's side need only draw to retain the trophy.
translation: Emndenini we-Ryder Cup kunesigaba esingu-2 sokuba neqembu elisuka emaphuzwini amane liya emidlalweni yokugcina, uFuryk udinga ukukhokha ukuze avikele indebe.

source: Ngemva kokwenza kangcono izinsuku ezimbili,  noma unjalo, ukuhlasela kwangeSonto ibonakala izobahlula.
reference: After being second-best for two days, however, a Sunday counter-attack looks as though it will be beyond them.
translation: Ngemva kokwenza kangcono izinsuku ezimbili, kodwa-ke, ukuhlasela ngeSonto kubonakala sekunqoba.

source: I-North Korea ithi ‚Äòangeke‚Äô  ingahlomi ngaphandle ayithembi.
reference: North Korea says 'no way' will disarm unilaterally without trust
translation: I-North Korea ithi 'ayikwazi' ukukhuluma ngaphandle uma ingakuthembi.

source: Ungqongqoshe wezangaphandle  waseNorth Korea watshela i- United Nations ngoMgqibelo iqhubeka ijulisa ukungathembeki United States kanti akunakwenzeka ngezwe ukuba lingadedela izikhali zenuzi ngaphansi kwanoma iziphi izimo.
reference: North Korea's foreign minister told the United Nations on Saturday continued sanctions were deepening its mistrust in the United States and there was no way the country would give up its nuclear weapons unilaterally under such circumstances.
translation: Ongqongqoshe wezangaphandle base-North Korea utshele i-United Nations ngomgqibelo ukuthi kuqhubeka kuvezwa ukungathembi kwe-United States futhi ayikwazi ukuvikela izikhali zenuzi ngaphansi kwanoma yiziphi izimo.

source: U-Ri Yong Ho watshela indikimba yomhlaba i-General Assembly ukuthi North Korea yenze ‚Äúukubuyisana‚Äù onyakeni odlule, njengokuvimba inuzi kanye nokuvivinya izikhali eziyigozi,  ukuqeda izindawo zenuzi, kanye nokuthembisa ukungazandisi izikhali zenuzi kanye nobuchwephe benuzi.
reference: Ri Yong Ho told the world body's annual General Assembly that North Korea had taken "significant goodwill measures" in the past year, such as stopping nuclear and missiles tests, dismantling the nuclear test site, and pledging not to proliferate nuclear weapons and nuclear technology.
translation: URi Yong Ho utshele inhlangano yomhlaba i-General Assembly ukuthi i-North Korea yenza "ukubuyisana" onyakeni odlule, ngokuvimba inuzi, ukuvivinya izikhali eziyigozi, ukuqeda izindawo zenuzi, kanye nokuthembisa ukungazandisi izikhali zenuzi.

source: Uthe,‚ÄúNoma kunjalo, asiboni ukuziphendulela okuvela e U.S.‚Äù
reference: However, we do not see any corresponding response from the U.S., he said.
translation: Watsho, "Kodwa-ke, asiboni ukuphendula okuvela e-U.S."

source: ‚ÄúNgokungayethembi  U.S. angeke libe khona ithemba ukuvikeleka ezweni kanti ngaphansi kwalesi simo ayikho indlela yokuthi singazihlomisi thina kuqala.‚Äù
reference: Without any trust in the U.S. there will be no confidence in our national security and under such circumstances there is no way we will unilaterally disarm ourselves first.
translation: Ngokungathembi, i-U.S. ayikwazi ukukhona ithemba lokuvikeleka ezweni futhi ngaphansi kwalesi simo ayikho enye indlela yokuthi singahlasela.

source: Ngesikhathi Ri engavumelani ngokukhonda kwe North Korean mayelana nokwenqaba kwe Washington ‚Äúngesigaba‚Äù ukuqeda kwenuzi kuyilapho North Korea ingase iklonyeliswe ngokuthatha izinyathelo, istatimende sibonufakazi ekutheni asikuvimbi ukuqedwa kwenuzi ngokuphelele njengoba Pyongyang enza ngokwedlule.
reference: While Ri reprised familiar North Korean complaints about Washington's resistance to a "phased" approach to denuclearization under which North Korea would be rewarded as it took gradual steps, his statement appeared significant in that it did not reject unilateral denuclearization out of hand as Pyongyang has done in the past.
translation: Ngenkathi uRi engavumelani ngokukhonda kwe-North Korean mayelana nokwenqaba kwe-Washington "ngesigaba" ukuqeda kwenuzi lapho i-North Korea ingase iklonyeliswe, isitayitimenti sibonisa ukuthi asikuvimbi ukuqedwa kwenuzi ngokuphelele njengoba i-Pyongyang enza ngokwedlule.

source: U-Ri ubhekisele esitatimendeni emiswa ngu Kim Jong Un kanye Donald Trump okokuqala bedibana phakathi kukamongameli U.S kanye nomholi we North Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12,  lapho Kim ecela ukusebenza kwi ‚Äù denuclearization of the Korean peninsula‚Äù ngesikhathi Trump ethembisa ngokuvikeleka kwe North Korea.
reference: Ri referred to a joint statement issued by Kim Jong Un and Donald Trump at a first ever summit between a serving U.S. president and a North Korean leader in Singapore on June 12, when Kim pledged to work toward "denuclearization of the Korean peninsula" while Trump promised guarantees of North Korea's security.
translation: U-Ri ubhekisele esitatimendeni emiswa ngu Kim Jong Un kanye Donald Trump okokuqala bedibana phakathi kukamongameli U.S kanye nomholi we North Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12,  lapho Kim ecela ukusebenza kwi " denuclearization of the Korean peninsula" ngesikhathi Trump ethembisa ngokuvikeleka kwe North Korea.

source: I-North Korea beyilokhu ifuna ukuqeda kahle Impi ye Korea ka1950-53, kodwa United States yathi Pyongyang makadedele izikhali zenuzi kuqala.
reference: North Korea has been seeking a formal end to the 1950-53 Korea War, but the United States has said Pyongyang must give up its nuclear weapons first.
translation: I-North Korea beyilokhu ifuna ukuqeda kahle Impi ye Korea ka1950-53, kodwa United States yathi Pyongyang makadedele izikhali zenuzi kuqala.

source: Washington ibilokhu inqaba ukukhulula North Korea.
reference: Washington has also resisted calls to relax tough international sanctions on North Korea.
translation: Washington ibilokhu inqaba ukukhulula North Korea.

source: ‚ÄúU.S. iphikelela nge ‚Äù ukuqedwa kwenuzi-kuqala‚Äù kanti iphamakamisa amazinga okucindezela  umthetho ukufeza inhloso yayo ngempoqo, nokuthi futhi  inqabe ‚Äúisimemezelo sokuqeda impi‚Äù‚Äù kusho Ri.
reference: The U.S. insists on the denuclearization-first" and increases the level of pressure by sanctions to achieve their purpose in a coercive manner, and even objecting to the "declaration of the end of war,"" Ri said.
translation: U.S. iphikelela nge  ukuqedwa kwenuzi-kuqala" kanti iphamakamisa amazinga okucindezela umthetho ukufeza inhloso yayo ngempoqo, nokuthi futhi  inqabe "isimemezelo sokuqeda impi"" kusho Ri.

source: ‚ÄúUkuqonda ukuthi umthetho ungasithobisa okuyiphupho labantu abangendaba nathi.
reference: The perception that sanctions can bring us on our knees is a pipe dream of the people who are ignorant about us.	Ukuqonda ukuthi umthetho ungasithobisa okuyiphupho labantu abangendaba nathi.

source: Kodwa inkinga ukuthi ukuqhubeka phambili kujulisa ukungazethembi kwathina.
reference: But the problem is that the continued sanctions are deepening our mistrust."
translation: Kodwa inkinga ukuthi ukuqhubeka phambili kujulisa ukungazethembi kwathina.

source: U-Ri akazidalulanga izinhlelo zokuthi kuphinde  kube nokudibana phakathi kuka Kim kanye no-Trump ukuthi umholi we U.S. ekuvezile eZizweni Ezihlangene  zisuka evikini.
reference: Ri made no mention of plans for a second summit between Kim and Trump that the U.S. leader highlighted at the United Nations earlier in the week.
translation: U-Ri akazidalulanga izinhlelo zokuthi kuphinde  kube nokudibana phakathi kuka Kim kanye no-Trump ukuthi umholi we U.S. ekuvezile eZizweni Ezihlangene  zisuka evikini.

source: Ungqongqoshe okungenani ukuveze imihlangano emithathu phakathi ku  Kim kanye nomholi we South Korea Moon Jae-in ezinyangeni ezinhlanu ezedlule futhi wanezela: ‚Äú uma ingxenye kule ndaba yokuqedwa kwenuz bekwiyi South Korea kanti hhayi U.S., ukuqedwa kwenuzi Korean peninsula angeke kubangele kulokhu kuzibophezela.‚Äù
reference: The minister instead highlighted three meetings between Kim and South Korean leader Moon Jae-in in the past five months and added: "If the party to this issue of denuclearization were South Korea and not the U.S., the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula would not have come to such a deadlock."
translation: Ungqongqoshe okungenani ukuveze imihlangano emithathu phakathi ku  Kim kanye nomholi we South Korea Moon Jae-in ezinyangeni ezinhlanu ezedlule futhi wanezela: " uma ingxenye kule ndaba yokuqedwa kwenuz bekwiyi South Korea kanti hhayi U.S., ukuqedwa kwenuzi Korean peninsula angeke kubangele kulokhu kuzibophezela."

source: Noma kuthiwa kunjalo, ukuzwakala kwenkulumo kaRi bekuhluke ngokuphelele kweya ngonyaka odlule, lapho etshela i- U.N. General Assembly lena ebheke U.S. indawo ephambili ne North Korea's rockets eyenzeke ngemva ‚ÄúMnu. Mongameli Omubi‚Äù Trump ebize Kim ‚Äúrocket man‚Äù kulokhu.
reference: Even so, the tone of Ri's speech was dramatically different from last year, when he told the U.N. General Assembly that targeting the U.S. mainland with North Korea's rockets was inevitable after "Mr Evil President" Trump called Kim a "rocket man" on a suicide mission.
translation: Noma kuthiwa kunjalo, ukuzwakala kwenkulumo kaRi bekuhluke ngokuphelele kweya ngonyaka odlule, lapho etshela i- U.N. General Assembly lena ebheke U.S. indawo ephambili ne North Korea's rockets eyenzeke ngemva "Mnu. Mongameli Omubi" Trump ebize Kim "rocket man" kulokhu.

source: Kulo nyaka i-United Nations, Trump, lo owasongela ‚Äúngokuqeda ngokuphelele‚Äù North Korea, ukuziphakamisa Kim ngesibindi sakhe sokungathathi sinyathelo ngokuhloma, kodwa kuningi okusamelwe kwenziwe kanti umthetho uhlale ukhona kuze kube yilapho  North Korea iqeda inuzi.
reference: This year at the United Nations, Trump, who last year threatened to "totally destroy" North Korea, heaped praise on Kim for his courage in taking steps to disarm, but said much work still had to be done and sanctions must remain in place until North Korea denuclearizes.
translation: Kulo nyaka i-United Nations, Trump, lo owasongela "ngokuqeda ngokuphelele" North Korea, ukuziphakamisa Kim ngesibindi sakhe sokungathathi sinyathelo ngokuhloma, kodwa kuningi okusamelwe kwenziwe kanti umthetho uhlale ukhona kuze kube yilapho  North Korea iqeda inuzi.

source: NgoLwethathu, Trump uthe akanaso isikhathi sayo yonke lento, uthi ‚Äùuma kuthatha iminyaka emibili, emithathu, noma emihlanu ‚Äì akunankinga.‚Äù
reference: On Wednesday, Trump said he did not have a time frame for this, saying "If it takes two years, three years or five months - doesn't matter."
translation: NgoLwethathu, Trump uthe akanaso isikhathi sayo yonke lento, uthi "uma kuthatha iminyaka emibili, emithathu, noma emihlanu ‚Äì akunankinga."

source: China kanye Russia baphikasana ngokuthi I-U.N.  Security Council kuafenele baklomelise i- Pyongyang ngezinyathelo ezithathiwe.
reference: China and Russia argue that the U.N. Security Council should reward Pyongyang for steps taken.
translation: China kanye Russia baphikasana ngokuthi I-U.N.  Security Council kuafenele baklomelise i- Pyongyang ngezinyathelo ezithathiwe.

source: Noma kunjalo, U.S. UNobhala woMbuso Mike Pompeo watshela i-U.N. Security Council ngoLwesine ukuthi: Security Council ngoLwesine ukuthi: ‚ÄúUkuphoqelela kwe-Security Council kumelwe kuqhube ngamandla futhi ingahluleki kuze kube yilapho sibona isiphetho, ngokugcwele, nobufakazi bokuqedwa kwenuzi.‚Äù
reference: However, U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo told the U.N. Security Council on Thursday that: "Enforcement of Security Council sanctions must continue vigorously and without fail until we realize the fully, final, verified denuclearization."
translation: Noma kunjalo, U.S. UNobhala woMbuso Mike Pompeo watshela i-U.N. Security Council ngoLwesine ukuthi: Security Council ngoLwesine ukuthi: "Ukuphoqelela kwe-Security Council kumelwe kuqhube ngamandla futhi ingahluleki kuze kube yilapho sibona isiphetho, ngokugcwele, nobufakazi bokuqedwa kwenuzi."

source: Security Council ivumile ukusekela North Korea ekuphuleni umthetho kusukelango-2006 ekumiseni ukukhokheleni inuzi kanye nesimiso ballistic missile kaPyongyang.
reference: The Security Council has unanimously boosted sanctions on North Korea since 2006 in a bid to choke off funding for Pyongyang's nuclear and ballistic missile programs.
translation: Security Council ivumile ukusekela North Korea ekuphuleni umthetho kusukelango-2006 ekumiseni ukukhokheleni inuzi kanye nesimiso ballistic missile kaPyongyang.

source: U-Pompeo wahlangana Ri bama ne- U.N. General Assembly futhi bathi emva kwako konke sisazo vakashela  futhi Pyongyang ngenyanga ezayo ukulungiselela okwesibili.
reference: Pompeo met Ri on the sidelines of the U.N. General Assembly and said afterwards that he would visit Pyongyang again next month to prepare for a second summit.
translation: U-Pompeo wahlangana Ri bama ne- U.N. General Assembly futhi bathi emva kwako konke sisazo vakashela  futhi Pyongyang ngenyanga ezayo ukulungiselela okwesibili.

source: Pompeo ube kade evakashele North Korea izikhathi ezintathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugcina alubanga luhle.
reference: Pompeo has visited North Korea three times already this year, but his last trip did not go well.
translation: Pompeo ube kade evakashele North Korea izikhathi ezintathu kulo nyaka, kodwa uhambo lwakhe lokugcina alubanga luhle.

source: Washiya Pyongyang ngoJulayi  ethe inqubekela phambili yenziwa,  yeNorth Korea kuphela  ngokumveza obala ‚Äùngokuphoqa nje-sigebengu.‚Äù
reference: He left Pyongyang in July saying that progress had been made, only for North Korea within hours to denounce him for making "gangster-like demands."
translation: Washiya Pyongyang ngoJulayi  ethe inqubekela phambili yenziwa,  yeNorth Korea kuphela  ngokumveza obala "ngokuphoqa nje-sigebengu."

source: North Korea ihlela umhlangano no Moon kule nyanga ukuqeda indawo ye missile kanye nenhlanganisela yenuzi uma i- United States ithatha ‚Äùizinyathelo ezifanayo.‚Äù
reference: North Korea pledged in a meeting with Moon this month to dismantle a missile site and also a nuclear complex if the United States took "corresponding measures."
translation: North Korea ihlela umhlangano no Moon kule nyanga ukuqeda indawo ye missile kanye nenhlanganisela yenuzi uma i- United States ithatha "izinyathelo ezifanayo."

source: Wathi Kim wangitshela  ‚Äúngezinyathelo ezifanayo‚Äù  wayefuna ukuqinisa ezokuphepha lapho Trump ethembisa eseSingapore futhi ebangela isimo esivamile sobudlelwano ne Washington.
reference: He said Kim had told him the "corresponding measures" he was seeking were security guarantees Trump pledged in Singapore and moves toward normalization of relations with Washington.
translation: Wathi Kim wangitshela  "ngezinyathelo ezifanayo"  wayefuna ukuqinisa ezokuphepha lapho Trump ethembisa eseSingapore futhi ebangela isimo esivamile sobudlelwano ne Washington.

source: Abafundi be Harvard icourse iyabasiza ekulaleni ngokwanele
reference: Harvard students take course in getting enough rest
translation: Abafundi be Harvard icourse iyabasiza ekulaleni ngokwanele

source: Course entsha e Harvard University kulo nyaka bonke abangakaphothuli balala kakhulu ukuze ukunqoba ukumkhuba yokutadisa besebenzisa icaffeine ‚Äòubusuku bonke.‚Äô
reference: A new course at Harvard University this year has got all its undergraduates getting more sleep in a bid to combat the growing macho culture of studying through caffeine-fuelled 'all-nighters.'
translation: Course entsha e Harvard University kulo nyaka bonke abangakaphothuli balala kakhulu ukuze ukunqoba ukumkhuba yokutadisa besebenzisa icaffeine 'ubusuku bonke.'

source: Imikhakha yemfundo ithole abafundi abaningi emanyuvesi aphambili ukuthi abazalutho uma kuziwa ezintweni eziyisisekelo zokuthi bangazinakekela kanjai.
reference: An academic found students at the world's number one university are often clueless when it comes to the very basics about how to look after themselves.
translation: Imikhakha yemfundo ithole abafundi abaningi emanyuvesi aphambili ukuthi abazalutho uma kuziwa ezintweni eziyisisekelo zokuthi bangazinakekela kanjai.

source: Charles Czeisler, uprofesa womuthi wokulala  eHarvard Medical School futhi nongoti eBrigham kanye Women's Hospital, usungule i-icourse, ingoyokuqala ngqa yalolu hlobo US.
reference: Charles Czeisler, professor of sleep medicine at Harvard Medical School and a specialist at the Brigham and Women's Hospital, designed the course, which he believes is the first of its kind in the US.
translation: Charles Czeisler, uprofesa womuthi wokulala  eHarvard Medical School futhi nongoti eBrigham kanye Women's Hospital, usungule i-icourse, ingoyokuqala ngqa yalolu hlobo US.

source: Wakhuthazwe ukuqala i-course ngemva kokunika inkulumo mayelana nendlela ukulala okundinma ngayo ekufundeni.
reference: He was inspired to start the course after giving a talk on the impact sleep deprivation had on learning.
translation: Wakhuthazwe ukuqala i-course ngemva kokunika inkulumo mayelana nendlela ukulala okundinma ngayo ekufundeni.

source: ‚ÄòEkupheleni kwayo kweza intombazane kimi yathi: ‚ÄòKungani  ngitshelwa lokhu manje, onyakeni wami wamabanga aphakathi?‚Äô
reference: 'At the end of it one girl came up to me and said: 'Why am I only being told this now, in my senior year?'
translation: 'Ekupheleni kwayo kweza intombazane kimi yathi: 'Kungani  ngitshelwa lokhu manje, onyakeni wami wamabanga aphakathi?'

source: Yathi akekho owake wamtshela yena mayelana nokulala ‚Äì okungimangalisile,‚Äô utshele iTelegramu.
reference: She said no one had ever told her about the importance of sleep - which surprised me,' he told The Telegraph.
translation: Yathi akekho owake wamtshela yena mayelana nokulala ‚Äì okungimangalisile,' utshele iTelegramu.

source: Course ikhishwe okokuqala kulo nyaka, ichazela abafundi ukubaluleka kwemikhuba yokulala ngokwanele kusiza ikhademu kanye nokuzivocavoca, kanti ithuthukisa inhlalakahle yansuku zonke.
reference: The course, rolled out for the first time this year, explains to students the essentials of how good sleep habits help academic and athletic performance, as well as improve their general wellbeing.
translation: Ikhono likhutshalwe okokuqala kulo nyaka, lichazela abafundi ukubaluleka kwemikhuba yokulala ngokwanele kusiza ikhademu kanye nokuzivocavoca, kanti lethuthukisa inhlalakahle yansuku zonke.

source: U-Paul Barreira, profesa wengqondo eHarvard Medical School kanti futhi ongumqondisi we university's health services, uthe unyuvesi inqume ukufa i-course ngemva kokuthola ukuthi abafundi abaningi abalali nhlobo phakathi neviki.
reference: Paul Barreira, professor of psychiatry at Harvard Medical School and executive director of the university's health services, said the university decided to introduce the course after finding students were seriously sleep deprived during the week.
translation: U-Paul Barreira, profesa wengqondo eHarvard Medical School kanti futhi ongumqondisi we university's health services, uthe unyuvesi inqume ukufa ikhono ngemva kokuthola ukuthi abafundi abaningi abalali nhlobo phakathi neviki.

source: Ubude besifundo buhlanganisa uchungechunge lokhuthile okwenziwayo.
reference: The hour long course involves a series of interactive tasks.
translation: Ubude besifundo buhlanganisa uchungechunge lokhuthile okwenziwayo.

source: Ingxenye yokuqala kunesithombe  segumbi lesikole, lapho abafundi bekhetha izikhomishi ye-coffee, amakhethenisi, abaqeqeshi kanye nezincwadi ezikhuluma ngemiphumela ye-caffeine kanye nokukhanya ukuzivocavoca kusiza kanjani ekulaleni , kanye nendlela yokulala.
reference: In one section there is an image of a dorm room, where students click on coffee cups, curtains, trainers and books to be told about the effects of caffeine and light and how athletic performance is impacted by sleep deficiency, and the importance of a bedtime routine.
translation: Ingxenye yokuqala kunesithombe segumbi lesikole, lapho abafundi bekhetha izikhomishi ye-coffee, amakhethenisi, abaqeqeshi kanye nezincwadi ezikhuluma ngemiphumela ye-caffeine kanye nokukhanya ukuzivocavoca kusiza kanjani ekulaleni, kanye nendlela yokulala.

source: Kwenye ingxenye, abanengxenye bayatshelwa ukuthi ukugwema ukulala isikhathi eside kukhulisa amathuba esifo senhliziyo, isitilokhi, ukuncindeleka kanye nomdlavuza.
reference: In another section, participants are told how long-term sleep deprivation can increase risks of heart attacks, stroke, depression and cancer.
translation: Kwenye ingxenye, abanengxenye bayatshelwa ukuthi ukugwema ukulala isikhathi eside kukhulisa amathuba esifo senhliziyo, isitilokhi, ukuncindeleka kanye nomdlavuza.

source: Ibalazwe lekhempasi, linezimphawu eziwusizo, khona lizokhuthaza abanengxenye ekubakhuthazeni bacabange ngenqubo yabo yansuku zonke.
reference: A map of the campus, with interactive icons, then encourages participants to think about their daily routine.
translation: Ibalazwe lekhempasi, linezimphawu eziwusizo, khona lizokhuthaza abanengxenye ekubakhuthazeni bacabange ngenqubo yabo yansuku zonke.

source: ‚ÄòSiyazi ukuthi angeke ishintshe ukuziphatha kwabafundi‚Äô ngokushesha.
reference: 'We know it won't change students' behaviour instantly.
translation: 'Siyazi ukuthi angeke ishintshe ukuziphatha kwabafundi' ngokushesha.

source: Sikholelwa ukuthi banelungelo lokwazi ‚Äì njengoba nje nawe ilungelo lokwazi ngempilo yakho ngokukhetha ukubhema ugwayi,‚Äô enezela uProfesa u-Czeisler.
reference: But we believe they have a right to know - just as you have a right to know the health effects of choosing to smoke cigarettes,' Prof Czeisler added.
translation: Sikholelwa ukuthi banelungelo lokwazi ‚Äì njengoba nje nawe ilungelo lokwazi ngempilo yakho ngokukhetha ukubhema ugwayi,' enezela uProfesa u-Czeisler.

source: Isiko lokuzigqaja 'ekuhlaleni kuze kuse' yinto esenziwa, esho, engeza ukuthi ubuchwepheshe bethekhinoloji besimanje nengcindezi eyeqile kubafundi inciphisa amazinga okulala okuyinkinga eya ngokudlondlobala.
reference: The culture of pride in 'pulling an all-nighter' still exists, he said, adding that modern technology and ever-increasing pressure on students meant sleep deprivation was a growing problem.
translation: Isiko lokuzigqaja 'ekuhlaleni kuze kuse' yinto esenziwa, esho, engeza ukuthi ubuchwepheshe bethekhinoloji besimanje nengcindezi eyeqile kubafundi inciphisa amazinga okulala okuyinkinga eya ngokudlondlobala.

source: Ukuqinisekisa ukuthi ulala ngkwanele, ngokwanele, kumele kube ‚Äòisikhali esiyimfihlo‚Äô somfundi ukunqoba ingcindezi, ukukhathala nokukhathazeka, esho ‚Äìngisho kugwema ukukhuluphala, njengoba ukungalali kufaka ingqondo kwisimo sendlala, okwenza balambe.
reference: Ensuring you have enough sleep, of a good quality, should be a student's 'secret weapon' to combat stress, exhaustion and anxiety, he said - even to avoid putting on weight, as sleep deprivation puts the brain into starvation mode, making them constantly hungry.
translation: Ukuqinisekisa ukuthi ulala ngkwanele, ngokwanele, kumele kube 'isikhali esiyimfihlo' somfundi ukunqoba ingcindezi, ukukhathala nokukhathazeka, esho ‚Äìngisho kugwema ukukhuluphala, njengoba ukungalali kufaka ingqondo kwisimo sendlala, okwenza balambe.

source: Raymond Shuthi, umfundi oneminyaka engu 19 ubudala eCalifornia ofunda i-chemical ne-physical biology, wasiza uPhrofesa Czeisler ukuklama isifundo, eke wafunda kwelinye lamakilasi akhe nyakenye ngenkathi efunda unyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
reference: Raymond So, a 19-year-old Californian studying chemical and physical biology, helped Professor Czeisler design the course, having taken one of his classes last year during his first year at Harvard.
translation: Raymond Shuthi, umfundi oneminyaka engu 19 ubudala eCalifornia ofunda i-chemical ne-physical biology, wasiza uPhrofesa Czeisler ukuklama isifundo, eke wafunda kwelinye lamakilasi akhe nyakenye ngenkathi efunda unyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.

source: Uthe isifundo simvule amehlo futhi samgqugquzela ukuba aphushe lesifundo kube esesikhungo sonke.
reference: He said the course had opened his eyes and inspired him to push for a campus-wide course.
translation: Uthe isifundo simvule amehlo futhi samgqugquzela ukuba aphushe lesifundo kube esesikhungo sonke.

source: Isinyathelo esilandelayo, wethemba, esokucela abafundi beziqu eziphakeme ukuba bafunde ngendlela efanayo naloluhlelo lokufunda phambi kokuba bajoyine lesikhungo esinokuncintisana okucokeme.
reference: The next step, he hopes, it to ask all postgraduate students to complete a similar study programme before joining the competitive institution.
translation: Isinyathelo esilandelayo, wethemba, esokucela abafundi beziqu eziphakeme ukuba bafunde ngendlela efanayo naloluhlelo lokufunda phambi kokuba bajoyine lesikhungo esinokuncintisana okucokeme.

source: UProf Czeisler utuse ukuthi abafundi kumele bacabange ukusetha ama-alarm ngenkathi beya kolala, nakanjalo ukuthi bazovuka nin, nokuqonda imthelela emibi ‚Äòyokukhanya okuluhlaza sasibhakabhaka‚Äô ekhishwa izikrini zagesi kanye nokukhanya kwe-LED, okungakukhipha kwisigqi sokuzungeza, okuholela kwizinga mekumele.
reference: Prof Czeisler recommended that students should consider setting an alarm for when to go to bed, as well as for when to wake, and be aware of the harmful effects of 'blue light' emitted by electronic screens and LED lighting, which can throw your circadian rhythm out of kilter, leading to problems falling asleep.
translation: UProf Czeisler utuse ukuthi abafundi kumele bacabange ukusetha ama-alarm ngenkathi beya kolala, nakanjalo ukuthi bazovuka nin, nokuqonda imthelela emibi 'yokukhanya okuluhlaza sasibhakabhaka' ekhishwa izikrini zagesi kanye nokukhanya kwe-LED, okungakukhipha kwisigqi sokuzungeza, okuholela kwizinga mekumele.

source: Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Inqaku lika Menga lehlisa amadoda ka Gerrard
reference: Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Menga goal downs Gerrard's men
translation: Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Inqaku lika Menga lehlisa amadoda ka Gerrard

source: I-Rangers yehlelwe umshophi futhi behambile ngenkathi bezunywa uDolly Menga ohlasele icala lika Steven Gerrard elingabumbene waliqumba phansi bahluleka 1-0 eLivingston.
reference: Rangers suffered another bout of away-day blues as Dolly Menga's strike consigned Steven Gerrard's disjointed side to a 1-0 defeat at Livingston.
translation: I-Rangers yehlelwe umshophi futhi behambile ngenkathi bezunywa uDolly Menga ohlasele icala lika Steven Gerrard elingabumbene waliqumba phansi bahluleka 1-0 eLivingston.

source: I-Ibrox side ibihlose ukuqopha ukunqopha kwabo kokuqala behambile kusukela benqoba ngoFebhruwari 4-1 eSt Johnstone, kodwa iqembu lika Gary Holt ongumthelela wokuhlulwa kwesibili kuka Gerrard kwimidlalo engu 18 njengo mphathi oshiye icala lakhe esemuva ngamaphuzu ayisishiyagalombili kubaholi be-Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.
reference: The Ibrox side were looking to record their first win on the road since February's 4-1 triumph at St Johnstone, but Gary Holt's team inflicted just Gerrard's second defeat in 18 games as manager to leave his side eight points adrift of runaway Ladbrokes Premiership leaders Hearts.
translation: I-Ibrox side ibihlose ukuqopha ukunqopha kwabo kokuqala behambile kusukela benqoba ngoFebhruwari 4-1 eSt Johnstone, kodwa iqembu lika Gary Holt ongumthelela wokuhlulwa kwesibili kuka Gerrard kwimidlalo engu 18 njengo mphathi oshiye icala lakhe esemuva ngamaphuzu ayisishiyagalombili kubaholi be-Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.

source: Menga uhlasele emzuzwini eyisikhombisa phambi kwe-half-time kanti abadlali beRangers bekhuthazela bengagobi phondo.
reference: Menga struck seven minutes before half-time and a Rangers line-up short on inspiration never looked like levelling.
translation: Menga uhlasele emzuzwini eyisikhombisa phambi kwe-half-time kanti abadlali beRangers bekhuthazela bengagobi phondo.

source: Ngenkathi manje iRangers yehlela endaweni yesithupha, iLivingston iqhwakela endaweni yesithathu futhi ngemuva kweHibernian abashiyana ngenqaku vo.
reference: While Rangers now drop down to sixth spot, Livingston climb to third and only behind Hibernian on goal difference.
translation: Ngenkathi manje iRangers yehlela endaweni yesithupha, iLivingston iqhwakela endaweni yesithathu futhi ngemuva kweHibernian abashiyana ngenqaku vo.

source: Futhi kungahle kube khona inkinga ezayo kwi-Rangers ngemva kokuba usomugqa uCalum Spence enywangwe ngosizo lokuqala emva kwengozi ekhada ebangelwe okuthile okujikijelwe kude.
reference: And there could be further trouble in store for Rangers after linesman Calum Spence had to be treated for a head wound after an object was apparently thrown from the away end.
translation: Futhi kungahle kube khona inkinga ezayo kwi-Rangers ngemva kokuba usomugqa uCalum Spence enywangwe ngosizo lokuqala emva kwengozi ekhada ebangelwe okuthile okujikijelwe kude.

source: UGerrard wenze ushintsho kasishiyagalombili kwicala olwedlule i-Ayr ukuya kwi-Betfred Cup semi-finals.
reference: Gerrard made eight changes to the side which swept past Ayr into the Betfred Cup semi-finals.
translation: UGerrard wenze ushintsho kasishiyagalombili kwicala olwedlule i-Ayr ukuya kwi-Betfred Cup semi-finals.

source: UHolt, kwelinye icala, uhambe naleyo Livi 11 efanayo ephuce iphuzu kwiHearts ngesonto eledlule futhi ubenga thokoza ngendlela izambatho zakho ebezigqokwe kahle ebezincisha izi mbangi zakhe umoya kumacala onke.
reference: Holt, on the other hand, went with the same Livi 11 which took a point off Hearts last week and he would have been delighted with the way his well-drilled outfit suffocated their opponents at every turn.
translation: UHolt, kwelinye icala, uhambe naleyo Livi 11 efanayo ephuce iphuzu kwiHearts ngesonto eledlule futhi ubenga thokoza ngendlela izambatho zakho ebezigqokwe kahle ebezincisha izi mbangi zakhe umoya kumacala onke.

source: IRangers kungenzeka ukuthi ilibambe kakhulu ibhola kodwa iLivingston yenze okuningi ngebhola elitholile.
reference: Rangers may have dominated possession but Livingston did more with the ball they had.
translation: IRangers kungenzeka ukuthi ilibambe kakhulu ibhola kodwa iLivingston yenze okuningi ngebhola elitholile.

source: Ngabe bakorile ngemizuzu emibili bengenile ngenkathi ukulaliswa kukaMenga kuthumela uScott Pittman kwinqaku lika Allan McGregor kodwa umdlali odlala esiswini elahle ithuba elikhulu egeja ipali.
reference: They should have scored just two minutes in when Menga's first-time lay-off sent Scott Pittman through on Allan McGregor's goal but the midfielder tugged his big chance wide.
translation: Ngabe bakorile ngemizuzu emibili bengenile ngenkathi ukulaliswa kukaMenga kuthumela uScott Pittman kwinqaku lika Allan McGregor kodwa umdlali odlala esiswini elahle ithuba elikhulu egeja ipali.

source: I-free kick  ka-Keaghan Jacobs ethole uCraig Halkettoyi- skipper kodwa umvimbi ongumlingani wakhe u-Alan Lithgow ulihlabe kude le emuva.
reference: A deep Keaghan Jacobs free-kick then found skipper Craig Halkett but his defensive partner Alan Lithgow could only stab wide at the back post.
translation: I-free kick ya-Keaghan Jacobs ithole uCraig Halkett - ummeli, kodwa umvimbi ongumlingani wakhe u-Alan Lithgow ulihlabe kude le emuva.

source: IRangers ikwazile ukulawula kodwa bekungukwethemba kakhulu kunokukholwa kumdlalo wabo kwisigaba sesithathu sokugcina somdlalo.
reference: Rangers did grab control but there looked to be more hope than belief about their play in the final third.
translation: IRangers ikwazile ukulawula kodwa bekungukwethemba kakhulu kunokukholwa kumdlalo wabo kwisigaba sesithathu sokugcina somdlalo.

source: U-Alfredo Morelos ubezizwa ngathi bekumele athole i-penalty ngokwarathu ngesikhathi eshayisana noSteve Lawless kodwa unompempe uSteven Thomson usichithile isicelo sowase Colombian.
reference: Alfredo Morelos certainly felt he should have had a penalty on the quarter-hour mark as he and Steven Lawless collided but referee Steven Thomson waved away the Colombian's appeals.
translation: U-Alfredo Morelos ubezizwa ngathi bekumele athole i-penalty ngokwarathu ngesikhathi eshayisana noSteve Lawless kodwa unompempe uSteven Thomson usichithile isicelo sowase Colombian.

source: IRangers ikwazileukufaka amanqaku amabili ngesigamu sokuqala ebhekene ngqo nepali kodwa unozinti omdala we-Ibrox uLiam Kelly bengakhathazekile ngenqabu elifakwe ngekhanda lika Lassana Coulibaly nokuhlasela okuthotshiwe kuka Ovie Ejaria.
reference: Rangers managed just two first-half shots on target but former Ibrox goalkeeper Liam Kelly was barely troubled by Lassana Coulibaly's header and a tame Ovie Ejaria strike.
translation: IRangers ikwazile ukufaka amanqaku amabili ngesigamu sokuqala ebhekene ngqo nepali kodwa unozinti omdala we-Ibrox uLiam Kelly bengakhathazekile ngenqabu elifakwe ngekhanda lika Lassana Coulibaly nokuhlasela okuthotshiwe kuka Ovie Ejaria.

source: Ngenkathi uLivi evulela ngenaku ngomzumzu ka34 kungenzeka bekungekho ngokomdlalo, akekho obengaphika ukuthi bebelifanele ngokokusebenza kwabo.
reference: While Livi's 34th-minute opener may have been against the run of play, no one can deny they deserved it for their graft alone.
translation: Ngenkathi uLivi evulela ngenaku ngomzumzu ka34 kungenzeka bekungekho ngokomdlalo, akekho obengaphika ukuthi bebelifanele ngokokusebenza kwabo.

source: IRangers iphinde yahluleka ukumelana nencwenga yebhola lika Jacobs.
reference: Again Rangers failed to deal with a deep Jacobs set-piece.
translation: IRangers iphinde yahluleka ukumelana nencwenga yebhola lika Jacobs.

source: UScott Arfield akenzanga lutho ngenkathi uDeclan Gallagher ekhahlela uScott Robinson, obesipholele waphosela uMenga ukuba aqedele kalula.
reference: Scott Arfield did not react as Declan Gallagher slotted the ball to Scott Robinson, who kept his cool to pick out Menga for a simple finish.
translation: UScott Arfield akenzanga lutho ngenkathi uDeclan Gallagher ekhahlela uScott Robinson, obesipholele waphosela uMenga ukuba aqedele kalula.

source: UGerrardube nomnyakazo emva kwekhefu ngesikhathi eshintsha uCoulibaly ngo Ryan Kent futhi lolushintsho lucishe laba nothelela ngokushesha ngesikhathi umgadli ekhahlelela eMorelos kodwa uKelly ohlaba umxhwele ujime esuka kulayini wakhe ukuzovimba.
reference: Gerrard acted at the break as he swapped Coulibaly for Ryan Kent and the switch almost provided an immediate impact as the winger slotted in Morelos but the impressive Kelly raced from his line to block.
translation: UGerrard ube nomnyakazo emva kwekhefu ngesikhathi eshintsha uCoulibaly ngo Ryan Kent futhi lolushintsho lucishe laba nothelela ngokushesha ngesikhathi umgadli ekhahlelela eMorelos kodwa uKelly ohlaba umxhwele ujime esuka kulayini wakhe ukuzovimba.

source: Kodwa uLivingston uqhubekile nokuchaza ababukeli ngokudlala umdlalo abawuthakaselayo, noLithgow neHalkett beshanela amabhola amade emva kwamanye amade.
reference: But Livingston continued to suck the visitors into playing exactly the type of game they enjoy, with Lithgow and Halkett sweeping up long ball after long ball.
translation: Kodwa uLivingston uqhubekile nokuchaza ababukeli ngokudlala umdlalo abawuthakaselayo, noLithgow neHalkett beshanela amabhola amade emva kwamanye amade.

source: Icala lika Holt belingavula igebe kubuholi kwizigaba zokugcina kodwa uMcGregor usukumile wanqabela uJacobs phambi kokuba uLithgow eshaye ibhola ngekhanda ekhoneni.
reference: Holt's side could have stretched their lead in the final stages but McGregor stood up well to deny Jacobs before Lithgow headed wide from the corner.
translation: Icala lika Holt belingavula igebe kubuholi kwizigaba zokugcina kodwa uMcGregor usukumile wanqabela uJacobs phambi kokuba uLithgow eshaye ibhola ngekhanda ekhoneni.

source: Ongenele uRangers uGlenn Middleton uthola sekukudala iphenathi ngesikhathi ebambana noJacobs kodwa futhi uThomson ubheke eceleni.
reference: Rangers substitute Glenn Middleton had another late claim for a penalty as he tangled with Jacobs but again Thomson looked away.
translation: Ongenele uRangers uGlenn Middleton uthola sekukudala iphenathi ngesikhathi ebambana noJacobs kodwa futhi uThomson ubheke eceleni.

source: Almanac: Umsungli we-Geiger Counter
reference: Almanac: The inventor of the Geiger Counter
translation: Almanac: Umsungli we-Geiger Counter

source: And Futhi manje ikhasi lethu ‚ÄúleSonto Ekuseni‚Äù Almanac: Septhemba 30, 1882, eminyakeni ewu 136 eyedlule, futhi UBALA ... usuku lapho i-physicist yakusasa uJohannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger wazalwa eGermany.
reference: And now a page from our "Sunday Morning" Almanac: September 30, 1882, 136 years ago today, and COUNTING ... the day the future physicist Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger was born in Germany.
