reference: From November Kit will star in a revival of Sam Shepard's True West which is the story of a film producer and his brother, who is a robber.
translation: Kusukela ngoNovemba uKit uzodlala kwiTrue West kaSam Shepard okuyindaba yomakhi filimu nomfowabo, ogqekezayo.

source: Umlingisi usanda kuveza ukuthi ucabanga ukuthi unkosikazi wakhe u Rose uzoba yinto evelele eyake yaphuma ku Game of thrones.
reference: The actor recently revealed that he considers meeting his wife Rose to be the best thing to come out of Game of Thrones.
translation: Umlingisi usanda kuveza ukuthi ucabanga ukuthi unkosikazi wakhe u Rose uzoba yinto evelele eyake yaphuma ku Game of thrones.

source: ‚ÄòNgahlangana nonkosikazi wami kuwona lomdlalo, ingakho ke kwanginika umndeni wakusasa, impilo yami kusaka manje‚Äô, esho.
reference: 'I met my wife in this show, so in that way it gave me my future family, and my life from here on in,' he said.
translation: 'Ngahlangana nonkosikazi wami kuwona lomdlalo, ingakho ke kwanginika umndeni wakusasa, impilo yami kusaka manje', esho.

source: U- Rose wadlala Ygritte, Uthando luka Kit character Jon Snow, kwi lwama lwemiklomelo wakuma Emmy fantasy series.
reference: Rose played Ygritte, the love interest of Kit's character Jon Snow, in the Emmy award-winning fantasy series.
translation: U- Rose wadlala Ygritte, Uthando luka Kit character Jon Snow, kwi lwama lwemiklomelo wakuma Emmy fantasy series.

source: Lezi thandani zashada ngo Nhlangulana 2018 amagcekeni akubo ka Leslie eScotland.
reference: The couple married in June 2018 on the grounds of Leslie's family estate in Scotland.
translation: Lezi thandani zashada ngo Nhlangulana 2018 amagcekeni akubo ka Leslie eScotland.

source: HIV/Aids: I-China ibika u-14% ukuqhubekela phambili ezimweni ezintsha
reference: HIV/Aids: China reports 14% surge in new cases
translation: HIV/Aids: I-China ibika u-14% ukuqhubekela phambili ezimweni ezintsha

source: I-China isimemezela ukunyuka ngo 14% kwanani lwezakhamizi eziphila nengculazi ne sandulela ngculazi.
reference: China has announced a 14% jump in the number of its citizens who are living with HIV and Aids.
translation: I-China isimemezela ukunyuka ngo 14% kwanani lwezakhamizi eziphila nengculazi ne sandulela ngculazi.

source: Abantu abangaphezu kuka-820,000 bathinteka kuleli zwe, izikhulu zezempilo zithi.
reference: More than 820,000 people are affected in the country, health officials say.
translation: Abantu abangaphezu kuka-820,000 bathinteka kuleli zwe, izikhulu zezempilo zithi.

source: Amacala amasha angaba ngu-40,000 abikwa kwikota yesibili ka-2018 uwodwa.
reference: About 40,000 new cases were reported in the second quarter of 2018 alone.
translation: Amacala amasha angaba ngu-40,000 abikwa kwikota yesibili ka-2018 uwodwa.

source: Iningi lamacala amasha eze.
reference: The vast majority of new cases were transmitted through sex, marking a change from the past.
translation: Iningi lamacala amasha eze.

source: Iningi lamacala amasha adluliselwa ngezocansi, amaka ushintsho kusuka esikhathini esidlule.
reference: Traditionally, HIV spread rapidly through some parts of China as a result of infected blood transfusions.
translation: Iningi lamacala amasha adluliselwa ngezocansi, amaka ushintsho kusuka esikhathini esidlule.

source: Kodwa isibalo sabantu abathola ngculazi ngale ndlela siye sanciphisa cishe safika ku zero , izikhulu zempilo zase China zasho njalo emhlanganweni wesifundazwe saseYunnan.
reference: But the number of people contracting HIV in this way had been reduced to almost zero, Chinese health officials said at a conference in Yunnan province.
translation: Kodwa isibalo sabantu abathola ngculazi ngale ndlela siye sanciphisa cishe safika ku zero , izikhulu zempilo zase China zasho njalo emhlanganweni wesifundazwe saseYunnan.

source: Unyaka-no-nyaka, kodwa ke inani labantu abaphila negculazi nesandulela ngculazi sesinyuke ngaba abangu 100,000.
reference: Year-on-year, however, the number of those living with HIV and Aids in China has risen by 100,000 people.
translation: Unyaka-no-nyaka, kodwa ke inani labantu abaphila negculazi nesandulela ngculazi sesinyuke ngaba abangu 100,000.

source: Ukuthelelana kwengculazi ngoku cansi inkinga encane kwi LGBT community.
reference: HIV transmission through sex is an acute issue in China's LGBT community.
translation: Ukuthelelana kwengculazi ngoku cansi inkinga encane kwi LGBT community.

source: Ukubayicala ukuthandana nobuliliobufanayp e-China kwasulwa ngo 1997, kodwa kucwaswa kubantu abathandana nobulili obufanayo kudlangile.
reference: Homosexuality was decriminalised in China in 1997, but discrimination against LGBT people is said to be rife.
translation: Ukubayicala ukuthandana nobuliliobufanayp e-China kwasulwa ngo 1997, kodwa kucwaswa kubantu abathandana nobulili obufanayo kudlangile.

source: Ngenxa yendlela zokuphila, ucwaningo luke lwaveza ukuthi 70-90% wabantu besilisa abalala nabanye besilisa bagcine beshade nabantu besifazane.
reference: Because of the country's conservative values, studies have estimated that 70-90% of men who have sex with men will eventually marry women.
translation: Ngenxa yendlela zokuphila, ucwaningo luke lwaveza ukuthi 70-90% wabantu besilisa abalala nabanye besilisa bagcine beshade nabantu besifazane.

source: Okuningi ukutheleleka kwezifo kuqhamuka kukuzivikela akungalungile kucansi kulobu budlelwano.
reference: Many of the transmissions of the diseases come from inadequate sexual protections in these relationships.
translation: Okuningi ukutheleleka kwezifo kuqhamuka kukuzivikela akungalungile kucansi kulobu budlelwano.

source: Kusukela ngo 2003, uhulumeni wase China wathembisa ukufinyelela komhlaba kwimishwanguzo njengemizamoyokubhekana nenkinga.
reference: Since 2003, China's government has promised universal access to HIV medication as part of an effort to tackle the issue.
translation: Kusukela ngo 2003, uhulumeni wase China wathembisa ukufinyelela komhlaba kwimishwanguzo njengemizamoyokubhekana nenkinga.

source: UMaxine Waters uyaphika ukuthi omunye umsebenzi uputshize ulwazi lwe -GOP senators', kuqhuma 'amanga ayingozi' akanye 'nezinkolelwa zokubhozonyelwa‚Äô
reference: Maxine Waters denies staffer leaked GOP senators' data, blasts 'dangerous lies' and 'conspiracy theories'
translation: UMaxine Waters uyaphika ukuthi omunye umsebenzi uputshize ulwazi lwe -GOP senators', kuqhuma 'amanga ayingozi' akanye 'nezinkolelwa zokubhozonyelwa'

source: eU.S. I-Rep. Maxine Waters uchithe izinsolo zokuthi omunye kwizisebenzi zakhe ufake imniningwane yama-senator amathathu e-Republican eU.S. kwikhasi labaqambi mthetho kwi-Wikipedia.
reference: U.S. Rep. Maxine Waters on Saturday denounced allegations that a member of her staff had posted the personal information of three Republican U.S. senators onto the lawmakers' Wikipedia pages.
translation: eU.S. I-Rep. Maxine Waters uchithe izinsolo zokuthi omunye kwizisebenzi zakhe ufake imniningwane yama-senator amathathu e-Republican eU.S. kwikhasi labaqambi mthetho kwi-Wikipedia.

source: AmaDemocrat ase Los Angeles achazile ukuthi lezinsolo ibhebhethekiswe ompetha "be-ultra-right wing" namawebhusayithi.
reference: The Los Angeles Democrat asserted that the claims were being pedaled by "ultra-right wing" pundits and websites.
translation: AmaDemocrat ase Los Angeles achazile ukuthi lezinsolo ibhebhethekiswe ompetha "be-ultra-right wing" namawebhusayithi.

source: Amanga, amanga, namanye amanga amaningi anyantisayo, kusho uWaters kwisitatimende kuTwitter.
reference: Lies, lies, and more despicable lies, Waters said in a statement on Twitter.
translation: Amanga, amanga, namanye amanga amaningi anyantisayo, kusho uWaters kwisitatimende kuTwitter.

source: Imniningwane eputshukile ibandakanyanamakheli asemakhaya nezinombolo zase U.S. Sens. ULindsey Graham wase South Carolina, noMike Lee kanye  no-Orrin Hatch, bobabili abase Utah.
reference: The released information reportedly included the home addresses and phone numbers for U.S. Sens. Lindsey Graham of South Carolina, and Mike Lee and Orrin Hatch, both of Utah.
translation: Imniningwane eputshukile ibandakanyanamakheli asemakhaya nezinombolo zase U.S. Sens. ULindsey Graham wase South Carolina, noMike Lee kanye  no-Orrin Hatch, bobabili abase Utah.

source: Ulwazi luvele kwi-inthanethi ngoLwesine, ifakwe umuntu ongaziwa kuCapitol Hill ngenkathi kulalelwa iphaneli ye-Senate kwizinsolo yokungaziphathi kahle ngokocansi kowe-Supreme Court uBrett Kavanaugh.
reference: The information appeared online Thursday, posted by an unknown person on Capitol Hill during a Senate panel's hearing on the sexual misconduct allegations against Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh.
translation: Ulwazi lwavela ku-inthanethi ngeCawa, umuntu ongaziwa efakwe ePhalamende kaKhongolose ngesikhathi kulalelwa iphaneli yoMkhandlu woBuhlulu mayelana nokuziphatha ngokungcolile kwesiGqeba soMthetho uBrett Kavanaugh.

source: Lokuputshuka kuvele emva kokuba uKavanaugh efakwe imibuzo ama-senator amathathu.
reference: The leak came sometime after the three senators had questioned Kavanaugh.
translation: Lokhu kwenzeka ngemva kokuba uKavanaugh efakwe imibuzo emithathu.

source: Amasayithi akudala njenge Gateway Pundit ne RedState ibike ukuthi i-IP address ikhomba ukuthi ihhovisi laWaters lihlobene nayo nokuthi ilona elikhiphe lemniningwane yomsebenzi kaWaters, kubika i-Hill.
reference: Conservative sites such as Gateway Pundit and RedState reported that the IP address that identifies the source of the posts was associated with Waters" office and released the information of a member of Waters' staff, the Hill reported.
translation: Ama-website endala njenge-Gateway Pundit ne-RedState ayichaza i-IP address esikhundleni sikaMnu. Waters, ibika i-Hill.

source: Lezinsolo ezingaqinisekisiwe zamanga futhi azilona iqiniso, kuqhubeka uWaters.
reference: This unfounded allegation is completely false and an absolute lie, Waters continued.
translation: Lezi zinsolo azicaci futhi azingamsini, kusho uMnu. Waters.

source: Ilungi labasebenzi bami ‚Äì ubunikazi, imniningwane yomuntu, nokuphepha kwabasengcupheni njengomphumela wezinsolo zokukhwabanisa futhi zamanga ‚Äì alizange lizibandakanye nokuputshula lemniningwane.	The member of my staff - whose identity, personal information, and safety have been compromised as a result of these fraudulent and false allegations - was in no way responsible for the leak of this information.
reference: Abasebenzi bami ‚Äì ubunikazi, ulwazi lobuntu, nokuphepha kwabantu ‚Äì ayikaze ifakwe ekuphikiseni noma ekuxovuleni lolwazi.

source: Lezinsolo ezingeasisekelo zamanga impela futhi azilona iqiniso."
reference: This unfounded allegation is completely false and an absolute lie."
translation: Lezi zinsolo azingamsini futhi azicaci.

source: Isitatimende sikaWaters sisheshe saba ngukugxeka kwi-inthanethi, kubandakanya nonobhala omdala we-White House press u-Ari Fleischer.
reference: Waters' statement quickly drew criticism online, including from former White House press secretary Ari Fleischer.
translation: Izincazelo zikaWaters zagcina zaphakama ku-inthanethi, kubandakanya noMnu. Ari Fleischer, umphathi wesizinda seziqu zikahulumeni.

source: Lokuphika kunokudinwa, kubhala uFleischer.
reference: This denial is angry, Fleischer wrote.
translation: Lokhu kuchaza ukungahambi kahle, kubhala uFleischer.

source: Lokhu kuchaza ukuthi akanabo ubumnene bokua iLungu likaKhongolose.	This suggests she doesn't have the temperment to be a Member of Congress.

translation: They must be calm and serene."

source: UFleischer bengathi ufanisa impendulo kaWaters kukugxekwa iJaji lama-Democrat uKavanaugh, owasolwa abagxeki abebedinwe kakhulu ngesikhathi sokulalelwa kwecala ngoLwesine.
reference: Fleischer was appearing to compare Waters' reaction to the Democrats' criticism of Judge Kavanaugh, who was accused by critics of seeming too angry during Thursday's hearing.
translation: UFleischer ubeka umbono wokuphatha kaWaters ngokufana nokwethulwa koMqondisi uKavanaugh, owayesolwa futhi ebhekwe kanzima ngesikhathi sokuphonononga.

source: U-Omar Navarro, umngeneli weRepublican ozongena ezicathulweni zika Waters kukhetho lwaphakathi nesikhathi, uphefumule naye ngemcabango yakhe kuTwitter.
reference: Omar Navarro, a Republican candidate running to unseat Waters in the midterm elections, also voiced his thoughts on Twitter.
translation: UMnu. Omar Navarro, umnyamuleli weRepublican ozofika ezincathulweni zikaWaters, uphawule ngalokho kuTwitter.

source: Kukhulu bo uma kuyiqiniso, ebhala kuTwitter.
reference: Big if true, he tweeted.
translation: Kukhulu uma kuyiqiniso, kubhala kuTwitter.

source: Kwisitatimende sakhe, uWaters uthe ihhovisi lakhe lazise "izikhulu ezifanele nohlaka labezomthetho ngalezinsolo zokukhwabanisa.
reference: In her statement, Waters said her office had alerted "the appropriate authorities and law enforcement entities of these fraudulent claims.
translation: Esincazelelweni sakhe, uWaters uthe ihhovisi lakhe laxhumana "namalunga asemasikweni onke" ngalezi zinsolo.

source: Sizoqinisekisa ukuthi abanecala bayadalulwa, eqhubeka, "futhi bazobekwa icala ngezenzo zabo zonke zokucekela phansi neziyingozi kunoma yiba phi noma bonke abasebenzi bami."
reference: We will ensure that the perpetrators will be revealed, she continued, "and that they will be held legally liable for all of their actions that are destructible and dangerous to any and all members of my staff."
translation: Sizoqinisekisa ukuthi labo becala bahlawulwe, kusho yena, "futhi babekwe icala ngezenzo zonke zokukhohlisa nezingcolisa bonke abasebenzi bami."

source: Umbono ngoJohnny English Strikes Again ‚Äì yehlise amandla spy poof yaRowan Atkinson
reference: Johnny English Strikes Again review - underpowered Rowan Atkinson spy spoof
translation: Umbono weJohnny English Strikes Again ‚Äì ukwehlisa umculo wespy waRowan Atkinson

source: Kuyisiko manje ukubheka ukubaluleka kuka Brexit kunoma iyiphi i-engela ifilimu yase Britain futhi ayibukeki ihambisa nokuvuswa kwalomdlalo wamahlaya i-Johnny English ‚Äì eyaqala kudala ngo 2003 noJohnny English nokubuyiswa kwayo ngo 2011 i-Johnny English Reborn.
reference: It's traditional now to look for Brexit significances in any new film with a British slant and that does seem applicable to this revival of the Johnny English action-comedy spoof franchise - which started back in 2003 with Johnny English and spluttered back to life in 2011 with Johnny English Reborn.
translation: Kunesimo manje lokubheka ukubaluleka kwe-Brexit kunoma yiliphi ifilimu yaseMelika futhi ayibukeki ihamba namuhla nokuqala kabuhlungu komdlalo we-Johnny English ‚Äì owaqala ngo-2003 noJohnny English nokuphinda ngowe-2011 njenge-Johnny English Reborn.

source: Ukudla amazambane ashisayo njenge sisho kwisihloko sokuthi singaba nethuba elisha lokudayisa ngaphandle?
reference: Will tongue-in-cheek self-satire on the subject of how obviously rubbish we are be the nation's new export opportunity?
translation: Ukudla amazambane ashisayo - ngabe sesithole ithuba elisha lokudayisa?

source: Kunoma isiphi isilinganiso, ihlo elivuliwe, ubuso berabha baJohnny English obenegunya lokukhuthaza izinto ezintsha okwesibili ‚Äì lelo gama liyihlaya elikhulu eliklanyelwe izinkundla zamabhayisikobho zabantu abangasikhulumi Isingisi.
reference: At any rate, the pop-eyed, rubber-faced incompetent Johnny English has had his licence to cock things up renewed for the second time - that name of his signalling more than anything else that he is a broad comic creation designed for non-English-speaking cinemagoing territories.
translation: Ngakho noma kanjani, umlomo ovulekile, ubuso buka-Johnny English onegunya lokusungula izinto ezintsha - lelo gama liyihlaya elikhulu elichaswe yizinkundla zabantu abangasikhulumi isiNgisi.

source: Impela uyi-ejenti yenhloli engakhaliphile okudlula ngisho nokuzenzisa kwakhe okungajwayelekile kuya kubukhazikhazi kuveza  i-Clouseau, uchatha ka Mr Bean nomfutho wakhe ovela kushuni weChariots of Fire theme kumkhosi wokuvulwa weeLondon 2012 Olympics.
reference: He is of course the daft secret agent who despite his bizarre pretensions to smoothie glamour has got a little bit of Clouseau, a dash of Mr Bean and a dollop of that chap contributing a single note to the Chariots of Fire theme tune at the London 2012 Olympics opening ceremony.
translation: Ngempela yi-ejenti yokuhlola engakhaliphile, edlutha usizo lwakhe olungajwayelekile, ifana no-Clouseau, echaza uMr Bean nomqondo owavela kwiculo yaseChariots of Fire ngomcimbi wokuvulwa kweeLondon 2012 Olympics.

source: Futhi kususelwa kumhambi nendoda yemfihlakalo uAtkinson odlula kwizikhangiso omanje sewakhohlakala eBarclaycard TV, oshiye isiphithiphithi ekuvukeni kwakhe.
reference: He's also originally based on the traveller and international man of mystery Atkinson once played in the now forgotten Barclaycard TV ads, leaving chaos in his wake.
translation: Futhi esikhathini samuva uAtkinson oshiye izincazelo zika-Barclaycard TV, ewele isiphithiphithi ekuvukeni kwakhe.

source: Kunezikhathi ezinye nezimbili kulokuvakasha kwamanje e-JE.
reference: There are one or two nice moments in this latest JE outing.
translation: Kunenkulungwane ezinye kulokhu kwakanjalo kwe-JE.

source: Ngiyamthanda uJohnny English eyogibela ihelicopter ebe egqke isudi yakudala yamasosha nezinkemba ezincane zilenga esigqokweni sakhe.
reference: I loved Johnny English approaching a helicopter while dressed in a medieval suit of armour and the rotor blades briefly clanging against his helmet.
translation: Ngiyamthanda uJohnny English eyogibela ihelicopter ebe egqke isudi yakudala yamasosha nezinkemba ezincane zilenga esigqokweni sakhe.

source: Isipho sika Atkinson samahlaya siwumbukiso, kodwa ukuhlekisa kubukeka ngathi kuphansi futhi kuyihaba kakhulu, ikakhulukazi kumkhiqizo wamafilimu ‚Äúajulile‚Äù njengo 007 neMission Impossible uqobo manje anikeza amahlaya njengesithako.
reference: Atkinson's gift for physical comedy is on display, but the humour feels pretty underpowered and weirdly superfluous, especially as the "serious" film brands like 007 and Mission Impossible themselves now confidently offer comedy as an ingredient.
translation: Isipho sika Atkinson samahlaya siwumbukiso, kodwa ukuhlekisa kubukeka ngathi kuphansi futhi kuyihaba kakhulu, ikakhulukazi kumkhiqizo wamafilimu "ajulile" njengo 007 neMission Impossible uqobo manje anikeza amahlaya njengesithako.

source: Amahlaya ngathi aphezuukwizingane kunabantu abadala, kanti kimi uhambo luka Johnny English awanahlonze futhi awamasha futhi awagxilile kwifilimu ka Atkinson engenamsindo eyengezwe ngemisindo nobuntu buka Bean.
reference: The humour feels as if it is pitched at kids rather than adults, and for me Johnny English's wacky misadventures aren't as inventive and focused as Atkinson's silent-movie gags in the persona of Bean.
translation: Amahlaya ngathi aphezuukwizingane kunabantu abadala, kanti kimi uhambo luka Johnny English awanahlonze futhi awamasha futhi awagxilile kwifilimu ka Atkinson engenamsindo eyengezwe ngemisindo nobuntu buka Bean.

source: Indaba esegudwini manje ileyo yokuthi iGreat Britain isenkigeni enkulu.
reference: The perennially topical premise now is that Great Britain is in serious trouble.
translation: Indaba esegudwini manje ileyo yokuthi iGreat Britain isenkigeni enkulu.

source: Icyber-hacker ingene kwinethiwekho eymfihlo yezinhloli yase Britain, iveza imniningwane yama-ejenti aseBritain kumkhakha, okukhathaze i-ejenti ebibekiwe emsebenzini ‚Äì okuwumsebenzi omncane kuKevin Eldon.
reference: A cyber-hacker has infiltrated Britain's super-secret web network of spies, revealing the identities of all Britain's agents in the field, to the dismay of the agent on duty - a regrettably small role for Kevin Eldon.
translation: Icyber-hacker ingene kwinethiwekho eymfihlo yezinhloli yase Britain, iveza imniningwane yama-ejenti aseBritain kumkhakha, okukhathaze i-ejenti ebibekiwe emsebenzini ‚Äì okuwumsebenzi omncane kuKevin Eldon.

source: Umzuzu wokugcina kwi-prime minister ozithwele  nosemnkantsha ubovu, obhekene nokwahluleka kumphakathi wezepolitiki: U-Emma Thompson uzama ngokusemandleni ukulingisa uTeresa-May kodwa akukho okutheni kumbhalo angasebeza ngakho.
reference: It's the last straw for a prime minister who is a pompous and embattled figure, already suffering a complete meltdown of political unpopularity: Emma Thompson does her very best with this quasi-Teresa-May character but there's nothing much in the script to work with.
translation: Umzuzu wokugcina kwi-prime minister ozithwele  nosemnkantsha obovu, obhekene nokwahluleka kumphakathi wezepolitiki: U-Emma Thompson uzama ngokusemandleni ukulingisa uTeresa-May kodwa akukho okutheni kumbhalo angasebeza ngakho.

source: Abayali bakhe bobunhloli bamazisa ukuthi yonke inhloli impintshiwe, kuzomele alande umuntu osesempeshenini.
reference: Her intelligence advisers inform her that as every single active spy has been compromised, she will have to bring someone out of retirement.
translation: Abayali bakhe bobunhloli bamazisa ukuthi yonke inhloli impintshiwe, kuzomele alande umuntu osesempeshenini.

source: Lokhu kusho ukuthi uJohnny English uqobo, manje njengo schoolmaster endaweni ebizayo, kodwa enika izifundo ezingaqoshiwe zokuthi ubakanjani inhloli: amahlaya lawa, njengoba u-English unikeza imfundiso zobunhloli eRock-type academy.
reference: And that means bumbling Johnny English himself, now employed as a schoolmaster in some posh establishment, but giving off-the-record lessons in how to be an undercover operative: some nice gags here, as English offers a School of Rock-type academy of spying.
translation: Lokhu kusho ukuthi uJohnny English uqobo, manje njengo schoolmaster endaweni ebizayo, kodwa enika izifundo ezingaqoshiwe zokuthi ubakanjani inhloli: amahlaya lawa, njengoba u-English unikeza imfundiso zobunhloli eRock-type academy.

source: U-Englishugijinyiswe eWhitehall ukuba anikwe imiyalo ephuthumayo futhi ahlanganiswe nomlingani uBough, pedlalwa futhi uBen Miller.
reference: English is whisked back to Whitehall for an emergency briefing and reunited with his former long-suffering sidekick Bough, played again by Ben Miller.
translation: U-Englishugijinyiswe eWhitehall ukuba anikwe imiyalo ephuthumayo futhi ahlanganiswe nomlingani uBough, pedlalwa futhi uBen Miller.

source: UBough useyindoda eshadile, ohlanganiswa ne-submarine commander, indawo emnandi edlalwa ngu Vicki Pepperdine okudlalwe ngaye.
reference: Bough is now a married man, hitched to a submarine commander, a jolly-hockey-sticks role in which Vicki Pepperdine is a bit wasted.
translation: UBough useyindoda eshadile, ohlanganiswa ne-submarine commander, indawo emnandi edlalwa ngu Vicki Pepperdine okudlalwe ngaye.

source: Ngakho ke uBatman noRobin wokwenza izinto zibhede impela kuSevisi eyimfihlo yeNdlovukazi ibuyile, ihlangabezana no-Olga Kurylenko's beautiful femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova.
reference: So the Batman and Robin of getting things terribly wrong on Her Majesty's Secret Service are back in action, encountering Olga Kurylenko's beautiful femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova.

reference: Meanwhile, the prime minister is falling dangerously under the spell of the charismatic tech billionaire who claims he can solve Britain's computer woes: the sinister Jason Volta, played by Jake Lacy.
translation: Lapho ke, uprime minister uyadobeka ngokushesha kwimpucuzeko zasozigidi othi yena angaxazulula izinkinga zamakhompuyutha: the sinister Jason Volta, edlalwa ngu Jake Lacy.

reference: English and Bough begin their odyssey of farcical high-jinks: disguised as waiters, they set fire to a flash French restaurant; they create mayhem smuggling themselves aboard Volta's luxury yacht; and English triggers pure anarchy as he attempts to use a Virtual Reality headset to familiarise himself with the interior of Volta's house.
translation: U-English no Bough baqala uhambo lwabooluyindida: becashe njengo weta, baqala umlilo kwindawo yokudlela eFrance; baqala inkinga bezishushumbisa ngesikebhe sikanokusho iVolta; noEnglish okususe indida ngenkathi efunda  ukusebenzisa iVirtual Reality headset ukuzijwyeza indlu kaVolt.

translation: Yonke imizamo yenziwe ukwenza ngcono isiqephu sokugcina noma sinobungane nomfutho, kune TV yezingane mayelana nayo yonke into.

source: ULabour uyaphika ukuthi besungula icebo lokuba uBritons ukusebenza izinsuku ezine kodwa kukhokhelwe izinsuku ezinhlanu
reference: Labour denies it is devising a plan for Britons to work a four day week but be paid for five days
translation: ULabour uyaphika ukuthi besungula icebo lokuba uBritons ukusebenza izinsuku ezine kodwa kukhokhelwe izinsuku ezinhlanu

source: Iqembu lika Jeremy Corbyn le- Labour ukucabanga icebo elimangalisayo elizobona uBritons esebenza izinsulu ezine ‚Äì kodwa akhokhelwe ezinhlanu.
reference: Jeremy Corbyn's Labour Party is to consider a radical plan which will see Britons working a four day week - but getting paid for five.
translation: Iqembu lika Jeremy Corbyn le- Labour ukucabanga icebo elimangalisayo elizobona uBritons esebenza izinsulu ezine ‚Äì kodwa akhokhelwe ezinhlanu.

source: Iqembu libike ukuthi lifuna abaphathi benkampani ukuba badlulise inzuzo eyenziwe nge-Artificial Intelligence (AI) kubasebenzi ngokubanika usuku olwengeziwe.
reference: The party reportedly wants company bosses to pass on savings made through the artificial intelligence (AI) revolution to workers by giving them an extra day off.
translation: Iqembu libike ukuthi lifuna abaphathi benkampani ukuba badlulise inzuzo eyenziwe nge-Artificial Intelligence (AI) kubasebenzi ngokubanika usuku olwengeziwe.

source: Kubonakala abasebenzi bethokozela izinsuku ezintathu zempela sonto ‚Äì kodwa bahole imali efanayo.
reference: It would see employees enjoy a three-day weekend - but still take home the same pay.
translation: Kubonakala abasebenzi bethokozela izinsuku ezintathu zempela sonto ‚Äì kodwa bahole imali efanayo.

source: Imithombo ithi lombono ungafanela inhloso yezomnotho yeqembu kanye nohlelo ukuguqulela isizwe kubasebenzi.
reference: Sources said the idea would 'fit' with the party's economic agenda and plans to tilt the country in favour of workers.
translation: Imithombo ithi lombono ungafanela inhloso yezomnotho yeqembu kanye nohlelo ukuguqulela isizwe kubasebenzi.

source: Ukushintshela kwizinsuku ezine kugunyazwe i-Trades Union Congress njengendlela yokuthatha ithuba lokushimtsha ummnotho.
reference: Shifting to a four-day week has been endorsed by the Trades Union Congress as a way for workers to take advantage of the changing economy.
translation: Ukushintshela kwizinsuku ezine kugunyazwe i-Trades Union Congress njengendlela yokuthatha ithuba lokushimtsha ummnotho.

source: Umthombo Labour Party osukhulile utshele The Sunday Times: 'Ukuhlolwa kwepholisi kulindeleke ukuba kwenziwa phambi kokuphela konyaka.
reference: A senior Labour Party source told The Sunday Times: 'A policy review is expected to be announced before the end of the year.
translation: Umthombo Labour Party osukhulile utshele The Sunday Times: 'Ukuhlolwa kwepholisi kulindeleke ukuba kwenziwa phambi kokuphela konyaka.

source: 'Ngeke kwenzeke ngobusuku kodwa ngeznsuku ezine esontweni kodwa ukusebenza izinsuku ezine kuyinto elangazelwe yindlela yeqembu yokubhalansa kabusha umnotho uvune abasebenzi kanye nomqondo wonke womkhakha.'
reference: 'It won't happen overnight but a four-day working week is an aspiration that fits in with the party's approach to rebalancing the economy in favour of the worker as well as the party's overall industrial strategy.'
translation: 'Ngeke kwenzeke ngobusuku kodwa ngeznsuku ezine esontweni kodwa ukusebenza izinsuku ezine kuyinto elangazelwe yindlela yeqembu yokubhalansa kabusha umnotho uvune abasebenzi kanye nomqondo wonke womkhakha.'

source: ILabour Party angeke ngeyokuqala ukutusa isu, neGreen Party ezibophezela kwizinsuku ezine zokusebenza ngesikhathi se2017 general election campaign yayo.
reference: The Labour Party would not be the first to endorse such an idea, with the Green Party pledging a four-day working week during its 2017 general election campaign.
translation: ILabour Party angeke ngeyokuqala ukutusa isu, neGreen Party ezibophezela kwizinsuku ezine zokusebenza ngesikhathi se2017 general election campaign yayo.

source: Inhloso ayikasekwa iLabour Party yonke, noma kunjalo.
reference: The aspiration is currently not being endorsed by the Labour Party as a whole, however.
translation: Inhloso ayikasekwa iLabour Party yonke, noma kunjalo.

source: Okhulumela i-Labour Party uthe: 'Umsebenzi wezinsuku ezine akuyona ipholisi yenhlangano futhi akucatshangwa nhlobo yiqembu.'
reference: A Labour Party spokesman said: 'A four-day working week is not party policy and it is not being considered by the party.'
translation: Okhulumela i-Labour Party uthe: 'Umsebenzi wezinsuku ezine akuyona ipholisi yenhlangano futhi akucatshangwa nhlobo yiqembu.'

source: Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell usebenzise inkomfa yesonto eledlule leLabour ukuveza umbono wakhe ngesocialist revolution kumnotho.
reference: Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell used last week's Labour conference to flesh out his vision for a socialist revolution in the economy.
translation: Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell usebenzise inkomfa yesonto eledlule leLabour ukuveza umbono wakhe ngesocialist revolution kumnotho.

source: Mnz McDonnell uthe uzimisele ukuqwaba futhi amandla abuye ‚Äòkubaqondisi abangaziwa‚Äô ‚Äònabazuzi‚Äô kumafemu omhiqizo.
reference: Mr McDonnell said he was determined to claw back power from 'faceless directors' and 'profiteers' at utility firms.
translation: Mnz McDonnell uthe uzimisele ukuqwaba futhi amandla abuye 'kubaqondisi abangaziwa' 'nabazuzi' kumafemu omhiqizo.

source: Uhlelo futhi le-shadow chancellor luchaza futhi ukuthi ama-shareholders ezinkampanini zamanzi kungenzeka bangasitholi sonke isiteki njengohulumeni weLabour enza ‚Äòukudonsa‚Äô ngokwezindlela ezingalungile.
reference: The shadow chancellor's plans also mean current shareholders in water companies may not get back their entire stake as a Labour government could make 'deductions' on the grounds of perceived wrongdoing.
translation: Uhlelo futhi le-shadow chancellor luchaza futhi ukuthi ama-shareholders ezinkampanini zamanzi kungenzeka bangasitholi sonke isiteki njengohulumeni weLabour enza 'ukudonsa' ngokwezindlela ezingalungile.

source: Uphinde waqinisekisa ukufaka abasebenzi kumabhodi enkampani naku-Inclusive Ownership Funds ukunika 10 per cent of private-sector firms' equity kubasebenzi, abazohlomula ngonyaka inzuzo elinganiselwe ku¬£500.
reference: He also confirmed plans to put workers on company boards and create Inclusive Ownership Funds to hand 10 per cent of private-sector firms' equity to employees, who stand to pocket annual dividends of up to ¬£500.
translation: Uphinde waqinisekisa ukufaka abasebenzi kumabhodi enkampani naku-Inclusive Ownership Funds ukunika 10 per cent of private-sector firms' equity kubasebenzi, abazohlomula ngonyaka inzuzo elinganiselwe ku¬£500.

translation: Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy batshena "60 Minutes" ukuthi ucwaningo lweFBI ngoKavanaugh kungashintsha izingqondo zabo.

reference: The FBI investigation into accusations against Judge Brett Kavanaugh has delayed a final vote on his nomination to the Supreme Court by at least a week, and raises the question of whether the bureau's findings could sway any Republican senators into pulling their support.
translation: Uphenyo ngezinsolo zeFBI ngejaji uBrett Kavanaugh kuhlehlise isikhathi sokuvotelwa ukuaqokelwe iSupreme Court ngesonto eledlule, nokuphakamisa imibuzo ukuthi okutholwe abaseshi kungashintsha indlela ama-senator eRepublican anxenxa ngayo abalandeli.

source: Yini i-Global Citizen Festival futhi Isike Yazama Ukunciphisa Ububha?
reference: What is the Global Citizen Festival and Has it Done Anything to Decrease Poverty?
translation: Yini i-Global Citizen Festival futhi Isike Yazama Ukunciphisa Ububha?

source: Kulo Mgqibelo iNew York izosingatha iGlobal Citizen Festival, umcimbi wanyaka yonke olunohlu lwabadlali abanohlonzeabazodlala nabanenhloso efanayo; yokuqeda ububha emhlabeni.
reference: This Saturday New York will host the Global Citizen Festival, an annual music event which has a hugely impressive line-up of stars performing and an equally impressive mission; ending world poverty.
translation: Kulo Mgqibelo iNew York izosingatha iGlobal Citizen Festival, umcimbi wanyaka yonke olunohlu lwabadlali abanohlonzeabazodlala nabanenhloso efanayo; yokuqeda ububha emhlabeni.

source: Manje kunyaka wesikhombisa, iGlobal Citizen Festival izoba nezinkumbi zabantu betheleka egcekeni elikhulu eCentral Park ukungathokoziswa kuphela uJanet Jackson, Cardi B no Shawn Mendes, kodwa ukuqwashisa ngenhloso yangempela yokuqeda ububha ngo 2030.
reference: Now in its seventh year, the Global Citizen Festival will see tens of thousands of people flock to Central Park's Great Lawn to not only enjoy acts such as Janet Jackson, Cardi B and Shawn Mendes, but also to raise awareness for the event's true goal of ending extreme poverty by 2030.
translation: Manje kunyaka wesikhombisa, iGlobal Citizen Festival izoba nezinkumbi zabantu betheleka egcekeni elikhulu eCentral Park ukungathokoziswa kuphela uJanet Jackson, Cardi B no Shawn Mendes, kodwa ukuqwashisa ngenhloso yangempela yokuqeda ububha ngo 2030.

source: I-Global Citizen Festival, echazwe ngo 2012, okuyisixhantela seGlobal Poverty Project, iqembu lomhlaba olulwela ukuqeda ububha ngokwandisa abantu abakulwelayo.
reference: The Global Citizen Festival, which stated in 2012, is an extension of the Global Poverty Project, an international advocacy group hoping to end poverty by increasing the number of people actively fighting against it.
translation: I-Global Citizen Festival, echazwe ngo 2012, okuyisixhantela seGlobal Poverty Project, iqembu lomhlaba olulwela ukuqeda ububha ngokwandisa abantu abakulwelayo.

source: Ukuze uthole ithikithi lomcimbi (ngaphandle kokuthi ufuna ukukhokhela amathikithi e- VIP ticket), abahambi khionsathi bekumele benze kuthile ‚Äúokuyizenzo‚Äù njengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyili kumholi womhlaba, ukufona noma ukwenza okunye okujulile ukusiza uqwashise ngokuqeda ububha.
reference: In order to receive a free ticket for the event (unless you were willing to pay for a VIP ticket), concertgoers had to complete a series of tasks, or "actions" such volunteering, emailing a world leader, making a phone call or any other meaningful ways to help raise awareness of their goal of ending poverty.
translation: Ukuze uthole ithikithi lomcimbi (ngaphandle kokuthi ufuna ukukhokhela amathikithi e- VIP ticket), abahambi khionsathi bekumele benze kuthile "okuyizenzo" njengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyili kumholi womhlaba, ukufona noma ukwenza okunye okujulile ukusiza uqwashise ngokuqeda ububha.

source: Ingabe ibe yimpumelelo kangakanani i-Global Citizen eminyakeni engu 12 esele ukufinyelela lumgomo wayo?
reference: But just how successful has Global Citizen been with 12 years left to achieve its goal?
translation: Ingabe ibe yimpumelelo kangakanani i-Global Citizen eminyakeni engu 12 esele ukufinyelela lumgomo wayo?

source: Ingabe umqondo wokuzuzisa abantu ngekhonsathi yamahhala kuyindlela efanele ukuzama abantu ukuba benze okuthile, noma okunye nje okubizwa "i-clicktivism" ‚Äì abantu abazizwa ngathi benza umehluko ngokusayina uhlu kwikhompiyutha noma ukuthumela kutwitter?
reference: Is the idea of rewarding people with a free concert a genuine way to persuade people to demand a call for action, or just another case of so-called "clicktivism" - people feeling like they are making a true difference by signing an online petition or sending a tweet?
translation: Ingabe umqondo wokuzuzisa abantu ngekhonsathi yamahhala kuyindlela efanele ukuzama abantu ukuba benze okuthile, noma okunye nje okubizwa "i-clicktivism" ‚Äì abantu abazizwa ngathi benza umehluko ngokusayina uhlu kwikhompiyutha noma ukuthumela kutwitter?

source: Kusukela ngo 2011, i-Global Citizen isiqophe ‚Äúizenzo‚Äù zabalandeli babo ezingaphezu kwa 19 million, kuphushwa ukusingathwa kwezinhloso ezahlukene.
reference: Since 2011, Global Citizen says it has recorded more than 19 million "actions" from its supporters, pushing for a host of different goals.
translation: Kusukela ngo 2011, i-Global Citizen isiqophe "izenzo" zabalandeli babo ezingaphezu kwa 19 million, kuphushwa ukusingathwa kwezinhloso ezahlukene.

source: Ithi lezenzo sisizile ukucijisa abahli bomhlaba ekwathuleni ukuzinekela kanye nezinqubomgomo ezinga phezu kwa $37 billion ezothinta izimpilo zabantu abangu 2.25 billion ngo 2030.
reference: It says that these actions have helped spur world leaders to announce commitments and policies equating to more than $37 billion that is set to affect the lives of more than 2.25 billion people by 2030.
translation: Ithi lezenzo sisizile ukucijisa abahli bomhlaba ekwathuleni ukuzinekela kanye nezinqubomgomo ezinga phezu kwa $37 billion ezothinta izimpilo zabantu abangu 2.25 billion ngo 2030.

source: Ngo 2018 uqala, iqembu licoshe imibono engu 390 kanye nezaziso kusukela kwizenzo zabo, cishe $10 billion osukhishiwe noma wazanywa ukuqoqwa.
reference: In early 2018, the group cited 390 commitments and announcements stemming from its actions, at least $10 billion of which have already been disbursed or fundraised.
translation: Ngo 2018 uqala, iqembu licoshe imibono engu 390 kanye nezaziso kusukela kwizenzo zabo, cishe $10 billion osukhishiwe noma wazanywa ukuqoqwa.

source: Iqembu lilinganisela ukuthi imali etholiwe ibenomthelela ngqo kubantu cishe abawu 649 million emhlabeni jikelele.
reference: The group estimates the secured funds have so far made a direct impact on nearly 649 million people across the world.
translation: Iqembu lilinganisela ukuthi imali etholiwe ibenomthelela ngqo kubantu cishe abawu 649 million emhlabeni jikelele.

source: Okunye ukuzinikela kubandakanya The Power of Nutrition, abalingani base U.K. babatshali zimali nobaqalisi abazinikele "ukusiza abantwana ngendlela efanele," kuthenjiswa ukunikeza Rwanda $35 million ukusiza kupheliswe indlala ezweni emvakokuthola 4,700 tweets kwiGlobal Citizens.
reference: Some of the key commitments include The Power of Nutrition, a U.K. based partnership of investors and implementers committed to "helping children grow to their full potential," promising to provide Rwanda with $35 million to help end malnutrition in the county after receiving more than 4,700 tweets from Global Citizens.
translation: Okunye ukuzinikela kubandakanya The Power of Nutrition, abalingani base U.K. babatshali zimali nobaqalisi abazinikele "ukusiza abantwana ngendlela efanele," kuthenjiswe ukunikeza Rwanda $35 million ukusiza kupheliswe indlala ezweni emvakokuthola 4,700 tweets kwiGlobal Citizens.

source: Ngokokusekwa uhulumeni wase UK, abanikelayo, ohulumeni bamazwe, ne Global Citizens efana nawe, singazama ukwenza kube umlando ukungondleki kwabantu ngenxa yokungabikho kobulungiswa kumphakathi, I- Power of Nutrition ambassador Tracey Ullman utshene uquqaba bukhoma kwikhonsathi eLondon ngo April 2018.
reference: With support from the UK government, donors, national governments, and Global Citizens just like you, we can make the social injustice of undernutrition a footnote in history, The Power of Nutrition ambassador Tracey Ullman told the crowd during a live concert in London in April 2018.
translation: Ngokokusekwa uhulumeni wase UK, abanikelayo, ohulumeni bamazwe, ne Global Citizens efana nawe, singazama ukwenza kube umlando ukungondleki kwabantu ngenxa yokungabikho kobulungiswa kumphakathi, I- Power of Nutrition ambassador Tracey Ullman utshene uquqaba bukhoma kwikhonsathi eLondon ngo April 2018.

source: Iqembu liphinde lathi kube neminyakazo engaphezu kwe 5,000 ukubiza U.K. yenze ngcono ukudla okunomsoco komama nabantwana, uhulumeni umemezele uxhaso lwephrojekthi, i-Power of Nutrition, ezofinyelela kwabesifazane nezingane ezingu 5 million ngokungenelel ngokokudla okunomsoco.
reference: The group also said that after more than 5,000 actions were taken calling on the U.K. improve nutrition for mothers and children, the government announced funding for a project, the Power of Nutrition, that will reach 5 million women and children with nutrition interventions.
translation: Iqembu liphinde lathi kube neminyakazo engaphezu kwe 5,000 ukubiza U.K. yenze ngcono ukudla okunomsoco komama nabantwana, uhulumeni umemezele uxhaso lwephrojekthi, i-Power of Nutrition, ezofinyelela kwabesifazane nezingane ezingu 5 million ngokungenelel ngokokudla okunomsoco.

source: Ekuphenduleni eminye ye-FAQs kwiwebhusayithi yabo ebuza "yini ocabanga ukuthi singayenza ukuqeda ububha obukhulu?"
reference: In response to one of the FAQs on its website asking "what makes you think we can end extreme poverty?"
translation: Ekuphenduleni eminye ye-FAQs kwiwebhusayithi yabo ebuza "yini ocabanga ukuthi singayenza ukuqeda ububha obukhulu?"

source: Global citizen iphendulile: "Kuzoba indlela ende nenzima ‚Äì ngezinye isikhathi sizowa futhi sehluleke.
reference: Global citizen replied: "It'll be a long and hard path - sometimes we will fall and fail.
translation: Global citizen iphendulile: "Kuzoba indlela ende nenzima ‚Äì ngezinye isikhathi sizowa futhi sehluleke.

source: Kodwa, njengamalungelo omphakathi nemibhikisho ye-anti-apartheid phambi kwethu, sizonqoba, ngoba sinamandla kakhulu ndawonye.
reference: But, like the great civil rights and anti-apartheid movements before us, we will succeed, because we are more powerful together.
translation: Kodwa, njengamalungelo omphakathi nemibhikisho ye-anti-apartheid phambi kwethu, sizonqoba, ngoba sinamandla kakhulu ndawonye.
