reference: Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Mon√°e are among some of the acts performing at this year's event in New York, which will be hosted by Deborra-Lee Furness and Hugh Jackman.
translation: Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Mon√°e abanye abazonandisa kulo mcimbi walonyaka eNew York, ezobe ibungazwe ngu Deborra-Lee Furness no Hugh Jackman.

source: US ingahle isebenzzise Amantilosi "kukuvimba" ukuvimbela ukuthunyelwa kwe-energy yase Russia - Interior Secretary
reference: US could use Navy for "blockade" to hamper Russian energy exports - Interior Secretary
translation: US ingahle isebenzzise Amantilosi "kukuvimba" ukuvimbela ukuthunyelwa kwe-energy yase Russia - Interior Secretary

source: Washington "uma kudingeka" ingasebenzisa Amantilosi ukuvimba izimakethe zase Russian ze-energy,kubandakanya  i-Middle East, US Internal Secretary Ryan Zinke wambule, ngokucoshwe iWashington Examiner.
reference: Washington can "if necessary" resort to its Navy to prevent Russian energy hitting the markets, including in the Middle East, US Internal Secretary Ryan Zinke has revealed, as cited by Washington Examiner.
translation: Washington "uma kudingeka" ingasebenzisa Amantilosi ukuvimba izimakethe zase Russian ze-energy,kubandakanya  i-Middle East, US Internal Secretary Ryan Zinke wambule, ngokucoshwe iWashington Examiner.

source: Zinke uthe izingxoxo zeRussia neSyria - ngokucacile, lapho isebenza ngokumenya kukahulumeni osemthethweni ‚Äì kuyindlela yokuzama ezinye izimakethe ezintsha ze-energy.
reference: Zinke alleged that Russia's engagement in Syria - notably, where it is operating at the invitation of the legitimate government - is a pretext to explore new energy markets.
translation: Zinke uthe izingxoxo zeRussia neSyria - ngokucacile, lapho isebenza ngokumenya kukahulumeni osemthethweni ‚Äì kuyindlela yokuzama ezinye izimakethe ezintsha ze-energy.

source: Ngiyakholelwa kwisizathu sokuba se-Middle East bafuna ukuthola i-energy njengase eastern Europe, nasenkabeni yase nigizimu ne-Europe, ebika.
reference: I believe the reason they are in the Middle East is they want to broker energy just like they do in eastern Europe, the southern belly of Europe, he has reportedly said.
translation: Ngiyakholelwa kwisizathu sokuba se-Middle East bafuna ukuthola i-energy njengase eastern Europe, nasenkabeni yase nigizimu ne-Europe, ebika.

source: Futhi, ngokuvumelana nesisebenzi, kunezindlela zokuyilungisa.
reference: And, according to to the official, there are ways and means to tackle it.
translation: Futhi, ngokuvumelana nesisebenzi, kunezindlela zokuyilungisa.

source: I-United States iyakwazi, Ngebutho lethu, ukuqinisekisa ukuthi izindlela zasolwandle ziyavulwa, futhi, uma kudingeka, zivalwe, ukuze kuqikelelwe ukuthi amandla abo awayi ezimakethe, kusho yena.
reference: The United States has that ability, with our Navy, to make sure the sea lanes are open, and, if necessary, to blockade, to make sure that their energy does not go to market, he said.
translation: I-United States iyakwazi, Ngebutho lethu, ukuqinisekisa ukuthi izindlela zasolwandle ziyavulwa, futhi, uma kudingeka, zivalwe, ukuze kuqikelelwe ukuthi amandla abo awayi ezimakethe, kusho yena.

source: U-Zinke ubekhuluma nababekhona emcimbini ebisingathwa yi-Consumer Energy Alliance, iqembu elingenzi nzuzo elizibiza ngokuthi "iphimbo lomsebenzisi wamandla" e-US.
reference: Zinke was addressing the attendees of the event hosted by the Consumer Energy Alliance, a non-profit group which styles itself as the "voice of the energy consumer" in the US.
translation: U-Zinke ubekhuluma nababekhona emcimbini ebisingathwa yi-Consumer Energy Alliance, iqembu elingenzi nzuzo elizibiza ngokuthi "iphimbo lomsebenzisi wamandla" e-US.

source: Wabuye waqhathanisa nemizamo yase-Washington wokusebenzelana ne-Russia ne-Iran, ethi imiphumela iyafana.
reference: He went to compare Washington's approaches to dealing with Russia and Iran, noting that they are effectively the same.
translation: Wabuye waqhathanisa nemizamo yase-Washington wokusebenzelana ne-Russia ne-Iran, ethi imiphumela iyafana.

source: Ukukhetha ukuhwebelana ne-Iran ne-Russia, ngokwezinga elithile, kuyindlela yokuzuza nokuthola uwoyela, kusho yena, ngesikhathi ekhuluma nge-Russia ethi "liyihhashi elinamaqhinga" futhi linomnotho othembele ezinsaleleni zikawoyela.
reference: The economic option on Iran and Russia is, more or less, leveraging and replacing fuels, he said, while referring to Russia as a "one trick pony" with an economy dependent on fossil fuels.
translation: Ukukhetha ukuhwebelana ne-Iran ne-Russia, ngokwezinga elithile, kuyindlela yokuzuza nokuthola uwoyela, kusho yena, ngesikhathi ekhuluma nge-Russia ethi "liyihhashi elinamaqhinga" futhi linomnotho othembele ezinsaleleni zikawoyela.

source: Lezi zitatimende zivele njengoba abehhovisi lika-Trump benza imizamo yokukhuthaza ukuthunyelwa kwegesi yabo yemvelo ewuketshezi eYurophu, ingene esikhundleni se-Russia, indlela eshibhe kakhulu kubathengi baseYurophu.
reference: The statements come as Trump administration has been on a mission to boost the export of its liquefied natural gas to Europe, replacing Russia, the far cheaper option for European consumers.
translation: Lezi zitatimende zivele njengoba abehhovisi lika-Trump benza imizamo yokukhuthaza ukuthunyelwa kwegesi yabo yemvalo ewuketshezi eYurophu, ingene esikhundleni se-Russia, indlela eshibhe kakhulu kubathengi baseYurophu.

source: Ngenxa yalokho, izikhulu zehhovisi lika-Trump, kuhlanganise nomongameli wase-US u-Donald Trump ngokwakhe, zizama ukukhuthaza iJalimane ukuba liphume kuprojekthi yamapayiphi ye-Nord Stream 2 "engafaneleki", ngokuka-Trump, eyenze i-Berlin yaba "ngaphansi" kwe-Moscow.
reference: For that effect, the Trump administration officials, including US President Donald Trump himself, try to persuade Germany to pull out of the "inappropriate" Nord Stream 2 pipeline project, which according to Trump, made Berlin Moscow's "captive."
translation: Ngenxa yalokho, izikhulu zehhovisi lika-Trump, kuhlanganise nomongameli wase-US u-Donald Trump ngokwakhe, zizama ukukhuthaza iJalimane ukuba liphume kuprojekthi yamapayiphi ye-Nord Stream 2 "engafaneleki", ngokuka-Trump, eyenze i-Berlin yaba "ngaphansi" kwe-Moscow.

source: I-Moscow iye yagcizelela ngokuphindaphindiwe ukuthi amapayipi e-Nord Stream 2 angu-$11 billion, okuhlelwe ukuba iwuphinde kabili umthamo wamapayipi akhona manje ube ngamamitha angu-110 billion cubic, ngempela ayiphrojekthi yezomnotho.
reference: Moscow has repeatedly stressed that the $11 billion Nord Stream 2 pipeline, which is set to double the existing pipeline capacity to 110 billion cubic meters, is a purely economic project.
translation: I-Moscow iye yagcizelela ngokuphindaphindiwe ukuthi amapayipi e-Nord Stream 2 angu-$11 billion, okuhlelwe ukuba iwuphinde kabili umthamo wamapayipi akhona manje ube ngamamitha angu-110 billion cubic, ngempela ayiphrojekthi yezomnotho.

source: Amalungu endibano (AMs) yaseWales anexhala lokukhangeleka ngathi azizidenge
reference: Welsh AMs worried about 'looking like muppets'
translation: Amalungu endibano (AMs) yaseWales anesidingo sokwazi ngokucacileyo

source: Kukho ii-AMs ezinexhala kuba kuphakanyiswa ukuba kutshintshwe indlela ezibizwa ngayo ibe ngu-MWPs (Ilungu Lepalamente YaseWales).
reference: There is consternation among some AMs at a suggestion their title should change to MWPs (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
translation: Kukho ii-AMs ezinengxaki kuba kuphakanyiswa ukuba kutshintshwe indlela ezibizwa ngayo ibe ngu-MWPs (Ilungu Lepalamente YaseWales).

source: Kuye kwaphakanyiswa loo nto kuba kukho izicwangciso zokutshintsha igama lendibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.
reference: It has arisen because of plans to change the name of the assembly to the Welsh Parliament.
translation: Kuye kwaphakanyiswa loo nto kuba kukho izicwangciso zokutshintsha igama lendibano libe yiPalamente yaseWales.

source: Ii-AMs kwezopolitiko zonke zinexhala lokuba le nto iza kwenza zigezelwe.
reference: AMs across the political spectrum are worried it could invite ridicule.
translation: Ii-AMs kwezopolitiko zonke zinengxaki yokuba le nto iza kwenza zikhathazeke.

source: Enye i-AM YeLabour ithi iqela lakhe linexhala lokuba indlela elibizwa ngayo eli gama litsha isondele kwindlela ekubizwa ngayo u‚ÄùTwp‚Äù no‚ÄúPwp.‚Äù
reference: One Labour AM said his group was concerned "it rhymes with Twp and Pwp."
translation: Enye i-AM YeLabour ithi iqela lakhe linengxaki lokuba indlela elibizwa ngayo eli gama litsha isondele kwindlela ekubizwa ngayo u"Twp" no"Pwp."

source: Kumfundi ongahlali eWales: NgesiWelsh utwp uthetha isidenge kanti upwp uthetha ituwa.
reference: For readers outside of Wales: In Welsh twp means daft and pwp means poo.
translation: Kumfundi ongahlali eWales: NgesiWelsh utwp uthetha isidenge kanti upwp uthetha ituwa.

source: I-AM yombutho waseWales uthe umbutho wonke awuyithandi le nto, ibe ucebise ngamanye amagama.
reference: A Plaid AM said the group as a whole was "not happy" and has suggested alternatives.
translation: I-AM yombutho waseWales uthe umbutho wonke awuyithandi le nto, ibe ucebise ngamanye amagama.

source: Ilungu le-Conservative eWales lona lithi iqela lakhe alinangxaki nokutshintshwa kwegama, kodwa libonile ukuba kungalula ukubiza u-MWP ngendlela obiza ngayo isidenge.
reference: A Welsh Conservative said his group was "open minded" about the name change, but noted it was a short verbal hop from MWP to Muppet.
translation: Ilungu le-Conservative eWales lona lithi iqela lakhe alinangxaki nokutshintshwa kwegama, kodwa libonile ukuba kungalula ukubiza u-MWP ngendlela obiza ngayo isidenge.

source: Kule meko indlela unobumba ongu-w abizwa ngayo ngesiWelsh iyafana nendlela abizwa ngayo unobumba ongu-u ngesiNgesi.
reference: In this context The Welsh letter w is pronounced similarly to the Yorkshire English pronunciation of the letter u.
translation: Kule meko indlela unobumba ongu-w abizwa ngayo ngesiWelsh iyafana nendlela abizwa ngayo unobumba ongu-u ngesiNgesi.

source: I-Assembly Commission, exakeke kukuqulunqa umthetho ongowokutshintsha igama ibe leli litsha, ithe: "Isigqibo sendlela yokubiza Amalungu Endibano siza kuthathwa ngamalungu ngokwawo."
reference: The Assembly Commission, which is currently drafting legislation to introduce the name changes, said: "The final decision on any descriptors of what Assembly Members are called will of course be a matter for the members themselves."
translation: I-Assembly Commission, exakeke kukuqulunqa umthetho ongowokutshintsha igama ibe leli litsha, ithe: "Isigqibo sendlela yokubiza Amalungu Endibano siza kuthathwa ngamalungu ngokwawo."

source: I-Government of Wales Act 2017 yanika indibano yaseWales imvume yokuba ilitshintshe igama layo.
reference: The Government of Wales Act 2017 gave the Welsh assembly the power to change its name.
translation: I-Government of Wales Act 2017 yanika indibano yaseWales imvume yokuba ilitshintshe igama layo.

source: NgoJuni, i-Commission ikhuphe iziphumo zeempendulo zabantu ibe ifumanise ukuba uninzi luyayixhasa into yokuba indibano itshintshe ibizwe ngokuba yiPalamante yaseWales.
reference: In June, the Commission published the results of a public consultation on the proposals which found broad support for calling the assembly a Welsh Parliament.
translation: NgoJuni, i-Commission ikhuphe iziphumo zeempendulo zabantu ibe ifumanise ukuba uninzi luyayixhasa into yokuba indibano itshintshe ibizwe ngokuba yiPalamante yaseWales.

source: Kumba wendlela yokubiza ii-AMs, i-Commission ithande eli lithi Amalungu EPalamente yaseWales okanye ii-WMPs, kodwa abantu bona baxhase le ka-MWP.
reference: On the matter of the AMs' title, the Commission favoured Welsh Parliament Members or WMPs, but the MWP option received the most support in a public consultation.
translation: Kumba wendlela yokubiza ii-AMs, i-Commission ithande eli lithi Amalungu EPalamente yaseWales okanye ii-WMPs, kodwa abantu bona baxhase le ka-MWP.

source: II-AMs kuthiwa zicebisa ngenye indlela, kodwa into yokuba kunzima ukuba kuvisiswane ngalo mba kumele ukuba yingxaki kuElin Jones, Igosa Elongamelayo , olindeleke ukuba afake umthetho ngotshintsho kwiiveki nje ezizayo.
reference: AMs are apparently suggesting alternative options, but the struggle to reach consensus could be a headache for the Presiding Officer, Elin Jones, who is expected to submit draft legislation on the changes within weeks.
translation: II-AMs kuthiwa zicebisa ngenye indlela, kodwa into yokuba kunzima ukuba kuvisiswane ngalo mba kumele ukuba yingxaki kuElin Jones, Igosa Elongamelayo, olindeleke ukuba afake umthetho ngotshintsho kwiiveki nje ezizayo.

source: Lo mthetho wotshintsho uza kuquka nezinye izinto eziza kutshintshwa njengendlela indibano esebenza ngayo, kuquka imithetho yokuyekisa ii-AMs nendlela ebunjwe ngayo inkqubo yekomiti.
reference: The legislation on the reforms will include other changes to the way the assembly works, including rules on disqualification of AMs and the design of the committee system.
translation: Lo mthetho wotshintsho uza kuquka nezinye izinto eziza kutshintshwa njengendlela indibano esebenza ngayo, kuquka imithetho yokuyekisa ii-AMs nendlela ebunjwe ngayo inkqubo yekomiti.

source: Zivoti zee-AMs eziza kubala ekugqibeleni xa kuxoxwa ngalo mthetho kumbuzo wokuba zibizwe njani.
reference: AMs will get the final vote on the question of what they should be called when they debate the legislation.
translation: Zivoti zee-AMs eziza kubala ekugqibeleni xa kuxoxwa ngalo mthetho kumbuzo wokuba zibizwe njani.

source: Abantu baseMakedoni bayokuvotela ukutshintsha igama lelizwe labo
reference: Macedonians go to polls in referendum on changing country's name
translation: Abantu baseMakedoni bayokuvotela ukutshintsha igama lelizwe labo

source: Abavoti baza kuvota ngeCawa enoba batshintshe igama lelizwe labo libe yi"Riphablikhi Yomntla Makedoni."
reference: Voters will vote Sunday on whether to change their country's name to the "Republic of North Macedonia."
translation: Abavoti baza kuvota ngeCawa enoba batshintshe igama lelizwe labo libe yi"Riphablikhi Yomntla Makedoni."

source: Le voti yenzelwe ukucombulula ingxabano enamashumi eminyaka iqhuba nelizwe eliselumelwaneni iGrisi enephondo elibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.
reference: The popular vote was set up in a bid to resolve a decades-long dispute with neighboring Greece, which has its own province called Macedonia.
translation: Le voti yenzelwe ukucombulula ingxabano enamashumi eminyaka iqhuba nelizwe eliselumelwaneni iGrisi enephondo elibizwa ngokuba yiMakedoni.

source: Ama-Athene wona kudala ema ngelithi igama labamelwane abo abasemntla lenza ngathi banebango kummandla wabo, ibe kudala bephikisana nesicelo sabo sokuba ngamalungu e- EU nawe-NATO.
reference: Athens has long insisted that its northern neighbor's name represents a claim on its territory and has repeatedly objected to its membership bids for the EU and NATO.
translation: Ama-Athene wona kudala ema ngelithi igama labamelwane abo abasemntla lenza ngathi banebango kummandla wabo, ibe kudala bephikisana nesicelo sabo sokuba ngamalungu e- EU nawe-NATO.

source: Umongameli waseMakedoni, uGjorge Ivanov, ochasene nale voti yokutshintshwa kwegama, uthe akazoyihoya yena ivoti.
reference: Macedonian President Gjorge Ivanov, an opponent of the plebiscite on the name change, has said he will disregard the vote.
translation: Umongameli waseMakedoni, uGjorge Ivanov, ochasene nale voti yokutshintshwa kwegama, uthe akazoyihoya yena ivoti.

source: Kodwa ke, abantu abayixhasayo le voti, kuquka iNkulumbuso Zoran Zaev, uthi le nto yokutshintsha igama lixabiso ekufuneka belibhatele ukuze bajoyine i-EU ne-NATO.
reference: However, supporters of the referendum, including Prime Minister Zoran Zaev, argue that the name change is simply the price to pay to join the EU and NATO.
translation: Kodwa ke, abantu abayixhasayo le voti, kuquka iNkulumbuso Zoran Zaev, uthi le nto yokutshintsha igama lixabiso ekufuneka belibhatele ukuze bajoyine i-EU ne-NATO.

source: Iintsimbi Zase-St. Martin Azibethwa Njengoko Zitsala Nzima IiCawa E-Harlem
reference: The Bells of St. Martin's Fall Silent as Churches in Harlem Struggle
translation: Iintsimbi Zase-St. Martin Azibethwa Njengoko Zitsala Nzima IiCawa E-Harlem

source: UMnu. uAdams uthe: "Abantu abadala endithethe nabo bathi kudala kwakukho ibhari necawa kuyo yonke indawo."
reference: Historically, the old people I've talked to say there was a bar and a church on every corner, Mr. Adams said.
translation: UMnu. uAdams uthe: "Abantu abadala endithethe nabo bathi kudala kwakukho ibhari necawa kuyo yonke indawo."

source: Namhlanje, akukho nenye yazo.
reference: Today, there's neither.
translation: Namhlanje, akukho nenye yazo.

source: Uthe uyaqonda ukuba kutheni iibhari zavele azabikho.
reference: He said the disappearance of bars was understandable.
translation: Uthe uyaqonda ukuba kutheni iibhari zavele azabikho.

source: Uthe: "Abantu bazonwabisa ngenye indlela" kule mihla.
reference: People socialize in a different way nowadays, he said.
translation: Uthe: "Abantu bazonwabisa ngenye indlela" kule mihla.

source: IIbhari ayisezo ndawo zokuhlala elumelwaneni apho abantu baya khona qho.
reference: Bars are no longer neighborhood living rooms where people go on a regular basis.
translation: IIbhari ayisezo ndawo zokuhlala elumelwaneni apho abantu baya khona qho.

source: Unexhala ngeecawa ngoba ucinga ukuba imali eziyifumene ngokuthengisa izinto zayo ayizokuhlala ixesha elide njengokuba iinkokeli zicinga njalo, "ibe kungekudala ziza kubuyela kwimeko ebezikuzo ekuqaleni."
reference: As for churches, he worries that the money from selling assets will not last as long as leaders expect it to, "and sooner or later they'll be right back where they started."
translation: Unexhala ngeecawa ngoba ucinga ukuba imali eziyifumene ngokuthengisa izinto zayo ayizokuhlala ixesha elide njengokuba iinkokeli zicinga njalo, "ibe kungekudala ziza kubuyela kwimeko ebezikuzo ekuqaleni."

source: Wongeze ngelithi, iicawa zinokuthathelwa iindawo ziifleti ezinabantu ezingasoze zincede ekugcineni iindawo ezingcwele zasekuhlaleni ezisashiyekileyo.
reference: Churches, he added, could be replaced by apartment buildings with condominiums filled with the kind of people who will not help the neighborhood's remaining sanctuaries.
translation: Wongeze ngelithi, iicawa zinokuthathelwa iindawo ziifleti ezinabantu ezingasoze zincede ekugcineni iindawo ezingcwele zasekuhlaleni ezisashiyekileyo.

source: Uthe: "Abantu abaninzi abathenga ezi fleti ngabantu abamhlophe. Ngoko iza kukhawuleza ukufika imini eziya kuthi zivalwe tu ngayo iicawa, kuba akubonakali ngathi aba bantu abathuthela kwezi fleti bangabangamalungu ezi cawa."
reference: The overwhelming majority of people who buy condominiums in these buildings will be white, he said, "and therefore will hasten the day that these churches close altogether because it is unlikely that most of these people who move into these condominiums will become members of these churches."
translation: Uthe: "Abantu abaninzi abathenga ezi fleti ngabantu abamhlophe. Ngoko iza kukhawuleza ukufika imini eziya kuthi zivalwe tu ngayo iicawa, kuba akubonakali ngathi aba bantu abathuthela kwezi fleti bangabangamalungu ezi cawa."

source: Zombini ezi cawa zazingamabandla abantu abamhlophe ngaphambi kokuba i-Harlem ibe yindawo yabantu abamnyama, i- Metropolitan Community ngo-1870, e-St. Martin kwishumi leminyaka kamva.
reference: Both churches were built by white congregations before Harlem became a black metropolis - Metropolitan Community in 1870, St. Martin's a decade later.
translation: Zombini ezi cawa zazingamabandla abantu abamhlophe ngaphambi kokuba i-Harlem ibe yindawo yabantu abamnyama, i- Metropolitan Community ngo-1870, e-St. Martin kwishumi leminyaka kamva.

source: Ibandla lamaWesile lokuqala elalimhlophe laphuma ngeeminyaka yoo-1930.
reference: The original white Methodist congregation moved out in the 1930s.
translation: Ibandla lamaWesile lokuqala elalimhlophe laphuma ngeeminyaka yoo-1930.

source: Ibandla elimnyama ebelikhonzela kufutshane laba lesaso eso sakhiwe.
reference: A black congregation that had been worshiping nearby took title to the building.
translation: Ibandla elimnyama ebelikhonzela kufutshane laba lesaso eso sakhiwe.

source: I-St. Martin yaba libandla elimnyama phantsi koMfu. uJohn Howard Johnson, owayekhokela itoyitoyi yabathengisi e125th Street, esona sitrato kuthengwa kuso eHarlem, ababechasene nokungaqeshwa nokungaxhaswa kwabantu abamnyama.
reference: St. Martin's was taken over by a black congregation under the Rev. John Howard Johnson, who led a boycott of retailers on 125th Street, a main street for shopping in Harlem, who resisted hiring or promoting blacks.
translation: I-St. Martin yaba libandla elimnyama phantsi koMfu. uJohn Howard Johnson, owayekhokela itoyitoyi yabathengisi e125th Street, esona sitrato kuthengwa kuso eHarlem, ababechasene nokungaqeshwa nokungaxhaswa kwabantu abamnyama.

source: Ngo-1939 esi sakhiwo sonakaliswa kakhulu ngumlilo, kodwa njengoko amarhamente kaTat‚Äô uJohnson ayelungiselela ukuphinda asakhe, kwathiwa makubethwe iintsimbi.
reference: A fire in 1939 left the building badly damaged, but as Father Johnson's parishioners made plans to rebuild, they commissioned the carillon.
translation: Ngo-1939 esi sakhiwo sonakaliswa kakhulu ngumlilo, kodwa njengoko amarhamente kaTat' uJohnson ayelungiselela ukuphinda asakhe, kwathiwa makubethwe iintsimbi.

source: Umfu. uDavid Johnson, unyana nowangena ezihlangwini zikaTat‚Äô uJohnson e- St. Martin's, wayibiza ngebhongo le nto yokubethwa kweentsimbi ngokuba "zintsimbi zabantu abahluphekayo."
reference: The Rev. David Johnson, Father Johnson's son and successor at St. Martin's, proudly called the carillon "the poor people's bells."
translation: Umfu. uDavid Johnson, unyana nowangena ezihlangwini zikaTat' uJohnson e- St. Martin's, wayibiza ngebhongo le nto yokubethwa kweentsimbi ngokuba "zintsimbi zabantu abahluphekayo."

source: Umntu olichule ekubetheni iintsimbi, nowayezibetha, yena wayibiza ngenye indlela: "Ubuncwane benkcubeko" nokuba "sisixhobo sembali esingasoze sithathelwe ndawo."
reference: The expert who played the carillon in July called it something else: "A cultural treasure" and "an irreplaceable historical instrument."
translation: Umntu olichule ekubetheni iintsimbi, nowayezibetha, yena wayibiza ngenye indlela: "Ubuncwane benkcubeko" nokuba "sisixhobo sembali esingasoze sithathelwe ndawo."

source: Eli chule, uTiffany Ng wakwiYunivesiti yaseMichigan, uphinde wathi ibi kokuqala emhlabeni ukuba esi sixhobo sokubetha iintsimbi sidlalwe ngumntu womculo omnyama, uDionisio A. Lind, owafudukela e-Riverside Church eneentsimbi ezininzi kwiminyaka eyi-18 eyadlulayo.
reference: The expert, Tiffany Ng of the University of Michigan, also noted that it was the first carillon in the world to be played by a black musician, Dionisio A. Lind, who moved to the larger carillon at the Riverside Church 18 years ago.
translation: Eli chule, uTiffany Ng wakwiYunivesiti yaseMichigan, uphinde wathi ibi kokuqala emhlabeni ukuba esi sixhobo sokubetha iintsimbi sidlalwe ngumntu womculo omnyama, uDionisio A. Lind, owafudukela e-Riverside Church eneentsimbi ezininzi kwiminyaka eyi-18 eyadlulayo.

source: UMnu. uMerriweather uthe i-St. Martin's zange ifake omnye umntu endaweni yakhe.
reference: Mr. Merriweather said that St. Martin's did not replace him.
translation: UMnu. uMerriweather uthe i-St. Martin's zange ifake omnye umntu endaweni yakhe.

source: Eyona nto ibiphambili apha e-St. Martin's kwezi nyanga zimbalwa zidlulileyo ibiyintsumantsumane yabazobi beeplani nabakhi, abanye babo beziswe zinkokheli zecawa ezingengobafundisi, abanye yicawa yamaRabe.
reference: What has played out at St. Martin's over the last few months has been a complicated tale of architects and contractors, some brought in by the lay leaders of the church, others by the Episcopal diocese.
translation: Eyona nto ibiphambili apha e-St. Martin's kwezi nyanga zimbalwa zidlulileyo ibiyintsumantsumane yabazobi beeplani nabakhi, abanye babo beziswe zinkokheli zecawa ezingengobafundisi, abanye yicawa yamaRabe.

source: Ibandla - ibhunga lolawulo lwamarhamente, elibunjwa zikhokeli ezingengobafundisi - libhalele inqila ngoJulayi lixhalabele ukuba inqila ingasuke ibeke ityala ibandla, nangona lona lingakhange libe nesandla ekuqeshweni kwabazobi beeplani nabakhi abathunyelwe yinqila.
reference: The vestry - the parish's governing body, made up of lay leaders - wrote the diocese in July with concerns that the diocese "would seek to pass along the costs" to the vestry, even though the vestry had not been involved in hiring the architects and contractors the diocese sent in.
translation: Ibandla - ibhunga lolawulo lwamarhamente, elibunjwa zikhokeli ezingengobafundisi - libhalele inqila ngoJulayi lixhalabele ukuba inqila ingasuke ibeke ityala ibandla, nangona lona lingakhange libe nesandla ekuqeshweni kwabazobi beeplani nabakhi abathunyelwe yinqila.

source: Amanye amarhamente akhalazela into yokuba inqila ayizibeki lubala izinto .
reference: Some parishioners complained of a lack of transparency on the diocese's part.
translation: Amanye amarhamente akhalazela into yokuba inqila ayizibeki lubala izinto .

source: Ukrebe wonzakalisa umntwana oneminyak-13-year entywilela ukufumana ii-lobster e-California
reference: Shark injures 13-year-old on lobster dive in California
translation: Ukrebe wonzakalisa umntwana oneminyak-13-year entywilela ukufumana ii-lobster e-California

source: Amagosa athe, ukrebe uhlasele waza wonzakalisa inkwenkwe ena-13 ngoMgqibelo, xa ebentywila ukuze abambe i-lobster e-California ngosuku ebekuvulwa ngalo ixesha lonyaka lokubambisa i-lobster.
reference: A shark attacked and injured a 13-year-old boy Saturday while he was diving for lobster in California on the opening day of lobster season, officials said.
translation: Amagosa athe, ukrebe uhlasele waza wonzakalisa inkwenkwe ena-13 ngoMgqibelo, xa ebentywila ukuze abambe i-lobster e-California ngosuku ebekuvulwa ngalo ixesha lonyaka lokubambisa i-lobster.

source: Olu hlaselo lwenzeka ngaphambi nje kokuba kubethe u-7 kusasa kufutshane nase-Beacon's Beach e-Encinitas.
reference: The attack occurred just before 7 a.m. near Beacon's Beach in Encinitas.
translation: Olu hlaselo lwenzeka ngaphambi nje kokuba kubethe u-7 kusasa kufutshane nase-Beacon's Beach e-Encinitas.

source: UChad Hammel uxelele i-KSWB-TV e-San Diego ukuba ebesele equbha nabahlobo inoba kangangesiqingatha seyure ngoMgqibelo kusasa xa ebesiva le nkwenkwe ikhwaza ifuna uncedo. Baza baqubha baya kuyo ukuze bayincede bayikhuphe emanzini.
reference: Chad Hammel told KSWB-TV in San Diego he had been diving with friends for about half an hour Saturday morning when he heard the boy screaming for help and then paddled over with a group to help pull him out of the water.
translation: UChad Hammel uxelele i-KSWB-TV e-San Diego ukuba ebesele equbha nabahlobo inoba kangangesiqingatha seyure ngoMgqibelo kusasa xa ebesiva le nkwenkwe ikhwaza ifuna uncedo. Baza baqubha baya kuyo ukuze bayincede bayikhuphe emanzini.

source: UHammel uthe, ekuqaleni bendicinga ukuba ivuyiswa kukubamba i-lobster, kodwa kamva "waqonda ukuba iyakhwaza isithi, ‚ÄòNdilunyiwe!‚Äô
reference: Hammel said at first he thought it was just excitement of catching a lobster, but then he "realized that he was yelling, 'I got bit!
translation: UHammel uthe, ekuqaleni bendicinga ukuba ivuyiswa kukubamba i-lobster, kodwa kamva "waqonda ukuba iyakhwaza isithi, 'Ndilunyiwe!'

source: ‚ÄòNdilunyiwe!‚Äô
reference: I got bit!'
translation: 'Ndilunyiwe!'

source: Eli thambo lisezantsi  komqala liphezu kwesifuba belivele lonke," UHammel uthe uqaphele loo nto xa efika kule nkwenkwana.
reference: His whole clavicle was ripped open," Hammel said he noticed once he got to the boy.
translation: Eli thambo lisezantsi komqala liphezu kwesifuba belivele lonke," UHammel uthe uqaphele loo nto xa efika kule nkwenkwana.

source: Ndakhwaza ukuba wonke umntu makaphume emanzini: 'Kukho ukrebe emanzini!' wongeze watsho uHammel.
reference: I yelled at everyone to get out of the water: 'There's a shark in the water!' Hammel added.
translation: Ndakhwaza ukuba wonke umntu makaphume emanzini: 'Kukho ukrebe emanzini!' wongeze watsho uHammel.

source: Le nkwenkwe ihanjiswe ngenqwelo-ntaka ukuya e-Rady Children's Hospital e-San Diego apho akwimeko emandundu.
reference: The boy was airlifted to Rady Children's Hospital in San Diego where he is listed in critical condition.
translation: Le nkwenkwe ihanjiswe ngenqwelo-ntaka ukuya e-Rady Children's Hospital e-San Diego apho akwimeko emandundu.

source: Akwaziwa ukuba loluphi uhlobo lukakrebe olu lumhlaseleyo.
reference: The species of shark responsible for the attack was unknown.
translation: Akwaziwa ukuba loluphi uhlobo lukakrebe olu lumhlaseleyo.

source: Umhlanguli waselwandle, uKapt. Larry Giles uthe xa ebethetha nonoondaba, ukrebe ebekhe wabonwa apho kwiiveki ezidlulileyo, kodwa kwathiwa ayilohlobo olunobungozi lukakrebe.
reference: Lifeguard Capt. Larry Giles said at a media briefing that a shark had been spotted in the area a few weeks earlier, but it was determined not to be a dangerous species of shark.
translation: Umhlanguli waselwandle, uKapt. Larry Giles uthe xa ebethetha nonoondaba, ukrebe ebekhe wabonwa apho kwiiveki ezidlulileyo, kodwa kwathiwa ayilohlobo olunobungozi lukakrebe.

source: UGiles wongeze ngelithi eli xhoba lonzakele nyhani kulo mzimba ungentla.
reference: Giles added the victim sustained traumatic injuries to his upper torso area.
translation: UGiles wongeze ngelithi eli xhoba lonzakele nyhani kulo mzimba ungentla.

source: Amagosa aluvalile ulwandle ukususela e-Ponto Beach e-Casablad ukuya kutsho e-Swami's e-Ecinitas kangangeeyure eziyi-48 ukuze kuphandwe kuqinisekiswe nokhuseleko.
reference: Officials shut down beach access from Ponto Beach in Casablad to Swami's in Ecinitas for 48 hours for investigation and safety purposes.
translation: Amagosa aluvalile ulwandle ukususela e-Ponto Beach e-Casablad ukuya kutsho e-Swami's e-Ecinitas kangangeeyure eziyi-48 ukuze kuphandwe kuqinisekiswe nokhuseleko.

source: UGiles uthe kukho iintlobo zookrebe ezingaphezu kwe-135 kulo ndawo, kodwa uninzi lwazo kuthiwa azinabungozi.
reference: Giles noted that there are more than 135 shark species in the area, but most are not considered dangerous.
translation: UGiles uthe kukho iintlobo zookrebe ezingaphezu kwe-135 kulo ndawo, kodwa uninzi lwazo kuthiwa azinabungozi.

source: I-Sainsbury's iceba ukusa iimveliso zayo kwimarike yezithambiso e-UK
reference: Sainsbury's plans push into UK beauty market
translation: I-Sainsbury's iceba ukusa iimveliso zayo kwimarike yezithambiso e-UK

source: I-Sainsbury's ikhuphisana no-Boots, u-Superdrug no-Debenhams ngokuba neevenkile ezinezithambiso nabantu abazingcaphephe ukuze bancede abantu.
reference: Sainsbury's is taking on Boots, Superdrug and Debenhams with department store-style beauty aisles staffed with specialist assistants.
translation: I-Sainsbury's ikhuphisana no-Boots, u-Superdrug no-Debenhams ngokuba neevenkile ezinezithambiso nabantu abazingcaphephe ukuze bancede abantu.

source: Njengendlela ebalulekileyo yokungena kwimarike yezithambiso yase-UK‚Äô eyenza imali engange-¬£2.8bn, neqhubeka ikhula ngoxa iintengiso zefashoni nezezinto zendlu zisihla, ezi paseji zinkulu zinezithambiso ziza kuvavanywa kwiivenkile eziyi-11 kulo lonke ilizwe, ibe ziza kubakho kwiivenkile ezingakumbi kunyaka ozayo ukuba ziqhube kakuhle.
reference: As part of a substantial push into the UK's ¬£2.8bn beauty market, which is continuing to grow while fashion and homeware sales fall back, the larger beauty aisles will be tested out in 11 stores around the country and taken to more stores next year if it proves a success.
translation: Njengendlela ebalulekileyo yokungena kwimarike yezithambiso yase-UK' eyenza imali engange-¬£2.8bn, neqhubeka ikhula ngoxa iintengiso zefashoni nezezinto zendlu zisihla, ezi paseji zinkulu zinezithambiso ziza kuvavanywa kwiivenkile eziyi-11 kulo lonke ilizwe, ibe ziza kubakho kwiivenkile ezingakumbi kunyaka ozayo ukuba ziqhube kakuhle.

source: Ukutyala imali kwizithambiso kubekho ngenxa yokuba ezi venkile zifuna ukusebenzisa iishelfu ezingenanto emva kokumangalelwa ngee-TV, ii-microwave nezinto zendlu.
reference: The investment in beauty comes as supermarkets hunt for ways to use up shelf space once sued for TVs, microwaves and homeware.
translation: Ukutyala imali kwizithambiso kubekho ngenxa yokuba ezi venkile zifuna ukusebenzisa iishelfu ezingenanto emva kokumangalelwa ngee-TV, ii-microwave nezinto zendlu.

source: I-Sainsbury's iza kwandisa iimveliso zezithambiso enazo ngophindwe kabini zifikelele kwi-3 000, ziquka amagama anje ngo-Revlon, u-Essie, u-Tweezerman no-Dr. PawPaw okokuqala.
reference: Sainsbury's said it would be doubling the size of its beauty offering to up to 3,000 products, including brands such as Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman and Dr. PawPaw for the first time.
translation: I-Sainsbury's iza kwandisa iimveliso zezithambiso enazo ngophindwe kabini zifikelele kwi-3 000, ziquka amagama anje ngo-Revlon, u-Essie, u-Tweezerman no-Dr. PawPaw okokuqala.

source: Abasele benazo njengo- L'Oreal, uMaybelline no-Burt's Bees ziza kuba nendawo eninzi yokuzibeka kwiindawo ezinamagama ezifana nezo ukuzifumana ezivenkileni ezifana no-Boots.
reference: Existing ranges from L'Oreal, Maybelline and Burt's Bees will also get more space with branded areas similar to those found in shops like Boots.
translation: Abasele benazo njengo- L'Oreal, uMaybelline no-Burt's Bees ziza kuba nendawo eninzi yokuzibeka kwiindawo ezinamagama ezifana nezo ukuzifumana ezivenkileni ezifana no-Boots.

source: Le venkile iza kuphinda yazise iimveliso zokuzilungisa ze-Boutique ukuze ezininzi zilungele abantu abangatyi nyama - into efunwa ngamandla ngabathengi abasebatsha.
reference: The supermarket is also relaunching its Boutique makeup range so that the majority of products are vegan-friendly - something increasingly demanded by younger shoppers.
translation: Le venkile iza kuphinda yazise iimveliso zokuzilungisa ze-Boutique ukuze ezininzi zilungele abantu abangatyi nyama - into efunwa ngamandla ngabathengi abasebatsha.

source: Enye into, umthengisi wezinto zokuzinukisa kamnandi i-Fragrance Shop iza kuvavanya izinto ezifunwayo kwiivenkile ezimbini zakwa-Sainsbury's, eyokuqala ivulwe e-Croydon, kumzantsi weLondon, kule veki iphelileyo kanti eyesibini iza kuvulwa e-Selly Oak, e-Birmingham, ekuhambeni konyaka.
reference: In addition, perfume retailer the Fragrance Shop will be testing out concessions in two Sainsbury's stores, the first of which opened in Croydon, south London, last week while a second opens in Selly Oak, Birmingham, later this year.
translation: Enye into, umthengisi wezinto zokuzinukisa kamnandi i-Fragrance Shop iza kuvavanya izinto ezifunwayo kwiivenkile ezimbini zakwa-Sainsbury's, eyokuqala ivulwe e-Croydon, kumzantsi weLondon, kule veki iphelileyo kanti eyesibini iza kuvulwa e-Selly Oak, e-Birmingham, ekuhambeni konyaka.

source: Ukuthenga kwi-intanethi nokuba ngoku abantu bethenga ukutya okuncinci ngosuku kwivenkile ezikufutshane, le nto ifuna ukub iivenkile ezinkulu zenze okungakumbi ekukhuthazeni abantu ukuba baye kuzo.
reference: Online shopping and a shift towards buying small amounts of food daily at local convenience stores means supermarkets are having to do more to persuade people to visit.
translation: Ukuthenga kwi-intanethi nokuba ngoku abantu bethenga ukutya okuncinci ngosuku kwivenkile ezikufutshane, le nto ifuna ukub iivenkile ezinkulu zenze okungakumbi ekukhuthazeni abantu ukuba baye kuzo.

source: UMike Coupe, umphathi oyintloko wase-Sainsbury's uthe, ezi venkile ziza kukhangeleka njengeevenkile ezinkulu ezineemveliso ezahlukahlukeneyo, njengoko bezama ukulwa neevenkile ezinamaxabiso anezaphulelo njego-Aldi no-Lidl ngeenkonzo ezingakumbi nezinye izinto ezingengokutya.
reference: Mike Coupe, the chief executive of Sainsbury's, has said the outlets will look increasingly like department stores as the supermarket chain tries to fight back against the discounters Aldi and Lidl with more services and non-food.
translation: UMike Coupe, umphathi oyintloko wase-Sainsbury's uthe, ezi venkile ziza kukhangeleka njengeevenkile ezinkulu ezineemveliso ezahlukahlukeneyo, njengoko bezama ukulwa neevenkile ezinamaxabiso anezaphulelo njego-Aldi no-Lidl ngeenkonzo ezingakumbi nezinye izinto ezingengokutya.

source: I-Sainsbury's ibibeka iindawo onokuthenga i-Argos kuzo kwiivenkile ezininzi kwaye iqalisile nango-Habitats kuba yazithenga zombini kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo. Loo nto inyuse ukuthengwa kokutya ibe nokuzithenga kwenze ingeniso.
reference: Sainsbury's has been putting Argos outlets in hundreds of stores and has also introduced a number of Habitats since it bought both chains two years ago, which it says has bolstered grocery sales and made the acquisitions more profitable.
translation: I-Sainsbury's ibibeka iindawo onokuthenga i-Argos kuzo kwiivenkile ezininzi kwaye iqalisile nango-Habitats kuba yazithenga zombini kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo. Loo nto inyuse ukuthengwa kokutya ibe nokuzithenga kwenze ingeniso.

source: Imizamo yale venkile yangaphambili yokuphucula amasebe ezithambiso nawezamayeza iye yawa phantsi.
reference: The supermarket's previous attempt to revamp its beauty and pharmacy departments ended in failure.
translation: Imizamo yale venkile yangaphambili yokuphucula amasebe ezithambiso nawezamayeza iye yawa phantsi.

source: I-Sainsbury's yakhe yazama ukudibana no-Boots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yoo-2000, kodwa bohlukana emva kokulwa ngendlela yokwahlula iingeniso zevenkile zamayeza kwiivenkile zayo.
reference: Sainsbury's tested a joint venture with Boots in the early 2000s, but the tie-up ended after a row over how to split the revenues from the chemist's stores in its supermarkets.
translation: I-Sainsbury's yakhe yazama ukudibana no-Boots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yoo-2000, kodwa bohlukana emva kokulwa ngendlela yokwahlula iingeniso zevenkile zamayeza kwiivenkile zayo.

source: Eli cebo litsha libekho emva kokuba i-Sainsbury's ithengisele u-Celesio, umnikazi weevenkile ezingu-Lloyds Pharmacy ibhizinesi yayo yezamayeza ezizivenkile eziyi- 281 nge-¬£125m, kwiminyaka emithathu edlulileyo.
reference: The new strategy comes after Sainsbury's sold its 281-store pharmacy business to Celesio, the owner of the Lloyds Pharmacy chain, for ¬£125m, three years ago.
translation: Eli cebo litsha libekho emva kokuba i-Sainsbury's ithengisele u-Celesio, umnikazi weevenkile ezingu-Lloyds Pharmacy ibhizinesi yayo yezamayeza ezizivenkile eziyi- 281 nge-¬£125m, kwiminyaka emithathu edlulileyo.

source: Ithi u-Lloyds naye uza kuba nenxaxheba kweli cebo, ngokwandisa iimveliso zokuziphophotha ezikwizinga eliphezulu eziquka u- La Roche-Posay no-Vichy kwiivenkile ezine.
reference: It said Lloyds would play a role in the plan, by adding an extended range of luxury skincare brands including La Roche-Posay and Vichy in four stores.
translation: Ithi u-Lloyds naye uza kuba nenxaxheba kweli cebo, ngokwandisa iimveliso zokuziphophotha ezikwizinga eliphezulu eziquka u- La Roche-Posay no-Vichy kwiivenkile ezine.

source: UPaul Mills-Hicks, umlawuli wezorhwebo e-Sainsbury's ,uthe: "Siyitshintshile indlela ezibonakala ngayo iipaseji ezinezithambiso zethu ukuze siyiphuculele abathengi bethu.
reference: Paul Mills-Hicks, Sainsbury's commercial director, said: "We've transformed the look and feel of our beauty aisles to enhance the environment for our customers.
translation: UPaul Mills-Hicks, umlawuli wezorhwebo e-Sainsbury's ,uthe: "Siyitshintshile indlela ezibonakala ngayo iipaseji ezinezithambiso zethu ukuze siyiphuculele abathengi bethu.

source: Sityale imali kubantu esibaqeshileyo abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo ukuze bakwazi ukucebisa.
reference: We've also invested in specially trained colleagues who will be on hand to offer advice.
translation: Sityale imali kubantu esibaqeshileyo abaqeqeshwe ngokukhethekileyo ukuze bakwazi ukucebisa.

source: Iimveliso esinazo ezahlukahlukeneyo zenzelwe ukuba zilungele mfuno nganye, zenza umntu azifune nendawo esifumaneka kuyo kulula ukuyifumana, ngoku siyindawo yezithambiso ebangela umdla ibe loo nto ayifani tu nendlela yokuthenga yakudala."
reference: Our range of brands is designed to suit every need and the alluring environment and convenient locations mean we're now a compelling beauty destination which challenges the old way of shopping."
translation: Iimveliso esinazo ezahlukahlukeneyo zenzelwe ukuba zilungele mfuno nganye, zenza umntu azifune nendawo esifumaneka kuyo kulula ukuyifumana, ngoku siyindawo yezithambiso ebangela umdla ibe loo nto ayifani tu nendlela yokuthenga yakudala."

source: UPeter Jones 'unomsindo‚Äô kuba uHolly Willoughby eyeke ushishino oluyi-¬£11million
reference: Peter Jones 'furious' after Holly Willoughby pulls out of ¬£11million deal
translation: UPeter Jones 'unomsindo' kuba uHolly Willoughby eyeka ushishino oluyi-¬£11million

source: UPeter Jones odume kwiDragons Den uhambe 'enomsindo' emva kokuba umqhubi wenkqubo uHolly Willoughby eyeka ushishino oluyi-¬£11million lwemveliso yendlela yokuphila ukuze ajongane kakuhle nezivumelwano ezintsha anazo no-Marks and Spencer kunye ne-ITV
reference: Dragons Den star Peter Jones left 'furious' after TV presenter Holly Willoughby pulls out of ¬£11million deal with his lifestyle brand business to focus on her new contracts with Marks and Spencer and ITV
translation: UPeter Jones odume kwiDragons Den uhambe 'enomsindo' emva kokuba umqhubi wenkqubo uHolly Willoughby eyeka ushishino oluyi-¬£11million lwemveliso yendlela yokuphila ukuze ajongane kakuhle nezivumelwano ezintsha anazo no-Marks and Spencer kunye ne-ITV

source: UWilloughby akanaxesha lemveliso zabo zezinto zendlu nezokuzihombisa ezifana no-Truly.
reference: Willoughby has no time for their homewear and accessories brand Truly.
translation: UWilloughby akanaxesha lemveliso zabo zezinto zendlu nezokuzihombisa ezifana no-Truly.

source: Ushishino lwesi sibini belufaniswa nemveliso engu-Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
reference: The pair's business had been likened to Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand.
translation: Ushishino lwesi sibini belufaniswa nemveliso engu-Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.

source: Umqhubi wenkqubo engu-This Morning, ona-37, uyifake ku-Instagram into yokuba uyahamba.
reference: This Morning presenter, 37, took to Instagram to announce she is leaving.
translation: Umqhubi wenkqubo engu-This Morning, ona-37, uyifake ku-Instagram into yokuba uyahamba.

source: UHolly Willoughby ushiye odume kwi-Dragons" Den, uPeter Jones ebibitheka ngumsindo kuba ephume ngomzuzu wokugqibela kwibhizinesi yemveliso yendlela yokuphila - ukuze ahoye kakuhle izivulwano zakhe ezintsha no-Marks & Spencer kunye ne- ITV.
reference: Holly Willoughby has left Dragons" Den star Peter Jones fuming by pulling out of their lucrative lifestyle brand business at the last minute - to focus on her own new bumper contracts with Marks & Spencer and ITV.
translation: UHolly Willoughby ushiye odume kwi-Dragons" Den, uPeter Jones ebitheka ngumsindo kuba ephume ngomzuzu wokugqibela kwibhizinesi yemveliso yendlela yokuphila - ukuze ahoye kakuhle izivulwano zakhe ezintsha no-Marks & Spencer kunye ne- ITV.

source: Imithombo ithi uJones ebe "nomsindo" xa intombi ebalulekileyo kwi-TV ivuma kwintlanganiso ebishushu ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu leebhizinesi zakhe e-Marlow, e-Buckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano zakhe ezintsha - ezifikelela kwi-¬£1.5 million - zimenza angabi naxesha laneleyo lokuhoya imveliso yezinto zendlu nezokuzihombisa ezifana no-Truly.
reference: Sources say Jones was "furious" when TV's golden girl admitted during a tense meeting on Tuesday at the headquarters of his business empire in Marlow, Buckinghamshire, that her new deals - worth up to ¬£1.5 million - meant she no longer had enough time to devote to their homewear and accessories brand Truly.
translation: Imithombo ithi uJones ebe "nomsindo" xa intombi ebalulekileyo kwi-TV ivuma kwintlanganiso ebishushu ngoLwesibini kwikomkhulu leebhizinesi zakhe e-Marlow, e-Buckinghamshire, ukuba izivumelwano zakhe ezintsha - ezifikelela kwi-¬£1.5 million - zimenza angabi naxesha laneleyo lokuhoya imveliso yezinto zendlu nezokuzihombisa ezifana no-Truly.

source: Eli shishini lifaniswa nemveliso engu-Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop ibe belifumene imali yokuyiphinda kabini imali kaWilloughby's eqikelelwa kwi-¬£11 miliyoni.
reference: The business had been likened to Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand and was tipped to double Willoughby's estimated ¬£11 million fortune.
translation: Eli shishini lifaniswa nemveliso engu-Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop ibe belifumene imali yokuyiphinda kabini imali kaWilloughby's eqikelelwa kwi-¬£11 miliyoni.

source: Linyukile inani labasweleke kwitsunami yaseIndonesia laya kutsho ku-832

reference: The death toll in Indonesia's earthquake and tsunami has climbed to 832, the country's disaster agency said early Sunday.
translation: Inani labasweleke kwinyikima netsunami yaseIndonesia liye lenyuka laya kutsho kuma-832, iziko lelo lizwe leentlekele litshilo ekuseni ngeCawa.

source: Kunikelwe ingxelo yokuba abantu abaninzi bavaleleke phantsi kwengqushu yezakhiwo ezidilizwe yinyikima ebumandla buyi-7.5 eye yahlasela ngoLwesihlanu yaza yabangela amaza aphakame kangangeenyawo ezingama-20, uSutopo Purwo Nugroho osisithethi seziko uxelele inkomfa yeendaba.
reference: Many people were reported trapped in the rubble of buildings brought down in the 7.5 magnitude earthquake which struck Friday and triggered waves as high as 20 feet, agency spokesman Sutopo Purwo Nugroho told a news conference.
translation: Kunikelwe ingxelo yokuba abantu abaninzi bavaleleke phantsi kwengqushu yezakhiwo ezidilizwe yinyikima ebumandla buyi-7.5 eye yahlasela ngoLwesihlanu yaza yabangela amaza aphakame kangangeenyawo ezingama-20, uSutopo Purwo Nugroho osisithethi seziko uxelele inkomfa yeendaba.

source: Isixeko sasePalu, esinabantu abangaphezu kwe-380,000 besigutyungelwe luthuli oluvela kwizakhiwo eziwileyo.
reference: The city of Palu, which has more than 380,000 people, was strewn with debris from collapsed buildings.
translation: Isixeko sasePalu, esinabantu abangaphezu kwe-380,000 besigutyungelwe luthuli oluvela kwizakhiwo eziwileyo.

source: Amapolisa abambe indoda eneminyaka eyi-32 ubudala, ngezityholo zokubulala emva kokuba ibhinqa lihlatywe lasweleka
reference: Police arrest man, 32, on suspicion of murder after woman is stabbed to death
translation: Amapolisa abambe indoda eneminyaka eyi-32 ubudala, ngezityholo zokubulala emva kokuba ibhinqa lihlatywe lasweleka

source: Kuqaliswe uphando ngokubulala emva kokuba kufunyenwe umzimba webhinqa eBirkenhead, eMerseyside ngale ntsasa.
reference: A murder investigation has been launched after woman's body was found in Birkenhead, Merseyside this morning.
translation: Kuqaliswe uphando ngokubulala emva kokuba kufunyenwe umzimba webhinqa eBirkenhead, eMerseyside ngale ntsasa.

source: Eli bhinqa lineminyaka engama-44 ubudala lifunyenwe ngo- 7.55am linamanxeba okuhlatywa eGrayson Mews eJohn Street, kwaza kwabanjwa indoda eneminyaka engama-32-ubudala etyholwa ngokubulala.
reference: The 44-year-old was found at 7.55am with stab wounds on Grayson Mews on John Street, with a 32-year-old man being arrested on suspicion of murder.
translation: Eli bhinqa lineminyaka engama-44 ubudala lifunyenwe ngo- 7.55am linamanxeba okuhlatywa eGrayson Mews eJohn Street, kwaza kwabanjwa indoda eneminyaka engama-32-ubudala etyholwa ngokubulala.

source: Amapolisa aye abongoza abantu baloo ndawo abaye babona okanye beva nantoni na ukuba beze ngaphambili.
reference: Police have urged people in the area who saw or heard anything to come forward.
translation: Amapolisa aye abongoza abantu baloo ndawo abaye babona okanye beva nantoni na ukuba beze ngaphambili.

source: Umcuphi uBrian O'Hagan uthe: 'Uphando lusaqala kodwa ndibongoza nabani na obekummandla weJohn Street eBirkenhead obone okanye ove nantoni na ebanga urhano ukuba aqhagamshelane nathi.
reference: Detective Inspector Brian O'Hagan said: 'The investigation is in the early stages but I would appeal to anyone who was in the vicinity of John Street in Birkenhead who saw or heard anything suspicious to contact us.
translation: Umcuphi uBrian O'Hagan uthe: 'Uphando lusaqala kodwa ndibongoza nabani na obekummandla weJohn Street eBirkenhead obone okanye ove nantoni na ebanga urhano ukuba aqhagamshelane nathi.

source: Kanti ndithanda ukubongoza nabani na, ingakumbi oonoteksi, ekusenokwenzeka bafote nantoni na ngedashcam ukuba baqhagamshelane nathi njengoko kusenokwenzeka unenkcazelo ebalulekileyo.'
reference: I would also appeal to anyone, particularly taxi drivers, who may have captured anything on dashcam footage to contact us as they may have information which is vital to our investigation.'
translation: Kanti ndithanda ukubongoza nabani na, ingakumbi oonoteksi, ekusenokwenzeka bafote nantoni na ngedashcam ukuba baqhagamshelane nathi njengoko kusenokwenzeka unenkcazelo ebalulekileyo.'

source: Isithethi samapolisa siqinisekisile ukuba ibhinqa ekufunyenwe umzimba walo lelaseBirkenhead ibe lifunyenwe phakathi kwipropati.
reference: A police spokesman has confirmed the woman whose body was found is local to Birkenhead and she was found inside a property.
translation: Isithethi samapolisa siqinisekisile ukuba ibhinqa ekufunyenwe umzimba walo lelaseBirkenhead ibe lifunyenwe phakathi kwipropati.

source: Izihlobo ezicinga ukuba ziyalazi eli bhinqa`ziye zafika kule ndawo yexhwayela zize kubuza imibuzo ngendawo elifunynwe kuyo ngale ntsasa.
reference: This afternoon friends who believe they know the woman have arrived at the scene to ask questions about where she was found this morning.
translation: Izihlobo ezicinga ukuba ziyalazi eli bhinqa`ziye zafika kule ndawo yexhwayela zize kubuza imibuzo ngendawo elifunynwe kuyo ngale ntsasa.

translation: Uphando luyaqhubeka njengoko amapolisa eye athi azama ukwazisa izizalwana ezisondeleyo zexhoba.

reference: A taxi driver who lives in Grayson Mews has just tried to get back into his flat but is being told by police no one is allowed in or out of the building.
translation: Unoteksi ohlala eGrayson Mews usandul' ukuzama ukubuyela kwiflethi yakhe kodwa uxelelwe ngamapolisa ukuba akho mntu uvunyelweyo ukuba aphume engena kwesi sakhiwo.

source: Ebebamb‚Äô ongezantsi akuva okwenzekileyo.
reference: He was speechless when he discovered what happened.
translation: Ebebamb' ongezantsi akuva okwenzekileyo.

source: Ngoku abantu balapha baxelelwe ukuba baya kuvunyelwa emva kweeyure eziliqela ukuba babuyele ngaphakathi.
reference: Residents are now being told it will be hours until they are allowed back in.
translation: Ngoku abantu balapha baxelelwe ukuba baya kuvunyelwa emva kweeyure eziliqela ukuba babuyele ngaphakathi.

translation: Ipolisa livakele lixelela enye indoda ukuba le ndawo sele ijongwa njengendawo yolwaphulo-mthetho.

source: Kufike ibhinqa kuloo ndawo ligixa.

translation: Kufike ibhinqa kuloo ndawo ligixa.

source: SOko liphindaphinda amazwi athi 'Imbi kakhulu le nto'.
reference: She keeps repeating 'it's so awful'.
translation: Soko liphindaphinda amazwi athi 'Imbi kakhulu le nto'.

source: Ngo-2pm iiveni ezimbini zamapolisa beziphakathi kulo mda kunye nenye engaphandle nje kancinci.
reference: At 2pm two police vans were inside the cordon with another van just outside.
translation: Ngo-2pm iiveni ezimbini zamapolisa beziphakathi kulo mda kunye nenye engaphandle nje kancinci.

source: Nabani na oneenkcukacha uyacelwa ukuba enze iDM @MerPolCC, atsalele u-101 okanye aqhagamshelane neeCrimestoppers angachazi gama ku-0800 555 111 akowute ilogi 247 ye-30th Septemba.

source: Umfanekiso oqingqiweyo kaCromwell ngowokugqibela ukufunyanwa yingxwabangxwaba ‚Äòyokubhalwa ngokutsha kwembali
reference: Parliament's statue of Cromwell becomes latest memorial hit by 'rewriting history' row
translation: Umfanekiso oqingqiweyo kaCromwell ngowokugqibela ukufunyanwa yingxwabangxwaba 'yokubhalwa ngokutsha kwembali

source: Ukususwa kwawo kuya kuba bubulungisa obubumbongo ngenxa yembubhiso yakhe efana neyeTaliban kwimifanekiso emininzi kakhulu yaseNgilani yemveli neyonqulo eyayiqhutywa ngabalandeli bakhe abanenzondelelo abangamaPuritan.
reference: Its banishment would be poetic justice for his Taliban-like destruction of so many of England's cultural and religious artefacts carried out by his fanatical Puritan followers.
translation: Ukususwa kwawo kuya kuba bubulungisa obubumbongo ngenxa yembubhiso yakhe efana neyeTaliban kwimifanekiso emininzi kakhulu yaseNgilani yemveli neyonqulo eyayiqhutywa ngabalandeli bakhe abanenzondelelo abangamaPuritan.

source: Kodwa iCromwell yachaza icebiso likaMnu Crick ‚Äúnjengobudenge‚Äù ‚Äúnokuzama ukubhala imbali ngokutsha."
reference: But the Cromwell Society described Mr Crick's suggestion as "folly" and "attempting to rewrite history."
translation: Kodwa iCromwell yachaza icebiso likaMnu Crick "njengobudenge" "nokuzama ukubhala imbali ngokutsha."

source: ]UJohn Goldsmith, usihlalo weCromwell Society, uthe: "Bekungenakuphepheka ukuba kule ngxoxo ikhoyo ngokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo ukuba umfanekiso oqingqiweyo kaOliver Cromwell ongaphandle kwePalace of Westminster ube lixhoba.
reference: John Goldsmith, chairman of the Cromwell Society, said: "It was inevitable in the present debate about the removal of statues that the figure of Oliver Cromwell outside the Palace of Westminster would become a target.
translation: UJohn Goldsmith, usihlalo weCromwell Society, uthe: "Bekungenakuphepheka ukuba kule ngxoxo ikhoyo ngokususwa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo ukuba umfanekiso oqingqiweyo kaOliver Cromwell ongaphandle kwePalace of Westminster ube lixhoba.

source: Ukonakaliswa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo kwiimfazwe zamaNgesi akuzange kuyalelwe okanye kwenziwe nguCromwell.
reference: The iconoclasm of the English civil wars was neither ordered nor carried out by Cromwell.
translation: Ukonakaliswa kwemifanekiso eqingqiweyo kwiimfazwe zamaNgesi akuzange kuyalelwe okanye kwenziwe nguCromwell.

source: Mhlawumbi uCromwell orongo kuya kunikelwa ngaye ngenxa yezenzo zikakhokho wakhe uThomas wenkulungwane engaphambili.
reference: Perhaps the wrong Cromwell would be sacrificed for the actions of his ancestor Thomas in the previous century.
translation: Mhlawumbi uCromwell orongo kuya kunikelwa ngaye ngenxa yezenzo zikakhokho wakhe uThomas wenkulungwane engaphambili.

source: Indlela esemagqabini uMhlekazi uWilliam Hamo Thorneycroft amchaza ngayo uCromwell ibubungqina bezimvo zenkulungwane ye-19 nenxalenye yembali yomntu abaninzi abasacinga ukuba ubomi bakhe bumele bubhiyozelwe.
reference: Sir William Hamo Thorneycroft's magnificent representation of Cromwell is evidence of 19th century opinion and part of the historiography of a figure who many believe is still worth celebrating.
translation: Indlela esemagqabini uMhlekazi uWilliam Hamo Thorneycroft amchaza ngayo uCromwell ibubungqina bezimvo zenkulungwane ye-19 nenxalenye yembali yomntu abaninzi abasacinga ukuba ubomi bakhe bumele bubhiyozelwe.

source: UMnu Goldsmith uyixelele oku iThe Sunday Telegraph: "UCromwell ugqalwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ubukhulu becala ngasekupheleni kweenkulungwane ye-19 kunangoku, njengomkhuseli wepalamente nxamnye noxinzelelo lwangaphandle, ubukhulu becala kwimeko yakhe uxinzelelo oluvela ebukhosini.
reference: Mr Goldsmith told The Sunday Telegraph: "Cromwell is regarded by many, perhaps more in the late 19th century than today, as a defender of parliament against external pressure, in his case of course the monarchy.
translation: UMnu Goldsmith uyixelele oku iThe Sunday Telegraph: "UCromwell ugqalwa ngabaninzi, mhlawumbi ubukhulu becala ngasekupheleni kweenkulungwane ye-19 kunangoku, njengomkhuseli wepalamente nxamnye noxinzelelo lwangaphandle, ubukhulu becala kwimeko yakhe uxinzelelo oluvela ebukhosini.

source: Enoba le ndlela yokumchaza ichane ngokupheleleyo ixhomekeke kwingxoxo mpikiswano yezembali eqhubekayo.
reference: Whether that is a wholly accurate representation is the subject of continuing historical debate.
translation: Enoba le ndlela yokumchaza ichane ngokupheleleyo ixhomekeke kwingxoxo mpikiswano yezembali eqhubekayo.

source: Okuqinisekileyo kukuba ingxwabangxwaba eyayikho phakathi kwinkulungwane ye-17 iye yanefuthe kuphuhliso lwelizwe lethu okwalandelayo, yaye lo kaCromwell ungumntu oye wazibalula omela icala elinye kuloo ngxwabangxwaba.
reference: What is certain is that the conflict of the mid 17th century has shaped the subsequent development of our nation, and Cromwell is an individual recognisable figure who represents one side of that divide.
translation: Ngokukhangeleka kukuba ukunyanzela kwamanye amaqela kwakukho phakathi kwenkulu yamashumi ayisikhombisa (17) iye namatyala oluhlu-lwe-Afrika, uCromwell unguye umntu oye wabalula emele enye yalezi ziqala.

source: Awakuphumezayo njengeNkosi enguMkhuseli zimele zibhiyozelwe zize zikhunjulwe."
reference: His achievements as Lord Protector are also worth celebrating and commemorating."
translation: Ayikuphumezeli njengeNkosi enguMkhuseli zibhiyozelwe zize zikhunjulwe.

source: Ihagu Ebulalayo Ihlasele Umfama WaseTshayina Yambulala
reference: Killer Pig Mauls Chinese Farmer to Death
translation: Ihagu Ebulalayo Ihlasele Umfama WaseTshayina Yambulala

source: Umfama uye wahlaselwa wabulawa yihagu kwimarike ekumzantsi ntshona weTshayina, ngokutsho kweengxelo zeendaba zalapho.
reference: A farmer was attacked and killed by a pig in a market in southwest China, according to local media reports.
translation: Umfama uye wahlaselwa wabulawa yihagu kwimarike ekumzantsi ntshona weTshayina, ngokutsho kweengxelo zeendaba zalapho.

source: Indoda, echazwe kuphela ngefani yayo "uYuan," ifunyenwe iswelekile inomthambo oqhaqhiweyo, ugqunywe ligazi kufutshane nehoko yeehagu ekwimarika yaseLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou, iSouth China Morning Post yenze loo ngxelo ngeCawa.
reference: The man, identified only by his surname "Yuan," was found dead with a severed artery, covered in blood near a sty at the market in Liupanshui in Guizhou province, the South China Morning Post reported Sunday.
translation: Indoda, echazwe kuphela ngefani yayo "uYuan," ifunyenwe iswelekile inomthambo oqhaqhiweyo, ugqunywe ligazi kufutshane nehoko yeehagu ekwimarika yaseLiupanshui kwiphondo laseGuizhou, iSouth China Morning Post yenze loo ngxelo ngeCawa.

source: Umfama weehagu ulungiselela ukutofa iihagu zakhe kwiindawo yeehag ngoMeyi 30, 2005 eXining ekwPhondo iQinghai, eTshayina.
reference: A pig farmer prepares to inject vaccines into pigs at a hoggery on May 30, 2005 in Xining of Qinghai Province, China.
translation: Umfama weehagu ulungiselela ukutofa iihagu zakhe kwiindawo yeehag ngoMeyi 30, 2005 eXining ekwPhondo iQinghai, eTshayina.

source: Kuthiwa wayehamba nomzala wakhe ukusuka kwiphondo eliselumelwaneni iYunnan ngoLwesithathu eyokuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 emarikeni.
reference: He had reportedly travelled with his cousin from the neighboring Yunnan province Wednesday to sell 15 pigs at the market.
translation: Kuthiwa wayehamba nomzala wakhe ukusuka kwiphondo eliselumelwaneni iYunnan ngoLwesithathu eyokuthengisa iihagu ezili-15 emarikeni.

source: Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana eswelekile, waza wafumanisa ukuba umnyango oya kwihoko yeehagu ekufutshane uvulekile.
reference: The following morning, his cousin found him dead, and discovered a door to a neighbouring pig sty open.
translation: Ngentsasa elandelayo, umzala wakhe wamfumana eswelekile, waza wafumanisa ukuba umnyango oya kwihoko yeehagu ekufutshane uvulekile.

source: Uthi kule hoko kwakukho inkunzi enkulu yehagu enegazi emlonyeni.
reference: He said that in the sty was a large male pig with blood on its mouth.
translation: Uthi kule hoko kwakukho inkunzi enkulu yehagu enegazi emlonyeni.

source: Uphando lweforenziki lwaqinisekisa ukuba le hagu ibunzima buziphawundi ezingama-550 yamenzakalisa yambulala lo mama, ngokutsho kwengxelo.
reference: A forensic examination confirmed that the 550 pound hog had mauled the farmer to death, according to the report.
translation: Uphando lweforenziki lwaqinisekisa ukuba le hagu ibunzima buziphawundi ezingama-550 yamenzakalisa yambulala lo mama, ngokutsho kwengxelo.

reference: My cousin's legs were bloody and mangled, the cousin, referred to by his surname "Wu," said, as quoted by the Guiyang Evening News.
translation: Imilenze kamzala yayinegazi yaye ijijekile, watsho njalo lo mzala ubizwa ngegama lakhe elingu"Wu," njengoko ecatshulwa yiGuiyang Evening News.

translation: Le hagu yabulala uYuan asiyoyakhe okanye umzala wakhe.

translation: Umphathi wemarike waxelela iEvening News ukuba le hagu ibitshixelwe ukuze ingahlaseli abanye abantu, ngoxa amapolisa eqokelela ubungqina kwindawo yexhwayela.
