source: Njengoko lusitho uqikelelo lwemo yezulu, uHerican Rosa uyasilela njengoko esukile waya ngaphezulu kwamanzi apholileyo kumnxweme lwasemantla aseMexico.
reference: As forecast, Hurricane Rosa is weakening as it moves over the cooler waters of the northern coast of Mexico.
translation: Njengoko lusitho uqikelelo lwemo yezulu, uHerican Rosa uyasilela njengoko esukile waya ngaphezulu kwamanzi apholileyo kumnxweme lwasemantla aseMexico.

source: Nangona kunjalo, uRosa uya kuzisa iimvula ezizizikhukula kumantla aseMexico nasemazantsi ntshona ase U.S. kwezi ntsuku zizayo.
reference: However, Rosa will bring flooding rains across northern Mexico and the southwest U.S. over the coming days.
translation: Nangona kunjalo, uRosa uya kuzisa iimvula ezizizikhukula kumantla aseMexico nasemazantsi ntshona ase U.S. kwezi ntsuku zizayo.

source: URosa unemimoya engama-85 mph, iKhathegori 1 Hurricane, ukusuka ngo-5 a.m Kwixesha laseNtshona ngeCawe, kwaye yayihleli kwimayile ezingama-385 kumazantsi ntshona ase Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
reference: Rosa had winds of 85 mph, a Category 1 Hurricane, as of 5 a.m. Eastern time Sunday, and was located 385 miles southwest of Punta Eugenia, Mexico.
translation: URosa unemimoya engama-85 mph, iKhathegori 1 Hurricane, ukusuka ngo-5 a.m Kwixesha laseNtshona ngeCawe, kwaye yayihleli kwimayile ezingama-385 kumazantsi ntshona ase Punta Eugenia, Mexico.

source: URosa kulindeleke ukuba aye ngasentshona ngeCawe.
reference: Rosa is expected to move north on Sunday.
translation: URosa kulindeleke ukuba aye ngasentshona ngeCawe.

source: Okwangoku, i-trough iyaqala ukuthatha ukumila kulwandle lwePacific kwaye ihambe iye empuma ngakuNxweme lwasentshona yase U.S. Njengoko uRosa esiza Baja California peninsula ngoMvulo njengesichoitho setropical uza kuqala adudule ukufuma ubunzulu betropical ibuse ngasemantla kumazantsi ntshona ase U.S.
reference: Meanwhile, a trough is beginning to take shape over the Pacific Ocean and move east toward the West Coast of the U.S. As Rosa approaches the Baja California peninsula on Monday as a tropical storm it will begin to push deep tropical moisture northward into the southwest U.S.
translation: Okwangoku, i-trough iyaqala ukuthatha ukumila kulwandle lwePacific kwaye ihambe iye empuma ngakuNxweme lwasentshona yase U.S. Njengoko uRosa esiza Baja California peninsula ngoMvulo njengesichoitho setropical uza kuqala adudule ukufuma ubunzulu betropical ibuse ngasemantla kumazantsi ntshona ase U.S.

source: URosa uya kuzisa imvula ezi intshi ezili-10 kwiindawo zaseMexico ngoMvulo.
reference: Rosa will bring up to 10 inches of rain in parts of Mexico on Monday.
translation: URosa uya kuzisa imvula ezi intshi ezili-10 kwiindawo zaseMexico ngoMvulo.

source: Emva koko, ukufuma kwetropical okusebenzisana nokuza kwe trough kuya kuthi kudale ukunaba kokunetha kwemvula emaZantsi ntshona kwezi ntsuku zizayo.
reference: Then, tropical moisture interacting with the approaching trough will create widespread heavy rainfall in the Southwest over the coming days.
translation: Emva koko, ukufuma kwetropical okusebenzisana nokuza kwe trough kuya kuthi kudale ukunaba kokunetha kwemvula emaZantsi ntshona kwezi ntsuku zizayo.

source: Ngokwasekhaya, I intshi enye -kwezi-4 zemvula ziya kubangela ukhukuliseko oluyingozi, ukuhamba kweefregmenti kunye nezilayindi zomhlaba entlango.
reference: Locally, 1 to 4 inches of rain will cause dangerous flash flooding, debris flows and possibility landslides in the desert.
translation: Ngokwasekhaya, I intshi enye -kwezi-4 zemvula ziya kubangela ukhukuliseko oluyingozi, ukuhamba kweefregmenti kunye nezilayindi zomhlaba entlango.

source: Ngokwalapa ekhaya ukufuma ukunzulu kwetropical kuya kubangela imilinganiselo yemvula iya kuba kwii intshi ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-3 ngeyure kwispots, ngakumbi kwiindawo zomzantsi weNavada neArizona.
reference: Deep tropical moisture will cause rainfall rates to approach 2 to 3 inches per hour in spots, especially in parts of southern Nevada and Arizona.
translation: Ngokwalapa ekhaya ukufuma ukunzulu kwetropical kuya kubangela imilinganiselo yemvula iya kuba kwii intshi ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-3 ngeyure kwispots, ngakumbi kwiindawo zomzantsi weNavada neArizona.

source: Nangona kulindeleke ii intshi ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-4 zemvula kwiindawo zoMzantsi ntshona, ngakumbi kwicala leArizona.
reference: As much as 2 to 4 inches of rain is expected in parts of the Southwest, especially over much of Arizona.
translation: Nangona kulindeleke ii intshi ezi-2 ukuya kwezi-4 zemvula kwiindawo zoMzantsi ntshona, ngakumbi kwicala leArizona.

source: Ukungxola kokuhamba kwamanzi aphuphumayo kuyenzeka ngokukhawuleza kwiimeko zemo  efefayo yemvula zetropical.
reference: Flash flooding is possible with rapidly deteriorating conditions due to the scattered nature of tropical rain.
translation: Ukungxola kokuhamba kwamanzi aphuphumayo kuyenzeka ngokukhawuleza kwiimeko zemo efefayo yemvula zetropical.

source: Kuya kuba akuyo ngcebiso intle kakhulu ukuzama ukuhamba ngeenyawo entlango ngoloyiko lwelweemvula zetropical.
reference: It would be extremely ill advised to venture out into the desert on foot with the threat of tropical rainfall.
translation: Kuya kuba akuyo ngcebiso intle kakhulu ukuzama ukuhamba ngeenyawo entlango ngoloyiko lwelweemvula zetropical.

source: Iimvula ezinkulu zingabangela iicanyons ukuba zibe yimilambo enamandla kwaye neendudumo ziya kuzisa imimoya ebhudlayo ekuhlaleni kwaye kuya kubakho uthuli.
reference: Heavy rain could cause canyons to become raging rivers and thunderstorms will bring locally gusty winds and blowing dust.
translation: Iimvula ezinkulu zingabangela iicanyons ukuba zibe yimilambo enamandla kwaye neendudumo ziya kuzisa imimoya ebhudlayo ekuhlaleni kwaye kuya kubakho uthuli.

source: Ukuza kwalo kuya kuzisa iimvula ezithile ezinkulu ekuhlaleni  kwindawo ezithile zonxweme lwe- Southern California.
reference: The approaching trough will bring some locally heavy rain to parts of the Southern California coastline.
translation: Ukuza kwalo kuya kuzisa iimvula ezithile ezinkulu ekuhlaleni kwindawo ezithile zonxweme lwe- Southern California.

source: Iimvula xa zizonke ziphelele eziya kuthi zibekho ziya kuba ngaphezulu kwesiqingatha se intshi, esinokuthi sibangele iifragmenti ezincinci zokuhamba kwamanzi kwaye zibangele ukutyibilika ezindleleni.
reference: Rainfall totals of over half an inch are possible, which could cause minor debris flows and slick roadways.
translation: Iimvula xa zizonke ziphelele eziya kuthi zibekho ziya kuba ngaphezulu kwesiqingatha se intshi, esinokuthi sibangele iifragmenti ezincinci zokuhamba kwamanzi kwaye zibangele ukutyibilika ezindleleni.

source: Le mvula iya kuba yimvula yokuqala kule ngingqi ukubakho kwiseason yobumanzi.
reference: This would be the region's first rainfall of their wet season.
translation: Le mvula iya kuba yimvula yokuqala kule ngingqi ukubakho kwiseason yobumanzi.

source: Okunye ukufefa kweemvula zetropical zethutyana kuya kuqala kwenzeke eArizona ngorhatya lwangoMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula inabe yonke indawo ngorhatya lwangoMvulo nangolwesiBini.
reference: Some scattered tropical rain showers will begin to approach Arizona late Sunday and early Monday, before the rain becomes more widespread late Monday and Tuesday.
translation: Okunye ukufefa kweemvula zetropical zethutyana kuya kuqala kwenzeke eArizona ngorhatya lwangoMvulo, ngaphambi kokuba imvula inabe yonke indawo ngorhatya lwangoMvulo nangolwesiBini.

source: Imvula enkulu iyakunaba kwikona Zone ngolwesiBini kwaye iyeke ngolwesiThathu.
reference: Heavy rain will spread into the Four Corners on Tuesday and last through Wednesday.
translation: Imvula enkulu iyakunaba kwikona Zone ngolwesiBini kwaye iyeke ngolwesiThathu.

source: Ngo Okthobha singabona ukuxhalaba okuthile kubume bobushushu kwi-U.S. iphela njengoko iArctic ingafumana ukuphola, kodwa iitropics zona zihlale zishushu.
reference: October can see some intense temperature swings across the U.S. as the Arctic gets cooler, but the tropics remain quite warm.
translation: Ngo Okthobha singabona ukuxhalaba okuthile kubume bobushushu kwi-U.S. iphela njengoko iArctic ingafumana ukuphola, kodwa iitropics zona zihlale zishushu.

source: Ngamanye amaxesha oku luchaphazela utshintsho olubaxekileyo lobushushu ngaphezulu komgama omfutshane.
reference: Sometimes this leads to dramatic changes in temperature over short distances.
translation: Ngamanye amaxesha oku luchaphazela utshintsho olubaxekileyo lobushushu ngaphezulu komgama omfutshane.

source: Kukho umzekelo omhle weendidi zobushushu obubaxekileyo kwiindidi zobushushu ngombindi wase U.S. ngeCawe.
reference: There is a great example of dramatic temperature differences through the central U.S. on Sunday.
translation: Kukho umzekelo omhle weendidi zobushushu obubaxekileyo kwiindidi zobushushu ngombindi wase U.S. ngeCawe.

source: Kuphantse kwazidigri ezingama-20 zomahluko kubushushu phakathi kwase Kansas City, Missouri nase Omaha, Nebraka, nase St. Louis nase Des Monies, Iowa.
reference: There is nearly a 20-degree temperature difference between Kansas City, Missouri, and Omaha, Nebraska, and between St. Louis and Des Moines, Iowa.
translation: Kuphantse kwazidigri ezingama-20 zomahluko kubushushu phakathi kwase Kansas City, Missouri nase Omaha, Nebraka, nase St. Louis nase Des Monies, Iowa.

source: Kwezi ntsuku zimbalwa zidlulileyo,  ubushushu bokungena kwehlobo buyazama ukwakheka nokwanda.
reference: Over the next few days, lingering summer warmth will try to build and expand again.
translation: Kwezi ntsuku zimbalwa zidlulileyo,  ubushushu bokungena kwehlobo buyazama ukwakheka nokwanda.

source: kubukhulu bombindi kunye nempuma yase U.S. kulindeleke ukuba kubonakale ukuqala kobushushu ngo Okthobhakubekho nokwandlaleka obungama 80 ukusuka ngasemaZantsi ukuya ngasemaNtla mpuma.
reference: Much of the central and eastern U.S. is expected to see a warm start to October with widespread 80s from the Southern Plains to parts of the Northeast.
translation: kubukhulu bombindi kunye nempuma yase U.S. kulindeleke ukuba kubonakale ukuqala kobushushu ngo Okthobhakubekho nokwandlaleka obungama 80 ukusuka ngasemaZantsi ukuya ngasemaNtla mpuma.

source: IsiXeko saseNew York singafikelela kwiidigri ezingama-80 ngolwesibini, nto leyo inokubangela uqikelelo oluzii digri ezili-10 ngaphezu kobungakanani obuqhelekileyo.
reference: New York City could reach 80 degrees on Tuesday, which would be approximately 10 degrees above average.
translation: IsiXeko saseNew York singafikelela kwiidigri ezingama-80 ngolwesibini, nto leyo inokubangela uqikelelo oluzii digri ezili-10 ngaphezu kobungakanani obuqhelekileyo.

source: Uqikelelo lwethu lobume bezulu lwesithuba sexesha elide lubonakalisa amathuba aphezulu obushushu obungasentla obuphakathi kwimpuma yase U.S. ngesiqingatha sokuqala sikaOkthobha.
reference: Our long term climate forecast is indicating high chances for above-average temperatures for the eastern U.S. through the first half of October.
translation: Uqikelelo lwethu lobume bezulu lwesithuba sexesha elide lubonakalisa amathuba aphezulu obushushu obungasentla obuphakathi kwimpuma yase U.S. ngesiqingatha sokuqala sikaOkthobha.

source: Bangaphezulu kwezigidi ezingama-20 abantu ababukele uloluleko lukaKavanaugh Brett.
reference: More than 20 million people watched Brett Kavanaugh hearing
translation: Ngaphezulu kwe-20 zezigidi abantu babukele ukuchongwa kuka-Kavanaugh Brett.

source: Bangaphezulu kwezigidi ezingama-20 abantu abebebukele ubungqina obebuhambisa umzimba bangolweSine obebusenziwa ngumkhethwa weNkundla ePhezulu uBrett Kavanaugh kunye nomntu wasetyhini omtyhola ngokumxhaphaza ngokwesondo okwenzeka ngeminyaka yoo -1980, uChristine Blasey Ford, kwiinethiwekhi ezintandathu zikamabonwakude.
reference: More than 20 million people watched Thursday's gripping testimony by Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh and the woman who accused him of a sexual assault that allegedly occurred in the 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, on six television networks.
translation: Ngaphezulu kwe-20 zezigidi abantu bebukele ubuchule bendabuko obuboniswa ngomthombo, ngoLwesihlanu obwenze umthombo ka-Brett Kavanaugh nomfazi otshisa ngokufaka isijwara seminyaka ye-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford, kwii-network ezintandathu.

source: Ngokwalo mzuzu, ubume bemeko yezopolitiko isaaqhubeka, ngosasazzo oluphazamisaa uyilo lwenjqubo yesiqhelo yangolwesihlanu ukuba itshintshe ngomzuzu wokugqibela:isivumelwano esenziwe yiSen yase Arizona uJeff Flake ukuze iFBI iqhube uphando lweveki enye  kugwetyo lwetyala.
reference: Meanwhile, the political standoff continued, with broadcasters interrupting regular programming for Friday's last-minute twist: an agreement engineered by Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake for the FBI to conduct a one-week investigation of the charges.
translation: Ngoku, isimo sopolitiko siqhubeka, ngenxa yesiphoso esiphazamisa indlela yokuhamba ngokuhlukile kwimizuzu yokugqibela: isivumelwano esenziwe nguSenator uJeff Flake ukuba i-FBI ihlole imizuzu enye kwicala.

source: UFord uxelele iKomiti yoLawulo lweSenate ukuba uqiniseke ngokuziipesenti ezili 100 ukuba uKavanaugh wamfaka umnwe ephantsi kweempembelelo zotywala kwaye wazama nokumkhulula iimpahla kwitheko lesikolo esiphezulu.
reference: Ford told the Senate Judiciary Committee that she's 100 percent certain that Kavanaugh groped her drunkenly and tried to take off her clothes at a high school party.
translation: UFord utsho kuKomiti yeeSenate ukuba uyaqiniseka ngokunene ukuba uKavanaugh wamfaka umnwe phantsi kwamabele otywala kwaye wamfaka esikolweni esiphakamileyo.

source: UKavanaugh, kubungqina obuhambisa umzimba, uthe uqiniseke ngokuziipesenti ezili-100 ukuba oko zange kwenzeke.
reference: Kavanaugh, in impassioned testimony, said he's 100 percent certain that it didn't happen.
translation: UKavanaugh, ekubeni ubuchule bendabuko, uthe uyaqiniseka ngokupheleleyo ukuba into enganabanga kwenzeka.

source: Kuqhelekile ukuba babengaphezulu kwama-20.4 ezigidi abantu ebebebukele ingxelo ebisenziwa nguNelson ngolwesiHlanu.
reference: It's likely that more than the 20.4 million people reported by Nielsen on Friday watched it.
translation: Kubonakala bekungaphezulu kwe-20.4 zezigidi abantu bebukele ingxelo ngolwesihlanu.

source: Inkampani yayibala ubungakanani benani labalandeli  kwiindaba ze CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye neMSNBC.
reference: The company was counting average viewership on CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel and MSNBC.
translation: Inkampani yibala inani labalandeli kwiinethiwekhi ze-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye ne-MSNBC.

source: Amanani awakhange abekhona ngala mzuzu ukuze zibonakale kwezinye iinethiwekhi, kuquka PBS, C-SPAN kunye ne Fox Business Network.
reference: Figures weren't immediately available for other networks that showed it, including PBS, C-SPAN and the Fox Business Network.
translation: Amanani angekho manje ukuze abonakale kweenethiwekhi ezinye, kubandakanya i-PBS, C-SPAN kunye ne-Fox Business Network.

source: Kwaye unielsen unengxakana yokulinganisa abantu abaye babukele beseziofisini.
reference: And Nielsen usually has some trouble measuring people who watch in offices.
translation: Kunye ne-Nielsen inamaphutha ekubala abantu abababukele.

source: Ukubeka kula meko, bubungakanani babalandeli okuyeleleneyo naxa kubukelwe amagqibela kankqoyi kumdlawo webhola ekhatywayo okanye kwiiMbasa zeMfundo.
reference: To put that in perspective, that's an audience size similar to that for a playoff football game or the Academy Awards.
translation: Ngokwalo meko, yingakanani yababukeli kwizinto ezifana nemiba yeqela lobhalo kwintlanganiso.

source: Itshaneli yeFox yeeNdaba, embono wayo ikuba nenkqubo exhasa ukonyulwa kuKavanaugh ngamandla, izikhokele zonke ezinye iinethiwekhi ngokubanabalandeli abakwinqanaba lezigidi eziyi-5.69 ngexesha loluleko imini yonke, utshilo uNielsen.
reference: Fox News Channel, whose opinion hosts have strongly backed Kavanaugh's appointment, led all networks with an average of 5.69 million viewers during the all-day hearing, Nielsen said.
translation: I-Fox News, enengxaki yokwamkela uKavanaugh, yayiphezulu kuzo zonke iinethiwekhi ngabalandeli ababengama-5.69 zezigidi ngesondo, kubona uNielsen.

source: ABC yayikwindawo yesibini ngababukeli abazizigidi ezi-3.26.
reference: ABC was second with 3.26 million viewers.
translation: I-ABC yayisesibini ngabalandeli ababengama-3.26 zezigidi.

source: I-CBS ibine-3.1 yezigidi, i-NBC ibine -2.94 yezigidi, i-MSNBC ibine- 2.89 yezigidi kwaye  i-CNN ibine -2.52 yezigidi, utshilo uNielsen.
reference: CBS had 3.1 million, NBC had 2.94 million, MSNBC had 2.89 million and CNN had 2.52 million, Nielsen said.
translation: I-CBS inezigidiezi-3.1, i-NBC inezigidiezi-2.94, i-MSNBC inezigidiezi-2.89, i-CNN inezigidiezi-2.52, kubona uNielsen.

source: Umdla ushiyeke uphezulu emva koluleko.
reference: Interest remained high after the hearing.
translation: Umdla uphamba emva koluleko.

source: UFlake nguyena mntu bekujongwe kuye kwidrama yangolwesiHlanu
reference: Flake was the central figure in Friday's drama.
translation: UFake wayengumntu obalulekileyo kwidrama yolwesihlanu.

source: Emva kokuba iofisi ephakathi yamaRiphabhlikhi ikhuphe isithethimenti sokuba uza kube evota evotela uKavanaugh, ufunyenwe nguCNN kunye neeCamera ze-CBS ngentsasa yangolwesiHlanu eshawutwa ngabaqhankqalazi njengoba ezama ukukhwela elisftini esiya kuloluleko lweKomiti yoLawulo.
reference: After the moderate Republican's office issued a statement that he would be voting in favor of Kavanaugh, he was caught be CNN and CBS cameras Friday morning being shouted at by protesters as he tried to ride an elevator to a Judiciary Committee hearing.
translation: Emva kokuba iphini lemaRiphabhlikhi lithatha isicelo sokuba uza kuvota uKavanaugh, wafumanwa yi-CNN kunye neekhameni ze-CBS ngolwesihlanu, ehamba ngobubele, ufuna ukungena kuloluleko lweKomiti.

source: Uye wema amehlo enxunguphele kangangemizuzu eliqela njengoko ebegxeka, ebethetha ngalo mzuzu kwi-TV yakwa CNN.
reference: He stood with eyes downcast for several minutes as he was berated, televised live on CNN.
translation: Ebekade ema ixesha elide, eholela, ethetha ngeTV ye-CNN.

source: ‚ÄùNdime apha phambi kwenu‚Äù, utshilo umntu wasetyhini.
reference: I'm standing right here in front of you, one woman said.
translation: Ndime apha phambi kwenu, watsho.

source: ‚ÄùIngaba nicinga ukuba uthetha inyani kwilizwe?
reference: Do you think he's telling the truth to the country?	Nicinga ukuba nditsho inyani kulo mhlaba?"

source: Waxelelwa ukuba, ‚ÄúUnamandla ngelixa uninzi lwabasetyhini lungenamandla‚Äù.
reference: He was told, "you have power when so many women are powerless.""
translation: Watsho, "Unamandla kwaye abafazi abaninzi abanandla".

source: UFlake uthe iofisi yakhe ikhuphe isitethimenti kwaye wathi, ngaphambi kokuba ivale ilifti, bekukuninzi ebenokuthetha kwikomiti yoluleko.
reference: Flake said that his office had issued a statement and said, before the elevator closed, that he would have more to say at the committee hearing.
translation: UFake watsho iphini lakhe luthatha isicelo, kwaye watsho, ngaphambi kokuba lifike, bekukho okuninzi azakuthetha kuKomiti.

source: inethiwekhi zosasazo kunye ne-cable zonke bezisasaza ngalo mzuzu kwiyure ezilandelayo, ngelixa iKomiti yoLawulo yayiza kuvota ukuqhubela phambili ukonyulwa kukaKavanaugh kwisineyithi epheleleyo yokuvota.
reference: The cable and broadcast networks were all covering live hours later, when the Judiciary Committee was to vote to advance Kavanaugh's nomination to the full Senate for a vote.
translation: Zonke iinethiwekhi zasematheni nezokufaka iintetho, zisasaza ngolo hlobo kwiiyure ezizayo, iKomiti izonke izakuvota ukucuthela phambili ukubekwa kukaKavanaugh.

source: Kodwa uFlake uthe uya kuthi akwenze oko kuphela ngokuqondisana neFBI apho ayokuthi ajonge izityholo ngokuchasene nomkhethwa kule veki izayo, apho amaDemocrats angamaqela ambalwa ebecetyiswa khona.
reference: But Flake said he would only do so with the understanding that the FBI would look into the allegations against the nominee for the next week, which minority Democrats have been urging.
translation: Kodwa uFake uthe uza kubenza oku kuphela ngesivumelwano neFBI yokucubungula izityholo ngalo mkhonto kule veki ezayo, apho amaDemocrats bebekude.

source: UFlake ucebise oko ngokuthi athethe nesihlobo sakhe, I senator ye-Democrats uChris Coos.
reference: Flake was convinced in part by conversations with his friend, Democratic Sen. Chris Coons.
translation: UFake ucebise oku ngokuxoxa nesihlobo sakhe, uSenator wama-Democrats uChris Coons.

source: Emva kokuthetha noCoons kunye nezinye iisenators emva koko, uFlake uye wathatha isigqibo.
reference: After a conversation with Coons and several senators afterwards, Flake made his decision.
translation: Emva kokuxoxa noCoons nabanye, uFake wathatha isigqibo.

source: Okukhethwe nguFlake kunamandla, kuba kukho ubungqina bokuba amaRiphabhlikhi angangavoti ukkwamkela uKavanauh ngaphandle kokuba kwenziwe uphando.
reference: Flake's choice had power, because it was evident Republicans would not have the votes to approve Kavanaugh without the investigation.
translation: Okukhethwe nguFlake kunamandla, kuba kukho ubungqina bokuba amaRiphabhlikhi angangavoti ukkwamkela uKavanauh ngaphandle kokuba kwenziwe uphando.

source: UMongameli uTrump uvule uphando lweFBI ukuba kuphandwe ngezityholo abekwa zona uKavanaugh.
reference: President Trump has opened an FBI investigation into the allegations against Kavanaugh.
translation: UMongameli uTrump uvule uphando lweFBI ukuba kuphandwe ngezityholo abekwa zona uKavanaugh.

source: I-PM yaseBritain uMay utyhola iindlela ‚Äòzokudlalwa ngeepolitiki‚Äô ngaphezu kweBrexit.
reference: British PM May accuses critics of 'playing politics' over Brexit
translation: I-PM yaseBritain uMay utyhola iindlela 'zokudlalwa ngeepolitiki' ngaphezu kweBrexit.

source: U-Prime Minister Theresa May utyhola iindlela zezicwangciso ukushiya iEuropean Union ‚Äòngokudlala ngepolitiki‚Äô kunye nekamva laseBritain kunye nokujongela phantsi umdla welizwe oko ukutsho kudliwano ndlebe nephepha i-Sunday Times.
reference: Prime Minister Theresa May accused critics of her plans to leave the European Union of "playing politics" with Britain's future and undermining the national interest in an interview with the Sunday Times newspaper.
translation: U-Prime Minister Theresa May utyhola iindlela zezicwangciso ukushiya iEuropean Union 'ngokudlala ngepolitiki' kunye nekamva laseBritain kunye nokujongela phantsi umdla welizwe oko ukutsho kudliwano ndlebe nephepha i-Sunday Times.

source: U-Prime Minister Theresa May ufike iBirmingham, eBritain eze kwiNkomfa yeQela leConservative, nge-29 Septemba 2018.
reference: Britain's Prime Minister Theresa May arrives for the Conservative Party Conference in Birmingham, Britain, September 29, 2018.
translation: U-Prime Minister Theresa May ufike iBirmingham, eBritain eze kwiNkomfa yeQela leConservative, nge-29 Septemba 2018.

source: Ungquzulwano phakathi kwabaqhankqalazi base-Catalan namapolisa ngaphambi kokuba kubekho isikhumbuzo sokuvota.

translation: Ungquzulwano phakathi kwabaqhankqalazi base-Catalan namapolisa ngaphambi kokuba kubekho isikhumbuzo sokuvota.

source: Kwabanjwa abantu abathandathu eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo  emva kokuba abaxhasi be-pro indipendence benze ungquzulwano lwezixholoxholo zamapolisa, kwaye amawakawaka abaqhankqalazi ajoyina uqhankqalazo lotshaba ukuphawula isikhumbuzo sokuqala samaCatalonia sokwahlula ukurhoxa ekuvoteni.
reference: Six people were arrested in Barcelona on Saturday after pro-independence protesters clashed with riot police, and as thousands joined rival demonstrations to mark the first anniversary of Catalonia's polarizing vote on secession.
translation: Kwabanjwa abantu abathandathu eBarcelona ngoMgqibelo  emva kokuba abaxhasi be-pro indipendence benze ungquzulwano lwezixholoxholo zamapolisa, kwaye amawakawaka abaqhankqalazi ajoyina uqhankqalazo lotshaba ukuphawula isikhumbuzo sokuqala samaCatalonia sokwahlula ukurhoxa ekuvoteni.

source: Iqela elizigqumileyo labaxhasi labaqhankqalazi ebelibanjwe zizixholoxholo zamapolisa lihlasele ngamaqanda kunye nokujula ngepeyinti engumgubo, lisenza iingqimba zothuli ezitrateni oluya kuthi luphazamise abakhenkethi.
reference: A group of masked pro-separatists held back by riot police pelted them with eggs and hurled powder paint, creating dark clouds of dust in streets that would usually be thronged with tourists.
translation: Iqela elizigqumileyo labaxhasi labaqhankqalazi ebelibanjwe zizixholoxholo zamapolisa lihlasele ngamaqanda kunye nokujula ngepeyinti engumgubo, lisenza iingqimba zothuli ezitrateni oluya kuthi luphazamise abakhenkethi.

source: Imilo iye yaqhambuka emva kwexesha ngexesha lasemini apho amapolisa aye asebenzisa iintonga zawo ukunqanda ukulwa.
reference: Scuffles also broke out later in the day with police using their batons to contain the fighting.
translation: Imilo iye yaqhambuka emva kwexesha ngexesha lasemini apho amapolisa aye asebenzisa iintonga zawo ukunqanda ukulwa.

source: Emva kwexesha leeyure ezithile amaqela e pro-independence aye enza imikhwazo ‚ÄúAkukho kulibala, akukho kuxolela‚Äù aye ajongana ngqo nabaqhankqalazi bee-unionista bebeshawutisa , ‚ÄúUbomi obude Spain‚Äù.
reference: Over several hours pro-independence groups chanting "No forgetting, no forgiveness" faced off with unionist protesters shouting, "Long live Spain."
translation: Emva kwexesha leeyure ezithile amaqela e pro-independence aye enza imikhwazo "Akukho kulibala, akukho kuxolela" aye ajongana ngqo nabaqhankqalazi bee-unionista bebeshawutisa , "Ubomi obude Spain".

source: Abantu abalishumi elinesine baye bafumana unyango lomenzakalwana ongephi abawufumene kuqhankqalazo, lenze ingxelo iphepha lasekuhlaleni.
reference: Fourteen people received treatment for minor injuries received in the protests, local press reported.
translation: Abantu abalishumi elinesine baye bafumana unyango lomenzakalwana ongephi abawufumene kuqhankqalazo, lenze ingxelo iphepha lasekuhlaleni.

source: Ukuzibamba ngenxa yoloyiko kuhlale kunjalo kukwizinga eliphezuli kwingingqi ye-independennce, emva kwerefurundum yomhla we-1 Okthobha eqale ngokungekho mthethweni ngabantu baseMadrid kodwa yabe ibhiyozelwa ngabaqhankqalazi bee-Catalans.
reference: Tensions remain high in the independence-minded region a year after the October 1 referendum deemed illegal by Madrid but celebrated by separatist Catalans.
translation: Ukuzibamba ngenxa yoloyiko kuhlale kunjalo kukwizinga eliphezulu kwingingqi ye-independennce, emva kwerefurundum yomhla we-1 Okthobha eqale ngokungekho mthethweni ngabantu baseMadrid kodwa yabe ibhiyozelwa ngabaqhankqalazi bee-Catalans.

reference: Voters chose overwhelmingly to become independent, though turnout was low with those against secession largely boycotting the vote.
translation: Abavoti bakhethe ngokuzidla ukuba kwicala le-independent, nangona kuye kwafumaniseka ukuba kwakukwizinga eliphantsi kwaba bangahambelaniyo nokurhoxa kwizinga eliphezulu lokukwaya ukuvota.

source: Ngaphandle kokubanakho ukulawula uloyiso olucekeceke kulonyulo lwezithili ngoDisemba odlulileyo, amaqela e pro-independence aseCatalan aye asokola ukugcina loo meko kulo nyaka ngenxa yokuba iinkokheli zabo ezizezona zaziwayo zizigcine elubhacweni ngokunokwazo okanye ziphantsi kogcino lwamapolisa zilindele ukuxoxwa kwamatyala ngenxa yendima ezithe zayidlala ekuququzeleleni ireferundum kunye  nokulandela ukubhengezwa okuyimpumelelo kwenkululeko.
reference: Despite managing a vital if narrow victory in regional elections last December, Catalan pro-independence parties have struggled to retain momentum this year with many of their best known leaders either in self imposed exile or in detention awaiting trial for their role in organizing the referendum and subsequent declaration of independence.

source: Kunqabile ukuba  uxinzelelo lwetropical luhlasele iArizona, kodwa oko kunokwenzeka ngqo ekuqaleni kwale veki izayo njengoko i Hurricane Rosa isahleli inamandla okuhamba eNtlango yaseMzantsi mpuma, ahambisa imingcipheko yezikhukula ezinamanzi ahambela phezulu.
reference: It's rare for a tropical depression to hit Arizona, but that's exactly what's likely to happen early happen early next week as Hurricane Rosa's remaining energy tracks across the Desert Southwest, delivering flash flooding risks.
translation: Kunqabile ukuba  uxinzelelo lwetropical luhlasele iArizona, kodwa oko kunokwenzeka ngqo ekuqaleni kwale veki izayo njengoko i Hurricane Rosa isahleli inamandla okuhamba eNtlango yaseMzantsi mpuma, ahambisa imingcipheko yezikhukula ezinamanzi ahambela phezulu.

source: Inkonzo yeSimo sezulu kuZwelonke sele izinikezele izixhobo zokuqwalasela izikhukula zamanzi ngoMvulo nangolwesiBini kwintshona yeArizona nakwimpuma yeNavada, emazantsi ntshona eCalifornia naseUtah, kubandakanya ezi zixeko zilandelayo of Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, and Salt Lake City.
reference: The National Weather Service has already issued flash flood watches for Monday and Tuesday for western Arizona into southern and eastern Nevada, southeastern California and Utah, including the cities of Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, and Salt Lake City.
translation: Inkonzo yeSimo sezulu kuZwelonke sele izinikezele izixhobo zokuqwalasela izikhukula zamanzi ngoMvulo nangolwesiBini kwintshona yeArizona nakwimpuma yeNavada, emazantsi ntshona eCalifornia naseUtah, kubandakanya ezi zixeko zilandelayo of Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, and Salt Lake City.

source: Amakhulukhulu eIndonesianabulewe yinyikima, iTsunami ebonakala inesangqa esikhulayo
reference: Hundreds killed by Indonesian quake, tsunami, with toll seen rising
translation: Amakhulukhulu eIndonesianabulewe yinyikima, iTsunami ebonakala inesangqa esikhulayo

source: Ubuncinci bangama-384 abantu ababuleweyo, abaninzi batshayelwe bayowa kude ngamaza amakhulukazi angqubeke kumalwandle, apho inyikima enkulu kunye netsunami ziye zabetha isiqithi saseIndonesia eSulawesi, abasemagunyeni batshilo ngomgqibelo.
reference: At least 384 people were killed, many swept away as giant waves crashed onto beaches, when a major earthquake and tsunami hit the Indonesian island of Sulawesi, authorities said on Saturday.
translation: Ubuncinci bangama-384 abantu ababuleweyo, abaninzi batshayelwe bayowa kude ngamaza amakhulukazi angqubeke kumalwandle, apho inyikima enkulu kunye netsunami ziye zabetha isiqithi saseIndonesia eSulawesi, abasemagunyeni batshilo ngomgqibelo.

source: Amakhulukhulu abantu bebedibene kwifestivali ebikulwandle lwasePalu ngolwesiHlanu apho amaza ebephezulu kangangemitha ezintandathu (18 iinyawo) zingqubeke kumhlaba owomileyo, abatshayele abantu kuba abulele abantu abaninzi kwaye ebetshabalalisa kwanto isendleleni yawo.
reference: Hundreds of people had gathered for a festival on the beach in the city of Palu on Friday when waves as high as six meters (18 feet) smashed onshore at dusk, sweeping many to their deaths and destroying anything in their path.
translation: Amakhulukhulu abantu bebedibene kwifestivali ebikulwandle lwasePalu ngolwesiHlanu apho amaza ebephezulu kangangemitha ezintandathu (18 iinyawo) zingqubeke kumhlaba owomileyo, abatshayele abantu kuba abulele abantu abaninzi kwaye ebetshabalalisa kwanto isendleleni yawo.

source: Itsunami ilandela imagnitude yenyinkima engama-7.5.
reference: The tsunami followed a 7.5 magnitude earthquake.
translation: Itsunami ilandela imagnitude yenyinkima engama-7.5.

source: ‚ÄúNgelixa itsunami ithembisa ngokuvela izolo, abantu bebesenza imisebenzi yabo elwandle kwaye abakhange babaleke kwangoko yaye kuphele bengamaxhoba,‚Äù uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi searhente yaseIndonesia seeNkonzo zikaXakeka iBNPB uthethe watso xa ebenika amagqabantshintshi eJakarta.
reference: When the tsunami threat arose yesterday, people were still doing their activities on the beach and did not immediately run and they became victims, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, the spokesman for Indonesia's disaster mitigation agency BNPB said in a briefing in Jakarta.
translation: Ngelixa itsunami ithembisa ngokuvela izolo, abantu bebesenza imisebenzi yabo elwandle kwaye abakhange babaleke kwangoko yaye kuphele bengamaxhoba, uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi searhente yaseIndonesia seeNkonzo zikaXakeka iBNPB uthethe watso xa ebenika amagqabantshintshi eJakarta.

source: Itsunami ayizanga ihamba yodwa, irhuqe iimoto, iziqobo, izindlu, itsale yonke into esemhlabeni‚Äù, utshilo uNugroho,wongeze wathi itsunami ihambe ngolwandle oluvulekileyo ngesantya esingama-800 kph (497 mph) ngaphambi kokuba iyokufika elunxwemeni.	The tsunami didn't come by itself, it dragged cars, logs, houses, it hit everything on land," Nugroho said, adding that the tsunami had traveled across the open sea at speeds of 800 kph (497 mph) before striking the shoreline.
reference: Itsunami ayizanga ihamba yodwa, irhuqe iimoto, iziqobo, izindlu, itsale yonke into esemhlabeni, utshilo uNugroho, wongeze wathi itsunami ihambe ngolwandle oluvulekileyo ngesantya esingama-800 kph (497 mph) ngaphambi kokuba iyokufika elunxwemeni.

source: Abanye abantu bakhwele emithini kuba bezama ukuphepha itsunami kwaye basinde, utshilo.
reference: Some people climbed trees to escape the tsunami and survived, he said.
translation: Abanye abantu bakhwele emithini kuba bezama ukuphepha itsunami kwaye basinde, utshilo.

source: Malunga nabantu abangama- 6,700 baye bakhutshwa bashiya imizi yabo  baya kumaziko angama-24 ase Palu.

translation: Malunga nabantu abangama-6,700 baye bakhutshwa bashiya imizi yabo baya kumaziko angama-24 ase Palu.

source: I-Aerial photographsezikhutshwe yiarhente yeenkonzo zikaxakekazibonise izakhiwo ezininzi kunye neevenkile ezitshatyalaliswe yitsunami, iibhulorho ezikumila kumbi neziwileyo kunye nemosque ebirhangqwe ngamanzi.
reference: Aerial photographs released by the disaster agency showed many buildings and shops destroyed, bridges twisted and collapsed and a mosque surrounded by water.
translation: I-Aerial photographsezikhutshwe yiarhente yeenkonzo zikaxakekazibonise izakhiwo ezininzi kunye neevenkile ezitshatyalaliswe yitsunami, iibhulorho ezikumila kumbi neziwileyo kunye nemosque ebirhangqwe ngamanzi.

source: Uthotho lweenyikima luvakele kwingingqi enabantu abazizigidi ezingama-2.4.

translation: Uthotho lweenyikima luvakele kwingingqi enabantu abazizigidi ezingama-2.4.

source: Iarhente yaseIndonesia yekuVavanywa kkokuSetyenziswa kweTekhnoloji (BPPT) ithethe yathi kwintetho yayo inyikima ebinkulu kakhulu ibikhona ngamandla aphindwe amaxesha angama-200 xa uthelekisa nesiqhashumbisi senuclear esiphoswe  eHiroshima kuMlo wesiBini weHlabathi.
reference: Indonesia's Agency for the Assessment and Application of Technology (BPPT) said in statement the energy released by Friday's massive quake was around 200 times the power of the atomic bomb dropped on Hiroshima in World War Two.
translation: Iarhente yaseIndonesia yekuVavanywa kkokuSetyenziswa kweTekhnoloji (BPPT) ithethe yathi kwintetho yayo inyikima ebinkulu kakhulu ibikhona ngamandla aphindwe amaxesha angama-200 xa uthelekisa nesiqhashumbisi senuclear esiphoswe eHiroshima kuMlo wesiBini weHlabathi.

source: Ubunzululwazi ngezelizwe kwisiXeko, obuthi buhlale ekupheleni kobude, ukuvaleka kwetheku, kunokwandisa ubungakanani betsumani, itshilo.
reference: The geography of the city, which sits at the end of a long, narrow bay, could have magnified the size of the tsunami, it said.
translation: Ubunzululwazi ngezelizwe kwisiXeko, obuthi buhlale ekupheleni kobude, ukuvaleka kwetheku, kunokwandisa ubungakanani betsumani, itshilo.

source: UNugroho umonakalo uwuchaze njengo‚Äùmkhulu‚Äù kwaye uthe ngamawaka ezindlu, izibhedlele, udederhu lweevenkile kunye neehotele zidilikile.

source: UMongameli waseMexico u Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador uthembisile ukuba akasoze asebenzise imikhosi yokhuselo ngakubemi njengoko ilizwe lifikelele kwisikhumbuzo sama-50 sokwenzakala nokungaziphindezeli kwabafundi.
reference: Mexican President-elect Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador has vowed to never use military force against civilians as the country approaches the 50th anniversary of a bloody reprisal against students.
translation: UMongameli waseMexico u Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador uthembisile ukuba akasoze asebenzise imikhosi yokhuselo ngakubemi njengoko ilizwe lifikelele kwisikhumbuzo sama-50 sokwenzakala nokungaziphindezeli kwabafundi.

source: ULopez Obrador uthembise ngoMgqibelo eTlatelolco Plaza ukuba "akasoze asebenzise imikhosi ukucinezela abantu baseMexico."
reference: Lopez Obrador promised Saturday at Tlatelolco Plaza to "never ever use the military to repress the Mexican people."
translation: ULopez Obrador uthembise ngoMgqibelo eTlatelolco Plaza ukuba "akasoze asebenzise imikhosi ukucinezela abantu baseMexico."

source: Imikhosi yaqala ukudubula kumboniso wocwangco ubuseplaza ngo Oct. 2, 1968, yabulala abantu abaninzi abangama-300 people ngexesha lwemibutho yabafundi engcambu zayo ziseLatin America.
reference: Troops fired on a peaceful demonstration at the plaza on Oct. 2, 1968, killing as many as 300 people at a time when leftist student movements were taking root throughout Latin America.
translation: Imikhosi yaqala ukudubula kumboniso wocwangco ubuseplaza ngo Oct. 2, 1968, yabulala abantu abaninzi abangama-300 ngexesha lwemibutho yabafundi engcambu zayo ziseLatin America.

reference: Lopez Obrador has pledged to support young Mexicans by giving monthly subsidies to those who study and opening more free public universities.
translation: ULopez Obrador uthembisile ukuxhasa ulutsha lwaseMexico ngokulunika inkxaso yenyanga nenyanga kwabo bafundayo kunye nokuvula iiyunivesithi ezininzi nezivulelekileyo kuluntu.

source: Watsho ukuba ukungaqehswa kunye nokusilela kwamathuba emfundo kwenza ukuba ulutsha luzibandakanye namaqela abaphuli mthetho.

translation: Watsho ukuba ukungaqeshwa kunye nokusilela kwamathuba emfundo kwenza ukuba ulutsha luzibandakanye namaqela abaphuli mthetho.

source: I-U.S. iyiphindaphinde inkxaso mali yeA.I.
reference: U.S. should double A.I. funding
translation: I-U.S. iyiphindaphinde inkxaso mali yeA.I.

source: I-China iye ikhuthala ngakumbi kubuNgqondi obungebobamanyhani, iU.S. kufuneka iliphindaphinde ixesha elichitha kwicandelo lophando, utsho umxhasi ngezimali kunye ne-AI practitioner Kai-Fu Lee, osebenzela u Google, Microsoft no Apple.
reference: As China becomes more active in artificial intelligence, the U.S. should double the amount it spends on research in the field, says investor and AI practitioner Kai-Fu Lee, who has worked for Google, Microsoft and Apple.
translation: I-China iye ikhuthala ngakumbi kubuNgqondi obungebobamanyhani, iU.S. kufuneka iliphindaphinde ixesha elichitha kwicandelo lophando, utsho umxhasi ngezimali kunye ne-AI practitioner Kai-Fu Lee, osebenzela u Google, Microsoft no Apple.

source: Ezi khommenti ziza emva kokuba amacandelo ohlukeneyo orhulumente waseU.S. enze izibhengezo zeAI, nanjenge-U.S. esilela kuzo zonke iindlela zeAI ezisemthethweni.
reference: The comments come after various parts of the U.S. government have made AI announcements, even as the U.S. overall lacks a formal AI strategy.
translation: Ezi khommenti ziza emva kokuba amacandelo ohlukeneyo orhulumente waseU.S. enze izibhengezo zeAI, nanjenge-U.S. esilela kuzo zonke iindlela zeAI ezisemthethweni.

translation: Okwangoku, iChina yazise ngesicwangciso sayo kulo nyaka uphelileyo: ibijolise ekubeni ngu No.1 kuyilo lwe-AI ngo 2030.

source: Ukuphindaphindwa kwebhajethi yophando lwe-AI kuya kuba sisiqalo esifanelekileyo, njengoko onke amanye amazwe angemva lee kwiU.S., kwaye sijonge kuyilo olulandelayo lwe-AI, utshilo uLee.
reference: Double the AI research budget would be a good start, given that all other countries are so much farther behind U.S., and we're looking for the next breakthrough in AI, said Lee.
translation: Ukuphindaphindwa kwebhajethi yophando lwe-AI kuya kuba sisiqalo esifanelekileyo, njengoko onke amanye amazwe angemva lee kwiU.S., kwaye sijonge kuyilo olulandelayo lwe-AI, utshilo uLee.

source: Ukuphindaphinda inkxaso mali kungaphindaphinda amathuba okuphumelela kwe okukhulu okulandelayo kwe-AI okuya kwenziwa eU.S., utshilo uLee kudliwano ndlebe nabakwa-CNBC kule veki.
reference: Doubling funding could double the chances that the next big AI achievement will be made in the U.S., Lee told CNBC in an interview this week.
translation: Ukuphindaphinda inkxaso mali kungaphindaphinda amathuba okuphumelela kwe okukhulu okulandelayo kwe-AI okuya kwenziwa eU.S., utshilo uLee kudliwano ndlebe nabakwa-CNBC kule veki.

source: ULee, ongumbhali wencwadi ethi "Amandla amakhulu e-AI: I-China, Silicon Valley kunye ne New World Order" zipapashwe kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, iCEO yeSinovation Ventures, exhase ngezimali enye yeenkampani ezizezona zinkulu ze- AI eChina, iFace++.
reference: Lee, whose book "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" was published this month by Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, is CEO of Sinovation Ventures, which has invested in one of the most prominent AI companies in China, Face++.
translation: ULee, ongumbhali wencwadi ethi "Amandla amakhulu e-AI: I-China, Silicon Valley kunye ne New World Order" zipapashwe kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, iCEO yeSinovation Ventures, exhase ngezimali enye yeenkampani ezizezona zinkulu ze-AI eChina, iFace++.

reference: Macedonians vote in referendum on whether to change country's name
translation: Abantu baseMacedonia bavotile kwireferendum ukuba kutshintshwe igama lelizwe labo.

source: Abantu baseMacedonia bavotile kwireferendum ngeCawe ukuba kutshintshwe igama lelizwe libe "Riphabhlikhi yasemaNtla aseMacedonia," intshukumo eyakuthi isombulule ukuphikisana okudala kweminyaka elishumi nebhloke amalungu aye ukuba babize amaxabiso kwi European Union nakwi NATO.
reference: The people of Macedonia voted in a referendum on Sunday on whether to change its name to "Republic of North Macedonia," a move that would resolve a decades-old dispute with Greece which had blocked its membership bids for the European Union and NATO.
translation: Abantu baseMacedonia bavotile kwireferendum ngeCawe ukuba kutshintshwe igama lelizwe libe "Riphabhlikhi yasemaNtla aseMacedonia," intshukumo eyakuthi isombulule ukuphikisana okudala kweminyaka elishumi nebhloke amalungu aye ukuba babize amaxabiso kwi European Union nakwi NATO.

reference: Greece, which has a province called Macedonia, maintains that its northern neighbor's name represents a claim on its territory and has vetoed its entrance into NATO and the EU.
translation: IGreece, enephondo elibizwa ngokuba yiMacedonia, lifuna ukuba lasebumelwaneni balo ngasemaNtla limele ibango elikwindawo yalo kwaye liphelise isango elingena kwi NATO nakwi EU.

I came today to vote for the future of the country, for young people in Macedonia so they can be live freely under the umbrella of the European Union because it means safer lives for all of us," said Olivera Georgijevska, 79, in Skopje.

translation: Apho kubi khona ke namhlanje, le ntlanganiso yanamhlanje ayisiyotone yeentlanganiso esidla ngokuba nazo "inobuntu kwaye ithambile, itiphantsi" ezopolitika sezalibaleka ukba, kunjalo phofu, zingaphinde ziqale.

source: Kubonakala kuyinto ekhulayo ukohluka kwezimvo okwa kohluka akwamkelwa  kwiqela le-Labour kwaye lonke uluvo luyaphononongwa ngaphambi kokwamkelwa kwiqela lobunkekeli.
reference: It has become increasingly apparent that differing views are not tolerated in the Labour party and every opinion is judged on whether it is acceptable to the party leadership.
translation: Kubonakala kuyinto ekhulayo ukohluka kwezimvo okwa kohluka akwamkelwa kwiqela le-Labour kwaye lonke uluvo luyaphononongwa ngaphambi kokwamkelwa kwiqela lobunkekeli.

source: Oku kuqale emva kokungena kukaJeremy kwisihlalo sobunkokheli,njengomntu osebenza naye  nebendifudula ndinengcinga zokwabelana naye ngombono oyeleleneyo oawakhe ngezopolitiko nekulindeleke ukuba ndiyijike ngkukhawuleza kwaye ndithathe iindawo endingazange ndavuma ukuba ndingavumelana nazo-nokuba kungokhuseleko le-national okanye intengiso nokuba inye ye-EU.
reference: This started shortly after Jeremy became leader, as colleagues with whom I had previously thought I shared a similar political outlook began expecting me to do a U-turn and take positions I would never have otherwise agreed with - whether on national security or the EU single market.
translation: Oku kuqale emva kokungena kukaJeremy kwisihlalo sobunkokheli, njengomntu osebenza naye nebendifudula ndinengcinga zokwabelana naye ngombono oyeleleneyo oawakhe ngezopolitiko nekulindeleke ukuba ndiyijike ngkukhawuleza kwaye ndithathe iindawo endingazange ndavuma ukuba ndingavumelana nazo-nokuba kungokhuseleko le-national okanye intengiso nokuba inye ye-EU.

source: Nanini na ndithetha phandle- kwaye oko andibinandaba nako-kuye kulandele ukuhlukunyezwa kumakhasi onxibelelwano kisithiwa mandehliswe esihlalweni, kungamkelwa iipolitiki zeziko, ndixelelwa ukuba andikufanelanga ukuba ndikwiqela leLabour.
reference: Whenever I speak publicly - and it doesn't really matter what I say - there follows a tirade of abuse on social media calling for deselection, denouncing the politics of the centre, telling me I should not be in the Labour party.
translation: Nanini na ndithetha phandle- kwaye oko andibinandaba nako-kuye kulandele ukuhlukunyezwa kumakhasi onxibelelwano kisithiwa mandehliswe esihlalweni, kungamkelwa iipolitiki zeziko, ndixelelwa ukuba andikufanelanga ukuba ndikwiqela leLabour.

source: Kwaye oko kungamava am.
reference: And that is not just my experience.
translation: Kwaye oko kungamava am.

source: Ngokunjalo, ndiyazi ukuba ndinethamsanqa ngakumbi kunabanye endisebenza nabo njengoko iikhomenti zisiziswa kum ngqo ziye zithande ukuba zezepolitiki.
reference: Indeed, I know I am more fortunate than some of my colleagues as the comments directed at me tend to be political.
translation: Ngokunjalo, ndiyazi ukuba ndinethamsanqa ngakumbi kunabanye endisebenza nabo njengoko iikhomenti zisiziswa kum ngqo ziye zithande ukuba zezepolitiki.

source: Ndiyabuhlonipha ubugcisa kunye nokuzimisela kwabantu endisebenza nabo abajongene nokunyamezela ukuhlukunyezwa ngokwesini okanye ngokobuhlanga yonke imihla kodwa bengenakho ukugibisela kude bona.
reference: I am in awe of the professionalism and determination of those colleagues who face a torrent of sexist or racist abuse every day but never shy away.
translation: Ndiyabuhlonipha ubugcisa kunye nokuzimisela kwabantu endisebenza nabo abajongene nokunyamezela ukuhlukunyezwa ngokwesini okanye ngokobuhlanga yonke imihla kodwa bengenakho ukugibisela kude bona.

source: Enye yezinto ezizezona ziphoxayo kule era yezopolitiko yindlela angayo amanqanaba ohlukumezo nasele ethande ukuqheleka.
reference: One of the most disappointing aspects of this era of politics is how levels of abuse have become normalised.
translation: Enye yezinto ezizezona ziphoxayo kule era yezopolitiko yindlela angayo amanqanaba ohlukumezo nasele ethande ukuqheleka.

source: UJeremy Corbyn uchaze kule veki iphelileyo ukuba iqela le-Labour lithathele kulo inkcubeko yokunyamezela.
reference: Jeremy Corbyn claimed last week that the Labour party should foster a culture of tolerance.
translation: UJeremy Corbyn uchaze kule veki iphelileyo ukuba iqela le-Labour lithathele kulo inkcubeko yokunyamezela.

source: Inyani yile yokuba asiseyiyo la cawe inkulu kwaye ngemo "yokungabi nathemba" okanye eyokutshintsha imigaqo yeqelaeye yabacekeceke.
reference: The reality is we are no longer that broad church and with every "no-confidence" motion or change of selection rules the party becomes narrower.
translation: Inyani yile yokuba asiseyiyo la cawe inkulu kwaye ngemo "yokungabi nathemba" okanye eyokutshintsha imigaqo yeqelaeye yabacekeceke.

source: INdineengcebiso ezininzi kule minyaka mibini idlulileyo zindicela ukuba mandiyekelele, ndingathethi ngale ndlela ndithetha ngayo kwaye emva koko ‚Äúkonke kuyakulunga."
reference: I have had lots of advice over the past two years urging me to keep my head down, not to be so vocal and then I would "be all right."
translation: Ndinengcebiso ezininzi kule minyaka mibini idlulileyo zindicela ukuba mandiyekelele, ndingathethi ngale ndlela ndithetha ngayo kwaye emva koko "konke kuyakulunga."

source: Kodwa le ayisiyiyo into endizoyenza kwezopolitiko.
reference: But that is not what I came into politics to do.
translation: Kodwa le ayisiyiyo into endizoyenza kwezopolitiko.

source: Okoko ndathi ndajoyina iLabour kwimunyaka engama-32 njengomntwana wesikolo, ukuxhokonkxwa ngurhulumente kaThatcher ungakukhathaleli ukungahoyi igumbi ebendifundela kulo alishiye lisiwa phantsi, ukusukela ngoko ndafunga ukuba ndizakulwela ezona nkonzo zingcono zoluntu nabazidingayo, kakhulu-nokuba ndibenguceba okanye umphathiswa karhulumente..
reference: Ever since I joined Labour 32 years ago as a school pupil, provoked by the Thatcher government's neglect that had left my comprehensive school classroom literally falling down, I've sought to champion better public services for those who need them most - whether as a local councillor or government minister.
translation: Okoko ndathi ndajoyina iLabour kwimunyaka engama-32 njengomntwana wesikolo, ukuxhokonkxwa ngurhulumente kaThatcher ungakukhathaleli ukungahoyi igumbi ebendifundela kulo alishiye lisiwa phantsi, ukusukela ngoko ndafunga ukuba ndizakulwela ezona nkonzo zingcono zoluntu nabazidingayo, kakhulu-nokuba ndibenguceba okanye umphathiswa karhulumente.

source: Zange ndakufihla ukubandakanyeka kwam kwezopolitiko, kuquka nakolu lonyulo ludlulileyo.
reference: I have never hidden my politics, including at the last election.
translation: Zange ndakufihla ukubandakanyeka kwam kwezopolitiko, kuquka nakolu lonyulo ludlulileyo.

source: Akukho namnye kwiMpuma yaseNottingham onokubhideka yiyo nayiphi na indlela malunga nendawo endime kuyo kwipolisi yam, nakwiindawo endingavumelani kuzo nezinkokheli zikhoyo ngoku.
reference: No one in Nottingham East could have been in any way confused about my policy positions and areas of disagreement with the current leadership.
translation: Akukho namnye kwiMpuma yaseNottingham onokubhideka yiyo nayiphi na indlela malunga nendawo endime kuyo kwipolisi yam, nakwiindawo endingavumelani kuzo nezinkokheli zikhoyo ngoku.

source: Kwezi meko zonyuselweyo ngoku ngolwesiHlanu, kuzo zonke ndingathi ngelixa uBrexit aphembelela ukukwenzakalisa ezindlini, kumashishini nakwiinkonzo zethu zoluntu, andiwuqondi umnqweno wakhe wokuchitha ixesha kunye namandla kuthembeko lwam kwinkokheli yeqela le- Labour.
reference: To those who promoted the motion on Friday, all I would say is that when the country is ploughing towards a Brexit that will hurt households, businesses and our public services, I do not understand the desire to waste time and energy on my loyalty to the Labour party leader.
translation: Kwezi meko zonyuselweyo ngoku ngolwesiHlanu, kuzo zonke ndingathi ngelixa uBrexit aphembelela ukukwenzakalisa ezindlini, kumashishini nakwiinkonzo zethu zoluntu, andiwuqondi umnqweno wakhe wokuchitha ixesha kunye namandla kuthembeko lwam kwinkokheli yeqela le-Labour.

source: Kpdwa eyona nyani kukuba umyalezo omnye endinawo awuyi kwiNottingham Momentum, uya kubantu bam, nokuba bangamalungu eLabour okanye abangawo: Ndiyazingca ngokusebenza phantsi kwenu kwaye ndiyathembisa ukuba akukho xabiso lakuyekwa kwezoyikso okanye uncedo lwezopolitiko linokundinqanda ekwenzeni into endikholelwa ukuba izezona mfuno zenu ziphambili kuni nonke.
reference: But really the one message I have is not to Nottingham Momentum, it is to my constituents, whether Labour members or not: I am proud to serve you and I promise that no amount of deselection threats or political expediency will deter me from acting in what I believe are the best interests of you all.
translation: Kodwa eyona nyani kukuba umyalezo omnye endinawo awuyi kwiNottingham Momentum, uya kubantu bam, nokuba bangamalungu eLabour okanye abangawo: Ndiyazingca ngokusebenza phantsi kwenu kwaye ndiyathembisa ukuba akukho xabiso lakuyekwa kwezoyikso okanye uncedo lwezopolitiko linokundinqanda ekwenzeni into endikholelwa ukuba izezona mfuno zenu ziphambili kuni nonke.

source: UChris Leslie yi -MP yaseMpuma Nottingham
reference: Chris Leslie is MP for Nottingham East
translation: UChris Leslie yi-MP yaseMpuma Nottingham

source: Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: U-Ayr uya phambili
reference: Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: Unbeaten Ayr go top
translation: Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: U-Ayr uya phambili

source: Iitries ezimbini zamva zikekelele kumagqibela kankqoyi aphantse akhokelela kwiziphumo, kodwa akukho kuthandabuza ukuba uAyr ulufanele olu loyiso luhle kangaka lokubhiyozelwa komdlalo wosuku weTennent's Premiership .
reference: Two late tries may have skewed the final result somewhat, but there is no doubt Ayr deserved to triumph in this wonderfully-entertaining Tennent's Premiership match of the day.
translation: Iitries ezimbini zamva zikekelele kumagqibela kankqoyi aphantse akhokelela kwiziphumo, kodwa akukho kuthandabuza ukuba uAyr ulufanele olu loyiso luhle kangaka lokubhiyozelwa komdlalo wosuku weTennent's Premiership.

source: Ngoku bonyusa izinga, elona cala lingohlulwayo.
reference: They now top the table, the only unbeaten side of the ten.
translation: Ngoku bonyusa izinga, elona cala lingohlulwayo.

source: Ekugqibeleni, yayikukukhuselwa kwabo okukumgangatho ophezulu, nqwa nethuba labo lokuba bathathe ithuba elingcono, elibangele ukoniliseka kwecala lasekhaya kunye nomqeqeshi uPeter Murchie.
reference: In the end, it was their superior defence, as much as their better chance-taking, which carried the home side and coach Peter Murchie had every right to be pleased.
translation: Ekugqibeleni, yayikukukhuselwa kwabo okukumgangatho ophezulu, nqwa nethuba labo lokuba bathathe ithuba elingcono, elibangele ukoniliseka kwecala lasekhaya kunye nomqeqeshi uPeter Murchie.

source: Sivavanyiwe kwimidlalo yethu ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, kwaye asikabethwa nangoku, ngako oko kumele ndonwabe, utshilo.
reference: We've been tested over our games this far, and we're still unbeaten, so I have to be happy, he said.
translation: Sivavanyiwe kwimidlalo yethu ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, kwaye asikabethwa nangoku, ngako oko kumele ndonwabe, utshilo.

source: URobyn Christie wase Melrose utshilo: "Ukuncoma uAyr, benze ngcono kunokuba thina senzile."
reference: Robyn Christie of Melrose said: "Credit to Ayr, they took their chances better than we did."
translation: URobyn Christie wase Melrose utshilo: "Ukuncoma uAyr, benze ngcono kunokuba thina senzile."

source: UGrant Anderson kwi-try yakhe ebe kwimizuzu engama-14, etshintshwe nguFrazier Climo,uye wabeka u Ayr ngaphambili, kodwa, ikhadi eliyellow lwe-cap yase Scotland uRory Hughes, likhutshelwe umdlalo ziiWarriors, kumvumele uMelrose ukuba enze iinamabari azixele kwaye uJason Baggot athathe ezingatshintshwanga azame ukuzitshintsha.
reference: Grant Anderson's 14th minute try, converted by Frazier Climo, put Ayr in front, but, a yellow card for Scotland cap Rory Hughes, released for the game by Warriors, allowed Melrose to make numbers tell and Jason Baggot grabbed an unconverted try.
translation: UGrant Anderson kwi-try yakhe ebe kwimizuzu engama-14, etshintshwe nguFrazier Climo, uye wabeka u Ayr ngaphambili, kodwa, ikhadi eliyellow lwe-cap yase Scotland uRory Hughes, likhutshelwe umdlalo ziiWarriors, kumvumele uMelrose ukuba enze iinamabari azixele kwaye uJason Baggot athathe ezingatshintshwanga azame ukuzitshintsha.

source: UClimo wolule ubunkokheli buka Ayr ngepenalty, ngaphambi, kwexesha lesiqingatha somdlalo, uye wafaka inqaku emva koko watshintsha isolo try yenza u17-5 ku-Ayr ngexesha lokuphumla.
reference: Climo stretched the Ayr lead with a penalty, before, right on half-time, he scored then converted a solo try to make it 17-5 to Ayr at the break.
translation: UClimo wolule ubunkokheli buka Ayr ngepenalty, ngaphambi, kwexesha lesiqingatha somdlalo, uye wafaka inqaku emva koko watshintsha isolo try yenza u17-5 ku-Ayr ngexesha lokuphumla.

source: Kodwa iMelrose isiqalise kakuhle isiqingatha sesibini yaye itrayi kaPatrick Anderson', eyaguqulwa nguBaggot, yanciphisa ithuba lamanqaku amahlanu.
reference: But Melrose began the second half well and Patrick Anderson's try, converted by Baggot, reduced the leeway to five points.
translation: Kodwa iMelrose isiqalise kakuhle isiqingatha sesibini yaye itrayi kaPatrick Anderson', eyaguqulwa nguBaggot, yanciphisa ithuba lamanqaku amahlanu.

source: Kukhe kwathiwa xhaa ixesha elide ngenxa yokwenzakala kakhulu kukaRuaridh Knott, oye wakhutshwa ngestretsha, yaye xa bekuphinda kuqalwa iAyr iye yenyuka ngokukhawuleza ngetrayi kaStafford McDowall, eguqulwe nguClimo.
reference: There was then a lengthy hold-up for a serious injury to Ruaridh Knott, who was stretchered off, and from the restart, Ayr surged further ahead through a Stafford McDowall try, converted by Climo.
translation: Kukhe kwathiwa xhaa ixesha elide ngenxa yokwenzakala kakhulu kukaRuaridh Knott, oye wakhutshwa ngestretsha, yaye xa bekuphinda kuqalwa iAyr iye yenyuka ngokukhawuleza ngetrayi kaStafford McDowall, eguqulwe nguClimo.

source: Ukapteni obambeleyo weAyr uBlair Macpherson uye wanikwa ikhadi elityheli, yaye kwakhona, iMelrose iye yahlawulisa enye indoda ngetrayi engaguqulwanga kaBruce Colvine, phantsi koxinezelelo olumandla.
reference: Ayr acting captain Blair Macpherson was then yellow-carded, and again, Melrose made the extra man pay with an unconverted Bruce Colvine try, at the end of a spell of fierce pressure.
translation: Ukapteni obambeleyo weAyr uBlair Macpherson uye wanikwa ikhadi elityheli, yaye kwakhona, iMelrose iye yahlawulisa enye indoda ngetrayi engaguqulwanga kaBruce Colvine, phantsi koxinezelelo olumandla.

source: Noko ke, kubuyelwe ekhaya yaye kuthe xa uStruan Hutchinson enikwa ikhadi elityheli ngenxa yokulenga uClimo engenabhola ngaphandle komgca wepenalti, uMacPherson uye waya kulala emva njengoko eleqwa yi-Ayr.
reference: The home side came back, however, and when Struan Hutchinson was yellow-carded for tackling Climo without the ball, from the penalty line-out, MacPherson touched down at the back of the advancing Ayr maul.
translation: Noko ke, kubuyelwe ekhaya yaye kuthe xa uStruan Hutchinson enikwa ikhadi elityheli ngenxa yokulenga uClimo engenabhola ngaphandle komgca wepenalti, uMacPherson uye waya kulala emva njengoko eleqwa yi-Ayr.

source: UClimo uye waguqula, njengoko phantse ukususela xa bekuqalwa kwakhona, emva kokuba uKyle Rowe ehlanganise iibhola zikaDavid Armstrong azikhabele ebhokisini waza wathumela iflenka uGregor Henry kude ngokufaka itrayi yesihlanu.
reference: Climo converted, as he did again almost from the restart, after Kyle Rowe gathered David Armstrong's box kick and sent flanker Gregor Henry away for the home side's fifth try.
translation: UClimo uye waguqula, njengoko phantse ukususela xa bekuqalwa kwakhona, emva kokuba uKyle Rowe ehlanganise iibhola zikaDavid Armstrong azikhabele ebhokisini waza wathumela iflenka uGregor Henry kude ngokufaka itrayi yesihlanu.

source: Kuyo yonke iBolivia evaleleke emhlabeni, iinkumbulo zonxweme lolwandle olwathathwa yiChile kwimfazwe yokulwela ubuncwane eyaba nophalalo gazi oluninzi ngenkulungwane ye-19 zisathe tha ezingqondweni - njengoko kunjalo nangomnqweno wokuphinda bahambe kuLwandlekazi lwePasifiki.
reference: Throughout landlocked Bolivia, the memory of a coastline lost to Chile in a bloody 19th-century resource conflict is still vivid - as is the yearning to sail the Pacific Ocean once more.
translation: Kuyo yonke iBolivia evaleleke emhlabeni, iinkumbulo zonxweme lolwandle olwathathwa yiChile kwimfazwe yokulwela ubuncwane eyaba nophalalo gazi oluninzi ngenkulungwane ye-19 zisathe tha ezingqondweni - njengoko kunjalo nangomnqweno wokuphinda bahambe kuLwandlekazi lwePasifiki.

source: Mhlawumbi la mathemba aphakame ngeyona ndlela kwiinkulungwane, njengoko iBolivia ilindele isigwebo senkundla yomthetho yehlabathi ngo-Oktobha 1 emva kweminyaka emihlanu yeengxoxo.
reference: Those hopes are perhaps at their highest in decades, as Bolivia awaits a ruling by the international court of justice on 1 October after five years of deliberations.
translation: Mhlawumbi la mathemba aphakame ngeyona ndlela kwiinkulungwane, njengoko iBolivia ilindele isigwebo senkundla yomthetho yehlabathi ngo-Oktobha 1 emva kweminyaka emihlanu yeengxoxo.

source: IBolivia inamandla, umoya womanyano nokuzola, yaye izilinde ngomoya omhle iziphumo,‚Äù utshilo uRoberto Calzadilla, unozakuzaku waseBolivia.	Bolivia has the momentum, a spirit of unity and serenity, and is of course expecting with a positive view the outcome," said Roberto Calzadilla, a Bolivian diplomat.
reference: IBolivia inamandla, umoya womanyano nokuzola, yaye izilinde ngomoya omhle iziphumo, utshilo uRoberto Calzadilla, unozakuzaku waseBolivia.

source: Abantu abaninzi baseBolivi baya kuphulaphula isigwebo seNkundla yoMthetho Yehlabathi kwizikrini ezikhulu kulo lonke elo lizwe, benethemba lokuba inkundla yaseHague iya kuma ngakwibango leBolivia lokuba - emva kwamashumi eminyaka okumana kuthethwana kuphinde kuyekwe - iChile inyanzelekile ukuba icinge ngokunika iBolivia indawo enobunganga engena elwandle.
reference: Many Bolivians will watch the ICJ ruling on big screens across the country, hopeful that the tribunal in The Hague will find in favour of Bolivia's claim that - after decades of fitful talks - Chile is obliged to negotiate granting Bolivia a sovereign outlet to the sea.
translation: Abantu abaninzi baseBolivi baya kuphulaphula isigwebo seNkundla yoMthetho Yehlabathi kwizikrini ezikhulu kulo lonke elo lizwe, benethemba lokuba inkundla yaseHague iya kuma ngakwibango leBolivia lokuba - emva kwamashumi eminyaka okumana kuthethwana kuphinde kuyekwe - iChile inyanzelekile ukuba icinge ngokunika iBolivia indawo enobunganga engena elwandle.

source: UEvo Morales, umongameli waseBolivia onobomi noyinzalelwane yalapho - ojongene nedabi elinzimal okuphinda anyulwe kunyaka ozayo - naye unento eninzi exhomekeke kwesi sigwebo sangoMvulo.
reference: Evo Morales, Bolivia's charismatic indigenous president - who faces a controversial battle for re-election next year - also has plenty riding on Monday's ruling.
translation: UEvo Morales, umongameli waseBolivia onobomi noyinzalelwane yalapho - ojongene nedabi elinzimal okuphinda anyulwe kunyaka ozayo - naye unento eninzi exhomekeke kwesi sigwebo sangoMvulo.

source: Sesisondele kakhulu ekubuyeleni kuLwandlekazi lwePasifiki, uqinisekise ngelitshoyo ngasekupheleni kuka-Agasti.
reference: We are very close to returning to the Pacific Ocean, he vowed in late August.
translation: Sesisondele kakhulu ekubuyeleni kuLwandlekazi lwePasifiki, uqinisekise ngelitshoyo ngasekupheleni kuka-Agasti.

source: Kodwa abanye abahlalutyi baciinga ukuba akunakufane kwenzeke inkundla igwebe ngakwicala leBolivia - akhonto iya kuuitshintsha kangako loo nto.
reference: But some analysts believe that the court is unlikely to decide in Bolivia's favour - and that little would change if it did.
translation: Kodwa abanye abahlalutyi baciinga ukuba akunakufane kwenzeke inkundla igwebe ngakwicala leBolivia - akhonto iya kuuitshintsha kangako loo nto.

source: IQumrhu leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo elizinze eNetherlands-alinamandla okukhupha umhlaba waseChile, yaye litshilo ukuba alinakuzazi iziphumo zeentetho ezinokubakho.
reference: The Netherlands-based UN body has no power to award Chilean territory, and has stipulated that it will not determine the outcome of possible talks.
translation: IQumrhu leZizwe Ezimanyeneyo elizinze eNetherlands-alinamandla okukhupha umhlaba waseChile, yaye litshilo ukuba alinakuzazi iziphumo zeentetho ezinokubakho.

source: Isibakala sokuba isigwebo seNkundla yoMthetho Yehlabathi siphume kwiinyanga ezintandathu kuphela emva kokuba kuxoxiwe kubonisa ukuba eli ityala ‚Äúbelingenabuzaza,‚Äù utshilo uPaz Z√°rate, ingcali yaseChile kwezomthetho wehlabathi.
reference: That the ICJ's ruling comes only six months after the final arguments were heard indicates the case "wasn't complicated," said Paz Z√°rate, a Chilean expert in international law.
translation: Isibakala sokuba isigwebo seNkundla yoMthetho Yehlabathi siphume kwiinyanga ezintandathu kuphela emva kokuba kuxoxiwe kubonisa ukuba eli ityala "belingenabuzaza," utshilo uPaz Z√°rate, ingcali yaseChile kwezomthetho wehlabathi.

source: Yaye kunokuba incedisane neminqweno yeBolivia, iminyaka emine kusenokwenzeka iyibuyisele umva.
reference: And far from furthering Bolivia's cause, the past four years may have set it back.
translation: Yaye kunokuba incedisane neminqweno yeBolivia, iminyaka emine kusenokwenzeka iyibuyisele umva.

source: Umba wofikelelo lwaselwandle uye waqweqwediswa ngurhulumente okhoyo waseBolivia, utshilo uZ√°rate.
reference: The issue of access to the sea has been hijacked by the current Bolivian administration, said Z√°rate.
translation: Umba wofikelelo lwaselwandle uye waqweqwediswa ngurhulumente okhoyo waseBolivia, utshilo uZ√°rate.

source: Amazwi okulwa kaMorales aye agqiba nabuphi na ububele ebisenabo iChile, utshilo.
reference: Morales's belligerent rhetoric has sapped any residual Chilean goodwill, she suggested.
translation: Amazwi okulwa kaMorales aye agqiba nabuphi na ububele ebisenabo iChile, utshilo.

source: IBolivia neChile ziya kuphinda zithethe ngenye imini, kodwa kuya kuba nzima gqitha ukubamba iingxoxo emva kwale nto.
reference: Bolivia and Chile will at some point continue to talk, but it will be extremely difficult to hold discussions after this.
translation: IBolivia neChile ziya kuphinda zithethe ngenye imini, kodwa kuya kuba nzima gqitha ukubamba iingxoxo emva kwale nto.

source: La mazwe mabini akakhange athumelelane oonozakuzaku ukususela ngowe-1962.
reference: The two countries have not exchanged ambassadors since 1962.
translation: La mazwe mabini akakhange athumelelane oonozakuzaku ukususela ngowe-1962.

source: Owayesakuba nguMongameli uEduardo Rodr√≠guez Veltz√©, ongummeli weBolivia eThe Hague, uyikhabile into ethi le nkundla ithathe isigqibo ngokukhawuleza ngendlela engaqhelekanga.
reference: Former president Eduardo Rodr√≠guez Veltz√©, Bolivia's representative at The Hague, rejected the idea that the court's decision-making was unusually speedy.

source: UMvulo uya kunika iBolivia "ithuba elikhethekileyo lokutyhila kwiphepha elitsha lokusebenzisana neChile‚Äù nethuba ‚Äúlokuphelisa iminyaka eli-139 yokungavisisani kuumaneke iinzuzo," utshilo.
reference: Monday will bring Bolivia "an extraordinary opportunity to open a new era of relations with Chile" and a chance to "put an end to 139 years of disagreements with mutual benefits," he said.
translation: UMvulo uya kunika iBolivia "ithuba elikhethekileyo lokutyhila kwiphepha elitsha lokusebenzisana neChile" nethuba "lokuphelisa iminyaka eli-139 yokungavisisani kuumaneke iinzuzo," utshilo.

source: UCalzadilla ukwasikhabile isibakala sokuba Morales - ongomnye woomongameli abathandwa kakhulu eLatin Amerika - usebenzisa lo mba wolwandle njengexhadi lezopolitiko.
reference: Calzadilla also denied that Morales - still one of Latin America's most popular presidents - was using the maritime issue as a political crutch.
translation: UCalzadilla ukwasikhabile isibakala sokuba Morales - ongomnye woomongameli abathandwa kakhulu eLatin Amerika - usebenzisa lo mba wolwandle njengexhadi lezopolitiko.

source: IBolivia ayisoze iliyeke nje ilungelo layo lokukwazi ukufikelela kuLwandlekazi iPasiifiki, waleke ngelitshoyo.
reference: Bolivia will never give up its right to have access to the Pacific Ocean, he added.
translation: I-Bolivia ayisoze iliyeke nje ilungelo layo lokukwazi ukufikelela kuLwandlekazi iPasiifiki, waleke ngelitshoyo.

source: Esi sigwebo silithuba lokubona ukuba kufuneka sizoyise izinto ezenzeke kwixa elidluleyo.
reference: The ruling is an opportunity to see that we need to overcome the past.
translation: Esi sigwebo silithuba lokubona ukuba kufuneka sizoyise izinto ezenzeke kwixa elidluleyo.

source: UMntla Korea ithi ayisayi kuzilahla izixhobo zenyukliya de ibe inokuyithemba iUnited States
reference: North Korea says nuclear disarmament won't come unless it can trust US
translation: UMntla Korea ithi ayisayi kuzilahla izixhobo zenyukliya de ibe inokuyithemba iUnited States

source: UMphathiswa Wezangaphandla kuMntla Korea uRi Yong Ho uthi ilizwe lakhe alisayi kwahlukana nezixhobo zayo zenyukliya kuqala ukuba aliyithembi iWashington.

reference: Ri was speaking Saturday at the United Nations General Assembly.
translation: URi ebethetha ngoMgqibelo kwiNdlu Yowiso-mthetho yeZizwe Ezimanyeneyo.

reference: He called on the United States to follow through on promises made during a summit in Singapore between the rivals' leaders.
translation: Ucele iUnited States ukuba ilandelele izithembiso ezenziwe ebudeni bengqungquthela eyayiseSingapore phakathi kweenkokeli ezijongene ngezikhondo zamehlo.

reference: His comments come as US. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo seems to be on the verge of restarting deadlocked nuclear diplomacy more than three months after the Singapore with North Korea's Kim Jong Un.
translation: Uthetha la mazwii xa kanye uSihlalo weLizwe uMike Pompeo ebonakala sele eza kuphinda aqale uthethwano obelusele luyekiwe ngenyukliya ngaphezu kweenyanga ezintathu emva kwezo zaseSingapore kunye noKim Jong Un wakuMntla Korea.

source: URi uthi "yintsom‚Äô emini‚Äù into yokuba ukwayo oluqhubekayo nokwala kweUnited States isindululo esiphelisa iMfazwe yaseKorea kuya kuze kwenze uMntla unikezele.
reference: Ri says it's a "pipe dream" that continued sanctions and U.S. objection to a declaration ending the Korean War will ever bring the North to its knees.
translation: URi uthi "yintsom' emini" into yokuba ukwayo oluqhubekayo nokwala kweUnited States isindululo esiphelisa iMfazwe yaseKorea kuya kuze kwenze uMntla unikezele.

translation: IWashington ikulumkele ukusivuma esi sivumelwano ngaphambi kokuba uPyongyang aqale athathe amanyathelo okwahlukana nezi zixhobo.

source: UKim noMongameli waseUnited States uDonald Trump bafuna ingqungquthela yesibini.
reference: Both Kim and U.S. President Donald Trump want a second summit.
translation: UKim noMongameli waseUnited States uDonald Trump bafuna ingqungquthela yesibini.

source: Kodwa abantu abaninzi bayathandabuza ukuba uPyongyang uzimisele ukuncama izixhobo ezigqalwa leli lizwe njengekuphela kwendlela yokuqinisekisa ukuba likhuselekile.
reference: But there is widespread skepticism that Pyongyang is serious about renouncing an arsenal that the country likely sees as the only way to guarantee its safety.
translation: Kodwa abantu abaninzi bayathandabuza ukuba uPyongyang uzimisele ukuncama izixhobo ezigqalwa leli lizwe njengekuphela kwendlela yokuqinisekisa ukuba likhuselekile.

translation: UPompeo uceba ukutyelela uPyongyang kule nyanga izayo ukuze alungiselele ingqungquthela kaKim noTrump.

source: Imiboniso yefashoni yaseParis ibonisa ngeminqwazi eyahlukeneyo yakutshanje oza kuyibona kwizitrato zedolophu ekufutshane nawe
reference: Paris fashion shows reveal latest line in massive headwear on it's way to a High Street near you
translation: Imiboniso yefashoni yaseParis ibonisa ngeminqwazi eyahlukeneyo yakutshanje oza kuyibona kwizitrato zedolophu ekufutshane nawe

source: Ukuba ufuna ukwandisa iminqwazi onayo okanye ufuna ukusitha ilanga ngoko sukuya kwenye indawo.
reference: If you want to upsize your hat collection or completely block out the sun then look no further.
translation: Ukuba ufuna ukwandisa iminqwazi onayo okanye ufuna ukusitha ilanga ngoko sukuya kwenye indawo.

source: Abayili uValentino noThom Browne baye baqalisa ukwenza intaphane yeminqwazi engaqhelekanga emikhulu kakhulu yemiboniso i-SS19 eye yaphum ecaleni kumgangatho obekwe kwiVeki yeFashoni yaseParis.
reference: Designers Valentino and Thom Browne unveiled an array of wacky oversized head gear for their SS19 collection on the runway which dazzled the style set at Paris Fashion Week.
translation: Abayili uValentino noThom Browne baye baqalisa ukwenza intaphane yeminqwazi engaqhelekanga emikhulu kakhulu yemiboniso i-SS19 eye yaphum ecaleni kumgangatho obekwe kwiVeki yeFashoni yaseParis.

source: Le minqwazi ikhwankqisayo iye yagqugqisa ku-Instagram kweli hlobo yaye aba bayili baye bathumela le minqwazi yabo yothusayo embonisweni.
reference: Highly impractical hats have swept Instagram this summer and these designers have sent their eye-popping creations down the catwalk.
translation: Le minqwazi ikhwankqisayo iye yagqugqisa ku-Instagram kweli hlobo yaye aba bayili baye bathumela le minqwazi yabo yothusayo embonisweni.

source: Umnqwazi obuhamba wodwa kaValentino ububheyiji unosiba ubanzi uyigqume yonke intloko yombonisi mpahla.
reference: The stand out piece by Valentino was an over-the-top beige hat adorned with a feather-like wide brim that swamped the models heads.
translation: Umnqwazi obuhamba wodwa kaValentino ububheyiji unosiba ubanzi uyigqume yonke intloko yombonisi mpahla.

source: Eminye iminqwazi emikhulu ngokugqithiseleyo ibiquka iivatala ezinezacholo, umnqwazi wegqwiirha nkqu nepayina - kodwa ayenzelwanga ukufudumeza intloko yakho.
reference: Other over-sized accessories included bejeweled watermelons, a wizard hat and even a pineapple - but they are not designed to keep your head warm.
translation: Eminye iminqwazi emikhulu ngokugqithiseleyo ibiquka iivatala ezinezacholo, umnqwazi wegqwiirha nkqu nepayina - kodwa ayenzelwanga ukufudumeza intloko yakho.

source: Kanti uThom Browne weza nothotho leemaski ezothusayo kanye ngexesha looNohepeni.
reference: Thom Browne also revealed a selection of bizarre masks- and just in time for Halloween.
translation: Kanti uThom Browne weza nothotho leemaski ezothusayo kanye ngexesha looNohepeni.

source: Uninzi lwezi maski zimibalabala zinemilebe ethungelweyo yaye zifana nqwa noHannibal Lecter kuneefashoni ezingayiwayo.
reference: Many of the colourful masks had sewn up lips and resembled more like Hannibal Lecter than haute couture.
translation: Uninzi lwezi maski zimibalabala zinemilebe ethungelweyo yaye zifana nqwa noHannibal Lecter kuneefashoni ezingayiwayo.

source: Omnye umnqwazi ubungathi ngowokungena emanzini enento yokuphefumla neentanyongo ngoxa omnye ubufana nekhowuni ye-ayisi khrimu enyibilikileyo.
reference: One creation resembled scuba diving gear complete with snorkel and goggles, while another looked like a melted ice cream cone.
translation: Omnye umnqwazi ubungathi ngowokungena emanzini enento yokuphefumla neentanyongo ngoxa omnye ubufana nekhowuni ye-ayisi khrimu enyibilikileyo.

source: Yaye ukuba uthanda ezingayiwayo zefashoni unethamsanqa.
reference: And if you continue the huge fashion statement- you are in luck.
translation: Yaye ukuba uthanda ezingayiwayo zefashoni unethamsanqa.

source: Abantu abajongene nezefatshoni bathi ezi ntshokontshoko zeminqwazi zisenokuba ziyeza nakwindawo ohlala kuyo.
