translation: Abantu abajongene nezefatshoni bathi ezi ntshokontshoko zeminqwazi zisenokuba ziyeza nakwindawo ohlala kuyo.

source: Le minqwazi ibalaseleyo isemanyathelweni e'La Bomba', umnqwazi welanga onongqameko oluziinyawo ezimbini ububanzi onxitywa ngabantu abafana nooRihanna nooEmily Ratajkowski.
reference: The out-sized hats come hot on the heels of 'La Bomba', the straw hat with a two-foot wide brim that's been seen on everyone from Rihanna to Emily Ratajkowski.
translation: Le minqwazi ibalaseleyo isemanyathelweni e'La Bomba', umnqwazi welanga onongqameko oluziinyawo ezimbini ububanzi onxitywa ngabantu abafana nooRihanna nooEmily Ratajkowski.

source: Ileyibheli ebisenza le minqwazi ingaqhelekanga ebizalise amakhasi onxibelelwano iye yeza nenye into enkulu ebiboniswa - ibhegi yengca ephathwa kunxweme lolwandle ephantse ibe nkulu njengombonisi mpahla onxibe iimpahla zokuqubha oyiphetheyo.
reference: The cult label behind the highly impractical hat that was splashed across social media sent another big creation down the catwalk - a straw beach bag almost as big as the swimsuit-clad model toting it.
translation: Ileyibheli ebisenza le minqwazi ingaqhelekanga ebizalise amakhasi onxibelelwano iye yeza nenye into enkulu ebiboniswa - ibhegi yengca ephathwa kunxweme lolwandle ephantse ibe nkulu njengombonisi mpahla onxibe iimpahla zokuqubha oyiphetheyo.

source: Iraffia bhegi ebu-orenji, enemiphetho yeraffia phezulu enomqheba omhlophe wofele, ibihamba phambili kwingqokelela kaJacquemus' La Riviera SS19 kwiVeki yeFashoni yaseParis.
reference: The burnt orange raffia bag, trimmed with raffia fringing and topped with a white leather handle, was the stand out piece in Jacquemus' La Riviera SS19 collection at Paris Fashion Week.
translation: Inkanga ebomvu-orenji, enemiqu yeenkanga ephezulu enomqheba omhlophe, ibihamba phambili kwingqokelela kaJacquemus' La Riviera SS19 kwiVeki yeFashoni yaseParis.

source: Umakhwekhwetha wodumo womyili uLuke Armitage uyixelele oku iFEMAIL: 'Ndilindele ukubona iminqwazi emikhulu neebhegi zonxweme lolwandle zifika ebantwini kwihlobo elilandelayo - njengoko abayili beye bazijul‚Äô ijacu kuza kuba nzima ukungabahoyi abantu abazakuba bezifun‚Äô apha ezi zinto zinkulu ngokubaxekileyo.'
reference: Celebrity stylist Luke Armitage told FEMAIL: 'I'm expecting to see large hats and beach bags arrive on the high street for next summer - as the designer has made such a huge impact it would be hard to ignore the demand for the oversized accessories.'
translation: Umculi wodumo uLuke Armitage uyixelele oku iFEMAIL: 'Ndilindele ukubona iingcombolo ezinkulu neenkanga zonxweme lolwandle zifika ebantwini kwihlobo elilandelayo - njengoko abaculi beye bazijul' ijacu kuza kuba nzima ukungabahoyi abantu abazakuba bezifun' apha ezi zinto zinkulu ngokubaxekileyo.'

source: UJohn Edward: Izakhono zolwimi ezibalulekileyo kubantu behlabathi
reference: John Edward: Languages skills essential for global citizens
translation: UJohn Edward: Izakhono zolwimi ezibalulekileyo kubantu behlabathi

source: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zinodumo lokuphuma phambili ezifundweni, yaye oku kuye kwaqhubeka ngo-2018 nezinye iziphumo zeemviwo ezingekaphumi, nto leyo eyomelezwa ngumntu ngamnye nempumelelo yeqela kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo namanye amaphulo oluntu.
reference: Scotland's independent schools maintain a track record of academic excellence, and this has continued in 2018 with another set of outstanding exam results, which is only strengthened by individual and collective success in sports, art, music and other community endeavours.
translation: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlandi ziphawuleka ngokuphumela phambili ezifundweni, yaye oku kuye kwaqhubeka ngo-2018 nezinye iziphumo zeemviwo ezingekaphumi, nto leyo eyomelezwa ngumntu ngamnye nempumelelo yeqela kwezemidlalo, ubugcisa, umculo namanye amaphulo oluntu.

source: Njengoko zinabafundi abangaphezu kwe30,000 kulo lonke elaseSkotlani, ezi zikolo, zimelwa yiScottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), zizama ukunikezela ngomgangatho ophezulu wenkonzo kubafundi bazo nabazali.
reference: With upwards of 30,000 pupils across Scotland, these schools, represented by The Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), strive to deliver the best level of service to their pupils and parents.
translation: Njengoko zinabafundi abangaphezu kwe30,000 kulo lonke laseSkotlandi, ezi zikolo, zimelwa yiScottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), zizama ukunikezela ngomgangatho ophezulu wenkonzo kubafundi bazo nabazali.

source: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zizama ukulungiselela abafundi bazo xa besiya kumabanga angaphezulu emfundo, izifundo abazikhetahyo nendawo yabo njengabantu abaphila ehlabathini.
reference: Independent schools aim to prepare their pupils for further and higher education, their chosen career and their place as global citizens.
translation: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zizama ukulungiselela abafundi bazo xa besiya kumabanga angaphezulu emfundo, izifundo abazikhetahyo nendawo yabo njengabantu abaphila ehlabathini.

source: Njengecandelo lezemfundo elinokuyila lize lifake ikharityhulam yesikolo efanele iimeko, sibona iilwimi ezikhoyo ziqhubeka njengesifundo esithandwayo nesiyimfuneko esikhethisayo ezikolweni.
reference: As an education sector that can design and implement a bespoke school curriculum, we are seeing modern languages continue as a popular and desired subject of choice within schools.
translation: Njengecandelo lezemfundo elinokuyila lize lifake ikharityhulam yesikolo efanele iimeko, sibona iilwimi ezikhoyo ziqhubeka njengesifundo esithandwayo nesiyimfuneko esikhethisayo ezikolweni.

source: UNelson Mandela wakhe wathi: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi aluqondayo, ufikelela ingqondo yakhe.
reference: Nelson Mandela said: "If you talk to a man in a language he understands, that goes to his head.
translation: UNelson Mandela wakhe wathi: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi aluqondayo, ufikelela ingqondo yakhe.

source: Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe ufikelela intlizyo yakhe."
reference: If you talk to him in his own language that goes to his heart."
translation: Ukuba uthetha naye ngolwimi lwakhe ufikelela intlizyo yakhe."

reference: This is a powerful reminder that we can't just rely on English when wanting to build relationships and trust with people from other countries.
translation: Oku kusisikhumbuzo esinamandla sokuba asinakuthembela kwisiNgesi ukuze sakhe ubudlelwane nokuthembana nabantu abavela kwamanye amazwe.

source: Ngokusuka kwiziphumo zakutshanje zoviwo, sinokubona ukuba iilwimi ziphezulu kwitheyibhuli ngemlinganiselo ephezulu yokupasa kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.
reference: From this year's recent exam results, we can see that languages are topping the league tables with the highest pass rates within independent schools.
translation: Ngokusuka kwiziphumo zakutshanje zoviwo, sinokubona ukuba iilwimi ziphezulu kwitheyibhuli ngemlinganiselo ephezulu yokupasa kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.

source: Isimbuku se-68 pesenti yabafundi abafunde iilwimi zasemzini baye bafumana amanqaku eHigher grade A.
reference: A total of 68 per cent of pupils who studied foreign languages achieved a Higher grade A.
translation: Isimbuku se-68 pesenti yabafundi abafunde iilwimi zasemzini baye bafumana amanqaku eHigher grade A.

source: Inkcazelo eqokelelwe, kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezingamalungu e-SCIS, ibonisa ukuba ama-72 pesenti abafundi aye afumana iHigher grade A kwisiMandarin, ngoxa ama-72 pesenti abo bafunda isiJamani, ama-69 pesenti abo bafunda isiFrentshi kunye nabo bafunda isiSpanish abangama-63 pesenti baye bafumana u-A.
reference: The data, collected from SCIS's 74 member schools, showed that 72 per cent of students achieved a Higher grade A in Mandarin, while 72 per cent of those studying German, 69 per cent of those studying French and 63 per cent studying Spanish also achieved an A.
translation: Inkcazelo eqokelelwe, kwizikolo ezingama-74 ezingamalungu e-SCIS, ibonisa ukuba ama-72 pesenti abafundi aye afumana iHigher grade A kwisiMandarin, ngoxa ama-72 pesenti abo bafunda isiJamani, ama-69 pesenti abo bafunda isiFrentshi kunye nabo bafunda isiSpanish abangama-63 pesenti baye bafumana u-A.

source: Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eSkotlani zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo abantwana nabantu abaselula abazifunayo ngokuqinisekileo kwixa elizayo.
reference: This demonstrates that independent schools in Scotland are supporting foreign languages as vital skills that children and young people will undoubtedly require in the future.
translation: Oku kubonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eSkotlandi zixhasa iilwimi zasemzini njengezakhono ezibalulekileyo abantwana nabantu abaselula abazifunayo ngokuqinisekileo kwixa elizayo.

source: Ngoku iilwimi, njengesifundo esikhethwayo, zixatyiswe ngendlela efanayo njengezifundo zeSTEM (science, technology, engineering and mathematics) kwikharityhulam yezikolo ezizimeleyo nezinye.
reference: Languages now, as a subject choice, are being held in the same regard as STEM subjects (science, technology, engineering and mathematics) in independent school curriculums and elsewhere.
translation: Ngoku iilwimi, njengesifundo esikhethwayo, zixatyiswe ngendlela efanayo njengezifundo zeSTEM (science, technology, engineering and mathematics) kwikharityhulam yezikolo ezizimeleyo nezinye.

source: Uphando olwenziwey yiUK Commission for Employment and Skills ngo-2014 lufumanise ukuba kwizizathu ezanikwa ngabaqeshi zokuba nengxaki yokuzalisa izithuba emsebenzini, i-17 pesenti inxulunyaniswa nokungabikho kobuchule beelwimi.
reference: A survey by the UK Commission for Employment and Skills in 2014 found that of reasons employers gave for struggling to fill vacancies, 17 per cent were attributed to a languages skills shortage.
translation: Uphando olwenziwe yiUK Commission for Employment and Skills ngo-2014 lufumanise ukuba kwizizathu ezanikwa ngabaqeshi zokuba nengxaki yokuzalisa izithuba emsebenzini, i-17 pesenti inxulunyaniswa nokungabikho kobuchule beelwimi.

source: Ngenxa yoko ngakumbi nangakumbi, isakhono seelwimi siya sisiba yimfuneko ekulungiseleleni abantu abaselula imisebenzi abaza kuyenza kwixesha elizayo.
reference: Therefore more and more, language skills are becoming imperative in order to prepare young people for their future careers.
translation: Ngenxa yoko ngakumbi nangakumbi, isakhono seelwimi siya sisiba yimfuneko ekulungiseleleni abantu abaselula imisebenzi abaza kuyenza kwixesha elizayo.

source: Njengoko izithuba zomsebenzi ezingakumbi zifuna iilwimi, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi elisebenzisanayo.
reference: With more prospective job opportunities requiring languages, these skills are essential in a globalised world.
translation: Njengoko izithuba zomsebenzi ezingakumbi zifuna iilwimi, ezi zakhono zibalulekile kwihlabathi elisebenzisanayo.

source: Enoba umntu ukhetha wuphi umsebenzi, ukuba ufunde olunye ulwimi, uya kuba nethuba elingakumbi kwixesha elizayo lokuba nesakhono esingapheliyo esifana nesi.
reference: Regardless of the career someone chooses, if they've learned a second language, they'll have a real advantage in the future having a life-long skill such as this.
translation: Enoba umntu ukhetha wuphi umsebenzi, ukuba ufunde olunye ulwimi, uya kuba nethuba elingakumbi kwixesha elizayo lokuba nesakhono esingapheliyo esifana nesi.

source: Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu bamanye amazwe kuye kumenza abe namathuba amaninzi umntu owazi iilwimi ezininzi.
reference: Being able to communicate directly with people from foreign countries will automatically put a multilingual person ahead of the competition.
translation: Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu bamanye amazwe kuye kumenza abe namathuba amaninzi umntu owazi iilwimi ezininzi.

source: Ngokutsho kolingo lweYouGov olwenziwe kubantu abakhulileyo abangahezu kwama-4,000 base-UK ngowe-2013, ama-75 ekhulwini ebengakwazi ukuthetha olunye ulwimi kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukuba bancokole yaye sisiFrentshi kuphela esithethwa yipesenti engaphezu kweshuimi, 15 pesenti.
reference: According to a YouGov poll of more than 4,000 UK adults in 2013, 75 per cent were unable to speak a foreign language well enough to hold a conversation and with French being the only language spoken by a double-digit percentage, 15 per cent.
translation: Ngokutsho kolingo lweYouGov olwenziwe kubantu abakhulileyo abangahezu kwama-4,000 base-UK ngowe-2013, ama-75 ekhulwini ebengakwazi ukuthetha olunye ulwimi kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukuba bancokole yaye sisiFrentshi kuphela esithethwa yipesenti engaphezu kweshuimi, 15 pesenti.

source: Yiyo loo nto ukutyala imali ekuundiseni ulwimi ngoku kubalulekile kubantwana bangoku.
reference: This is why putting the investment into language teaching now is important for today's children.
translation: Yiyo loo nto ukutyala imali ekuundiseni ulwimi ngoku kubalulekile kubantwana bangoku.

source: Ukwazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zamazwe asakhasayo, kuya kuxhobisa abantwana ngamathuba amahle okufumana umsebenzi oncumisayo.
reference: Having multiple languages, particularly those of developing economies, will equip children with a better chance of finding meaningful employment.
translation: Ukwazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zamazwe asakhasayo, kuya kuxhobisa abantwana ngamathuba amahle okufumana umsebenzi oncumisayo.

source: ESkotlani, isikolo ngasinye siya kwahluka ngeelwimi esizifundisayo.
reference: Within Scotland, each school will differ in the languages they teach.
translation: ESkotlandi, isikolo ngasinye siya kwahluka ngeelwimi esizifundisayo.

source: Izikolo eziliqela ziya kunikela ingqalelo kwiilwimi zangoku ekudala zikho, ngoxa ezinye ziya kufundisa iilwimi ekucingwa ukuba zibaluleke kakhulu e-UK xa kujongwa ku-2020, njengesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.
reference: A number of schools will focus on the more classic modern languages, whereas others will teach languages that are deemed to be most important for the UK when looking ahead to 2020, such as Mandarin or Japanese.
translation: Izikolo eziliqela ziya kunikela ingqalelo kwiilwimi zangoku ekudala zikho, ngoxa ezinye ziya kufundisa iilwimi ekucingwa ukuba zibaluleke kakhulu e-UK xa kujongwa ku-2020, njengesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.

source: Enoba umntwana wakho uthanda ntoni, kuya kusoloko kukho iilwimi eziliqela onokukhetha kuzo kwizikolo ezizimeleyo, kukho nootitshala abaphum‚Äô izandla kweli candelo.
reference: Whatever your child's interest, there will always be a number of languages to choose from within independent schools, with teaching staff who are specialists in this area.
translation: Xa umntwana wakho uthanda ntoni, kusoloko kukho iilwimi eziliqela onokukhetha kuzo kwizikolo ezizimeleyo, kukho nootitshala abaphum' izandla kweli candelo.

source: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani zizimisele ekulungiseleleni imo yokufundisa eya kulungisa abantwana ibaxhobise ngezakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele, enoba baya phi na kwixesha elizayo.
reference: Scottish independent schools are dedicated to providing a learning environment that will prepare children and arm them with the skills required to succeed, whatever the future holds.
translation: Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseSkotlani ziyaqinisekisa ukuphucula imo yokufundisa ukuze iinceda abantwana baqeqeshe izakhono ezifunekayo ukuze baphumelele kwixesha elizayo.

source: Alinakuphikwa ngoku, kwimo yoshishino lwehlabathi, elokuba iilwimi ziyaqhubeka zibalulekile kwikamva lelizwe, ngoko oku kumele kubonakale kwimfundo.
reference: It can't be denied at this time, in a global business environment, that languages continue to be vitally important to the country's future, so this must be mirrored in education.
translation: Akukwazi ukuchitheka, kwimo yobuchule behlabathi, ukuba iilwimi ziyindlela ephukileyo yokwabelana nolwazi, oku kufuneka kubonakale kwimfundo.

source: Eneneni, iilwimi zangoku zimele zigqalwe ‚Äúnjengesakhono sokunxibelelana nehlabathi."
reference: Indeed, modern languages should really be considered "international communication skills."
translation: Ngokwenyaniso, iilwimi zamva zibekwe "njengendlela yokunikezela ngolwazi emhlabeni."

source: Izikolo ezizimeleyo ziya kuqhubeka zinikezela ngolu khetho, ukwahlukana nokuphum‚Äô izandla kubantu abaselula eSkotlani.
reference: Independent schools will continue to offer this choice, diversity and excellence for Scotland's young people.
translation: Izikolo ezizimeleyo ziya kuqhubeka zinikeza olu khetho, ukwahlukana nokuphumelela kwabaselula eSkotlani.

source: Il faut bien le faire.
reference: Il faut bien le faire.
translation: Kufuneka wenze ngobuchule.

source: UJohn Edward unguMphathi kwiBhunga laseSkotlani leZikolo Ezizimeleyo
reference: John Edward is Director of the Scottish Council of Independent Schools
translation: UJohn Edward unguMphathi kwiBhunga laseSkotlani leZikolo Ezizimeleyo

source: ULeBron uzakophula irekhodi leLakers ngeCawa eSan Diego
reference: LeBron to make Lakers debut Sunday in San Diego
translation: ULeBron uza kophula irekhodi leLakers ngeCawa eSan Diego

source: Ukulinda sele kuza kuphela kubalandeli abafuna ukubona uLeBron James eqala ngqa kwiLos Angeles Lakers.
reference: The wait is nearly over for fans looking to see LeBron James make his first start for the Los Angeles Lakers.
translation: Ukulinda kuzisale ixesha lokubona uLeBron James eqalisa kwiiLos Angeles Lakers.

source: Umqeqeshi weLakers oLuke Walton uvakalise ukuba uJames uza kudlala kwingabula-zigcawu yesizini yangeCawa nxamnye neDenver Nuggets eSan Diego.
reference: Lakers coach Luke Walton has announced that James will play in Sunday's preseason opener against the Denver Nuggets in San Diego.
translation: Umqeqeshi weLakers uLuke Walton uvakalise ukuba uJames uza kudlala kwingabula-zigcawu yesizini yangeCawa nxamnye neDenver Nuggets eSan Diego.

source: Kodwa iseza kubonakala eyoba uza kudlala imizuzu emingaphi.
reference: But just how many minutes he'll play has yet to be determined.
translation: Kodwa siza kubonakala ukuba uza kudlala imizuzu emingaphi.

source: Uya kuba ngaphezu komnye nangaphantsi kweyi-48, utshilo uWalton kwiwebhsayithi esemthethweni yeLakers.
reference: It will be more than one and less than 48, said Walton on the Lakers" official website.
translation: Uza kuba ephezulu okanye ngaphansi kwama-48, utshilo uWalton kwiwebhsayithi esemthethweni yeLakers.

source: Unondaba weLakers uMike Trudell uthe kuthwitha kusenokwenzeka ukuba uJames adlale imizuzu elinganiselweyo.
reference: Lakers reporter Mike Trudell tweeted that James will likely play limited minutes.
translation: Unondaba weLakers uMike Trudell uthe kunokwenzeka ukuba uJames adlale imizuzu elinganiselweyo.

source: Emva kokuzilolonga ebutsheni bale veki, uJames ubuzwe ngezicwangciso zakhe zeshedyuli yengabulazigcawu yesizini yeLakers.
reference: Following practice earlier this week, James was asked about his plans for the Lakers" six-game preseason schedule.
translation: Emva kokuzilolonga ebutsheni bale veki, uJames ubuzwe ngezicwangciso zakhe zeshedyuli yengabulazigcawu yesizini yeLakers.

source: Andiyifuni imidlalo yangaphambi kwesizini kweli nqanaba lomsebenzi wam ukuze ndilunge, utshilo.
reference: I don't need preseason games at this stage of my career to get ready, he said.
translation: Andifuni imidlalo yangaphambi kwesizini kweli nqanaba lomsebenzi wam ukuze ndilunge, utshilo.

source: I-Trump's West Virginia Rally Time, kwiYouTube Channel
reference: Trump's West Virginia Rally Time, YouTube Channel
translation: I-Trump's West Virginia Rally Time, kwiYouTube Channel

source: UMongameli Donald Trump uqalisa iimbutho zakhe ezidala ingxwabangxwaba ngokuhlwanje eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
reference: President Donald Trump begins a flurry of campaign rallies tonight in Wheeling, West Virginia.
translation: UMongameli Donald Trump uqalisa iimbutho zakhe ezidala ingxwabangxwaba ngokuhlwanje eWheeling, eWest Virginia.

source: Yindibano yalo kaTrump yokuqala kwezintlanu ezicwangcisiweyo kule veki izayo kuquka ukutyelela kwiindawo anobuhlobo nazo eziquka iTennessee neMississippi.
reference: It's Trump's first of five scheduled rallies in the next week, including stops in friendly places including Tennessee and Mississippi.
translation: Yindibano yalo kaTrump yokuqala kwezintlanu ezicwangcisiweyo kule veki izayo kuquka ukutyelela kwiindawo anobuhlobo nazo eziquka iTennessee neMississippi.

source: Njengoko ivoti yesiqinisekiso isamisiwe de akhethe aza kumfaka kwisithuba seNkundla Ephakamileyo, lo kaTrump uzama ukugaya inkxaso yonyulo lwesibini ekubeni iiRepublicans zisengozini yokuphulukana nolawulo lweCongress xa kuvotwa ngoNov.
reference: With the confirmation vote on hold for his pick to fill the Supreme Court vacancy, Trump is aiming to build support for upcoming mid-term elections since Republicans are at risk of losing control of Congress when votes are cast on Nov.
translation: Njengoko ivoti yesiqinisekiso isamisiwe de akhethe aza kumfaka kwisithuba seNkundla Ephakamileyo, lo kaTrump uzama ukugaya inkxaso yonyulo lwesibini ekubeni iiRepublicans zisengozini yokuphulukana nolawulo lweCongress xa kuvotwa ngoNov.

source: Iza kuba nini indibano kaTrump eNtshona Virginia ngokuhlwanje yaye ungayibukela njani kwi-intanethi?
reference: What time is Trump's West Virginia rally tonight and how do you watch online?
translation: Iza kuba nini indibano kaTrump eNtshona Virginia ngokuhlwanje yaye ungayibukela njani kwi-intanethi?

source: Indibano kaTrump yaseWheeling, eNtshona Virginia ibekelwe u-7 p.m. ET ngokuhlwanje, ngoMgqibelo, Septemba 29, 2018.
reference: Trump's Wheeling, West Virginia rally is scheduled for 7 p.m. ET tonight, Saturday, September 29, 2018.
translation: Indibano kaTrump yaseWheeling, eNtshona Virginia ibekelwe u-7 p.m. ET ngokuhlwanje, ngoMgqibelo, Septemba 29, 2018.

source: Ungabukela indibano kaTrump yaseWest Virginia kwi-intanethi ngelive strimu kuYouTube.
reference: You can watch Trump's West Virginia rally online below via live stream on YouTube.
translation: Ungabukela indibano kaTrump yaseWest Virginia kwi-intanethi ngelive strimu kuYouTube.

source: UTrump kujongwe ukuba athethe kwintlanganiso yale veki yomgqatswa weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh, okwimeko enzima ngenxa yezityholo zokungaziphathi kakuhle ngokwesondonekuqqqikelelwa ukuba kuya kumiswa ivoti yokuqinisekisa kangangeveki ngoxa iFBI iphanda.
reference: Trump is likely to address this week's hearings for Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh, which became tense over sexual misconduct allegations with an anticipated Senate confirmation vote on hold for up to a week while the FBI investigates.
translation: UTrump kujongwe ukuba athethe kwintlanganiso yale veki yomgqatswa weNkundla Ephakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh, okwimeko enzima ngenxa yezityholo zokungaziphathi kakuhle ngokwesondonekuqqqikelelwa ukuba kuya kumiswa ivoti yokuqinisekisa kangangeveki ngoxa iFBI iphanda.

source: Kodwa olona sukelo luphambili lolu thotho lweentlanganiso kukunceda iiRepublicans ukuba zikwazi ukumelana nonyulo lukaNovemba.
reference: But the primary aim of this flurry of rallies is helping Republicans facing touch November elections gain some momentum.
translation: Kodwa olona sukelo luphambili lolu thotho lweentlanganiso kukunceda iiRepublicans ukuba zikwazi ukumelana nonyulo lukaNovemba.

source: Ngenxa yoko, iphulo likaMongameli Trump lithe ezi ntlanganiso zintlanu kule veki izayo zijoliswe ‚Äúekomelezweni kwamatsha-ntliziyo nabaxhasi njengoko iiRepublicans zizama ukukhusela nokwandisa amanani ezinawo kwindlu yoWiso-mthetho nakwiNdlu yaBameli,‚Äù iReuters itshilo.
reference: Thus, President Trump's campaign said these five rallies in the next week are aimed at "energizing volunteers and supporters as Republicans try to protect and expand the majorities they hold in the Senate and House of Representatives," according to Reuters.
translation: Ngenxa yoko, iphulo likaMongameli Trump lithe ezi ntlanganiso zintlanu kule veki izayo zijoliswe "ekomelezweni kwamatsha-ntliziyo nabaxhasi njengoko iiRepublicans zizama ukukhusela nokwandisa amanani ezinawo kwindlu yoWiso-mthetho nakwiNdlu yaBameli," iReuters itshilo.

source: Ukulawula iCongress kuyeyona nto ibalulekileyo kuye kangangokuba umongameli uza kuya kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko njengoko sisondela kwisizini exakekileyo yokugaya ivoti,‚Äù isithethi sokugaya ivoti sikaTump esingakhange sifune kwaziwa simxelele oko iReuters.	Control of Congress is so critical for his agenda that the president will travel to as many states as possible as we head into the busy campaign season," a Trump campaign spokesman who declined to be named told Reuters.
reference: Ukulawula iCongress kuyeyona nto ibalulekileyo kuye kangangokuba umongameli uza kuya kumazwe amaninzi kangangoko njengoko sisondela kwisizini exakekileyo yokugaya ivoti, isithethi sokugaya ivoti sikaTump esingakhange sifune kwaziwa simxelele oko iReuters.

source: Ehlelwe eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, olu nganiso lwanamhlanje ebusuku lungagaya inkxaso kususela ‚Äúe-Ohio kunye nePensnsylvania kwaye yaziwe nasePittsburgh ngonondaba bakhona,‚Äù Kusitsho Iindaba Zesixeko saseWest Virginia.
reference: Scheduled for Wesbanco Arena in Wheeling, tonight's rally could bring supporters from "Ohio and Pennsylvania and draw coverage from the Pittsburgh media," according to the West Virginia Metro News.
translation: Ehlelwe eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, olu nganiso lwanamhlanje ebusuku lungagaya inkxaso kususela "e-Ohio kunye nePensnsylvania kwaye yaziwe nasePittsburgh ngonondaba bakhona," Kusitsho Iindaba Zesixeko saseWest Virginia.

source: UMgqibelo uzakuba lixesha lesibini uTrump etyelele iWest Virginia, icandelo larhulumente alinqoba ngamanqaku angamaphesenti angale kuka 40 ngo2016.
reference: Saturday will be the second time in the past month that Trump has visited West Virginia, the state he won by more than 40 percentage points in 2016.
translation: UMgqibelo uzakuba lixesha lesibini uTrump etyelele iWest Virginia, icandelo larhulumente alinqoba ngamanqaku angamaphesenti angale kuka 40 ngo2016.

source: UTrump uzama ukunceda Usenethe WamaRepublican WaseWest Virginia uPatrick Morrisey, ohamba emva kolu lonyulo.
reference: Trump is trying to help West Virginia Republican Senate candidate Patrick Morrisey, who is trailing in the polls.
translation: UTrump uzama ukunceda Usenethe WamaRepublican WaseWest Virginia uPatrick Morrisey, ohamba emva kolu lonyulo.

source: ‚ÄúAkusingumqondiso omhle kaMorrisey lo ukuba umongameli kunyanzeleke ukuba aze azomgayela inkxaso,‚Äù kusitsho uSimon Header, usosayensi wezopolotiki eYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, ngokutsho kweeReuters.
reference: It's not a good sign for Morrisey that the president has to come to try to give him a boost in the polls, said Simon Haeder, a political scientist at West Virginia University, according to Reuters.
translation: Akusingumqondiso omhle kaMorrisey lo ukuba umongameli kunyanzeleke ukuba aze azomgayela inkxaso, kusitsho uSimon Header, usosayensi wezopolotiki eYunivesithi yaseWest Virginia, ngokutsho kweeReuters.

source: IRyder Cup 2018: Iqela laseMelika libonisa ukuba xa ulambele impumelelo uzaqhubeka ulwa njengona ijonge ukuya emidlalweni yabantu ngabanye ngeSonto.
reference: Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA show stomach for fight to keep hopes alive heading into Sunday singles
translation: IRyder Cup 2018: Iqela laseMelika libonisa ukuba xa ulambele impumelelo uzaqhubeka ulwa njengona ijonge ukuya emidlalweni yabantu ngabanye ngeSonto.

source: Emva kwemidlalo emithathu umntu edlala yedwa, ukudlala njengeqala labantu abane yeyona nto ibidingwa yile Ryder Cup.
reference: After three one-sided sessions, Saturday afternoon's foursomes might just have been what this Ryder Cup needed.
translation: Emva kwemidlalo emithathu umntu edlala yedwa, ukudlala njengeqala labantu abane yeyona nto ibidingwa yile Ryder Cup.

source: Isikhundla sokuhamba phambili kunoma yiliphi iqela kwenze ingcamango yezemidlalo abadlali abakholelwa nyani kuyo, kwaye kukhuphiswano olufana nalolu.
reference: The swinging pendulum of momentum is a completely invented sporting concept but one that players truly believe in, and never more so than at competitions like these.
translation: Isikhundla sokuhamba phambili kunoma yiliphi iqela kwenze ingcamango yezemidlalo abadlali abakholelwa nyani kuyo, kwaye kukhuphiswano olufana nalolu.

source: Ngalo ndlela singathi ngubani ohamba phambili okwangoku?
reference: So where would they say the momentum is now?
translation: Ngalo ndlela singathi ngubani ohamba phambili okwangoku?

source: ‚ÄúBakhokhele ngamanqaku amathandathu kwaye ngoku asemane, ngalo ndlela ndicinga ba sihamba phambili,‚Äù kusitsho uJordan Spieth ngelixa ehamba okwangaleyo mini.
reference: They had a six-point lead and now it's four, so we are carrying that as a little bit of momentum I guess, said Jordan Spieth as he strolled off for the day.
translation: Bakhokhele ngamanqaku amathandathu kwaye ngoku asemane, ngalo ndlela ndicinga ba sihamba phambili, kusitsho uJordan Spieth ngelixa ehamba okwangaleyo mini.

reference: Europe have the advantage, of course, four points ahead with twelve more in play.
translation: IYurophu ithabathe eli thuba, ngokwenyani, inamanqaku amane ngaphezulu kwaye namanye angu12 angakaqinisekiswa.

source: AmaMelikana, njengoko uSpieth esitsho, ukuba uva ngathi ihamba kakuhle kwaye kuninzi abangafumana umdla kukho, kuquka indlela uSpieth kunye noJustin abadlale kakuhle ngayo imini yonke kwaye esi sibini sinamanqaku amathathu kwamane.
reference: The Americans, as Spieth says, feel they have a little wind in their sails though and they have plenty to be encouraged by, not least the form of Spieth and Justin Thomas who played together all day and each boast three points from four.
translation: AmaMelikana, njengoko uSpieth esitsho, ukuba uva ngathi ihamba kakuhle kwaye kuninzi abangafumana umdla kukho, kuquka indlela uSpieth kunye noJustin abadlale kakuhle ngayo imini yonke kwaye esi sibini sinamanqaku amathathu kwamane.

source: USpieth ubesoloko edlala kakuhle kususela xa kuqaliswa kwaye ukhokhela ngomzekelo.
reference: Spieth has been lethal from tee to green and is leading by example.
translation: USpieth ubesoloko edlala kakuhle kususela xa kuqaliswa kwaye ukhokhela ngomzekelo.

reference: Only twice in Ryder Cup history has a team come back from a four-point deficit going into the singles, although as holders Furyk's side need only draw to retain the trophy.

source: INorth Korea ithi ‚Äòsoze‚Äô yagqiba izixhobo zayo phambi kokuba ifumane ukhuseleko.
reference: North Korea says 'no way' will disarm unilaterally without trust
translation: INorth Korea ithi 'soze' yagqiba izixhobo zayo phambi kokuba ifumane ukhuseleko.

source: Umphathiswa weziko lezangaphandle eNorth Korea uxelele i-United Nations ngoMgqibelo ukuba ezi zigwebo zenza kungathenjwana phakathi kweMelika yaye kwakungekho ndlela yokuba iMelika ingagqiba izixhobo zayo zeNuclear xa ingafumana iziqinisekiso zokhuselo.
reference: North Korea's foreign minister told the United Nations on Saturday continued sanctions were deepening its mistrust in the United States and there was no way the country would give up its nuclear weapons unilaterally under such circumstances.
translation: Umphathiswa weziko lezangaphandle eNorth Korea uxelele i-United Nations ngoMgqibelo ukuba ezi zigwebo zenza kungathenjwana phakathi kweMelika yaye kwakungekho ndlela yokuba iMelika ingagqiba izixhobo zayo zeNuclear xa ingafumana iziqinisekiso zokhuselo.

source: URi Yong Ho uxelele ibhodi yababekhona ukuba ithabathe amanyathelo amahle ngonyaka odlulileyo, njengokuyekisa uvavanyo lwezixhobo kwaye nokudilizwa kweendawo ezinezixhobo zeNuclear, kwaye nokwenza isithembiso sokuba singaphinde senze izixhobo zeNuclear.
reference: Ri Yong Ho told the world body's annual General Assembly that North Korea had taken "significant goodwill measures" in the past year, such as stopping nuclear and missiles tests, dismantling the nuclear test site, and pledging not to proliferate nuclear weapons and nuclear technology.
translation: URi Yong Ho uxelele ibhodi yababekhona ukuba ithabathe amanyathelo amahle ngonyaka odlulileyo, njengokuyekisa uvavanyo lwezixhobo kwaye nokudilizwa kweendawo ezinezixhobo zeNuclear, kwaye nokwenza isithembiso sokuba singaphinde senze izixhobo zeNuclear.

source: ‚ÄúNangona kunjalo, asiwaboni amanyathelo ahambelanayo avela eMelika,‚Äù utshilo.
reference: However, we do not see any corresponding response from the U.S., he said.
translation: Nangona kunjalo, asiwaboni amanyathelo ahambelanayo avela eMelika, utshilo.

source: ‚ÄúXa kungekho sithembiso esivela eMelika soze kubekho nethemba kukhuseleko lwelizwe lethu kwaye kule meko soze sadiziliza izixhobo zethu singathethanga neMelika.‚Äù
reference: Without any trust in the U.S. there will be no confidence in our national security and under such circumstances there is no way we will unilaterally disarm ourselves first.
translation: Xa kungekho sithembiso esivela eMelika soze kubekho nethemba kukhuseleko lwelizwe lethu kwaye kule meko soze sadiziliza izixhobo zethu singathethanga neMelika.

source: Ngelixa uRi esitsho kwakhona into eqhelekileyo ebisitshiwo yiNorth Korea malunga nokungavumi kweMelika ukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear ngokwezigaba ngaphantsi koko iNorth Korea inikwe umvuzo malunga namanyathelo amancinane ewathathileyo, le ngxelo yakhe zange iyikhanyele laa nto yenziwa uPyongyang yokugqiba izixhobo okungahambanga kakuhle.
reference: While Ri reprised familiar North Korean complaints about Washington's resistance to a "phased" approach to denuclearization under which North Korea would be rewarded as it took gradual steps, his statement appeared significant in that it did not reject unilateral denuclearization out of hand as Pyongyang has done in the past.
translation: Ngelixa uRi esitsho kwakhona into eqhelekileyo ebisitshiwo yiNorth Korea malunga nokungavumi kweMelika ukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear ngokwezigaba ngaphantsi koko iNorth Korea inikwe umvuzo malunga namanyathelo amancinane ewathathileyo, le ngxelo yakhe zange iyikhanyele laa nto yenziwa uPyongyang yokugqiba izixhobo okungahambanga kakuhle.

source: URi uthethe ngengxelo edibeneyo ekhutshwe nguKim Jong Un kunye noDonald Trump kwingqungquthela yokuqala phakathi komongameli waseMelika kunye nomlawuli waseNorth Korea eyayiseSingapore ngoJuni 12, xa uKim ethembisa ukusebenzela ‚Äúukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear endaweni  yaseKorea‚Äù ngexesha uTrump ethembisa ukhuseleko lweKorea.
reference: Ri referred to a joint statement issued by Kim Jong Un and Donald Trump at a first ever summit between a serving U.S. president and a North Korean leader in Singapore on June 12, when Kim pledged to work toward "denuclearization of the Korean peninsula" while Trump promised guarantees of North Korea's security.
translation: Yiyo le ntetho edibeneyo ekhutshwe nguKim Jong Un kunye noDonald Trump kwingqungquthela yokuqala phakathi komongameli waseMelika kunye nomlawuli waseNorth Korea eyayiseSingapore ngoJuni 12, xa uKim ethembisa ukusebenzela "ukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear endaweni yaseKorea" ngexesha uTrump ethembisa ukhuseleko lweKorea.

source: UMntla Korea ubufuna ukuphelisa imfazwe yaseKorea yango-1950-53 ngokusesikweni, kodwa iMelika ithe uPyonyang kufanele aphelise izixhobo zeNuclear kuqala.
reference: North Korea has been seeking a formal end to the 1950-53 Korea War, but the United States has said Pyongyang must give up its nuclear weapons first.
translation: UMntla Korea ubufuna ukuphelisa imfazwe yaseKorea yango-1950-53 ngokusesikweni, kodwa iMelika ithe uPyonyang kufanele aphelise izixhobo zeNuclear kuqala.

source: IWahington izenqabile izicelo zokunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezijongene neNorth Korea.
reference: Washington has also resisted calls to relax tough international sanctions on North Korea.
translation: IWahington izenqabile izicelo zokunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezijongene neNorth Korea.

source: ‚ÄúIMelika inyanzelisa ‚Äúukugqitywa kwezixhobo zeNuclear kuqala‚Äù kwaye yandisa inqanaba loxinzelelo ngezigwebo ukufezekisa injongo yabo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, ichasa nezibhengezo zokuphela kwemfazwe,‚Äù‚Äù uRi esitsho.
reference: The U.S. insists on the denuclearization-first" and increases the level of pressure by sanctions to achieve their purpose in a coercive manner, and even objecting to the "declaration of the end of war,"" Ri said.
translation: IMelika inyanzelisa ukugqitywa kwezixhobo zeNuclear kuqala" kwaye yandisa inqanaba loxinzelelo ngezigwebo ukufezekisa injongo yabo ngendlela enyanzelisayo, ichasa nezibhengezo zokuphela kwemfazwe," uRi esitsho.

source: ‚ÄúIngcamango yokuthi izigwebo zingasoyikisa liphupha lobuxoki labantu abangazi nto ngathi.
reference: The perception that sanctions can bring us on our knees is a pipe dream of the people who are ignorant about us.	Ingcamango yokuthi izigwebo zingasoyikisa liphupha lobuxoki labantu abangazi nto ngathi.

source: Kodwa ingxaki kukuba ezi zigwebo ziyakwandisa ukungathembani.‚Äù
reference: But the problem is that the continued sanctions are deepening our mistrust."
translation: Kodwa ingxaki kukuba ezi zigwebo ziyakwandisa ukungathembani."

source: URi khange athethe ngezicwangciso zenye ingqungquthela kaKim kunye noTrump, ezo umholi waseMelika athethe ngazo phambi kwe-United Nations kule veki.
reference: Ri made no mention of plans for a second summit between Kim and Trump that the U.S. leader highlighted at the United Nations earlier in the week.
translation: URi khange athethe ngezicwangciso zenye ingqungquthela kaKim kunye noTrump, ezo umholi waseMelika athethe ngazo phambi kwe-United Nations kule veki.

source: Endaweni yoko lo mphathiswa uthethe ngeentlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim kunye nomlawuli wasemazantsi neKorea uMoon Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo kwaye wongeza ngelithi: ‚ÄúUkuba iqela kule meko yokugqitha izixhobo zeNuclear ngumzantsi Korea hayi iMelika, ngaba ukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear endaweni yaseKorea khange kume.‚Äù
reference: The minister instead highlighted three meetings between Kim and South Korean leader Moon Jae-in in the past five months and added: "If the party to this issue of denuclearization were South Korea and not the U.S., the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula would not have come to such a deadlock."
translation: Endaweni yoko lo mphathiswa uthethe ngeentlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim kunye nomlawuli wasemazantsi neKorea uMoon Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo kwaye wongeza ngelithi: "Ukuba iqela kule meko yokugqitha izixhobo zeNuclear ngumzantsi Korea hayi iMelika, ngaba ukugqiba izixhobo zeNuclear endaweni yaseKorea khange kume."

source: Nangona kunjalo, intetho kaRi ivakala yohlukile kunonyaka odlulileyo, xa ethetha nendibano jikelele ye-U.N. Ethi ukujoliswa kwezixhobo ezibhabhayo zaseNorth Korea elizweni laseMelika kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba ‚ÄúuMn. Ongendawo Umongameli‚Äù uTrump abiza uKim ‚Äúngendoda yezixhobo ezibhabhayo‚Äù ofuna ukuzibulala.
reference: Even so, the tone of Ri's speech was dramatically different from last year, when he told the U.N. General Assembly that targeting the U.S. mainland with North Korea's rockets was inevitable after "Mr Evil President" Trump called Kim a "rocket man" on a suicide mission.
translation: Nangona kunjalo, intetho kaRi ivakala yohlukile kunonyaka odlulileyo, xa ethetha nendibano jikelele ye-U.N. Ethi ukujoliswa kwezixhobo ezibhabhayo zaseNorth Korea elizweni laseMelika kwakungenakuphepheka emva kokuba "uMn. Ongendawo Umongameli" uTrump abiza uKim "ngendoda yezixhobo ezibhabhayo" ofuna ukuzibulala.

source: Kulo nyaka e-United Nations, uTrump, owasongela ‚Äúukutshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo‚Äù iNorth Korea, unike uKim indumiso ngesibindi ngokuthatha amanyathelo okuqeda izixhobo, kodwa esitsho oko kunomsebenzi omninzi ophambili kwaye nezigwebo ziya kuhlala kude iNorth Korea igqibe izixhobo zeNuclear.
reference: This year at the United Nations, Trump, who last year threatened to "totally destroy" North Korea, heaped praise on Kim for his courage in taking steps to disarm, but said much work still had to be done and sanctions must remain in place until North Korea denuclearizes.
translation: Kulo nyaka e-United Nations, uTrump, owasongela "ukutshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo" iNorth Korea, unike uKim indumiso ngesibindi ngokuthatha amanyathelo okuqeda izixhobo, kodwa esitsho oko kunomsebenzi omninzi ophambili kwaye nezigwebo ziya kuhlala kude iNorth Korea igqibe izixhobo zeNuclear.

source: NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathetha wathi akanaxesha elibekiwe loko, esitsho ethi "ukuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye izinyanga ezintlanu - akunandaba"
reference: On Wednesday, Trump said he did not have a time frame for this, saying "If it takes two years, three years or five months - doesn't matter."
translation: NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathetha wathi akanaxesha elibekiwe loko, esitsho ethi "ukuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye izinyanga ezintlanu - akunandaba"

source: ITshayina kunye neRussia ithi Ibhunga Lokhuseleko le-U.N  Kufanele imvuze uPyongyang ngamanyathelo awathathileyo.
reference: China and Russia argue that the U.N. Security Council should reward Pyongyang for steps taken.
translation: ITshayina kunye neRussia ithi Ibhunga Lokhuseleko le-U.N Kufanele imvuze uPyongyang ngamanyathelo awathathileyo.

source: Noba kunjalo, unobhala welizwe  waseMelika uMike Pompeo uxelele Ibhunga Lokhuseleko le-U.N ngoLwesine ukuthi: ‚ÄúUkunyazeliswa kwezigwebo zeBhunga Lokhuseleko akuqhubeke ngamandla kungayeki side sibone ukugqitshwa kwezixhobo zeNuclear ngokupheleleyo nangokuqinisekileyo."
reference: However, U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo told the U.N. Security Council on Thursday that: "Enforcement of Security Council sanctions must continue vigorously and without fail until we realize the fully, final, verified denuclearization."
translation: Noba kunjalo, unobhala welizwe  waseMelika uMike Pompeo uxelele Ibhunga Lokhuseleko le-U.N ngoLwesine ukuthi: "Ukunyazeliswa kwezigwebo zeBhunga Lokhuseleko akuqhubeke ngamandla kungayeki side sibone ukugqitshwa kwezixhobo zeNuclear ngokupheleleyo nangokuqinisekileyo."

source: Ibhunga Lokhuseleko liye landisa izigwebo ngokuvumelana eNorth Korea ukususela ngo-2006  ngenjongo yokupheliswa kwemali yeenkqubo zezixhobo zeNuclear ezibhabhayo zikaPyonyang.
reference: The Security Council has unanimously boosted sanctions on North Korea since 2006 in a bid to choke off funding for Pyongyang's nuclear and ballistic missile programs.
translation: Ibhunga Lokhuseleko liye landisa izigwebo ngokuvumelana eNorth Korea ukususela ngo-2006  ngenjongo yokupheliswa kwemali yeenkqubo zezixhobo zeNuclear ezibhabhayo zikaPyonyang.

source: UPompeo udibene noRi ngaphaya kweNdibano Jikelele ye-U.N kwaye wathi uzotyelela uPyonyang kwakhona ukulungiselela ingqungquthela yesibini.
reference: Pompeo met Ri on the sidelines of the U.N. General Assembly and said afterwards that he would visit Pyongyang again next month to prepare for a second summit.
translation: UPompeo udibene noRi ngaphaya kweNdibano Jikelele ye-U.N kwaye wathi uzotyelela uPyonyang kwakhona ukulungiselela ingqungquthela yesibini.

source: UPompeo sele etyelele iNorth Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa utyelelo lakhe lokugqibela khange luhambe kakuhle.
reference: Pompeo has visited North Korea three times already this year, but his last trip did not go well.
translation: UPompeo sele etyelele iNorth Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa utyelelo lakhe lokugqibela khange luhambe kakuhle.

source: Washiya uPyonyang ngoJuly esitsho ethi kunenkqubekela phambili eyenziwe, kodwa iNorth Korea yazimela isithi wenza ‚Äúiimfuno ezifana nezo ezinziwa abaphangi.‚Äù
reference: He left Pyongyang in July saying that progress had been made, only for North Korea within hours to denounce him for making "gangster-like demands."
translation: Washiya uPyonyang ngoJuly esitsho ethi kunenkqubekela phambili eyenziwe, kodwa iNorth Korea yazimela isithi wenza "iimfuno ezifana nezo ezinziwa abaphangi."

source: INorth Korea yathembisa ukudibana noMoon kule nyanga ukuze bakwazi ukuqhekeza indawo yezixhobo zeNuclear ezibhabhayo ukuba iMelika ‚Äúamanyathelo ahambelanayo.‚Äù
reference: North Korea pledged in a meeting with Moon this month to dismantle a missile site and also a nuclear complex if the United States took "corresponding measures."
translation: INorth Korea yathembisa ukudibana noMoon kule nyanga ukuze bakwazi ukuqhekeza indawo yezixhobo zeNuclear ezibhabhayo ukuba iMelika "amanyathelo ahambelanayo."

source: Uthe uKim umxelele ukuba ‚Äúamanyathelo ahambelanayo‚Äù awafunayo iziqinisekiso zokhuseleko uTrump azithembisa eSingapore kunye nenkqubela phambili kubudlelwane obuqhelekileyo neWashington
reference: He said Kim had told him the "corresponding measures" he was seeking were security guarantees Trump pledged in Singapore and moves toward normalization of relations with Washington.
translation: Uthe uKim umxelele ukuba "amanyathelo ahambelanayo" awafunayo iziqinisekiso zokhuseleko uTrump azithembisa eSingapore kunye nenkqubela phambili kubudlelwane obuqhelekileyo neWashington

source: Abafundi baseHarvard bathatha isifundo sokuphumla ngokwaneleyo
reference: Harvard students take course in getting enough rest
translation: Abafundi baseHarvard bathatha isifundo sokuphumla ngokwaneleyo

source: Isifundo esitsha eYunivesithi yaseHarvard kulo nyaka senza bonke abafundi abangakabi izithwalandwe balale ngokwaneleyo ngenjongo yokulwisana nekcubeko yokufunda ubusuku bonke besebenzisa i-caffeine.'
reference: A new course at Harvard University this year has got all its undergraduates getting more sleep in a bid to combat the growing macho culture of studying through caffeine-fuelled 'all-nighters.'
translation: Isifundo esitsha eYunivesithi yaseHarvard kulo nyaka senza bonke abafundi abangakabi izithwalandwe balale ngokwaneleyo ngenjongo yokulwisana nekcubeko yokufunda ubusuku bonke besebenzisa i-caffeine.'

source: Enye ingcali ifumene ukuba abafundi kule yunivesithi iphezulu abazi nto ngeziseko zokuzinakekela.
reference: An academic found students at the world's number one university are often clueless when it comes to the very basics about how to look after themselves.
translation: Enye ingcali ifumene ukuba abafundi kule yunivesithi iphezulu abazi nto ngeziseko zokuzinakekela.

source: UCharles Czeisler, utishala wamayeza okulala eSikolweni Sonyango SaseHarvard kanye nengcali esibhedlele saseBrigham and Women‚Äôs, benze lesi sifundo, akholelwa ukuba ngesokuqala salolu hlobo eMelika.
reference: Charles Czeisler, professor of sleep medicine at Harvard Medical School and a specialist at the Brigham and Women's Hospital, designed the course, which he believes is the first of its kind in the US.
translation: UCharles Czeisler, utishala wamayeza okulala eSikolweni Sonyango SaseHarvard kanye nengcali esibhedlele saseBrigham and Women's, benze lesi sifundo, akholelwa ukuba ngesokuqala salolu hlobo eMelika.

source: Wakhuthazwa yintetho yakhe malunga neziphumo zokungalali ngokwaneleyo ezifundweni.
reference: He was inspired to start the course after giving a talk on the impact sleep deprivation had on learning.
translation: Wakhuthazwa yintetho yakhe malunga neziphumo zokungalali ngokwaneleyo ezifundweni.

source: 'Xa sigqiba enye iklasi yaso esi sifundo enye intombazana yeza kumi yathi: ‚ÄòKutheni ndixelelwa oko ngoku, sendiza kugqiba esikolweni?‚Äô
reference: 'At the end of it one girl came up to me and said: 'Why am I only being told this now, in my senior year?'
translation: 'Xa sigqiba enye iklasi yaso esi sifundo enye intombazana yeza kumi yathi: 'Kutheni ndixelelwa oko ngoku, sendiza kugqiba esikolweni?'

source: Wathi kum akekho umntu okhe wamxelela ukubaluleka kokulala - oko kwandimangalisa,‚Äô esitsho exelela iThe Telegraph.
reference: She said no one had ever told her about the importance of sleep - which surprised me,' he told The Telegraph.
translation: Wathi kum akekho umntu okhe wamxelela ukubaluleka kokulala - oko kwandimangalisa,' esitsho exelela iThe Telegraph.

source: Esi sifundo siqalisiwe kulo nyaka, sicacisa inzuzo zokulala malunga nophuhliso lwezemfundo kunye nezemidlalo, kuquka nokuphucula impilo yabo jikelele.
reference: The course, rolled out for the first time this year, explains to students the essentials of how good sleep habits help academic and athletic performance, as well as improve their general wellbeing.
translation: Esi sifundo siqalisiwe kulo nyaka, sicacisa inzuzo zokulala malunga nophuhliso lwezemfundo kunye nezemidlalo, kuquka nokuphucula impilo yabo jikelele.

source: UPaul Barreira, utitshala wezifundo zengqondo eSikolweni Sonyango SaseHarvard kunye nomlawuli ophezulu weenkonzo zonyango eyunivesithi, uthe iyunivesithi yenze isigqibo sokuzisa esi sifundo emva kokufumana abafundi abangalali ngokwaneleyo nyani.
reference: Paul Barreira, professor of psychiatry at Harvard Medical School and executive director of the university's health services, said the university decided to introduce the course after finding students were seriously sleep deprived during the week.
translation: UPaul Barreira, utitshala wezifundo zengqondo eSikolweni Sonyango SaseHarvard kunye nomlawuli ophezulu weenkonzo zonyango eyunivesithi, uthe iyunivesithi yenze isigqibo sokuzisa esi sifundo emva kokufumana abafundi abangalali ngokwaneleyo nyani.

source: Esi sifundo esithatha ixesha elingangeyure enye esiquka imisebenzi elandelanayo emnandi.
reference: The hour long course involves a series of interactive tasks.
translation: Esi sifundo esithatha ixesha elingangeyure enye esiquka imisebenzi elandelanayo emnandi.

source: Kwicandelo elinye kunomfanekiso wegumbi lokulala laseyunivesithi, apho abafundi benkqakraza iikomityi zekofu, iikhethini, iimpahla zoqeqesho kunye neencwadi ngenjongo yokucaciselwa iziphumo ze-caffeine nokukhanya kunye nokuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kulichaphazela njani uphuhliso lwezemidlalo.
reference: In one section there is an image of a dorm room, where students click on coffee cups, curtains, trainers and books to be told about the effects of caffeine and light and how athletic performance is impacted by sleep deficiency, and the importance of a bedtime routine.
translation: Kwicandelo elinye kunomfanekiso wegumbi lokulala laseyunivesithi, apho abafundi benkqakraza iikomityi zekofu, iikhethini, iimpahla zoqeqesho kunye neencwadi ngenjongo yokucaciselwa iziphumo ze-caffeine nokukhanya kunye nokuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kulichaphazela njani uphuhliso lwezemidlalo.

source: Kwicandelo elinye, abathathi nxaxheba baxelelwa ukuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kuwandisa njani umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa yintliziyo, isifo esikhubaza icala elinye, isifo sokuxinezeleka kunye nomhlaza.
reference: In another section, participants are told how long-term sleep deprivation can increase risks of heart attacks, stroke, depression and cancer.
translation: Kwicandelo elinye, abathathi nxaxheba baxelelwa ukuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kuwandisa njani umngcipheko wokuhlaselwa yintliziyo, isifo esikhubaza icala elinye, isifo sokuxinezeleka kunye nomhlaza.

source: Imephu yesikolo, eneempawu ezivusa umdla, ikhuthaza abathathi nxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngezinto abaqhele ukuzenza imihla ngemihla.
reference: A map of the campus, with interactive icons, then encourages participants to think about their daily routine.
translation: Imephu yesikolo, eneempawu ezivusa umdla, ikhuthaza abathathi nxaxheba ukuba bacinge ngezinto abaqhele ukuzenza imihla ngemihla.

source: ‚ÄòSiyayazi ukuba soze yatshintsha ukuziphatha kwabafundi‚Äô ngoko nangoko.
reference: 'We know it won't change students' behaviour instantly.
translation: 'Siyayazi ukuba soze yatshintsha ukuziphatha kwabafundi' ngoko nangoko.

source: Nangoba kunjalo, sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokukwazi - njengoko nawe unelungelo lokukwazi iziphumo zempilo malunga nokutshaya iiguba,‚Äù kusitsho utitshala uCzeisler wongeza.
reference: But we believe they have a right to know - just as you have a right to know the health effects of choosing to smoke cigarettes,' Prof Czeisler added.
translation: Nangoba kunjalo, sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokukwazi - njengoko nawe unelungelo lokukwazi iziphumo zempilo malunga nokutshaya iiguba," kusitsho utitshala uCzeisler wongeza.

source: Inkcubeko yokuzidla ngokungalali ilokhu ikhona nangoku, esitsho, wongeza ngokuthi ubugcisa beli xesha langoku kunye noxinzelelo kubafundi olwenza bangalali yingxaki ekhulayo
reference: The culture of pride in 'pulling an all-nighter' still exists, he said, adding that modern technology and ever-increasing pressure on students meant sleep deprivation was a growing problem.
translation: Inkcubeko yokuzidla ngokungalali ilokhu ikhona nangoku, esitsho, wongeza ngokuthi ubugcisa beli xesha langoku kunye noxinzelelo kubafundi olwenza bangalali yingxaki ekhulayo

source: Ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulale ngokwaneleyo kufanele kube isixhobo esingaziwa mntu sokulwisana noxinezeleko, ukudinwa nokuxhalaba, watsho - kwanokuphepha ukutyeba, njengoko ukungalali kuyikhubaza ingqondo, kuyenze isoloko ilambile.
reference: Ensuring you have enough sleep, of a good quality, should be a student's 'secret weapon' to combat stress, exhaustion and anxiety, he said - even to avoid putting on weight, as sleep deprivation puts the brain into starvation mode, making them constantly hungry.
translation: Ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulale ngokwaneleyo kufanele kube isixhobo esingaziwa mntu sokulwisana noxinezeleko, ukudinwa nokuxhalaba, watsho - kwanokuphepha ukutyeba, njengoko ukungalali kuyikhubaza ingqondo, kuyenze isoloko ilambile.

source: URaymond So, oneminyaka engu19 ohlala eCalifornia ofunda izifundo zesayensi yeekhemikhali kunye nezinto eziphilayo, wanceda uNjingalwazi uCzeisler enze ufundo lwale klasi, emva kokuya eklasini yakhe yokuqala ngonyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
reference: Raymond So, a 19-year-old Californian studying chemical and physical biology, helped Professor Czeisler design the course, having taken one of his classes last year during his first year at Harvard.
translation: URaymond So, oneminyaka engu19 ohlala eCalifornia ofunda izifundo zesayensi yeekhemikhali kunye nezinto eziphilayo, wanceda uNjingalwazi uCzeisler enze ufundo lwale klasi, emva kokuya eklasini yakhe yokuqala ngonyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.

source: Uthi le klasi imvule amehlo kwaye yamnika umdla wokuba enze le klasi ifumaneke kuso sonke isikolo.
reference: He said the course had opened his eyes and inspired him to push for a campus-wide course.
translation: Uthi le klasi imvule amehlo kwaye yamnika umdla wokuba enze le klasi ifumaneke kuso sonke isikolo.

source: Uthemba ukuba eli nyathelo elilandelayo ukucela abafundi abazizithwalandwe ukuba benze inkqubo efanayo yokufunda ngaphambi kokuba bangenele eli ziko linokhuphiswano.
reference: The next step, he hopes, it to ask all postgraduate students to complete a similar study programme before joining the competitive institution.
translation: Uthemba ukuba eli nyathelo elilandelayo ukucela abafundi abazizithwalandwe ukuba benze inkqubo efanayo yokufunda ngaphambi kokuba bangenele eli ziko linokhuphiswano.

source: Utishala uCzeisler ucebise ukuba abafundi bacinge ukuba benze i-alamu yexesha lokulala, kunye nelokuvuka, nokuba balumke iziphumo eziyingozi zokukhanya kwezikrini zomatshini bakagesi kunye nokukhanya kweLED, okungaphazamisa ukulandelelana kwezinto ozenza imihla ngemihla, oko kungakhokhela ezingxakini zokungalali.
reference: Prof Czeisler recommended that students should consider setting an alarm for when to go to bed, as well as for when to wake, and be aware of the harmful effects of 'blue light' emitted by electronic screens and LED lighting, which can throw your circadian rhythm out of kilter, leading to problems falling asleep.
translation: Utishala uCzeisler ucebise ukuba abafundi bacinge ukuba benze i-alamu yexesha lokulala, kunye nelokuvuka, nokuba balumke iziphumo eziyingozi zokukhanya kwezikrini zomatshini bakagesi kunye nokukhanya kweLED, okungaphazamisa ukulandelelana kwezinto ozenza imihla ngemihla, oko kungakhokhela ezingxakini zokungalali.

source: ILivingston 1-0 iiRangers UMenga woyise amadoda kaGerrard ngenqaku linye
reference: Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Menga goal downs Gerrard's men
translation: ILivingston 1-0 iiRangers UMenga woyise amadoda kaGerrard ngenqaku linye

source: AmaRangers adibane nengxaki kwakhona xa edlalela esekuhambeni ngexesha uDolly Menga ebetha uSteven Gerrad ngenqaku lilinye eqandeni (1-0) eLivingston.
reference: Rangers suffered another bout of away-day blues as Dolly Menga's strike consigned Steven Gerrard's disjointed side to a 1-0 defeat at Livingston.
translation: AmaRangers adibane nengxaki kwakhona xa edlalela esekuhambeni ngexesha uDolly Menga ebetha uSteven Gerrad ngenqaku lilinye eqandeni (1-0) eLivingston.

source: Icala lama Ibrox belinomdla wokuqoba isekuhambeni okokuqala emva kokuba iSt Johnstone yayibetha ngo 4-1 ngeFebruwari. kodwa iqela likaGary Holt labetha uGerrard okwesibini emdlalweni engu 18  oko aqala ukuba umphathi njengoba aphulukwa amaphuzu ayisibhozo ngaphandle kweqela elabalekayo elihamba phambili kwiLadbrokes Premiership, iiHearts.
reference: The Ibrox side were looking to record their first win on the road since February's 4-1 triumph at St Johnstone, but Gary Holt's team inflicted just Gerrard's second defeat in 18 games as manager to leave his side eight points adrift of runaway Ladbrokes Premiership leaders Hearts.
translation: Icala lama Ibrox belinomdla wokuqoba isekuhambeni okokuqala emva kokuba iSt Johnstone yayibetha ngo 4-1 ngeFebruwari. kodwa iqela likaGary Holt labetha uGerrard okwesibhozo emdlalweni engu 18  oko aqala ukuba umphathi njengoba aphulukwa amaphuzu ayisibhozo ngaphandle kweqela elabalekayo elihamba phambili kwiLadbrokes Premiership, iiHearts.

source: UMenga wathola inqaku emizuzwini eyisixhengxe ngaphambili kwe half-time kwaye nabadlali beeRangers babenganamdla.
reference: Menga struck seven minutes before half-time and a Rangers line-up short on inspiration never looked like levelling.
translation: UMenga wathola inqaku emizuzwini eyisixhengxe ngaphambili kwe half-time kwaye nabadlali beeRangers babenganamdla.

source: Ngelixa iiRangers yehlela endaweni yesithandathu, iLivingston yonyukele kweyesithathu emva kwayo yiHibernian eyishiya ngenqaku linye.
reference: While Rangers now drop down to sixth spot, Livingston climb to third and only behind Hibernian on goal difference.
translation: Ngelixa iiRangers yehlela endaweni yesithandathu, iLivingston yonyukele kweyesithathu emva kwayo yiHibernian eyishiya ngenqaku linye.

source: Kwaye kunezingxaki eziseza kumaRangers emva kokuba u-linesman uCalum Spence enyangelwe ukonzakala entloko emva kokuba ebethwe yinto ephosiweyo ivela ecaleni lababedlala behambile.
reference: And there could be further trouble in store for Rangers after linesman Calum Spence had to be treated for a head wound after an object was apparently thrown from the away end.
translation: Kwaye kunezingxaki eziseza kumaRangers emva kokuba u-linesman uCalum Spence enyangelwe ukonzakala entloko emva kokuba ebethwe yinto ephosiweyo ivela ecaleni lababedlala behambile.

source: UGerrard utshintshe abadlali amaxesha ayisixhengxe okuhambe no-Ayr emdlalweni ophambi kowokugqibela weBetfred Cup.
reference: Gerrard made eight changes to the side which swept past Ayr into the Betfred Cup semi-finals.
translation: UGerrard utshintshe abadlali amaxesha ayisixhengxe okuhambe no-Ayr emdlalweni ophambi kowokugqibela weBetfred Cup.

source: Kwelinye icala, uHolt uqhubeke nabadlali abafanayo abangu11 beLivingstone abathathe iphuzu linye kwiHearts evekini edlulileyo kwaye uvuyile ngendlela iqela lakhe elibethe ngayo abachasi balo ngandlela zonke.
reference: Holt, on the other hand, went with the same Livi 11 which took a point off Hearts last week and he would have been delighted with the way his well-drilled outfit suffocated their opponents at every turn.
translation: Kwelinye icala, uHolt uqhubeke nabadlali abafanayo abangu11 beLivingstone abathathe iphuzu linye kwiHearts evekini edlulileyo kwaye uvuyile ngendlela iqela lakhe elibethe ngayo abachasi balo ngandlela zonke.

source: AmaRangers awulawulile umdlalo kodwa iLivingstone yenze okongeziwe ngelixa ilifumana ibhola.
reference: Rangers may have dominated possession but Livingston did more with the ball they had.
translation: AmaRangers awulawulile umdlalo kodwa iLivingstone yenze okongeziwe ngelixa ilifumana ibhola.

source: Kufanele ngabe ibethe inqaku emizuzwini wesibini ngelixa umdlali kaMenga evumela uScott Pittman adlule aye emapalini ka-Allan McGregor kodwa lo mdlali waphakathi khange alifumane.
reference: They should have scored just two minutes in when Menga's first-time lay-off sent Scott Pittman through on Allan McGregor's goal but the midfielder tugged his big chance wide.
translation: Kufanele ngabe ibethe inqaku emizuzwini wesibini ngelixa umdlali kaMenga evumela uScott Pittman adlule aye emapalini ka-Allan McGregor kodwa lo mdlali waphakathi khange alifumane.

source: UKeaghan Jacobs wakhaba ibhola yafunyanwa nguCraig Halkett kodwa iqabane lakhe uAlan Lithgow wakwazi ukuvula banzi kwiipali ezisemva.
reference: A deep Keaghan Jacobs free-kick then found skipper Craig Halkett but his defensive partner Alan Lithgow could only stab wide at the back post.
translation: UKeaghan Jacobs wakhaba ibhola yafunyanwa nguCraig Halkett kodwa iqawe lakhe uAlan Lithgow wakwazi ukuvula banzi kwiipali ezisemva.

source: AmaRangers khange afumane ulawulo kodwa bekukhangeleka kunethemba kuneenkolelo malunga nomdlalo wesithathu ngaphambi kowokugqibela.
reference: Rangers did grab control but there looked to be more hope than belief about their play in the final third.
translation: AmaRangers khange afumane ulawulo kodwa bekukhangeleka kunethemba kuneenkolelo malunga nomdlalo wesithathu ngaphambi kowokugqibela.

source: U-Almanac: Umvelisi weGeiger Counter
reference: Almanac: The inventor of the Geiger Counter
translation: I-Almanac: Umvelisi weGeiger Counter

source: Kwaye ngoku iphepha elivela ‚ÄúkuSunday Morning‚Äù U-Almanac: NgeSepthemba 30, 1882, eminyakeni engu136 edlulileyo namhlanje, kwaye SISABALA ... umhla usosayensi uJohannes Wilhelm ‚ÄúHans‚Äù Geiger azalwa ngawo eJamani.
reference: And now a page from our "Sunday Morning" Almanac: September 30, 1882, 136 years ago today, and COUNTING ... the day the future physicist Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger was born in Germany.
translation: Kwaye ngoku iphepha elivela "kuSunday Morning" I-Almanac: NgeSepthemba 30, 1882, eminyakeni engu136 edlulileyo namhlanje, kwaye SISABALA ... umhla usosayensi uJohannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger azalwa ngawo eJamani.

source: UGeiger waphuhlisa indlela yokukhangela kunye nokulinganisa ukusebenza kwemisebe, oko okwaveliswa ngolu phuhliso isixhobo esaziwa njengeGeiger Counter.
reference: Geiger developed a method for detecting and measuring radioactivity, an invention that eventually led to the device known as the Geiger Counter.
translation: UGeiger waphuhlisa indlela yokukhangela kunye nokulinganisa ukusebenza kwemisebe, oko okwaveliswa ngolu phuhliso isixhobo esaziwa njengeGeiger Counter.

source: Iye yasetyenziswa ukususela ngoko, iGeiger Counter iye yasetyenziswa nakwinkcubeko ye-pop ngokunjalo, njengoba yaboniswa kumboniso bhanyabhanya nge-1950 owaziwa ngelithi ‚ÄúBells of Corondao,‚Äù onabadlali abanomdla okungenakwenzeka babe ngoososayensi uRoy Rogers kunye noDale Evans:
reference: A mainstay of science ever since, the Geiger Counter became a pop culture mainstay as well, as in the 1950 movie "Bells of Coronado," starring those seemingly unlikely cowpoke scientists Roy Rogers and Dale Evans:
translation: Iye yasetyenziswa ukususela ngoko, iGeiger Counter iye yasetyenziswa nakwinkcubeko ye-pop ngokunjalo, njengoba yaboniswa kumboniso bhanyabhanya nge-1950 owaziwa ngelithi "Bells of Corondao," onabadlali abanomdla okungenakwenzeka babe ngoososayensi uRoy Rogers kunye noDale Evans:

source: Indoda: ‚ÄúNgaba yintoni leyo?‚Äù
reference: Man: "What in the world is that?"
translation: Indoda: "Ngaba yintoni leyo?"

source: URogers: ‚ÄúYiGeiger Counter, isetyenziselwa ukukhangela izitye ezixabisekileyo.
reference: Rogers: "It's a Geiger Counter, used to locate radioactive minerals, such as uranium.
translation: URogers: "YiGeiger Counter, isetyenziselwa ukukhangela izitye ezixabisekileyo.

source: Xa ubeka ezi zinto ezindlebeni zakho, uzokuva iziphumo zee-Atoms ezikhutshwa ukusebenza kwemisebe.‚Äù
reference: When you put these earphones on, you can actually hear the effects of the atoms given off by the radioactivity in the minerals."
translation: Xa ubeka ezi zinto ezindlebeni zakho, uzokuva iziphumo zee-Atoms ezikhutshwa ukusebenza kwemisebe."

source: Evans: ‚ÄúThetha, iyavela nyani ngoku!‚Äù
reference: Evans: "Say, it sure is popping now!"
translation: Evans: "Thetha, iyavela nyani ngoku!"

source: ‚ÄúUHans‚Äù Geiger wasweleka nge1945, emva kweentsuku ezimbalwa zosuku lakhe lokuzalwa lwesi63.

translation: UHans Geiger wasweleka nge1945, emva kweentsuku ezimbalwa zosuku lakhe lokuzalwa lwesi63.

source: Kodwa olu veliso olunegama lakhe liyakuphila liqhubeke.

source: Ugonya okutsha komdlavuza kufundisa amasotya omzimba ‚Äòukubona‚Äô iiseli ezinzima

translation: Indlela yokwenza oko iquka ukukhupha iiseli zamasotya omzimba kwisigulane, uze uzitshintshe e-lab

source: Ngoko ‚Äòzingabona‚Äô iiprotheni eziqhelekileyo kumdlavuza kwaye zibuyiselwe emzimbeni kwakhona

translation: Ngoko 'zingabona' iiprotheni eziqhelekileyo kumdlavuza kwaye zibuyiselwe emzimbeni kwakhona

source: Ugonya oluzanywayo luvelisa iziphumo ezithembisayo kwizigulane ezineenhlobo ezahlukeneyo zomdlavuza.
reference: A trial vaccine is showing promising results in patients with a range of cancers.
translation: Ugonya oluzanywayo luvelisa iziphumo ezithembisayo kwizigulane ezineenhlobo ezahlukeneyo zomdlavuza.

source: Omnye umntu obhinqileyo owafumana unyango ngalo gonyo, olufundisa amasotya omzimba ukuba abone iiseli ezingaqhelekile emzimbeni, wabona umdlavuza wesiyilelo-maqanda uphela emva kwezinyanga ezingale kwezingu-18.
reference: One woman treated with the vaccine, which teaches the immune system to recognise rogue cells, saw her ovarian cancer disappear for more than 18 months.
translation: Omnye umntu obhinqileyo owafumana unyango ngalo gonyo, olufundisa amasotya omzimba ukuba abone iiseli ezingaqhelekile emzimbeni, wabona umdlavuza wesiyilelo-maqanda uphela emva kwezinyanga ezingale kwezingu-18.

source: Indlela yokwenza oko iquka ukukhupha iiseli zamasotya omzimba kwisigulane, uze uzitshintshe e-laboratory de ‚Äúzibone‚Äù iiprotheni eziqhelekile kumdlavuza ezibizwa ngeeHER2, kwaye uzibuyisele emzimbeni kwakhona
reference: The method involves extracting immune cells from a patient, altering them in the laboratory so they can "see" a protein common to many cancers called HER2, and then reinjecting the cells.
translation: Indlela yokwenza oko iquka ukukhupha iiseli zamasotya omzimba kwisigulane, uze uzitshintshe e-laboratory de "zibone" iiprotheni eziqhelekile kumdlavuza ezibizwa ngeeHER2, kwaye uzibuyisele emzimbeni kwakhona

reference: Professor Jay Berzofsky, of the US National Cancer Institute in Bethesda, Maryland, said: "Our results suggest that we have a very promising vaccine."
translation: Utitshala waseyunivesithi uJay Berzofsky, weZiko Lomdlavuza KaZwelonke waseMelika ozinze eBethesda, eMaryland, uthe: "Iziphumo zethu zicebisa ukuba sinogonywa okungasebenza nyani."

source: IiHER2 ‚Äúzinika ukukhula komdlavuza owahlukeneyo umdla.‚Äù kuquka umdlavuza webele, wesiyilelo-maqanda, womphunga kunye nowesisu, kucacisa utitshala waseyunivesithi uBerzofsky.
reference: HER2 "drives the growth of several types of cancer," including breast, ovarian, lung and colorectal cancers, Prof Berzofsky explained.
translation: IiHER2 "zinika ukukhula komdlavuza owahlukeneyo umdla." kuquka umdlavuza webele, wesiyilelo-maqanda, womphunga kunye nowesisu, kucacisa utitshala waseyunivesithi uBerzofsky.

source: Indlela efanayo yokukhupha amasotya omzimba kwizigulane kunye ‚Äúnokuzifundisa‚Äù ukukhangela iiseli zomdlavuza kuye kwasebenza onyangweni lohlobo lwe-leukaemia.
reference: A similar approach of taking immune cells out of patients and "teaching" them how to target cancer cells has worked in treating a type of leukaemia.
translation: Indlela efanayo yokukhupha amasotya omzimba kwizigulane kunye "nokuzifundisa" ukukhangela iiseli zomdlavuza kuye kwasebenza onyangweni lohlobo lwe-leukaemia.
