source: Kuqhelekile kweezintsuku ukukhangela izinto ezimalunga neBrexit xa ubukela umboniso bhanya bhanya ohlobene namaNgesi kube ngokufanayo nakulo mboniso bhanya bhanya ovuselela eyakudala enamahlaya kunye nobudlova yeentloli iJohnny English - eyasuselwa nge2003 yase ibuya kwakhona ngo2011 ibizwa ngeJohnny English Reborn.
reference: It's traditional now to look for Brexit significances in any new film with a British slant and that does seem applicable to this revival of the Johnny English action-comedy spoof franchise - which started back in 2003 with Johnny English and spluttered back to life in 2011 with Johnny English Reborn.
translation: Kuqhelekile kweezintsuku ukukhangela izinto ezimalunga neBrexit xa ubukela umboniso bhanya bhanya ohlobene namaNgesi kube ngokufanayo nakulo mboniso bhanya bhanya ovuselela eyakudala enamahlaya kunye nobudlova yeentloli iJohnny English - eyasuselwa nge2003 yase ibuya kwakhona ngo2011 ibizwa ngeJohnny English Reborn.

source: Ingabe lo mboniso bhanya bhanya ovusa umdla uzakuthetha ngeendaba yokuba asisakwazi ukudayisela amazwe angaphandle?
reference: Will tongue-in-cheek self-satire on the subject of how obviously rubbish we are be the nation's new export opportunity?
translation: Ingabe lo mboniso bhanya bhanya ovusa umdla uzakuthetha ngeendaba yokuba asisakwazi ukudayisela amazwe angaphandle?

source: Lomntu onobuso bukapopayi obizwa ngoJohnny English ufumane ilayisense yakhe ukuvuselela - lelo gama lakhe elibonisa ukuba ungusumahlayo owenzelwe nababukeli abangewona amaNgesi bakwamanye amazwe.
reference: At any rate, the pop-eyed, rubber-faced incompetent Johnny English has had his licence to cock things up renewed for the second time - that name of his signalling more than anything else that he is a broad comic creation designed for non-English-speaking cinemagoing territories.
translation: Lomntu onobuso bukapopayi obizwa ngoJohnny English ufumane ilayisense yakhe ukuvuselela - lelo gama lakhe elibonisa ukuba ungusumahlayo owenzelwe nababukeli abangewona amaNgesi bakwamanye amazwe.

source: Unguye ngokwenene umsebenzi kaRhulumente oyiintloli nongona ezenzisa ngendlela eyohlukile unobuncinane bukaClouseau, nobukaMr. Bean kanye nobunye ubuncinane balaa kwenkwe ecula inqaku lomculo linye eculweni leChariots of Fire emcimbini wokuvula ama-Olimphikhi aseLondon ngo2012.
reference: He is of course the daft secret agent who despite his bizarre pretensions to smoothie glamour has got a little bit of Clouseau, a dash of Mr Bean and a dollop of that chap contributing a single note to the Chariots of Fire theme tune at the London 2012 Olympics opening ceremony.
translation: Unguye ngokwenene umsebenzi kaRhulumente oyiintloli nongona ezenzisa ngendlela eyohlukile unobuncinane bukaClouseau, nobukaMr. Bean kanye nobunye ubuncinane balaa kwenkwe ecula inqaku lomculo linye eculweni leChariots of Fire emcimbini wokuvula ama-Olimphikhi aseLondon ngo2012.

source: Ude abe umhambi kunye nendoda yeemfihlo eyaziwa ihlabathi lonke u-Atkinson owaske walingisa kwezikhangiso zeBarclaycard zomabonakude, etshiya iingxabano la ske ahamba khona.
reference: He's also originally based on the traveller and international man of mystery Atkinson once played in the now forgotten Barclaycard TV ads, leaving chaos in his wake.
translation: Ude abe umhambi kunye nendoda yeemfihlo eyaziwa ihlabathi lonke u-Atkinson owaske walingisa kwezikhangiso zeBarclaycard zomabonakude, etshiya iingxabano la ske ahamba khona.

source: Kunexesha elinye okanye amabini amandi kulo mboniso bhanya bhanya iJE.
reference: There are one or two nice moments in this latest JE outing.
translation: Kunexesha elinye okanye amabini amandi kulo mboniso bhanya bhanya iJE.

source: Ndithande la xesha uJohnny English eza kwihelikopta enxibe izambatho zokhuseleko zangaphambilini ngelixesha ophephela bebetha umnqwazo wakhe.
reference: I loved Johnny English approaching a helicopter while dressed in a medieval suit of armour and the rotor blades briefly clanging against his helmet.
translation: Bendithanda le xesha uJohnny English eza kwihelikopta enxibe izambatho zokhuseleko zangaphambilini ngelixesha ophephela bebetha umnqwazo wakhe.

source: Isipho sika-Atkinson sokuhlekisa engathethi nto sivusa umdla, kodwa abunamandla xa buthelekiswa ngeezimveliso ezinzima njenge 007 kunye neMission Impossinle eziquka namahlaya ngoku.
reference: Atkinson's gift for physical comedy is on display, but the humour feels pretty underpowered and weirdly superfluous, especially as the "serious" film brands like 007 and Mission Impossible themselves now confidently offer comedy as an ingredient.
translation: Isipho sika-Atkinson sokuhlekisa engathethi nto sivusa umdla, kodwa abunamandla xa buthelekiswa ngeezimveliso ezinzima njenge 007 kunye neMission Impossinle eziquka namahlaya ngoku.

source: La mahlaya kungathi ajongelwe abantwana hayi abantu abadala, xa ndithethela elami icala ukuhlekisa kukaJohnny English abubonisi isakhono esingaphi xa sithelekiswa nemiboniso bhanya bhanya engenamsindo ka-Atkinson ngelixa edlala uBean
reference: The humour feels as if it is pitched at kids rather than adults, and for me Johnny English's wacky misadventures aren't as inventive and focused as Atkinson's silent-movie gags in the persona of Bean.
translation: La mahlaya kungathi ajongelwe abantwana hayi abantu abadala, xa ndithethela elami icala ukuhlekisa kukaJohnny English abubonisi isakhono esingaphi xa sithelekiswa nemiboniso bhanya bhanya engenamsindo ka-Atkinson ngelixa edlala uBean

source: Iindaba kulo mboniso bhanya bhanya ukuba amaNgesi asengxakini enkulu
reference: The perennially topical premise now is that Great Britain is in serious trouble.
translation: Iindaba kulo mboniso bhanya bhanya ukuba amaNgesi asengxakini enkulu

source: Umphangi we-inthanethi ungene ngokungekhoyo esikweni kumnatha wezintoli okwi-inthanethi, wabona iinkcukacha zazo zonke izintloli zamaNgesi ezisebenzayo, kude kumangale intloli esemsebenzini - indima encane kakhulu kaKevin Eldon.
reference: A cyber-hacker has infiltrated Britain's super-secret web network of spies, revealing the identities of all Britain's agents in the field, to the dismay of the agent on duty - a regrettably small role for Kevin Eldon.
translation: Umphangi we-inthanethi ungene ngokungekhoyo esikweni kumnatha wezintoli okwi-inthanethi, wabona iinkcukacha zazo zonke izintloli zamaNgesi ezisebenzayo, kude kumangale intloli esemsebenzini - indima encane kakhulu kaKevin Eldon.

source: Ezi zindaba zivele zigqithe ngomphathiswa ophezulu onekratshi, ojongene nengxaki yokungathandwa njengosopolitiki: U-Emma Thompson uyazama ukwenza okolungileyo njengoba edlala uTeresa May kodwa umbhali walo mboniso bhanya bhanya akenzanga kakuhle xa ewubhala
reference: It's the last straw for a prime minister who is a pompous and embattled figure, already suffering a complete meltdown of political unpopularity: Emma Thompson does her very best with this quasi-Teresa-May character but there's nothing much in the script to work with.
translation: Ezi zindaba zivele zigqithe ngomphathiswa ophezulu onekratshi, ojongene nengxaki yokungathandwa njengosopolitiki: U-Emma Thompson uyazama ukwenza okolungileyo njengoba edlala uTeresa May kodwa umbhali walo mboniso bhanya bhanya akenzanga kakuhle xa ewubhala

source: Abacebisi bezobulumko bamxelela ukuba njengawo zonke izintloli zisemngciphekweni, kunyanzeleke ukuba abuyise umntu othathe umhlalaphantsi.
reference: Her intelligence advisers inform her that as every single active spy has been compromised, she will have to bring someone out of retirement.
translation: Abacebisi bezobulumko bamxelela ukuba njengawo zonke izintloli zisemngciphekweni, kunyanzeleke ukuba abuyise umntu othathe umhlalaphantsi.

source: Kwaye oko kutsho eso sdenge uJohnny English uqobo, osethole isikhundla sokuba ngutitshala ntloko esikolweni thizeni sesihle, kodwa enikeza izifundo ngokungekho esikweni zokuba yiintloli engaziwa muntu, ngelixesha u-English efundisa ngendlela engaqhelekanga ukuba uba njani yintloli kunamaxesha amandi nyani.
reference: And that means bumbling Johnny English himself, now employed as a schoolmaster in some posh establishment, but giving off-the-record lessons in how to be an undercover operative: some nice gags here, as English offers a School of Rock-type academy of spying.
translation: Kwaye oko kutsho eso sdenge uJohnny English uqobo, osethole isikhundla sokuba ngutitshala ntloko esikolweni thizeni sesihle, kodwa enikeza izifundo ngokungekho esikweni zokuba yiintloli engaziwa muntu, ngelixesha u-English efundisa ngendlela engaqhelekanga ukuba uba njani yintloli kunamaxesha amandi nyani.

source: U-English ubuyiselwa eWhitehall ze axelelwe ngalengxakeko adibane nomhlobo wakhe waphambili ayebandezeleka naye uBough, odlalwa uBen Miller kwakhona.
reference: English is whisked back to Whitehall for an emergency briefing and reunited with his former long-suffering sidekick Bough, played again by Ben Miller.
translation: U-English ubuyiselwa eWhitehall ze axelelwe ngalengxakeko adibane nomhlobo wakhe waphambili ayebandezeleka naye uBough, odlalwa uBen Miller kwakhona.

source: UBough yindoda etshatile, utshate nomlawuli weenqanawa ehamba ngaphantsi kwamanzi
reference: Bough is now a married man, hitched to a submarine commander, a jolly-hockey-sticks role in which Vicki Pepperdine is a bit wasted.
translation: UBough yindoda etshatile, utshate nomlawuli weenqanawa ehamba ngaphantsi kwamanzi

source: Esi sibini esinesakhono sokuwenza izinto eziphosakeleyo eenkonzweni zobuntloli sibuyela emsebenzini, base bedibana no-Ophelia Bulletova odlwa ngu-Olga Kurylenko
reference: So the Batman and Robin of getting things terribly wrong on Her Majesty's Secret Service are back in action, encountering Olga Kurylenko's beautiful femme fatale Ophelia Bulletova.
translation: Esi sibini esinesakhono sokuwenza izinto eziphosakeleyo eenkonzweni zobuntloli sibuyela emsebenzini, base bedibana no-Ophelia Bulletova odlw ngu-Olga Kurylenko

source: Ngelixa, umphathiswa ophezulu ukholelwa isityebi esinamabhiliyoni seteknoloji esithi sinokulungisa ezi zingxaki zekhomputha zamaNgesi: lomntu ongendawo uJason Volts, udlalwe nguJake Lacy
reference: Meanwhile, the prime minister is falling dangerously under the spell of the charismatic tech billionaire who claims he can solve Britain's computer woes: the sinister Jason Volta, played by Jake Lacy.
translation: Ngelixa, umphathiswa ophezulu ukholelwa isityebi esinamabhiliyoni seteknoloji esithi sinokulungisa ezi zingxaki zekhomputha zamaNgesi: lomntu ongendawo uJason Volts, udlalwe nguJake Lacy

source: U-English kunye noBough baqala obo bubangxa: bezenza abanikezi kutya, batshisa istolo sokutya samaFrentshi; baqalisa iingxaki xa bekhwela inqanawana yezityebi kaVolta; kwaye u-English uzisa uhlaselo ngelixa ezma ukusebenzisa okunxibwa entloko kweVirtual Reality ngenjongo yokufunda ingaphakathi yendlu kaVolta.
reference: English and Bough begin their odyssey of farcical high-jinks: disguised as waiters, they set fire to a flash French restaurant; they create mayhem smuggling themselves aboard Volta's luxury yacht; and English triggers pure anarchy as he attempts to use a Virtual Reality headset to familiarise himself with the interior of Volta's house.
translation: U-English kunye noBough baqala obo bubangxa: bezenza abanikezi kutya, batshisa istolo sokutya samaFrentshi; baqalisa iingxaki xa bekhwela inqanawana yezityebi kaVolta; kwaye u-English uzisa uhlaselo ngelixa ezma ukusebenzisa okunxibwa entloko kweVirtual Reality ngenjongo yokufunda ingaphakathi yendlu kaVolta.

source: Kwenziwe yonke into kwiicandelo lokugqibela, nangona inomdla futhi yonwabisa, kuneenkqubo zika mabonakude zabantwana abathetha ngayo yonke lento.
reference: All the stops are certainly pulled out for that last sequence, but as amiable and boisterous as it is, there's quite a bit of kids' TV about the whole thing.
translation: Kwenziwe yonke into kwiicandelo lokugqibela, nangona inomdla futhi yonwabisa, kuneenkqubo zika mabonakude zabantwana abathetha ngayo yonke lento.

source: Iinto eziqhelekileyo.
reference: Pretty moderate stuff.
translation: Iinto eziqhelekileyo.

source: Njengayo yonke eminye imiboniso bhanya bhanya kaJohnny English: Ndizibuze ukuba eli shishini lemi boniso bhanya bhanya lamaNgesi alinokwazi na ukunika uRowan Atkinson indima efanelekileyo kwisakhono sakhe?
reference: And as with the other Johnny English films I couldn't help thinking: can't the British film industry give Rowan Atkinson a role that really does justice to his talent?
translation: Njengayo yonke eminye imiboniso bhanya bhanya kaJohnny English: Ndizibuze ukuba eli shishini lemi boniso bhanya bhanya lamaNgesi alinokwazi na ukunika uRowan Atkinson indima efanelekileyo kwisakhono sakhe?

source: Iqela lezomsebenzi likhanyela ukuba lenza ucwangciso lokuba abahlali baseBrithani basebenze iintsuku ezine kodwa babhatalelwe ezintlanu
reference: Labour denies it is devising a plan for Britons to work a four day week but be paid for five days
translation: Iqela lezomsebenzi likhanyela ukuba lenza ucwangciso lokuba abahlali baseBrithani basebenze iintsuku ezine kodwa babhatalelwe ezintlanu

source: Iqela lezomsebenzi lika Jeremy Corbyn yenza ucwangciso lokwenza abaqeshwa basebenze iintsuku ezine evekini - kodwa babhatalelwe umvuzo wezintsuku ezintlanu.
reference: Jeremy Corbyn's Labour Party is to consider a radical plan which will see Britons working a four day week - but getting paid for five.
translation: Iqela lezomsebenzi lika Jeremy Corbyn yenza ucwangciso lokwenza abaqeshwa basebenze iintsuku ezine evekini - kodwa babhatalelwe umvuzo wezintsuku ezintlanu.

source: Iingxelo zithi eli qela lifuna abaphathi beenkampani bafuna abaqeshwa babhatalwe ngemali efumanwa xa iinkampani zisebenza i-Artificial Intelligence (AI) ngokubanikeza usuku.
reference: The party reportedly wants company bosses to pass on savings made through the artificial intelligence (AI) revolution to workers by giving them an extra day off.
translation: Iingxelo zithi eli qela lifuna abaphathi beenkampani bafuna abaqeshwa babhatalwe ngemali efumanwa xa iinkampani zisebenza i-Artificial Intelligence (AI) ngokubanikeza usuku.

source: Olu guquko lizakwenza abaqeshwa babe nempelaveki eneentsuku ezintathu - kodwa babhatalwe umvuzo ofanayo.
reference: It would see employees enjoy a three-day weekend - but still take home the same pay.
translation: Olu guquko lizakwenza abaqeshwa babe nempelaveki eneentsuku ezintathu - kodwa babhatalwe umvuzo ofanayo.

source: Imithombo isithi olu cwangciso luzo ‚Äòfaneleka‚Äô kakuhle neengcamango zoqoqosho zeli qela kunye nocwangciso lokutshinswa leli zwe lithathe icala labaqeshwa
reference: Sources said the idea would 'fit' with the party's economic agenda and plans to tilt the country in favour of workers.
translation: Imithombo isithi olu cwangciso luzo 'faneleka' kakuhle neengcamango zoqoqosho zeli qela kunye nocwangciso lokutshinswa leli zwe lithathe icala labaqeshwa

source: Ukutshintshela evekini eneentsuku ezine kugaye inkxaso yeTrades Union Congress njengendlela yabaqeshwa ukuba bathathe isithuba ekutshintsheni ezoqoqosho.
reference: Shifting to a four-day week has been endorsed by the Trades Union Congress as a way for workers to take advantage of the changing economy.
translation: Ukutshintshela evekini eneentsuku ezine kugaye inkxaso yeTrades Union Congress njengendlela yabaqeshwa ukuba bathathe isithuba ekutshintsheni ezoqoqosho.

source: Umthombo ophezulu weLabour Party uxelele iSunday Times esithi: ‚Äòukuhlolwa kweenkqubo kulindeleke ukuba kwaziswe ngaphambili kokuba unyaka ugqithe.
reference: A senior Labour Party source told The Sunday Times: 'A policy review is expected to be announced before the end of the year.
translation: Umthombo ophezulu weLabour Party uxelele iSunday Times esithi: 'ukuhlolwa kweenkqubo kulindeleke ukuba kwaziswe ngaphambili kokuba unyaka ugqithe.

source: ‚ÄòSoze kwenzeka ngoko nangoko kodwa iveki yokusebenza eneentsuku ezine yingcamango efanelekelayo yeli qela yokulinganisa kabutsha ezoqoqosho ukuze zibe secaleni labaqeshwa kunye nocwangciso lwezamashishini lweli qela.‚Äô
reference: 'It won't happen overnight but a four-day working week is an aspiration that fits in with the party's approach to rebalancing the economy in favour of the worker as well as the party's overall industrial strategy.'
translation: 'Soze kwenzeka ngoko nangoko kodwa iveki yokusebenza ineentsuku ezine yingcamango efanelekelayo yeli qela yokulinganisa kabutsha ezoqoqosho ukuze zibe secaleni labaqeshwa kunye nocwangciso lwezamashishini lweli qela.'

source: Iqela lezomsebenzi alingelokuqala ukunikeza inkxaso kwingcamango efana nale, neGreen Party yayenza ucwangciso lwezintsuku ezine ngelixa igaya inkxaso yolonyulo lwango2017.
reference: The Labour Party would not be the first to endorse such an idea, with the Green Party pledging a four-day working week during its 2017 general election campaign.
translation: Iqela lezomsebenzi alingelokuqala ukunikeza inkxaso kwingcamango efana nale, neGreen Party yayenza ucwangciso lwezintsuku ezine ngelixa igaya inkxaso yolonyulo lwango2017.

source: Olu cwangciso okwangoku aluyifumani inkxaso epheleleyo kwiLabour Party, noba kunjalo.
reference: The aspiration is currently not being endorsed by the Labour Party as a whole, however.
translation: Lo cwangciso wangoku awufumani inkxaso epheleleyo kwi-Labour Party, noba kunjalo.

source: Isithethi seQela Lezomsebenzi lithe: ‚ÄòIveki lezintsuku ezine zokusebenza akuyona inkqubo yeqela kwaye akusiyo nento eyiqwalaselayo.‚Äô
reference: A Labour Party spokesman said: 'A four-day working week is not party policy and it is not being considered by the party.'
translation: Isithethi seQela Lezomsebenzi sithe: 'Iveki lezintsuku ezine zokusebenza ayikwi inkqubo yeqela kwaye ayisiyonanto eyiqwalaselayo.'

source: Umphathi ongumncedisi uJohn McDonnell usebenzise inkomfa yangeveki edlule yezomsebenzi ukucacisa ingcamango yakhe ngoguqulelo lezoqoqosho olunceda abantu.
reference: Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell used last week's Labour conference to flesh out his vision for a socialist revolution in the economy.
translation: Umphathi ongumncedisi uJohn McDonnell usebenzise inkomfa yangeveki edlule yezomsebenzi ukucacisa ingcamango yakhe ngoguqulelo lezoqoqosho olunceda abantu.

source: Umnumzane McDonnell esitsho ethi uzimisele ukuthatha amandla ‚Äòkubalawuli abangafuni ukubonwa mntu‚Äô kunye ‚Äònabafumana inzuzo‚Äô emashishinini amakhulu.
reference: Mr McDonnell said he was determined to claw back power from 'faceless directors' and 'profiteers' at utility firms.
translation: Umnumzane McDonnell esitsho ethi uzimisele ukuthatha amandla 'kubalawuli abangafuni ukubonwa mntu' kunye 'nabafumana inzuzo' emashishinini amakhulu.

source: Ucwangciso lwalomphathi ongumncedisi lutsho ukuthi abanini-nxaxheba emashinini abathengisa amanzi bangangafumani isabelo sabo njengona urhulumente wezomsebenzi angabhatalisa ‚Äòintlawulo‚Äô esithi abenzi kakuhle.
reference: The shadow chancellor's plans also mean current shareholders in water companies may not get back their entire stake as a Labour government could make 'deductions' on the grounds of perceived wrongdoing.
translation: Ucwangciso lwalomphathi ongumncedisi lutsho ukuthi abanini-nxaxheba emashinini abathengisa amanzi bangangafumani isabelo sabo njengoba urhulumente wezomsebenzi angabhatalisa 'intlawulo' esithi abenzi kakuhle.

source: Waqinisekisa ucwangciso lwakhe kwakhona lokufaka abaqeshwa ezikhundleni zobuphathi emashishinini kwaye enze isikhwama semali yobunini obubandakanya wonke umuntu ngenjongo yokunikeza abaqeshwa isabelo samaphesenti angu10 samashishini angekhoyo phansi kukarhulumente okungabanikeza imali engango ¬£500
reference: He also confirmed plans to put workers on company boards and create Inclusive Ownership Funds to hand 10 per cent of private-sector firms' equity to employees, who stand to pocket annual dividends of up to ¬£500.
translation: Waqinisekisa ucwangciso lwakhe kwakhona lokufaka abaqeshwa ezikhundleni zobuphathi emashishinini kwaye enze isikhwama semali yobunini obubandakanya wonke umuntu ngenjongo yokunikeza abaqeshwa isabelo samaphesenti angu10 samashishini angekhoyo phansi kukarhulumente okungabanikeza imali engango ¬£500

source: ULindsey Graham, UJohn Kennedy baxelela ‚Äúi60 Minutes‚Äù ukuba iFBI ingabatshintshisa na umqondo
reference: Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy tell "60 Minutes" whether the FBI's investigation of Kavanaugh could change their minds
translation: ULindsey Graham, UJohn Kennedy baxelela "i60 Minutes" ukuba iFBI ingabatshintshisa na umqondo

source: Uphando lweFBI lwezityholo ezibekwe ijaji uBrett Kavanaugh zilibazise ivoti lokugqibela ngokuthunjwa kwakhe eNkundla Ephezulu ngeveki, kwaye ivusa umbuzo othi ingabe iziphumo zophando lwaleli ziko zingaguqula osenethe bamaRepublican ukuba batshintshe iingqondo zabo ngenkxaso abayinikezayo.
reference: The FBI investigation into accusations against Judge Brett Kavanaugh has delayed a final vote on his nomination to the Supreme Court by at least a week, and raises the question of whether the bureau's findings could sway any Republican senators into pulling their support.
translation: Uphando lweFBI lwezityholo ezibekwe ijaji uBrett Kavanaugh zilibazise ivoti lokugqibela ngokuthunjwa kwakhe eNkundla Ephezulu ngeveki, kwaye ivusa umbuzo othi ingabe iziphumo zophando lwaleli ziko zingaguqula osenethe bamaRepublican ukuba batshintshe iingqondo zabo ngenkxaso abayinikezayo.

source: Kuludliwano ndlebe elizosasazwa ngeSonto, intatheli ye‚Äù60 Minutes‚Äù uScott Pelley ubuze osenethe bamaRepublican uJohn Kennedy kunye noLindsey Graham ukuba ingabe iFBI ingafumana into engabenza bagqule izingqondo.
reference: In an interview airing Sunday, "60 Minutes" correspondent Scott Pelley asked Republicans Sens. John Kennedy and Lindsey Graham whether the FBI could unearth anything that would lead them to change their minds.
translation: Kuludliwano ndlebe elizosasazwa ngeSonto, intatheli ye"60 Minutes" uScott Pelley ubuze osenethe bamaRepublican uJohn Kennedy kunye noLindsey Graham ukuba ingabe iFBI ingafumana into engabenza bagqule izingqondo.

source: UKennedy ubevakala engena ngxaki ngokuthetha kunogxa wakhe ovela eSouth Carolina.
reference: Kennedy appeared more open than his colleague from South Carolina.
translation: UKennedy ubevakala engena ngxaki ngokuthetha kunogxa wakhe ovela eSouth Carolina.

source: ‚ÄúEwe kaloku‚Äù kusitsho uKennedy
reference: I mean, of course, said Kennedy.
translation: Ewe kaloku kusitsho uKennedy

source: ‚ÄúNditsho ndizongena ethyaleni, ndithe, ndithethile nejaji uKavanaugh.‚Äù
reference: I said going into the hearing, I said, I've talked to Judge Kavanaugh.	Nditsho ndizongena ethyaleni, ndithe, ndithethile nejaji uKavanaugh."

source: Ndimfownele emva kokuba lento ivelile, emva kokuba ezi zityholo zikhutshwe, ndithe, ‚Äòukwenzile na?‚Äô
reference: I called him after this happened, that allegation came out, said, 'Did you do it?'
translation: Ndimfownele emva kokuba lento ivelile, emva kokuba ezi zityholo zikhutshwe, ndithe, 'ukwenzile na?'

source: Wayezolile, eqiniseka, engoyiki.‚Äù
reference: He was resolute, determined, unequivocal."
translation: Wayezolile, eqiniseka, engoyiki."

source: Nangona kunjalo, kubonakala ngathi, ivoti likaGraham soze laguquka.
